songs.title: agape prem maile chakhisake (hajaaraau lakhau dhanayawaada)
lyrics: agape prem maile chakhisake
angalo dubisake
ho o
agape prem maile chakhisake
angalo dubisake
tyo prem chattanako mah bhanda mitho mitho mitho
tyo angalo aamako kakh bhanda nyano nayonao-nayonao
esto premakao lagi ma bhanchu
hazarau lakhau dhanyawad (3)
hallelujah hallelujah
hat uchalchu uccha atti uccha
sansar chadauchhu uccha atti uccha
uchalchu tapailai ma bhanchu
hazarau lakhau dhanyawad (4)

songs.title: aghai baढ़ kharaeeṣhaṭaeeya jawaana ho samayalaaee naparakha
lyrics: kao. aghai baढ़, kharaeeṣhaṭaeeya jawaana ho
samayalaaee naparakha bhaai hao, (haamaraa daulahaa aaundaaichhana‌) (2)
1. anataima chaihana daekhaindaaichha, bhawaiṣhayawaaṇaee paooraa haundaaichha (2)
saamsaaraika jaeewanalaaee tayogaee aaoo parabhaumaa nayon bhaye (2)
2. jaeewana parabhaumaa arapaṇa garaee samapaooraṇa wachana paalanaa garaee (2)
parabhaukao yao karaoosa uṭhaaee aghai baढ़ unamaa bhaye (2)
3. jayawanata jaeewana baitaaundaai jaaoo parabhaukao kaamamaa wayasata bhaye (2)
unamaa sadaa aashaa raakhadaai baढ़ ajha thakaita nabhaye (2)

songs.title: aghai baढ़ kharaeeṣhaṭaeeya yatana bachaaoo ekaai saathaeelaaee
lyrics: 1. aghai baढ़ kharaeeṣhaṭaeeya yatana, bachaaoo ekaai saathaeelaaee
laaikaaoo usalaaee Yeshukahaan chhaiṭao naai baaṭao daekhaaee .
kao. aghai baढ़ kharaeeṣhaṭaeeya yatana, sataya ra dharamalaaee baढ़aoo
anadhakaaramaa basanae sabalaaee naikaalaee jayaotaimaa layooo
2. aghai baढ़ kharaeeṣhaṭaeeya yatana kaina ḍhailao garadachhaaun
eeshawarakao dayo nabaujhanae saathaeelaaee bhanaidainachhaaun .
3. aghai baढ़ kharaeeṣhaṭaeeya yatana jaiundao raoṭaee baanड़nalaaee
Yeshukahaan sabaailaaee layooo maukatai dainachhana‌ sabaailaaee .
4. aghai baढ़, kharaeeṣhaṭaeeya yatana, banaaoo aananadaita sabalaaee
aghai baढ़, sawaragataira gaeetalae dauhkha bairasaaundaai .

songs.title: aghai baढ़ yawaa ho parabhaukao maaragamaa (2) parabhaukao maaragamaa
lyrics: kao. aghai baढ़ yawaa ho parabhaukao maaragamaa (2) parabhaukao maaragamaa (2)
1. baढ़ taimaee parabhaumaa paraarathanaakao jaeewana laiera (2)
saphalataakao shaikharamaa (2) pauganaechhaau ananatasamama (2)
2. kharaeeṣhaṭalae maatara dainaechha taimaeelaaee chhauṭakaaraa (2)
bishwas gara parabhau kharaeeṣhaṭamaa (2) paaunaechhaau ananata jaeewana (2)

songs.title: aghai baढ़aun (2) hae kharaeeṣhaṭaeeya daajayaoo-bhaai ho
lyrics: kao. aghai baढ़aun (2), hae kharaeeṣhaṭaeeya daajayaoo-bhaai ho
aghai baḍhaaun (2), hae kharaeeṣhaṭaeeya daidaee-bahainaee ho
1. maukatai taa haamaeelae paaisakayoun, aaphaoomaa maatara saeemaita naraakhaaun
taृṣhaita aatamaa hajaaraaun chhana‌, taee aatamaaharaookao upakaara garaaun (2)
2. karatawaya kae ho samajhaee-baujhaee karaoosalaaee sadhaain agai raakhaee
parabhaukao wachana parachaara garaaun, yasaailae haamarao kamamara kasaaun (2)
3. samayamaai haamaee baeeu chharaaun, pachhai naai haamaee kaoshaelaee baṭaulaaun
parabhaukao aagamana najaeekaai chha, yasakaaraṇa sadhaain tayora basaaun (2)

songs.title: angaga-paratayongagakaa maalaika ma garachhau paraṇaama‌
lyrics: kao. angaga-paratayongagakaa maalaika ma garachhau paraṇaama‌
dhanaya dhanaya saृṣhaṭaikarataa amara chha taimaraai naama (2) .
1. taimaraa saृṣhaṭai yaee daui hat chhana‌ katai raamaraa
taimaraa saृṣhaṭai yaee daui paau chhana‌ katai raamaraa
yaee maeraa hat yaee maeraa paau angaga hauna‌ taimaraa
jae garaoon ma, jahaan jaaoon ma, haosa‌ taimaraai mahaimaa .
2. taimaraa saृṣhaṭai yaee dauee kaana chhana‌ katai raamaraa
pataimaraa saृṣhaṭai yaee daui oṭha chhana‌ katai payoraa
yaee maeraa kaana, yaee maeraa oṭha anga hauna‌ taimaraa
jae saunaoon ma, jae baolaoon ma, haosa‌ taimaraai mahaimaa .
3. taimaraa saृṣhaṭai yaee daui aankhaa chhana‌ katai raamaraa
anadhao hauna‌ ta manakaa aankhaa chhana‌ taee chanaakhaa
chhana‌ jao maeraa yaee daui aankhaa angaga hauna‌ taimaraa
jahaan jae jatai daekhaen maailae, haosa‌ taimaraai mahaimaa .
4. janyona ra baudadhai jatai maeraa hauna‌, yaee taimaraai daana
angaga-paratayangagamaa payorakao taimarao rahaekao chha naishaana
shawaasa-parashawaasabaaṭa maerao, naisakaosa‌ taimaraai naaun
maerao yaee sarawaangagabaaṭa, haosa‌ taimaraai kaama (2) .

songs.title: achamamakao anaugarahalae baanchayao tauchachha paraaṇa maerao
lyrics: 1. achamamakao anaugarahalae, baanchayao tauchachha paraaṇa maerao,
haraaekao thaien aba paaiekao chhau, anadhao daekhanae bhaen .
2. anaugarahalae eeshawarakao bhaya, anaugarahalae shaanatai,
kasatao amaoolaya sawaada anaugarahakao, jaba bishwas garaem .
3. anaekaaun jayaokhaima paraeekaṣhaa, bhaera aaipaugaen,
yahaansamama layounae tyo anaugarahalae, pauganaechhau sawaraga maai .
4. parabhaukao waachaa bhalaaeekao, yao maerao bharaosaa,
uhaan naai maerao saooraya ra ḍhaala, paraaṇa maerao rahaunajaela .
5. hajaaraaun waraṣha sawaragamaa, saoorayajhaain chamakanachhaaun,
yao anaugarahakao parashamsaa gaaundaai, yauga yaugaaun rahanachhaaun .

songs.title: achamamakao prem garanaubhao paramaeshawaralae haamaeelaaee ekalao
lyrics: kao. achamamakao prem garanau bhao, paramaeshawaralae haamaeelaaee
ekalao pautara samaeta dainaubhao bachaauna bhanai sabaailaaee (2)
1. karaoosamaa chaḍhaee ragata bagaaee, paramaaṇaita garanaubhao, aaphanao prem
euṭaalaaee daiee saaraa bachaauna garanau bhao, yasatao achamamakao prem .
2. maृtayaulaaee jaitaee baauraee uṭhae Yeshu paramaeshawarakao mahaimaa daekhaauna
chaalaisa daina pachhai sabaai aajanyo daiee
gae sawaraga bhanadaai phaeraee aauchhau laina .
3. anaugarahakao samaya yahaee hao, nagaumaaoo yao maaukaa paraiya ho
banaaoo Yeshulaaee maitara ho
saanchachaai naai uhaan aaunae baelaa bhao .

songs.title: adana maem taoo nae khaudaabanada paaka bayohaa kaa inataijaama
lyrics: kao. adana maem taoo nae khaudaabanada, paaka bayohaa kaa inataijaama
rahamata sae maukararara kaiyo, tao inasaana kao ho aaraama
jaaisaa taoo nae barakata bakhashaee, pahalae marada aura aurata para
waaisaa taoo ina daonaom para bhaye, apanaee barakata naajaila kara .
1. kaanaa maem taoo nae daikhaaee, apanaee kaudarata o jalaala
aba haajaira hao, aura inakao phajala sae kara maalaamaala
unahae taoo paakaeejaa karakae, eka kao daoosarae sae mailaa
apanaee rahamata sae taoo ina para daaulada phajala kaee barasaa .
2. upara bhara taoo isakae saatha ho inakaee naita haidaayata kara
saathaom saatha yae dauhkha aura saukha maem, chala taeraee raahaom para
inahae barakata sae maamaoora kara, sadaa rahaem taerae paasa
inakaa saphara jaba tamaama ho inahaem bakhasha abadaee maeeraasa ॥

songs.title: adabhaoota saamaratha sae bharaa Yeshu naama
lyrics: kao. adabhaoota saamaratha sae bharaa Yeshu naama (2)
sawaraga aura paृthawaee usakaa sarawadhaikaara
adabhaoota saamaratha sae bharaa Yeshu naama,
waha parabhau haai parabhau haai, raajaa haai raajaa haai .
Yeshu kharaeeṣhaṭa parabhauom kaa parabhau haai (2)
1. sadaa jaya Yeshu kae lahaun maaim haai (2)
paapa aura maृtayau shaaitaana kaee shakatai para,
sadaa jaya Yeshu kae lahaun maem haai .
2. usakaee samgataee maem haai aananada apaara (2)
saarae dauhkha aura ḍarakaa haotaa haai naidaana
usakaee samgataee maem haai aananada apaara .
3. Yeshu naama maem raogaom sae maukatai haai (2)
Yeshu naama sae haotae haai adabhaoota kaama
yaishaoo naama maem raogaom sae maukatai haai .

songs.title: andhayorao jagata‌maa jayaotai phaailaaee ujajawala parabhau Yeshu
lyrics: kao. andhayorao jagata‌maa jayaotai phaailaaee ujajawala parabhau Yeshu
1. taimaeelae adharama paapalaaee karaoosamaa maeṭaaidaiyou
karaoosakao dauhkhalaaee sahaera paapaeelaaee maukata garaayou
gaairahaechhaaun taimarao sarawagauṇagaana, samajhairahaechhaaun yoda madhaurao prem .
2. nairaasha jaeewana laiera baitairahaethayou tayasaai
shauṣhaka haृdayakao taanamaa jaeewaita aashaa dailaayou
gaairahaechhaaun taimarao sarawagauṇagaana, samajhairahaechhaaun yoda madhaurao prem .
3. paapamaya jaeewanalaaee tayogaera aatamaakao daeepa jalaaunchhaaun
sawaragaeeya aashaiṣha‌, laiera satautai aaraadhanaa chaढ़aunchhaaun
gaairahaechhaaun taimarao sarawagauṇagaana, samajhairahaechhaaun yoda madhaurao prem .

songs.title: andhayoraomaa jaeeunaeharaoo daeepa jalaaee jaeeunae gara
lyrics: kao. andhayoraomaa jaeeunaeharaoo daeepa jalaaee jaeeunae gara
haara namaana jaeewanasaita jaeewaita parabhaulaaee khaojaee gara .
1. jae jatai bhaekaa taee manakaa sabaai wayarathaharaoo (2)
sabaaikao paapalaaee waijaya dainae parabhau Yeshumaa raakhaidaeoo (2)
2. udadhaara maukatai paaunchhaau taimaee parabhaulaaee bishwas garaepachhai (2)
aatamaamaa sadhaaim shaanatai paaunchhaau parabhau Yeshulaaee paaepachhai (2)

songs.title: ananata jaeewanakao baaṭaobharai jayaotai banaera sadhaain-sadhaain
lyrics: kao. ananata jaeewanakao baaṭaobharai, jayaotai banaera sadhaain-sadhaain
(ḍaorayounauhaosa‌ parabhau malaaee saatha dainauhaosa‌ sadaa-sadaa) (2)
1. aaunnaechhau parabhau taimarao saathamaa kaṭhaina yotaraa laamao nai bhae panai (2)
baaṭaobharai kaanड़alae baijae panai (2) tapaaeem maajha ekalao ma bhae panai .
ḍaubanaechha aashaakao jaba ghaama panai jayaotai banaera sadhaain-sadhaain
ḍaorayounauhaosa‌ parabhau malaaee saatha dainauhaosa‌ sadaa-sadaa .
2. parashamsaa dhanyawad chaढ़airahaoon aaraadhanaakao jaeewana daeoo malaaee (2)
parabhau taimarao charaṇamaa rahana daeoo (2) jaeewanakao anataima palasamama malaaee
anadhakaara samsaarakao yotaraabharai jayaotai banaera sadhaain-sadhaain
ḍaorayounauhaosa‌ parabhau malaaee saatha dainauhaosa‌ sadaa-sadaa .

songs.title: ananatakaalasamamaai haosa‌ tapaaeemkao
lyrics: (ananatakaalasamamaai haosa‌ tapaaeemkao mahaimaa) (4)
hae paramapaitaa, hae mahaana‌ eeshawara, hae pautara kharaeeṣhaṭa, hae aatamaa pawaitara
(yaugaanauyauga) (3) haosa‌, (mahaimaa) (6) haosa‌ .

songs.title: ananatakao tyo raajayamaa jaanalaaee haoaun tayora
lyrics: kao. ananatakao tyo raajayamaa jaanalaaee haoaun tayora
shaaitaanalae awashaya baadhaa naai dainachha paraarathanaamaa laagairahaaun
1. kasatao chha haolaa, ananatakao raajaya waraṇana garana naai sakadaainaaun
kasatao haolaa, jayaotaikao kairaṇa thaahaa paauna naai sakadaainaaun .
2. daootagaṇa sabaailae garadaai naai haolaa, parabhaukao jaya-jayagaana
anaekaaun dhawanai bajadaai naai haolaa, eeshawarakao premailao jana .
3. abaraahaama, isahaaka, yokaoobalae haamaeelaaee parakhamdaai haolaana‌ wahaan
kahailae pao aaunchha, ananata ṭhaaunmaa bhanadaai eeshawarasanga wahaan .
4. haamaee ramaaaun khaushaee bhaera wahaankao jayagaana garaaun
kainakai thaumaa aaphaai naai wahaan daulahaa banairahaekaa .

songs.title: ananatakao raajayamaa jaanakao lagi eeshawaraeeya shakatai
lyrics: kao. ananatakao raajayamaa jaanakao laagai,
eeshawaraeeya shakatai paaunakao lagi bhakataisaatha jaeewana jaiunakao laagai,
bishwasmaa waijaya bananakao lagi (paraarathanaamaa laagaee rahaaun) (4)
1. (shaaitanalae awashaya baadhaa naai layounchha,
dauhkha ra kaṣhaṭakao hauraee chalaainchha) (2)
kamajaora bishwaskao mauṭau halalaaunchha,
(tayasaailae ma bhanachhau, paraarathanaamaa laagaee rahaaun) (2)
2. (garajanae saimhajhaain tarasaauna aaunchha,
ghamaṇaḍa ra sawaaratha manamaa layoidainachha) (2)
bishwaskao jaeewanamaa, shamkaa layoidainachha
(tayasaailae ma bhanachhau, paraarathanaamaa laagaee rahaaun) (2)
3. (laobha ra laalachaamaa phansaai chhaड़chha,
samsaarakao paapamaa ḍaubaai dainachha) (2)
bishwasbaaṭa pachhai haṭaaunchha,
(tayasaailae ma bhanachhau, paraarathanaamaa laagaee rahaaun) (2)

songs.title: anaugarahakao inaara kharaeeṣhaṭakao maṇaḍalaee (2)
lyrics: anaugarahakao inaara kharaeeṣhaṭakao maṇaḍalaee (2)
jahaanbaaṭa ughaaera paurayounauchha daeshabharaee (2)
1. khaḍaeraee chha haai chaaraaitaira aatamaa naai raukhaaunae hao... hao... (2)
ukaalaee ghaamamaa shaeetalataa napaae yotaraee kahaan baisaaunae (2)
anaugarahakao chaautaaraee hae maṇaḍalaee hao... hao... (2)
jahaan aaera baisaaunchha thakaitalae aaphanao bhaaraee (2)
2. andhayorao chha haai chaaraaitaira anadhao naai bhaulayounae (2)
jaeewanakao yotaraa jayaotai napaae kasaraee kaṭaaunae (2)
saamadaamaathaikao batatai ho maṇaḍalaee (2)
jahaanbaaṭa chamakaiera chharainau chha daeshabharaee (2)

songs.title: anaugarahakao samaya chhandaai parabhau Yeshulaaee bishwas gara
lyrics: kao. anaugarahakao samaya chhandaai parabhau Yeshulaaee bishwas gara (2) anaugarahakao .
1. saaraa samsaaralaaee hat paarae panai aatamaa taimaeelae gaumaayou bhanae (2)
maitara, taimaeelaaee chhaaina kaehaee laabha (2) yao jaeewana paaera
premamaya aawaaja kharaeeṣhaṭakao saunaera haृdaya khaolaidaeoo
parabhau Yeshukao charaṇa paraee ananata maukatai laeoo (2)
2. dharama-karamakao samsakaaradawaaraa pawaitara taimaee banadaainaau (2)
bhakataikao bhaeṣha dhaaraṇa garaera (2) sawaragamaa paugana sakadaainaaun,
yasaailae maitara saaraa paapa taimaraa parabhaumaa maanailaeoo
mahaana‌ parabhaukao charaṇa paraee jaeewana arapaidaeoo (2)
3. saanchao maukataikao euṭaai chha baaṭao parabhau Yeshu kharaeeṣhaṭa baujhaidaeoo
paapa-maaraga tayogai pashachaatataapaee banaee (2) parabhaukao sharaṇa laeoo
dhaoimaaga taimaraa saaraa paapa aaja Yeshukao ragatamaa
sawaragaeeya aashaiṣha‌ ananata-jaeewana paaoo unakao saamarathayamaa (2)
4. kaewala kharaeeṣhaṭamaa chha ananata jaeewana sawaragaeeya aashaiṣha‌kao bharapaooraee (2)
maृtayaukao tayahaan parabhautawa chhaaina (2) kaewala Yeshumaa jaya
daṇaḍakao aajanyo ṭalaera gae kaewala kharaeeṣhaṭa Yeshumaa
narakakao ḍhaokaa banada sadaa chha unaaikao saamarathayamaa (2)

songs.title: anaugarahalae paramaeshawarakao chhaaun paae sabaai kaushala kaṣhaema
lyrics: 1. anaugarahalae paramaeshawarakao chhaaun paae sabaai kaushala kaṣhaema
yao dayo haamaeemaathai bhao’ ta garaaun unakao saewaa prem .
kao. satautai gaaee, satautai gaaee, yasa dainalaaee maanaaun parabhaukaai
paraayashachaita bhae Yeshu naai, maapha dainauhawasa‌ paapaeelaaee
satautai gaaee, satautai gaaee, yasa dainalaaee maanaaun parabhaukaai
2. ramaaee jaaaun gairajaaghara, aaraadhanaa garaaun eeshawarakao
hae eeshawara garanauhaosa‌ gaohaara ra hawasa‌ saewaa manaparadao .
3. tapaaeemlae shaikaṣhaa dainauhaosa‌ ra garanaosa‌ aaphanao dharama parakaasha
naishachainatalaaee jagaaunahaosa‌, nairaashadaekhai mana shaanata rahaosa‌ .
4. jaba paugaijaalaa maraṇakaala, taba haoaun khaushaee ra naiḍara
ra jaaaun tapaaeemkahaan kaृpaala ra paaaun waisharaama sadaabhara .

songs.title: anaugarahaee parabhau tapaaeem dayo daekhaaunaubhao’ malaaee
lyrics: 1. anaugarahaee parabhau tapaaeem, dayo daekhaaunaubhao’ malaaee
chaunanaubhao’ tapaaeemkao haunalaaee majasatao tauchachha paapaeelaaee
2. premailao parabhau tapaaeem, prem daekhaaunaubhao’ malaaee
sahanaubhao’ karaoosakao dauhkhalaaee ananata jaeewana dainalaaee .

songs.title: anaokhaa payora haai taeraa karaoongaa satautai taeraee maaim marawadaa
lyrics: kao. anaokhaa payora haai taeraa, karaoongaa satautai taeraee maaim marawadaa (2)
shaoonaya sae laekae taunae maujhae, rachalaiyo apanae hai raoopa maem
prem kaiyo haai ananata prem sae, daiyo pautara maerae maukatai kae laie (2)
1. jaga maem aayo Yeshu sawaraga chhaड़kara
maeraa saaraa daṇaḍa saha laiyo usanae, kaoड़e khaakae karaoosa uṭhaakae Yeshu nae
maujhae maukatai ora chamgaaee daedaee haai (2) ... anaokhaa payora
2. anana wasatara aura sabhaye aashaeeṣhae
daee maujhae usanae bharapaoorai sae, khataraom ora mausaeebataom sae
aankha kaee pautalaee jaaisaee samabhaalaa maujhae (2) ... anaokhaa payora .

songs.title: anaauṭhao yao jainadagaee jaiunau chha yahaan
lyrics: anaauṭhao yao jainadagaee jaiunau chha yahaan
kasatao haolaa kasatao haolaa (2)
1. raamarao bhanda naraamarao saunaidainae naraamarao ta jhana‌ bhananaai nahaunae (2)
dhana bhaekaakao manaai nahaunae mana bhaekaakao dhanaai nahaunae
kasatao haolaa kasatao haolaa (2)
2. kasalae khaojanae ho saanchao kauraa jasalae
maanaisalaaee baaṭao daekhaaunchha (2)
kasalae baujhanae ho saanchao prem Yeshu masaeehakao jaeewana dainae prem
kasatao haolaa kasatao haolaa (2)

songs.title: anaauṭhao yao samsaaramaa kharaeeṣhaṭa Yeshulaaee paae maile (2)
lyrics: kao. anaauṭhao yao samsaaramaa kharaeeṣhaṭa Yeshulaaee paae maile (2)
(chhaṭao jaeewanakao gaoraeṭaomaa) (2)
1. aghai aghai Yeshu hainड़e pachhai pachhai ma hainड़na laagaen (2)
jaeewanakao gaoraeṭaomaa kharaeeṣhaṭalae malaaee angaalaera (2)
2. kaṣhaitaija maathai aakaashamaa uड़chha mana baegamaaraee (2)
maukataidaataa paae maile yao mana daien bhaeṭaee saraee (2)
3. aashaa mailayao kharaeeṣhaṭa Yeshumaa ramana thaalayao mana maerao (2)
sataya wachana angaalaera hainड़na laagaen kharaeeṣhaṭakao baaṭao (2)

songs.title: anataima dainasamamaai Yeshukao gaeeta ma gaairahanaechha
lyrics: anataima dainasamamaai Yeshukao gaeeta ma gaairahanaechha
maerao yao dhaḍakanamaa dhaḍakaeedainaubhayao
ṭauṭaekao yao manalaaee jaoḍaidainaubhayao (2)
1. ḍaubaisakaekao chhau Yeshukao maayomaa
baanchana sakadaina Yeshu wainaa aba (2)
yasaailae parabhau chaukana sakadaina ma yasaailae parabhau bhaoolana sakadaina ma
2. kasatao anamaola yao prem garanaubhayao malaaee
kasatao gahairao naataa kahailae nachhauṭanae (2)
yasaailae parabhau garachhau mahaimaa aadara yasaailae parabhau gaaunchhau Yeshukao gaeeta

songs.title: anadhakaara banadhana dauhkhadaekhai (Yeshu ma aaoon) (2)
lyrics: 1. anadhakaara, banadhana, dauhkhadaekhai, (Yeshu ma aaoon) (2)
paauna chhauṭakaaraa, haraṣha, daृṣhaṭai Yeshu ma aaundaaichhau,
aaphanao raogadaekhai aaraogayamaa, abhaawadaekhai parashasatataamaa
paapa-bhaooladaekhai pawaitarataamaa, Yeshu ma aaundaaichhau .
2. malaaee lajaaunae baanaeedaekhai, (Yeshu ma aaoon) (2)
tapaaeemkao charaṇa ghaopaṭao paraee, Yeshu ma aaundaaichhau .
aandhaeedaekhai tapaaeemkao aaड़maa, jagakao shaokadaekhai saanatawanaamaa
samkaṭadaekhai parashamsaamaa, Yeshu ma aaundaaichhau .
3. chainataa, ghamaṇaḍa baechaainaeedaekhai, (Yeshu ma aaoon) (2)
ichachhaa tapaaeemkao sawaeekaara garaee, Yeshu ma aaundaaichhau
sawaarathadaekhai tapaaeemkao premamaa, nairaashadaekhai paramaananadamaa
pakaṣhaeejhaain uड़ee pakhaeṭaamaa, Yeshu ma aaundaaichhau .
4. maृtayaukao taraasa bhayangakara daekhai (Yeshu ma aaoon) (2)
sawaragae gharataira aghai baढ़ee, Yeshu ma aaundaaichhau
satayanaashadaekhai asaeema apaara aasharayamaa paauna shaanatai udadhaara
haerana tapaaeemkao paraiya mauhaara, Yeshu ma aaundaaichhau .

songs.title: anadhakaarabaaṭa ujajayolae banadhanabaaṭa chhauṭakaaraa
lyrics: 1. anadhakaarabaaṭa ujajayolae banadhanabaaṭa chhauṭakaaraa
paapabaaṭa haamaeelaaee maukatai (2)
kaaraṇa Yeshu aaunaubhao haamarao maajha raaja garanaubhao (2)
aau raamaaaum parashamsaa garaaum daṇaḍawata garadaai aaradhanaa garaaum (2)
imamaanauela ha ... hallelujah (2)
2. ashaanataibaaṭa haamaeelaaee shaanatai raogaeebaaṭa aaraogaya
nairaashabaaṭa haamaeelaaee aashaa (2)
yaehaoo raajaa aaunaubhao maanaisa jasataai bhaera (2)
aau ramaaaum...

songs.title: anadhakaarabhaitara ajanyonataaharaoomaa saahaaraa baihaeena
lyrics: kao. anadhakaarabhaitara ajanyonataaharaoomaa
saahaaraa baihaeena awasathaaharaoomaa
banaera sahaaraa ḍaorayoe jayaotaimaa (2)
lakaṣhayahaina jaeewanakao lakaṣhaya banaee . (2)
1. masaihaee haoon ma gawaahaee dainachhau, Yeshukao premakao saaṭaomaa (2)
saba samsaara haansaetaa panai, rahanachhau kharaeeṣhaṭakao agauwaaeemaa (2)
aatamaikaee laड़aee laḍadaai rahanachhau, anatamaa paaunaechhau, kharaeeṣhaṭamaa waijaya (2)
2. masaihaee haoon tasawaeera chha maerao, haृdayakao amtasakaraṇamaa (2)
nairanatara gaaunchhau jaya halalaelaooyoha, Yeshukao pachhai laagaera (2)
euṭaai aashaamaa laḍachhau samsaaramaa, jaba aaunnaechhana‌ Yeshu laina malaaee (2‌)

songs.title: anadhakaaramaa bhaulairahaekaa maanawalaaee
lyrics: kao. anadhakaaramaa bhaulairahaekaa maanawalaaee
jayaotai daekhaaunae satautai mahaimaa chha parabhaulaaee (2)
1. naiṣhakalangaka balaidaana nairadaoṣha parabhaukao amaoolaya rakata udadhaarakao baaṭao banayao
saaṭaomaa yasakao tapaaeemlaaee kae chaढ़aoon, satautai-mahaimaa chha parabhaulaaee .
2. maृtayaumaathai jaya paraapata garaee paitaakao daahainae hat basaee bainataee garanae
saaṭaomaa yasakao tapaaeemlaaee kae chaढ़aoon, satautai-mahaimaa chha parabhaulaaee .
3. parataiphala jaeewanakao rakaṣhaka tapaaeem, naihsawaaratha premakao sataya jayaotai
ananata, shaanatai ra aashaa haamarao, satautai-mahaimaa chha parabhaulaaee .

songs.title: anadhaalaaee aankhaa bahairaolaaee kaana langaḍaaḍaalaaee khauṭaṭaa
lyrics: 1. anadhaalaaee aankhaa bahairaolaaee kaana
langaḍaaḍaalaaee khauṭaṭaa nairabalalaaee bala
(maraekaalaaee jaeewana samsaaralaaee jayaotai) (2)
(dainau bhao Yeshulae) (2)
kao. (aauna gaauna uhaankao shakataimaa
aauna nachaaumna uhaankao mahaimaamaa) (2)
2. paapaeelaaee kaṣhamaa raogaeelaaee chamgaaee
haraekaalaaee aashaa jaeeundao balaidaana
(ananata jaeewana jaeewanakao paanaee)
(dainau bhao Yeshulae) (2)
(maerao jaeewanamaa uhaan chha
maerao aatamaamaa uhaan chha
maerao haृdayamaa uhaan chha) (2)

songs.title: anadhaalaaee daृṣhaṭai dainae langagaḍaalaaee changagaai dainae
lyrics: 1. anadhaalaaee daृṣhaṭai dainae langagaḍaalaaee changagaai dainae
aakaasha dharataeelaaee wachanalae saृṣhaṭai garanae (2)
haosananaa Yeshulaaee mahaimaa thaumaalaaee (4)
2. paapaeelaaee kaṣhamaa dainae aanshaoolaaee pauchhaidainae
anadhakaara haraaunae nayon jaeewana dainae (2)
haosananaa...
3. nairabala balaiyao haunachha raogaeelae changagaaee paaunchha
saaraa saृṣhaṭailae aaja uhaankao mahaimaa gaaunchha (2)
haosananaa...

songs.title: apanaa baojha parabhau para ḍaala kabhaye na ghabaraanaa
lyrics: kao. apanaa baojha parabhau para ḍaala, kabhaye na ghabaraanaa
taeraa aadara maana karaegaa, aashacharaya karama karaegaa (2)
1. bhakataom kao waha bhaoolaegaa nahaeem
hamaeshaa unakaee samabhaala karaegaa (2)
2. maataa paitaa yadai chhaड़ daewae
waha tao galae sae lagaaegaa (2)
3. parabhau hamaarae saatha rahae
saamahanaa kaauna kara paaegaa (2)
4. paooraṇa samarapaṇa usakao karae
waha tao saba kauchha daekhaegaa (2)
5. baojha parabhau para ḍaala daiyo haai
aba kayaom ghabaraanaa (2)

songs.title: apanaom kao tao isa daunaiyo maem saba payora karatae haai
lyrics: kao. apanaom kao tao isa daunaiyo maem saba payora karatae haai
daushamana kao bhaye payora karanaa masaeehaa saikhaataa haai .
1. eka gaala para kaoee maarae jao chaamṭaa daoosaraa gaala bhaye daenaa
lae jaae kaoee eka maeela jabarana dao maeela taoo saatha jaanaa
apanaom kao tao apanaa saba kauchha saba laoga daetae haaim .
gaairaom para bhaye saba kauchha lauṭaanaa – masaeehaa saikhaatae haai ॥
2. apanaom pae jaaisaa waaisaa haee, apanae paड़osaee sae payora karao
Yeshu maraa taerae paapaom kae kaaraṇa yaha bishwas karao
apanaom para tao laoga yahaan para aitabaara karatae haai
kalaamaem khaudaa pae bishwas karanaa- masaeehaa saikhaatae haai .
3. jao dae taumakao kaanṭae usakaa daamana phaoolaom sae bhara dao
parabhau nae taumakao maapha kaiyo tauma bhaye maapha kara dao
apanaom kao tao gaunaahaom kaee maaphaee saba laoga daetae haai
baairaom kao bhaye maapha karanaa- masaeehaa saikhaatae haai .
apanaom kao... ॥

songs.title: apaara chha parabhau prem kalawaraeekao waraṇana kasaraee garaaun ?
lyrics: kao. apaara chha parabhau, prem kalawaraeekao waraṇana kasaraee garaaun ?
dhanyawad khaalai dainachhau tapaaeemlaaee, araoo ma kae chaढ़aoon ?
1. udadhaara garana ma eka paapaeekao, karaoosa bhaaraee baokanau bhao’,
samarapaṇa garaee aadara, parashamsaa, gailalaa naai raojanau bhao’ .
2. sharaapaita sathaana tyo kalawaraeemaa, kaohaee thaiena parabhaukao,
taai panai katarao udadaeshaya thaiyao, dawaara khaolanae maukataikao .
3. paapaee pailaatausa atai naai naiṣhaṭhaura, daoṣha bhaeṭana chaahanathayao,
chaora panai tayahaan parabhau tapaaeemkao nainadaa naai garadathayao .

songs.title: aba arakao saataa (waraṣha) baitaechha hae maerao mana chaeta gara
lyrics: 1. aba arakao saataa (waraṣha) baitaechha, hae maerao mana, chaeta gara
eeshawaralae rakaṣhaa garaechhana‌ parabhaukao dhanyawad gara .
2. yasa saataa (waraṣha) katai thaie baimaara ra katai maraechhana‌
shaaitaanadaekhai katai ḍaraaee dauṣhaṭa aatamaa paujaechhana‌ .
3. malaaee ta jaurayao aatamaika janyona, sharaeerakao saukha ra aaढ़
dhaera raoṭaee, wasatara, maeeta, ṭhaegaana ṭhaeeka khaanchao naai anausaara .
4. yasa saataa (waraṣha) kaa saba paapa aparaadha hae eeshawara maapha garanaosa‌
ṭhaeeka dharama garanauchha, asaadhaya anaugaraha daana dainaosa‌ .

songs.title: aba aao bishwasiyaom jaya-jaya karatae aao
lyrics: kao. aba aao bishwasiyaom jaya-jaya karatae aao
aba aao hama chalaem baaitalahama kao
charanaee maem daekhao mahaeemaa kaa raajaa
aba aao hama saraahaem . (3) kharaeeṣhaṭa parabhau kao... .
1. waha eeshawara sae eeshawara jayaotaikaa sanaatana
ghaृṇaa usanae na kaiyo garabha kaunwaaraee sae
sachachaa paramaeshawara na saृjaa para janamaa
aba aao hama saraahaem . (3) kharaeeṣhaṭa parabhau kao... .
2. hae saarae daoota gaṇaom jaya-jayakaara tauma gaao
haan sawaragao kae sawaraga maem tauma gaatae rahao
mahaimaa aura satautai eeshawara sarawa paradhaanakao
aba aao hama saraahaem . (3) kharaeeṣhaṭa parabhau kao... .
3. aamaeena parabhau dhanaya ho paraaṇa kae laie janamaa
hae Yeshu taeraee ananata mahaimaa
paitaa kaa wachana aba daehadhaaraee hauaa
aba aao hama saraahaem . (3) kharaeeṣhaṭa parabhau kao... .

songs.title: aba uṭha‌ hae jawaana ho samsaaralaaee kharaeeṣhaṭamaa jaitanalaaee
lyrics: kao. aba uṭha‌ hae jawaana ho
samsaaralaaee kharaeeṣhaṭamaa jaitanalaaee (2)
taimarao jayaotai aaekao chha, parakaashamaana haaum (2)
paramaparabhaukao mahaimaa udaaekao chha (2)
1. andhayoraolae paृthawaeelaaee ḍhaakaekao chha
paapakao jawaalaalae maanaisalaaee paalaekao chha (2)
aba uṭha‌ hae saathaee ho
maukataikao dhauna laiera (2)
taimarao jayaotai... paramaparabhaukao...
2. paiḍaa baedanaalae maanaisa chhaṭapaṭaee rahaechhana‌
satayakao khaojaimaa bhaaitaaraee rahaechhana‌ (2‌)
aba uṭha‌ hae samgaee ho
shaanataikao naaraa laiera (2)
taimarao jayaotai... paramaparabhaukao...

songs.title: aba jaagaृtai aaekaochha yao daeshamaa (2)
lyrics: (aba jaagaृtai aaekaochha yao daeshamaa) (2)
paoorawadaekhai pashachaimasamama, utataradaekhai dakaṣhaiṇasamama
(aba jaagaृtai aaekaochha) (3) yao daeshamaa
(aba jaagaृtai aaekaochha yao daeshamaa) (2)
paoorawadaekhai pashachaimasamama, utataradaekhai dakaṣhaiṇasamama
(aba jaagaृtai aaekaochha) (3) yao daeshamaa
(Yeshu maathai uchaalainauhaunaechha yao daeshamaa) (2)
maechaeedaekhai mahaakaalaeesamama, haimaaladaekhai taraaeesamama Yeshulaaee
sabaailae daekhanaechhana‌, Yeshulaaee sabaailae chainanaechhana‌
Yeshu maathai uchaalainauhaunaechha yao daeshamaa
(Yeshu maathai uchaalainauhaunaechha yao daeshamaa) (2)
maechaeedaekhai mahaakaalaeesamama, haimaaladaekhai taraaeesamama Yeshulaaee
sabaailae daekhanaechhana‌, Yeshulaaee sabaailae chainanaechhana‌
Yeshu maathai uchaalainauhaunaechha yao daeshamaa

songs.title: ababaa paitaa tapaaeemmaai maatara ma rahaun
lyrics: ababaa paitaa tapaaeemmaai maatara ma rahaun,
maerao ichachhaa tapaaeemkaai jasatao sadaa rahaosa‌
maerao haृdaya nanaibhaaoonauhaosa‌
malaaee nachhaaḍanauhaosa‌
ababaa paitaa tapaaeemmaai maatara ma rahaun .

songs.title: abhaiṣhaeka garanauhaosa‌ bharanaosa‌ pawaitara aatamaalae (2)
lyrics: (abhaiṣhaeka garanauhaosa‌, bharanaosa‌ pawaitara aatamaalae) (2)
(tapaaeemkao yaojanaa baujhana sahaayataa garanauhaosa‌‌) (2)
(najaeeka hauna chaahanachhau, atai najaeeka hauna) (2)
najaeeka hauna chaahanachhau (tapaaeemkaai) (3)

songs.title: amaola ragata Yeshu kharaeeṣhaṭakao daie kalawaraeemaa
lyrics: 1. amaola ragata Yeshu kharaeeṣhaṭakao daie kalawaraeemaa
paapaeeharaoo ra waidaraohaee aaoo saba unaeekahaan .
kao. amaola-amaola ragata unakao dhaeraai naai bahaekao
gara bishwas anai garahaṇa naimatao unakao
2. amaola ragatalae Yeshukao naikao paaradachha
taimarao paraaṇalaaee saphaa garadaai ahailae pakhaalachha .
3. amaola ragata jasalae haamaee laड़ainmaa jaitachhaaun
paapa, shaaitaana, dauṣhaṭamaathai saamaratha ragatalae .
4. amaola ragatalae parabhaukao paugachhaau eeshawarakahaan
baaṭao haamarao mahaimaakao amaola ragatalae .

songs.title: arau kaohai chhaaina‌ aadarakao yaogaya ekamaatara maalaika tapaaee
lyrics: (arau kaohai chhaaina‌ aadarakao yaogaya ekamaatara maalaika tapaaee
arau kaohai chhaaina‌ saihaamsanakao yaogaya ekamaatara raajaa tapaaee) (2)
(saaraa aadara saaraa mahaimaa taimaraai taimaraai) (2)
(arau kaohai chhaaina‌ mahaimaakao yaogaya ekamaatara parabhau tapaaee
arau kaohai chhaaina‌ naiṣhakamlangaga pawaitara ekamaatara thaumaa tapaaee) (2)
(saaraa aadara saaraa mahaimaa taimaraai taimaraai) (2)
(naanu unakao uchacha) (3) naaun Yeshu

songs.title: arajaee haamarao saunayou nai naepaalakao ḍhaokaa khaolayou nai parabhau
lyrics: kao. arajaee haamarao saunayou nai naepaalakao ḍhaokaa khaolayou nai parabhau
manakao ḍhaokaa chaanड़ai nai sabakaa khaolaidaeoo, parabhau naepaalaee bhaaikaa
1. sawaragakao waaibhawa tayogaera parabhau samsaaramaa aae nai (2)
taimaee ra malaaee maukatai dainau karaoosa uṭhaae nai (2)
2. naepaalaee bhaai, naepaalaee bahainaee abaera bhaisakayao (2)
kaina basachhaau naishachainata bhaye baelaa gaisakayao (2)
3. bishwas gara Yeshumaa haau, jaeewana amara laeoo (2)
kharaeeṣhaṭakaai naimatai balaiyao bhaye naepaala jaitaidaeoo (2)

songs.title: aradadha naishaamaa laiee sausanadaesha daeena banaee aayoun haamaee
lyrics: kao. aradadha naishaamaa laiee sausanadaesha, daeena banaee aayoun haamaee taimarao dawaaramaa
1. dauradashaa yao saba daekhai samsaarakao paapakao bhaaralae maanawa maichaekao (2)
jaunadagaeekao haala saudhaarana bhanaee (2) eeshawara pautara jagamaa aae samkaocha namaanaee
2. eeshawara ra maanawabaeechakao paradaa paapaee maanawakao paapalae garadaa (2)
taoड़ee maanawalaaee laana eeshawarakahaan (2) aaunaubhao’ mahaana‌ eeshawara dauṣhaṭa samsaaramaa .
3. shahara yaeraooshalaema, gaawaain baethalaehaema janamae gaoṭhaaimaa baalaka eka narama (2)
kharaeeṣhaṭa jaeewanadhaara, Yeshu taaraṇahaara (2) bishwas layoee aaunae jatai haunachhana‌ maृtayaupaara .

songs.title: arapaṇa garachhau yao jaeewana naiyanataraṇa garanaosa‌
lyrics: 1. arapaṇa garachhau yao jaeewana, naiyanataraṇa garanaosa‌
jataai panai pachhayounchhau, najaeeka haosa‌ yo ṭaaḍhao .
kao. tayora chhau ma jaana, tayora chhau ma jaana
saewaa paooraa garachhau ma, tayora chhau ma jaana
2. saidadha ichachhaa khaojadachhau, agauwaaee garanaosa‌
kahailayoi ma ḍaraaundaina, tapaaeem najaeeka haunaosa‌ .
3. daina-daina daekhachhau waraiparai, phasala aatamaakao
kharaeeṣhaṭakao premalae bharanauhaosa‌, malaaee paṭhaaunauhaosa‌ .
malaaee paṭhaaunauhaosa‌, malaaee paṭhaaunauhaosa‌
bishwasyaogaya haunachhau ma, malaaee paṭhaaunauhaosa‌ .

songs.title: arapaṇa garadachhaaun yao bhawanalaaee parabhau eeshawaralaaee taraaṇakarataa
lyrics: 1. arapaṇa garadachhaaun yao bhawanalaaee parabhau eeshawaralaaee, taraaṇakarataa Yeshulaaee
aaraadhanaa satautai bainataee ra paukaara, garachhaaum yahaan aba anataradhayona .
kao. saunaidainaosa‌ paukaara yao haamarao, parabhau, lainauhaosa‌ bhawana yao (2)
2. bhaokaa-payosa haृdaya, sawaragaeeya bhaojanakao banadhana ḍaoraee paapaaikao
charaṇa yahaan tapaaeemkao upadaeshaka tapaaeemkao daasadawaaraa dainauhaosa‌ bhaojana aatamaakao .
3. bhajanaadai satautai, arajabainataee yahaan chaढ़ainachhana‌ jaba tapaaeemkahaan saunaidainaosa‌ kharaeeṣhaṭa Yeshumaa,
wainaya utatara paaosa‌ mana shaanatai rahaosa‌, Yeshu naaun sadaa mahaimaita haosa‌ .
4. paratairaupa ho yao mana manadairakao kaaraeegaraee yao maanaiekao parabhau, nairajaeewa bhawana yao,
taai marajaee haoosa‌, parabhau, aaee basaee saunaaunlaa madhaurawaaṇaee tapaaeemkao .
5. naitaya-naitaya balaosa‌ chamakaee naai rahaosa‌ parakaashaita haoosa‌ Yeshu, sadabhaawanaa yao chha jahaan
bharapaoora jaeewana tayoraee sadaa paaranauhaosa‌, aaunchha jao yahaan sadaa .

songs.title: arapanachhau parabhau maerao jaeewana tapaaeemkao charaṇamaa
lyrics: kao. (arapanachhau parabhau maerao jaeewana tapaaeemkao charaṇamaa
lainaosa‌ parabhau maerao jaeewana tapaaeemkao raajayamaa tapaaeemkao raajayamaa) (2)
1. kalawaraee karaoosakao paiḍaa samajhandaa haृdaya maerao taḍapanachha
saagara jhaaim gahairao premalaaee baujhadaa mana maerao kamapanachha .
(aaphanaai jaeewana balai daiera paapa maerao dhaunaubhayao) (2)
ma maranau thaiyao maerao saṭaṭaamaa (Yeshujaee maranau bhao) (2)
2. samsaaraika jaeewana baitaae maile aaphanaai abhailaaṣhaamaa
saृṣhaṭaikarataalaaee bhaulaera maile satayataa khaojaen andhayoraomaa
(maailae chaunaina parabhau tapaaeemlaaee aaphaailae chaunanaubhayao) (2)
haraaekao ma paapaee bhaeḍaalaaee (Yeshulae bhaeṭaṭaaunau bhao) (2)

songs.title: alagaa chaauड़a parakhaalabhaitara sawaragaeeya shaharamaa
lyrics: 1. alagaa, chaauड़a parakhaalabhaitara sawaragaeeya shaharamaa
yauga-yauga, daesha-daeshakaa sabaai sanata basachhana‌ aananada saathamaa .
2. pawaitara jhauṇaḍa, eka daृड़ saenaa, eka sharaeṣhaṭha waichaara sabakao
gaaunchhana‌ eka raaga, garachhana‌ eka kaama eka mahaaraajaakao .
3. tapaaeemkao wachana saanchao chha pausataa-pausataadaekhai
sawatanatarataa, sataya ra prem yainakao raajaya chha baढ़daai .
4. na paairao, na ṭhaoolao bhalalae naṣhaṭa haunachha tyo paharaa
jahaan chha tyo shahara mahaana‌, amara ananata sadaa .

songs.title: alaphaa omaegaa aadai anaadai
lyrics: kao. (alaphaa omaegaa aadai anaadai) (2)
(tapaaee saृsaṭaikarataa , tapaaee jaiwanadaataa) (2)
(hao ho haoshananaa, haa haa haalaelauyoha) (2)
1. (sarawajanyonaee, sarawaauchacha pawaitara paramaeshawara tapaaee (2)
aadhaeelaaee shaanata garanae, banadhanaharau phaukaaeedainae
(shakataishaalaee paramaeshawara tapaaee) (2)
2. (sarawabayopai, yahaowaa raphaa premailao paramaeshawara tapaaee) (2)
parashamṣhaakao yaogaya tapaaee, aaraadhanaakao yaogaya tapaaee
(yaehaowaa yairae tapaaee) (2)

songs.title: awataara bhayao parabhau Yeshukao unakao haosa‌ jaya
lyrics: kao. awataara bhayao parabhau Yeshukao unakao haosa‌ jaya
1. saaraa jagatakao hauna maukataidaataa (2), baaṭao, sachachaain ra
jaeewanakao daataa aaunaubhao’ parabhau (2) haamarao naimataimaa .
2. paapamaya jaeewana haamarao ḍaubaekao (2) daekhaauna aaunaubhao’
prem eeshawarakao aaunaubhao’ Yeshu (2) shaanatai laiera .
3. uhaankao lagi haृdaya khaolaidaeoo (2) phaikaraeekao jaeewana
unalaaee laina daeoo, nawaeena jaeewana laiee (2) jaaoo ramaaundaai .

songs.title: ashaanataikao paeera baढ़yao dhaunaee lagaaera (2)
lyrics: kao. ashaanataikao paeera baढ़yao dhaunaee lagaaera (2)
parabhau kharaeeṣhaṭamaa bishwas gara manalaaee jagaaera haai, sauna naepaalaee
1. saukha, shaanatai naepaalaeekao maailaa pakhaalaera (2)
amara jaeewana mailanae chhaaina, dhaeraai parakhaiera haai, sauna naepaalaee .
2. maukatai chhaaina samsaaramaa manalae gaunailaie (2)
daajayaoo-bhaai, daidaee-bahainaee, bishwas garailaie haai, sauna naepaalaee .
3. saunaee bishwas nagaraemaa ṭhaoolao haamarao bhaoola (2)
maukatai dainae parabhau Yeshu jaeewanakao maoola haai, sauna naepaalaee .
4. sawaragabaaṭa parabhau aae maukatai laiera (2)
karaoosamaathai maranaubhayao jaeewana dainalaaee haai, sauna naepaalaee .
5. paapakao baojhaa uṭhaailaanae arakao chhaaina kaohaee (2)
euṭaai maataraai parabhau Yeshu jaeewana dainae unaai haai, sauna naepaalaee .

songs.title: ashaanataimaa jaiunnaeharaoo kharaeeṣhaṭalae taimaeelaaee khaojairahaechhana‌
lyrics: kao. ashaanataimaa jaiunnaeharaoo (kharaeeṣhaṭalae taimaeelaaee khaojairahaechhana‌) (2)
(ashaanataimaa shaanatai daina baolaairahaechha) (2)
1. ṭaaढ़a bhaagaee najaau kharaeeṣhaṭakao premadaekhai
kharaeeṣhaṭalae taimaeelaaee bairasana sakadaainna (2)
(aakaashabhanadaa ṭaaढ़o chha taimaee paratai kharaeeṣhaṭakao prem
saagara bhanda gahairao chha taimaee paratai unakao prema) (2)
2. samsaaramaa rahaunnajaela maayo garachhana‌ dhaeraailae
eka daina maraepachhai maayo garachhana‌ kasalae (2)
(samsaarakao aaphanatalae raundaai waidaa daelaana‌
chhaainana‌ kaohaee kharaeeṣhaṭa baahaeka maayo garanae taimaeelaaee) (2)

songs.title: ashakaom maem ḍaubaa yae jaeewana khaushaiyaom sae bhara jaaegaa
lyrics: kao. ashakaom maem ḍaubaa yae jaeewana khaushaiyaom sae bhara jaaegaa
jaatae haaim hama aisae daesha saba kauchha badala jaaegaa . (2)
1. bhaookhae na haomgae wahaan payosaee lawa na haogaee
usakaa parashamsaa maaim karaoongaa jaeewana samwara jaaegaa (2)
2. aanshau maerae paochhakara taaja aasamaanaee waha daegaa (2)
usakae kadamaom maem jaeewana maeraa gama sae ubhara jaaegaa (2)
3. khaushaiyon haai baankaee jahaan kaee eka daina tamaama haogaee (2)
jaisakaee najara haai Yeshu masaeeha para wao usakae samga jaaegaa (2)

songs.title: asataachalapaarai mahaimaita daeshamaa maerao chha euṭaa ghara (2)
lyrics: kao. asataachalapaarai mahaimaita daeshamaa maerao chha euṭaa ghara (2)
chaanḍaai naai Yeshu aaunaubhaera paurayounchhana‌ saraasara (2)
1. saanao gharakao chhaanaomaunai, thaoraai kaurao bhae panai
sabaaibhanadaa saukhaee chhau ma, kaaraṇa saatha chhana‌ jayawanata Yeshu,
yahaan sadhaain basanae haoina mahaimaita daeshamaa jaanauchha
saunadara shahara, saunakao saḍaka, kainaara sawachachha chaandaeekao chha (2)
2. naachadaai, haansadaai, satautai gaaundaai sanataharaoosaita hainड़naechhau
waeeṇaa bajaaundaai gaaunaechhau, ma maukauṭa paaee ramaaumaechhau,
yao ho taerao chamakailao ghara, bhanachhana‌ malaaee premaee eeshawara
tayora chha yao taeraolaagai, raaja gara‌ yahaan sadhaain naanaee (2)

songs.title: ahao katai ramaailao khaushaeekao daina aayao
lyrics: kao. ahao katai ramaailao khaushaeekao daina aayao
maukataidaataa parabhaukao baethalaehaemamaa janama bhao’
chhana‌ jao maerao haृdayamaa kharaeeṣhaṭa raajaa basaekao (2)
jaya jaya baalaka raajaakao jaya jaya jaya haosa‌ sadaa (2)
1. eeshawarakao paraiya pautara parabhau kharaeeṣhaṭa sawaragamaa mahaimaita (2)
baalakakao raoopamaa pasaraiya ḍaunड़maa, waishawamaa awahaelaita .
2. sauna-chaandaee chhaaina, dhaoopa panai haoina, samapaooraṇa jaeewana laeoo (2)
gaoṭharaoopaee haृdaya dhaoera aajaai parabhaujaee raaja garaidaeoo .

songs.title: aa masaeehaa mana maem (2)
lyrics: kao. aa masaeehaa mana maem, (2) payora taeraa mailae, daina maeraa khailae
isa dauhkhaee jaeewana maem... aa masaeehaa... .
1. isa samsaara kae baataom maaim, chaaina nahaeem paayo maainae
paayo haai dau:kha darada yahaan, aura khaoee shaanatai maainae (2)
aaja pataa chalaa, tau agara mailaa, payora kae jaeewana maem .
2. aaja nahaeem tao kala jaraoora, jaga yae chhaड़ kae jaanaa haai
phaira kayaom isa daunaiyon maem maai, apanae daila kao lagaa laungaa (2)
dailakae dawaara para, kayaom khaड़a haai aajaa mana maem .

songs.title: aa haa haa haa haa haa haa haa haa haa haa dhainataangaga haai
lyrics: dhainataangaga haai dhainataangaga manaaimaa basayao maadalaukao taala (haa) (4)
kalawaraee saakaṣhaee raakhaee gaansaekao chhauṭalaa haai maayo jaala
(laaibaraee laai laai laai) (2)
dhainataangaga haai dhainataangaga manaaimaa basayao maadalaukao taala
kalawaraee saakaṣhaee raakhaee gaansaekao chhauṭalaa haai maayo jaala
e haai chhauṭalaa haai maayo jaala
kalawaraee saakaṣhaee raakhaee gaansaekao chhauṭalaa haai maayo jaala (haun) (5)
2. dhara haai dhara aansaukao dhaaraa Yeshulae chauhaae (haa) (4)
paapakao kaalao daagalaaee dhauna ragata bahaae
(laaibaraee laai laai laai) (2)
dhara haai dhara aansaukao dhaaraa Yeshulae chauhaae
paapakao kaalao daagalaaee dhauna ragata bahaae,
e haai ragata bahaae .
paapakao kaalao daagalaaee dhauna ragata bahaae .
3. phairaimaa phairai tyo jaoonakaeeraee chamakaejhaain aunsaeemaa (haa) (4)
baalae haai kharaeeṣhaṭalae amara jayaotai manakao kaausaeemaa
(laaibaraee laai laai laai) (2)
phairaimaa phairai tyo jaoonakaeeraee chamakaejhaain aunsaeemaa
baalae haai kharaeeṣhaṭalae amara jayaotai manakao kaausaeemaa,
e haai manakao kaausaeemaa
baalae haai kharaeeṣhaṭalae amara jayaotai manakao kaausaeemaa (haun) (5)
4. jhala ra mala sadhaain halachala kaṣhaṇaika jaeewanamaa (haun) (5)
Yeshumaa bishwas garanaechhau sadhaain, raakhanaechhau yao manamaa
(laaibaraee laai laai laai) (2)
jhala ra mala sadhaain halachala kaṣhaṇaika jaeewanamaa
pauganaechhau Yeshu bhajanaechhau sadhaain, raakhanaechhau yao manamaa,
e haai raakhanaechhau yao manamaa
(Yeshumaa bishwas garanaechhau sadhaain, raakhanaechhau yao manamaa) (4)

songs.title: aairahaekaa chhaaun (3) thaumaakao ragatakao kaaraṇa
lyrics: (aairahaekaa chhaaun) (3), thaumaakao ragatakao kaaraṇa
chhauna saimhaasanalaaee, (aairahaekaa chhaaun) (2)
daṇaḍawata‌ garana Yeshulaaee aaraadhanaa garana parabhaulaaee
(aairahaekaa chhaaun) (3)

songs.title: aaunchha jhajhalakao tyo karaoosakao ma paapaeekao lagi
lyrics: kao. aaunchha jhajhalakao tyo karaoosakao ma paapaeekao lagi
maerao parabhau maraekao (2)
1. baaikauṇaṭha dhaama tayogaera, maanawa banaee aaunaubhayao (2)
daladalae hailaobaaṭa malaaee bachaaunau bhayao (2)
haraaee gaekao bhaeड़a jhaain malaaee (2) aaphanao bagaalamaa layounau bhayao (2)
2. aaja panai baolaaee rahaechhana‌ maerao raajaa Yeshulae (2)
gahabharai aanshau laiee, pharakai aaunae aashaalae (2)
chhaeड़eeekao hat pasaaraera (2) parakhaee rahaechhana‌ angalo lainalaaee (2)

songs.title: aaundachhau tapaaeemkao charaṇamaa paradachhau tapaaeemkao sharaṇamaa
lyrics: kao. aaundachhau tapaaeemkao charaṇamaa, paradachhau tapaaeemkao sharaṇamaa
paapakao baojha chha jaeewanamaa, haṭaaee basanauhaosa‌ haृdayamaa
1. saikaaunauhaosa‌ malaaee payora garana tapaaeemlaaee (2)
parabhau malaaee tapaaeemlae payora garanaubhao’ pahailae (2)
2. samaataee maerao hat raakhanauhaosa‌ malaaee saatha (2)
jaeewanakao jayaotai daiee chamakaaunauhaosa‌ malaaee (2)

songs.title: aaundaaichhau pharakaera ghaumadaa ghaumadaai Yeshukahaan (2)
lyrics: kao. aaundaaichhau pharakaera, ghaumadaa ghaumadaai Yeshukahaan (2)
(baaṭao daobaaṭaomaa alamalairahaen ma aaphaai naai haraairahae) (2)
1. premakao parataeekalaaee khaojae prem paauna maile (2)
ma bhaautaarairahaen shaanataikao khaojaeemaa ma haraairahaen
ma ḍaulaee hainड़e lakaṣha baaṭao wainaa maukataikao baaṭao aatamaakao shaanatai
ma khaojaee rahaen ma lagi rahaen
2. baitairahae taee dainaharaoo aashaa nairaashaamaa (2)
ma khaojaee rahaen samsaaramaa maile paaen sawaarathaee jaeewanaharaoo
dhaokaai dhaokaa jhauṭhao samsaaramaa parabhau taimaeelae daiyou ananata jaeewana
naihsawaaratha prem shaanatai aananada .

songs.title: aauna daidaee, daajayaoo bhaaee, kalawaraeekao ḍaanड़aimaa
lyrics: kao. aauna daidaee, daajayaoo bhaaee, kalawaraeekao ḍaanड़aimaa
paapakao baojha raakhaidaeoo, karaoosakao phaedai maaim
dhaowa taimarao paapaee haृdaya, Yeshukao ragatalae, maukatai udadhaara ra shaanatai
taba paaunchhaaum taimaeelae (2)
1. haimaalakao paanaee gamgaajala ra taraiwaeṇaeelae
kae taimarao paapa dhaoidaiyao kae taimaee shaudadha bhayou (2)
haimaalakao paanaeebhanadaa chaokhao paanaee bagaechha yahaan (2)
Yeshulae maatara taimarao paapaharaoo, dhaunasakanau haunachha (2)
2. pamkaṣhaee paraaṇaeekao ragatalae taimaeelae chaढ़aekao balaidaanalae
kae taimarao paapa maochana bhao, kae taimaeelae maukatai paayou (2)
pamkaṣhaee paraaṇaeekao ragatabhanadaa shaudadha ragata bagaechha yahaan (2)
taimarao lagi Yeshu balai bhaisakaekaa chhana‌ (2)
3. tairatha warata garaera daana pauṇaya chaढ़aera
kae taimaeelae shaanatai paayoum kae taimarao udadhaara bhayao (2)
tairatha warata daana pauṇaya garana paradaaina aba (2)
maukatai saitathaaimaa Yeshulae daina sakanauhaunachha (2)

songs.title: aauna pharakaee aauna parabhau Yeshu masaeehamaa
lyrics: kao. aauna pharakaee aauna parabhau Yeshu masaeehamaa
parakhaee rahaechhana‌ taimaeelaaee saitataaimaa maukataidaana dainalaaee .
1. maanawakao paapa maeṭaaunalaaee aaunaubhao parabhau jagamaa
kaoosakao kaaṭha baokaera jaanaubhao kalawaraee ḍaeenड़amaa (2)
2. paapakao banadhana taoड़nalaaee dau:kha ra darada sahanau bhayao
taimarao ra maerao udadhaara garanalaaee aaphanaai paraaṇa panai dainaubhayao (2)
3. samaya haundaai naai mana phairaaoo parabhaulae naishachaya amgaalanae chhana‌
uhaankao chamakailao jayaotaimaa taimaeelaaee sadhaaim ḍaoraaunaechhana‌ (2)

songs.title: aaunau bhao’ sawaragadaekhai maukauṭalaaee tayogaee maerao lagi
lyrics: 1. aaunau bhao’ sawaragadaekhai maukauṭalaaee tayogaee, maerao lagi laiee awataara
baethalaehaemakao gaaunmaa thaiena ṭhaaun aaphanao lagi hae taaraṇahaara,
makahaan parabhau Yeshu aaunaosa‌, maerao haृdayamaa dhaeraai chha ṭhaaun .
2. sayolakaa haunachhana‌ kaura ra charaakaa gaunड़ tainalae laaunchhana‌ jamgalamaa
tara tapaaeemkaai shaira raakhanalaaee ṭhaaun thaiena gaalaeelamaa .
makahaan parabhau Yeshu aaunaosa‌, maerao haृdayamaa dhaeraai chha ṭhaaun .
3. jaeewaita wachana saatha laiee sawaragadaekhai oralaee maukataidaana daina aaunaubhao’
tara ṭhaṭaṭaalae karaoosamaa chaढ़ae, lagaaee maukauṭa kaanड़akao,
makahaan parabhau Yeshu aaunaosa‌, maerao haृdayamaa dhaeraai chha ṭhaaun .
4. sawaragakao dawaara khaolaindaa, daootagaṇalae gaaundaa, tapaaeem mahaimaasaatha aaundaa
shabada saunana paaun “tanlaaee dhaeraai chha ṭhaaun, maeraochhaeu sadaa basana aa”
maerao mana taba khaushaee haunachha, jaba paitaakahaan pauganaechhau .

songs.title: aaunauhaosa‌ aaoonauhaosa‌ ma bhaitara bhaitaraai gahairaaeemaa
lyrics: aaunauhaosa‌, aaunauhaosa‌
ma bhaitara bhaitaraai gahairaaeemaa chhauhaunaosa‌
ṭaaḍhaa kataai najaanau haosa‌ - 6

songs.title: aaunauhaosa‌ pawaitara aatamaa (6) chhaunauhaosa‌ malaaee
lyrics: 1. aaunauhaosa‌ pawaitara aatamaa (6)
(chhaunauhaosa‌ malaaee tapaaeekao haatalae
dhaunauhaosa‌ malaaee pawaitara ragatalae) (2)
2. shaanataikao aatamaa...
3. chamgaaeekao aatamaa...

songs.title: aaunauhaosa‌ pawaitara aatamaa bainataee chha (2)
lyrics: kao. aaunauhaosa pawaitara aatamaa bainataee chha (2)
1. layounauhaosa‌ changagaai ra maukatai (yao haamarao haृdayakao chaeetakaara) (2)
2. layounauhaosa‌ jaagaृtai yahaan (yao haamarao haृdayakao chaeetakaara) (2)

songs.title: aaunauhaosa‌ pawaitara aatamaa haamaee tapaaeemkao saathamaa
lyrics: aaunauhaosa‌ pawaitara aatamaa, haamaee tapaaeemkao saathamaa
bharanaosa‌ tapaaeemkao shakatailae raaja garanauhaosa‌ manamaa
tapaaeem jaiundao paanaee, kahailayoi nasaukanae jharanaa
saanatawanaa ra salalaahaakaara, lainaosa‌ aaphanao washamaa . aaunauhaosa‌...

songs.title: aaunauhaosa‌ parabhau (2) aaunauhaosa‌ parabhau maerao haृdayamaa
lyrics: aaunauhaosa‌ parabhau (2), aaunauhaosa‌ parabhau maerao haृdayamaa
tapaaeemkao upasathaitailae malaaee sadhaain bharanauhaosa‌
aaunauhaosa‌ Yeshu, aaunauhaosa‌ pawaitara aatamaa .

songs.title: aaunauhaosa‌ parabhau tapaaeem haamarao maajhamaa dainaosa‌ tapaaeemkao
lyrics: aaunauhaosa‌ parabhau tapaaeem, haamarao maajhamaa, dainaosa‌ tapaaeemkao pawaitara aatamaa
tapaaeemkao aananadalae bharaina sakaoon, tapaaeemlaaee sadhaain dhanayakao bhanaoon
hallelujah (4) satautai gachha (3) tapaaeemlaaee .

songs.title: aaunauhaosa‌ parabhau maerao jainadagaeemaa
lyrics: aaunauhaosa‌ parabhau maerao jainadagaeemaa
raakhanauhaosa‌ malaaee tapaaee kaai sharaṇamaa
dainauhaosa‌ malaaee tapaaee kaai hat
ḍagamagaae kao chhau jaba ma tapaaee kaai saatha
maerao payorao maerao parabhau maerao bharaosaa tapaaee parabhau (2)
(samajhainachha maerao ataitalaaee paapamaa ḍhaubaekao ma tauchachhalaaee
tapaaee bairaudhamaa ma haiḍanaelaaee
amgaalanaubhao bhaulaaee maerao paapalaaee
amgaalanaubhao bhaulaaee maerao paapalaaee) (2)
maerao payarao maerao parabhau maerao bharaosaa tapaaee parabhau (2)
maerao yao manamaa rahanauhaosa‌ malaaee paapabaaṭa bachaaunauhaosa‌
maerao jaiwanakao haraeka paaeelaamaa (tapaaee maerao saatha dainauhaosa‌) (2)

songs.title: aaunaechhana‌ (4) baihaanaeekao taaraalae andhayorao haṭaaunaechhana‌
lyrics: kao. aaunaechhana‌ (4) baihaanaeekao taaraalae andhayorao haṭaaunaechhana‌
1. haamarao parataeekaṣhaa paoorao haunae bhao’, kharaeeṣhaṭakao parataijanyo saanchao haunae bhao’ (2)
haunae bhao’ (3) aaunaechhana‌ (2) malaaee laina aaunaechhana‌ .
2. shaira uṭhaaee maathai haera taimarao chhauṭakaaraa najaeeka aa’kao chha (2)
aa’kao chha (3) aaunaechhana‌ (2) malaaee laina aaunaechhana‌ .

songs.title: aaoo aba parakaashamaana haooo jayaotaikaa sanataana bhaye
lyrics: kao. aaoo aba parakaashamaana haooo jayaotaikaa sanataana bhaye
anadhakaara sabalaaee tayogaera mahaimaa ra paooraṇataamaa aaoo .
1. (mahaana aajanyolaaee paoorao garana jayaotai dhaaraṇa garanauchha) (2)
jaiundao wachanalaaee shakataikao saathamaa
jayaotaikao sanataana bhaye yao waisha‍walaaee saunaaunauchha .
2. (saiyaonakaa raajaalaaee sawaagata garana raajapatha haamaeelae banaaunauchha) (2)
laiera upahaara tayao, haera, kaohaee aaundaaichhana,
jayaotaikaa sanataana bhaye yao pausataalaaee bachaaunauchha .

songs.title: aaoo aaoo daajayaoo-bhaai mailaeejaulaee gaaaun (2)
lyrics: kao. aaoo-aaoo, daajayaoo-bhaai, mailaeejaulaee gaaaun (2)
1. Yeshu maukataidataalae maृtayau jaya garae,
aaoo-aaoo, sabaai bhaai, aananada manaaaun .
2. shaaitaanamaathai jayawanata bhaye phaerai jaiiuṭhae,
aaoo-aaoo, bhaai-bahainaee, unakaai jaya manaaaun .
3. maृtayau-banadhana taoड़ikana sabalaaee bachaae
aaoo-aaoo, kharaeeṣhaṭaeeya bhaai, jayajayakaara manaaaun
4. taeenaai dainamaa baauraee uṭhae, shatarau lajaae
aaoo-aaoo, payoraa bhaai, jayakao shabada saunaaaun .
5. bishwas garaee kamamara kasaee kharaeeṣhaṭakaai pachhai jaaaun
aaoo-aaoo, paraiya bahainaee, unaailaaee pachhayoaun .
6. premaee eeshawara pautara dainae unakaai gauṇa gaaaun
bhaai-bahainaee saba mailaee dhanyawad chaढ़aaun .

songs.title: aaoo aaoo Yeshukahaan aaoo unalae ḍaakadaaichhana‌ ahailae
lyrics: kao. aaoo, aaoo, Yeshukahaan aaoo, unalae ḍaakadaaichhana‌ ahailae
thaakaekaa sabaai, bhaaraeelae thaichaekao, paapadaekhai maukatai unaaimaa paaunchha
1. Yeshu kharaeeṣhaṭalae ḍaakaekaa saunaera dhayona nadaiekao kaina ?
samsaaramaa dauhkha katai sahanachhaau, maehanata garachhaau, chaaina paaundaainaau .
2. ḍaakadaaichhana‌ ahailae bhaai, ṭhaaun khaalaee chha, maaukaa paaundaainaau phaerai,
baelaa chhaaina, daina baitaijaanachha, samsaaramaa andhayoraolae chhapachha,
3. Yeshu kharaeeṣhaṭakao naaundaekhai baahaeka maukatai paaundaainaau kahailayoi,
unaaimaa chha saba paapaeedaekhai chhauṭakaaraa, dainausakachha khaushaee unalae maatara bhaai .

songs.title: aaoo kaama garaaun kaṭanaeemaa alachhae garaee kao basalaa ?
lyrics: 1. aaoo kaama garaaun, kaṭanaeemaa alachhae garaee kao basalaa ?
sabataira anana paakaekao haundaa eka-ekaai daasalaaee unalae bhanadachhana‌‌,
jaaoo kaama gara .
2. aaoo kaama garaaun, daootalae napaaekao kaamamaa hat lagaaaun
sabaailaaee yao sausamaachaara saunaaaun, baitadaaichha baelaa
ḍhailao nagaraaun, raata paradaaichha .
3. aaoo kaama garaaun, shamkaa ra ḍara sabaai daoora garaera
yahaan sabaailae kaama ta garanau chha
unalae nairadhaabaaṭa garaaundachhana‌ aaphanao ichachhaa .
4. aaoo kaama garaaun, ghaama haundaa haamaeeharaoo nabaisaaaun
jahailaesamama haamarao dhaera kaama nahaosa‌ ra jabasamama unalae
bhanadaainana‌, “tan daasa dhanaya” .
5. aaoo kaama garaaun, kaama garanaelae naishachaya paaunaechhana‌ inaama
dhanaya jao anatasamama sathaira haolaana‌,
taee paaunaechhana‌ saukha, aananada ra waisharaama, parabhausanga .

songs.title: aaoo khaushaee manaaoon Yeshulaaee manamaa basaaoon
lyrics: aaoo khaushaee manaaoon, Yeshulaaee manamaa basaaoon,
haamarao haataharaoo uchaalaaun, uccha sawaralae gaaaun taalaee bajaaaun,
aaoo khaushaee manaaoon Yeshulaaee manamaa basaaoon,
unaee maaraiera gaaḍaiekaa, unaee gaaḍaiera baauraiekaa,
baauraiera sawaragamaa uchaalaiekaa (haamaraa jaeewaita Yeshu) (2)
haamaraa jaeewaita Yeshukaa saamanae aa... aa... aaoo, khaushaee manaaoon .

songs.title: aaoo jagata‌kaa bhaai-bahainaee Yeshulae taimaeelaaee ḍaakadaaichhana‌
lyrics: kao. aaoo jagata‌kao bhaai-bahainaee,
Yeshulae taimaeelaaee ḍaakadaaichhana‌ (2)
1. jagata‌maa taimarao gharaai chhaaina (2),
jagata‌maa taimarao maana panai chhaaina (2)
raajaya taimaeelaaee dainakaa lagi Yeshulae taimaeelaaee ḍaakadaaichhana‌ .
2. jagata‌maa taimaee dharama khaojachhaau (2)
jagata‌maa taimaee ghaumaihainड़chhaau (2)
jaeewana maukatai dainakaa lagi Yeshulae taimaeelaaee ḍaakadaaichhana‌ .
3. shairamaa unakao kaanड़akao maukauṭa (2)
kaokhamaa unalaaee bhaalaalae ghaochae (2)
chhaeड़ekao hat pasaaraera Yeshulae taimaeelaaee ḍaakadaaichhana‌ .
4. aaoo daajayaoo-bhaai, aaoo daidaee-baainaee (2)
aaera Yeshumaa bishwas gara (2)
sabaai paapalaaee lainakaa lagi Yeshulae taimaeelaaee ḍaakadaaichhana‌ .

songs.title: aaoo paujaaun raajapaujaaraee aaoo bhajaaun pawaitara jaatai
lyrics: 1. aaoo paujaaun raajapaujaaraee, aaoo bhajaaun, pawaitara jaatai
bhaja Yeshu maukataidaataa, unaee paraiya mahaimaakaa raajaa, (halalaelaooyoha) (8)
2. dhanaya bhana uhaankao naaunlaaee, dhanaya bhanaaun uhaankao naaunlaaee
bhaja Yeshu maukataidaataa, unaee paraiya mahaimaakaa raajaa, (halalaelaooyoha) (8)

songs.title: aaoo bachaaoo parabhau haamaeelaaee kaehaee daekhaindaaina
lyrics: aaoo, bachaaoo parabhau, haamaeelaaee, kaehaee daekhaindaaina andhayoraobaahaeka
chhaelaidaeoo, chhapaidaeoo ḍhaakaidaeoo malaaee
Yeshu parabhau, bhana ma kae garaoon, samsaarakao anata aba chaanḍa haundaaichha
baadalamaathai taimaee aaundaa chainaidaeoo malaaee

songs.title: aaoo maeraa saathaee daui hata
lyrics: kao. aau maeraa saathaee daui hata uchaalaee
ekaai manakaa bhaai dhanyawad chaḍhaaaum
1. baalaka haamaee sabaai mailaee Yeshukahaan jaanachhaaum
sawaraga pauganae lakaṣhaya raakhaee sadhaaim aghai baḍhachhaaum (2)
Yeshu Yeshu Yeshulaaee haamaee bishwas garachhaau
anai haamaeelae Yeshubaaṭa nyano maayo paaunchhaaum (2)
2. baalaka haamaee sabaai mailaee sadhaaim wachana paḍhachhaaum
Yeshukao naaunmaa haansaee haansaee maeeṭhao gaeeta gaaunchhaaum (2)
Yeshu Yeshu Yeshulaaee bishwas gara bhanachhaaum
anai haamaeelae Yeshubaaṭa shaanatai aananada paaunchhaaum (2)

songs.title: aaoo Yeshu laau malaaee bachaaoo
lyrics: kao. aaoo, Yeshu, laau malaaee bachaaoo
paapakao yao bhaaraee aandhaeemaa (2)
1. samsaaraika saagarakao hae balaiyao maajhaee (2)
dauhkha-darada baujhaihainड़nae daunaiyonkao laagai,
paraaṇa dainae, jayona dainae parama upakaaraee (2)
sachachaa pakakaa dharama layounae adharama pakhaalaee .
2. saupadaesha dainathayou, parabhau, daunaiyon chahaaraee (2)
dharamaeelaaee dhanaya bhanaee paapaeelaaee utaaraee,
dauhkha-saukha saathaee samajhaee haansaoo-raooon nabhaye (2)
karaoosamaathai chaढ़you parabhau jaeewana daina kaṭhaai .
3. nagaraee daeoo ḍhailao parabhau, laau na chhaiṭao aaoo na (2)
dauṣhakaramakao baaढ़ee bagayao, bagae sabaai jana,
naau khaiyooo, paaraee laaijaaoo, sauna aaratatanaada (2)
hae jainadagaee daataa Yeshu, raakha aaphanaai saatha .

songs.title: aaoo Yeshukahaan aajaai hae bhaai unakao naimatao chha
lyrics: 1. aaoo Yeshukahaan aajaai, hae bhaai, unakao naimatao chha ahailae naai
kharaeeṣhaṭa najaeeka chhana‌ aashaiṣha‌ dainalaaee, bhanadachhana‌ makahaan aaoo .
kao. aananada-aananada garaaulaa sadhaain, khaushaee haaunlaa jaba naiṣhapaapaee bhaye
basaaunlaa naitaya sanga Yeshukaai ananata gharaaimaa
2. hae paapaee aaoo, parabhaukao baata saunaee, samaaoo hat
aaunchhana‌ jao unakahaan saba paaunchhana‌ saukha, kaaṭainachhana‌ tainakaa dauhkha .
3. aaoo Yeshukahaan waichaara gara bhaai chhana‌, unaee najaeeka wara dainalaaee
aaoo, saba chhaiṭao Yeshukahaan aaoo aashaiṣha‌ sadhaainkao paaoo .

songs.title: aaoo saba paapaee daeena daraidara lakhataraana dauhkhaita
lyrics: 1. aaoo saba paapaee, daeena, daraidara, lakhataraana, dauhkhaita, anaatha
Yeshu taimaeelaaee bachaauna parakhainachhana‌ prema, shakataisaatha .
kao. kharaeeṣhaṭa chhana‌ yaogaya, kharaeeṣhaṭa chhana‌ yaogaya, kharaeeṣhaṭa chhana‌ yaogaya
kharaeeṣhaṭa chhana‌ raajaee, naḍaraaoo, kharaeeṣhaṭa chhana‌ raajaee, naḍaraaoo
2. aaoo daraidara, kharaeeṣhaṭa naimatayounchhana‌, laeoo waradaana paramaeshawarakao
pashachaatataapa ra sataya bishwas saba anaugaraha chaahaindao
wainaapaaisaa, wainaapaaisaa (2) Yeshubaaṭa laina aaoo (2)
3. aaoo saba baesaraee laadaiekaa, paapakao saagaramaa ḍaubanae aaoo
shaudadha haunau parakhayou bhanae taimaee kahailayoi aaundaainaau
dhaaramaika haoina, dhaaramaika haoina (2) paapaeelaaee ḍaakachhana‌ Yeshu (2)
4. daehadhaaraee eeshawara Yeshu sawaraga pharakae taaraṇahaara
raakha unaaimaa bharaosaa, unakao wachanamaa patayora
khaalai Yeshu, khaalai Yeshu (2) garachhana‌ paapaeelaaee udadhaara (2)

songs.title: aaoo sabaai gaeeta gaaoo haai hallelujah aamaina‌
lyrics: 1. aaoo sabaai gaeeta gaaoo haai, hallelujah aamaina‌
haosa‌ baढ़ai Yeshukaai, hallelujah aamaina‌,
sawara ra mana uchaalaee saimhaasanakao aghai
manaparadao chha satautai, hallelujah aamaina‌ .
2. mana unbhao uchaaladaai, hallelujah aamaina‌
khaooba aakaasha garajaaundaai, hallelujah aamaina‌,
kharaeeṣhaṭa haamaraa hauna, haamaeemaa utaranachhana‌
prem unakao ṭaungagaidaaina, hallelujah aamaina‌ .
3. gauṇa gaaaun parabhaukao, hallelujah aamaina
shakatai bhara jaeewanakao, hallelujah aamaina‌,
sawaragamaa paugaaunlaa, unaailaaee bhaeṭaaunlaa,
sadhaain naai gaeeta gaaaunlaa, hallelujah aamaina‌ .

songs.title: aaoo sabaai daajayaoo-bhaai kharaeeṣhaṭakaai gauṇa gaaaun
lyrics: kao. aaoo sabaai daajayaoo-bhaai, kharaeeṣhaṭakaai gauṇa gaaaun
1. haamarao paapakao saaṭao unaee bhae paaṭhao
katarao prem ra katarao dayo haamaeemaathai garae .
aaoo sabaai daajayaoo-bhaai kharaeeṣhaṭakaai gauṇa gaaaun .
2. kharaeeṣhaṭaiyona daajayaoo, kharaeeṣhaṭayona bahainaee, kharaeeṣhaṭa hauna‌ haamaraa saathaee
sawaragalaokamaa paurayounae, maृtayaupaarai taaraee
aaoo sabaai daajayaoo-bhaai, kharaeeṣhaṭalaaee pachhayoaun .
3. jatai bhayao ghaṭaee haamarao, unalaaee sabaai manaaaun
paapalaaee laukaaee narakauṇaḍakao bhaagaee kaailae nahaoaun
aaoo sabaai daajayaoo-bhaai sawaragamaa jaaaun .

songs.title: aaoo sabaai maukatailaaee khaojaaun maukatai paaee sawaragamaa
lyrics: kao. aaoo sabaai, maukatailaaee khaojaaun maukatai paaee, sawaragamaa raaja garaaun
1. haamaee sabaai paapaee thaiyoun jaana laagayoun naashamaa (2)
naashadaekhai bachaaunalaaee (Yeshu aae jagamaa) (2)
2. Yeshu, tapaaeem jagamaa aai garanaubhayao prem (2)
prem garaee basanaubhayao (aaja haamarao saathamaa) (2)
3. raogaeeharaoo bishwas garadaai aae unakao chhaeumaa (2)
bishwas garaee naikao bhaye (gae aaphanaa gharamaa) (2)
4. haamaee sabaai paapaee bhayoun jaanachhaaun kayorae naashamaa (2)
naashadaekhai bachaaunalaaee (Yeshu marae karaoosamaa) (2)
5. maanaisakao paapa laiee ṭaansaidaie karausamaa (2)
karaoosamaa chaढ़ee ragata bahaaee (baauraee uṭhae anatamaa) (2)

songs.title: aaoo sabaai bishwasee aananada garadaai aaoo
lyrics: 1. aaoo sabaai bishwasee, aananada garadaai aaoo,
aaoo sabaaijanaa mailaee baethalaehaemamaa
jagata‌kao taraataa baalaka bhae haera
(aaoo bhajana garadaai paujaaun) (3) kharaeeṣhaṭa parabhaulaaee .
2. hae wachana sanaatana, paramaeshawarakao pautara,
parabhau Yeshu hauna‌ kharaeeṣhaṭa imamaanauela
kanayokao garabhadaekhai maanachhae janamaekao
(aaoo bhajana garadaai paujaaun) (3) kharaeeṣhaṭa parabhaulaaee .
3. hae saba sawaragadaoota hao, jayajayakaara garanaoo
paramaeshawaralaaee haosa‌ sawaragamaa dhanyawad
paृthawaeemaa kaushala maanachhaeharaoomaa mailaapa
(aaoo bhajana garadaai paujaaun) (3) kharaeeṣhaṭa parabhaulaaee .
4. aamaina‌ parabhau dhanaya haamarao lagi janamae
Yeshu sadaa tapaaeemkao naama paujaiosa‌
eeshawarakao wachana aba daehaee bhaekao
(aaoo bhajana garadaai paujaaun) (3) kharaeeṣhaṭa parabhaulaaee .

songs.title: aaoo haamaee aaphaailaaee tayora garaau
lyrics: aaoo haamaee aaphaailaaee tayora garaau
aaoo haamaee haृdayalaaee tayora garaau
sabhaai bhanda maathai, arau naaun bhanda maathai
yaeshaulaaee raakhaau, yaeshaulaaee raakhaau
ra haamarao saaraa haृdayalae, ra haamarao saaraa paraaṇalae, ra haamarao saaraa shakatailae
(yaeshaulaaee uchaalaau) (2) oha hao, yaesaulaaee uchaalaau
uchaalaau, uchaalaau, uchaalaau, yaeshaulaaee
mahaimaa, mahaimaa, mahaimaa, yaeshaulaaee
parashamsaa, parashamsaa, parashamsaa, yaeshaulaaee
aaraadhanaa, aaraadhanaa, aaraadhanaa, yaeshaulaaee
(yaeshaulaaee uchaalaau) (2), oha hao, yaeshaulaaee uchaalaau
ra haamarao saaraa haृdayalae, ra haamarao saaraa paraaṇalae, ra haamarao saaraa shakatailae
(yaeshaulaaee uchaalaau) (2), oha hao, yaeshaulaaee uchaalaau

songs.title: aaoo haamaee utasawa manaaaun utasawa manaaaun premadaanakao
lyrics: aaoo, haamaee utasawa manaaaun, utasawa manaaaun premadaanakao lagi
eeshawara-pautaralae prem garaee jaeewana daie, satautai chaḍhaaundachhaaun kasaailae nadainae
aananada dainaubhao’, bhaeṭaee laiera aaundachhaaun, utasawakao satautaimaa,
(aaoo haamaee utasawa manaaaun) (2) (utasawa manaaundaai gaaaun) (2) raajaalaaee .

songs.title: aaoo haamaee saba mailaee parabhaukao madhaura gaana
lyrics: kao. aaoo haamaee saba mailaee parabhaukao madhaura gaana gaaoo (2)
haamaraa parabhau maukatai dainae kharaeeṣhaṭa Yeshu hauna‌ (2)
1. chaahanaa gara ekapaṭaka chaokhao ra sataya taee wachanakao kalapanaa gara
ekapaṭaka anaauṭhao prem ra parataijanyokao (2)
paaunnaechhaaum taimaeelae khaushaeekao maola (2) jaba satayakao wachana saunanaechhaaum (2)
2. gahanaa banaidaeoo ekapaṭaka haamarao parabhau Yeshukao banaidaeoo haeeraa
maukauṭamaa jhalakaaidaeu yao samsaaranaai (2)
paaunnaechhaaum taimaeelae satayakao maola (2) jaba unakao pachhai laaganaechhaau (2)

songs.title: aaoo... na aaoo... na Yeshu kahaan
lyrics: kao. aaoo... na aaoo... na Yeshu kahaan,
unaailae taimaeelaaee baolaaundaai chhana‌ (2)
1. paapakao bhaaraee baokaera taimaee kahaansamama jaanae
yao bhaaraee baisaaunae ṭhaaun chaahain Yeshu hauna‌... (2)
2. Yeshu bhanachhana‌ makahaan aaunaelaaee kahailayae tayoganae chhauinan
yasakaaraṇa unakao charaṇamaa taimaee aaoo... (2)

songs.title: aae Yeshu yao samsaaramaa paapaeeharaoolaaee bachaaunalaaee
lyrics: kao. aae Yeshu yao samsaaramaa paapaeeharaoolaaee bachaaunalaaee
garaaun bishwas Yeshumaathai, paaunchhana‌ udadhaara paapakao kaṣhamaa (2)
1. Yeshu naasaraee janama laie baethalaehaemakao gaaeekao gaoṭhamaa (2)
chhaड़ee sawaraga aae unaee paapaeeharaoolaaee bachaaunalaaee (2)
2. saaraa samsaara paapa-saagaramaa ḍaubadaai thaiyao parabhauwainaa (2)
aaoo sabaai karaoosakao chhaeumaa maukatai dainachhana‌ Yeshu kharaeeṣhaṭalae (2)

songs.title: aae haai aae aae haai Yeshu samsaaramaa aae
lyrics: 1. aae haai, aae
aae haai, Yeshu samsaaramaa aae
gae haai, haamarao paapa maeṭaigae
(o ho aa haa) (4)
2. daui hajaara waraṣhaaghai gaaeekao gaoṭhama) (2)
paramaeshawarakao ekalao pautara (yasaai ṭhaawaainmaa) (2)
maukataidaataa (2) taaraṇahaara (maanaisa awataara bhae) (3)
(o ho aa haa) (2)
3. (haamaee sabaaikao dauhkha baujhana samsaaramaa aae) (2)
baaṭao, sataya, jaeewana sabaai (ekaai ṭhaaun aae) (2)
Yeshu raajaa (2) hamaraomaajha (maukatai banaee aae) (2)
(o ho aa haa) (2)

songs.title: aao (2) paramaparabhaukao naimatai haamaee gaaaun
lyrics: aao (2) paramaparabhaukao naimatai haamaee gaaaun
haamarao udadhaarakao chattanako naimatai jayajayakaara (3) garaaun
aao (2) dhanyawad garadaai uhaankao saamaunanae aao
bhajana gaaundaai uhaankao (2) jayajayakaara (3) garaaun .

songs.title: aao jaga kae laoga saba haee Yeshu raajaa baulaataa haai
lyrics: kao. aao jaga kae laoga saba haee Yeshu raajaa baulaataa haai .
1. jagamaem jaisakaa sathaana nahaeem haai, jagamaem jaisakaa maana nahaeem haai
raaja taumahaem daenae kae laie, Yeshu raajaa baulaataa haai .
2. jagamaem tauma ho bhaukhae maratae jagamaem tauma ho payosae maratae
bhaojana jala aba mauphata maem daenae, Yeshu raajaa baulaataa haai .
3. saira para kaanṭaom kaa taaja naishaanaee chhaapa haai usakaee bahataee pasalaee
chhaidae hat pasaarae haue, Yeshu raajaa baulaataa haai .
4. aao bhaaiyao aao bahainao aakara usakao parakhao daekhao
saaraa bhaara uṭhaanae kae laie, Yeshu raajaa baulaataa haai ॥

songs.title: aao daṇaḍawata‌ garaaun ra naihauraaun
lyrics: aao daṇaḍawata‌ garaaun ra naihauraaun
haamaraa saृṣhaṭaikarataa paramaparabhaukaai saamau ghauḍaa ṭaekaaun
kainabhanae uhaan naai haamaraa paramaeshawara haunauhaunachha
ra haamaee uhaankaa kharakakaa parajaa, uhaankaa haatakaa bhaeḍaa haaun .

songs.title: aao bahaenaa kaeṭaee- aao bhaiyo tauma bhaye saunaomnaa
lyrics: kao. kaeṭaa- aao bahaenaa kaeṭaee- aao bhaiyo
tauma bhaye saunaomnaa Yeshu kaee kahaemnaa aanaewaalaa raajaa aaegaa
usakae saatha hama mailakara jaaegaa saiyaona daesha... .
hae-hae-hae-hae... haa-haa-haa-haa- (2)
1. paranatau aatamaa sapaṣhaṭa kahataa haai
aanaewaalaa daina kaitanaa kaṭhaina haai,
jao anataima dainaom taka sathaira rahaegaa
usakaa udadhaara haowaegaa (2) (anataima dainaom maem)
2. jao paramaeshawara para bishwas rakhataem haai
ananata jaeewana usakao mailaegaa
jao paramaeshawara sae utapanana haotaa haai
waha usa sae bhaye parama waha karatae haai . (2) (anataima dainaom maem)
3. taunae maerae bachanakao thaamaa haai
samkaṭa kae dainaom maem rakaṣhaa karaoongaa
saarae samsaara para waha aanaewaalaa haai .
kaohaee taeraa maukauṭa chhainana na paae . (2) (anataima dainaom maem)

songs.title: aao mailakae satautai karaingagae Yeshukao gauna gaana karaingagae
lyrics: aao mailakae satautai karaingagae, Yeshukae gauna gaana karaingagae) (2)
(wao haee raajaa wao masaeeha maerae jaeewanakaa saahaaraa) (2)
(naachaingagae, gaangagae dhauma machaangagae, Yeshukae gauna gaana karaingagae) (2)
aao...
(jaya jaya baolao jaya Yeshu kaee jaya) (2)
wao haee raajaa wao masaeeha maerao jaeewanakaa saahaaraa (2)
naachaingagae, gaangagae dhauma machaangagae, Yeshukaee gauna gaana karaingagae (2)
jaya jaya baolao jaya Yeshu kaee jaya...

songs.title: aao yahaowaa kaa dhanyawad karae apanae saarae haृdaya sae
lyrics: kao. ao yahaowaa kaa dhanyawad karae
apanae saarae haृdaya sae banadanaa karae (2)
usakae phaaṭakaom maem satautai karae aura lalakaarae .
1. jaisanae banaayo hamae wao haai hamaaraa aadhaara
jaisanae dai hamakao sawaasa waha haai hamaaraa udadhaara (2)
usakaa ho jaya jaya ho aaraadhanaa
waha haai sabhaye kaa paradhaana . (2)
2. apanaee saaraee tana, mana sae hama parabhau kaee mahaimaa karae
waha haai shaiphaa aura najaata usakaa parashamsaa karae (2)
waha haai jagatakaa bhaataa aura taaraṇaahaara
usakaa ho jaya-jaya sadaa ॥ (2)

songs.title: aao sabaai pharakaera parabhau Yeshukahaan nagaraee baera
lyrics: kao. aao, sabaai pharakaera, parabhau Yeshukahaan nagaraee baera
yao jaeewana chhaṭao chha, maukataikao daina chhaaina aba dhaera .
1. jaba Yeshukahaan gaen, paapa-kaṣhamaakao daana paaen,
maukataikao anaubhawa garaem, unakao naamakao yasha gaaen .
2. Yeshu hauna‌ udaekakao naatha, dhanaechhana‌, taimarao saba paapa
garaera adharama maapha, raakhanaechhana‌ taimaeelaaee saatha .

songs.title: aao haalalaelaooyoha asakaee jaya aayae saaraee saृṣhaṭai
lyrics: aao haalalaelaooyoha asakaee jaya
aayae saaraee saृṣhaṭai usakaee jaya
parabhau mahaana haai satautai kae yaogaya haai ॥ (2)

songs.title: aaaun haamaee aaraadhanaa garaaun saृṣhaṭaikarataakaai saamau ghaunḍaa
lyrics: aaaun haamaee aaraadhanaa garaaun, saृṣhaṭaikarataakaai saamau ghaunḍaa ṭaekaaun
aaaun haamaee daṇaḍawata‌ garaaun, saृṣhaṭaikarataakaai saamau ghaunḍaa ṭaekaaun,
uhaan naai haamaraa paramaeshawara hauna‌ ra haamaee uhaankao kharakakaa parajaa
ra uhaankaa haatakaa bhaeḍaa haaun ra uhaankaa haatakaa bhaeḍaa haaun .

songs.title: aakaasha bharai janautaaraaharaoo gaaunchhana‌ Yeshukao mahaimaa
lyrics: aakaasha bharai janautaaraaharaoo gaaunchhana‌ Yeshukao mahaimaa
dharataikaa sabaai waृkaṣhaharaoolae garachhana Yeshukao parashamsaa
eeshawaralae aaphanaai sawaraoopamaa
haamaeelaaee saृjanau bhao
uhaankao mahaimaa garanakao naimatai
jaeewana dainau bhao (2)
aaoo haai saathaee mailaeejaulaee
gaaaum Yeshukao gaeeta
hat samaaee haiḍaaim samgaai
Yeshumaa chha haamarao jaeeta

songs.title: aakaasha maathai maathai uḍayao maerao mana (2)
lyrics: aakaasha maathai maathai uḍayao maerao mana (2)
haraṣhalae umangagakao saimaa chhaaina Yeshu taimaee aae pachhai (2)
1. saomchaekao thaiina jainadagaeemaa yatai dhaeraai khaushaee paaunchhau bhanaera (2)
aananadakao waraṣhaata bhayao Yeshu taimaee aae pachhai (2)
2. ekalao haunana ma kahailae aba
saaraa daunaiyonlae ṭaaḍaa phaalae panai (2)
ḍhaukaka chha jaeewana bharai Yeshu taimaee aae pachhai (2)

songs.title: aakaashabhanadaa uchacha-uchacha chha naaun
lyrics: 1. aakaashabhanadaa uchacha-uchacha chha naaun,
saagarabhanadaa gahairao gahairao chha prem
aasamaanabhanadaa waishaala-waishaala anaugaraha chha
haamarao parabhau Yeshukao .
kao. yasaailae garachhaau parashamsaa, gaaunchhaaun mahaimaa unaai Yeshukao (2)
2. waakayalae wayakata nahaunae, bhananalaaee shabada napauganae prema,
aadaidaekhai ahailaesamama samayalae saakaṣhaee daiekao prem
sawaraga chhaḍaee aaunaubhao’ karunaimaa maranaubhao’,
maृtayaulaaee jaitanaubhao’, haamaeelaaee maukatai dainalaaee .
3. saaraa saृṣhaṭailae ḍhaokanaechha, sabaai ghaunḍaaharaoo ṭaekanaechhana‌,
nairabala balaiyao haunaechha, laaṭaolae paukaaranaechha tyo naaun
anadhao lae daekhanaechha, bahairaolae saunanaechha,
mauradaa baiuntanaechha unaailaaee mahaimaa dainalaaee .

songs.title: aankhaakao eka naimaeshamaa taurahaeekao aakhaira aawaajamaa
lyrics: kao. aankhaakao eka naimaeṣhamaa, taurahaeekao aakhaira aawaajamaa
(baadalamaa haamaee uड़naechhaau, Yeshusanga haamaee haunaechhaaun) (2)
1. kharaeeṣhaṭamaa maraekaaharaoo pahailae jaiiuṭhachhana‌, tayasapachhai jaiundaaharaoo
(abishwasee ra paapaeeharaoo chaahain chhaड़inachhana‌ pachhautaaundaai) (2)
2. paancha baudadhaimataee kanayoharaoojasataai, laii raakhaaun phaalatau taela
(kauna baelaa aaunchhana‌ taimaraa daulahaa, nasauta dhaeraai baera) (2)
3. ḍhailaaunaechhaainana‌ taimaraa parabhaulae bhanaekaa chhana‌ chaanड़ai aaunchhau
(maृtayausamama naai bishwasee haooo, ma taimaeelaaee laaijaanachhau) (2)

songs.title: aankhaaimaa Yeshukao jhajhalakao manaaimaa unaaikao samajhanaa (2)
lyrics: 1. aankhaaimaa Yeshukao jhajhalakao, manaaimaa unaaikao samajhanaa (2)
2. maile ta Yeshulaaee bairasaechhau, samajhanauhaosa‌ Yeshu malaaee (2)
3. haamaee sabaai jaanaechhaaun sawaraga daeshamaa sadhaainlaaee (2)

songs.title: aankhaaimaa Yeshukao jhajhalakao, manaaimaa unaaikao samajhanaa
lyrics: 1. aankhaaimaa Yeshukao jhajhalakao, manaaimaa unaaikao samajhanaa (2)
2. maile ta Yeshulaaee bairasaechhau, samajhanauhaosa‌ Yeshu malaaee (2)
3. haamaee sabaai jaanaechhaaun sawaraga daeshamaa sadhaainlaaee (2)
saanao charaa, saanao charaa raukhamaa basaechha
maeeṭhao-maeeṭhao, baolaeelae gaeeta saunaaundaaichha
(e saanao naanaee) (2) taimaee kae garadaaichhaau ?
(Yeshukao prema) (2) jao ma gaaundaaichhau .
pakakaai ekajanaa pauḍakao maanaisa thaie, pauḍakao maanaisa thaie unaee
unaee euṭaa raudaraakaṣhakao raupamaa chaḍhae, parabhaulaaee naerana bhanaee
jaba maukataidaataa tyo baaṭao bhaera gara, unalae raukhamaathai haerae,
jakakaai tala orala, ma taimarao gharamaa aauna chaahaanachhau

songs.title: aagao khanayounauhaosa‌ maerao jaeewanamaa Yeshu pawaitara aatamaakao
lyrics: aagao khanayounauhaosa‌ maerao jaeewanamaa Yeshu pawaitara aatamaakao
aagao jalaaunauhaosa‌ maerao jaeewanamaa Yeshu pawaitara aatamaakao
chaisaopanalaaee haṭaaunauhaosa‌ alachhaepanalaaee haṭaaunauhaosa‌ (2)
pawaitara aatamaalae...
aagao khanayounau haosa‌ maerao jaeewanamaa Yeshu
pawaitara aatamaakao...

songs.title: aachhauchhauchhau bhayao nai jaaड़o sawara sabaailae khaolaaun saaharao
lyrics: kao. aachhauchhauchhau bhayao nai jaaड़o, sawara sabaailae khaolaaun saaharao (2)
haundaaina kasaailaaee gaauna gaaharao, (janamae gaoṭhamaa parabhau haamarao) (2) .
1. garaeeba gaoṭhaalaa darashanamaa aae, Yeshulaaee bhaeṭaee audhaee ramaae (2)
paapa kaṣhamaa jaeewana paae (2), sabaaikao lagi naai maukataidaana layoe (2)
2. sawaragalaaee chhaड़ee jagamaa aae, rauchaae garaeeba gaaeekao gaoṭha naai (2)
daienana‌ kaailae ṭhaaun tapaaeemlaaee (2), aaphanaailae latayoe hajauralaaee (2)

songs.title: aaja kaa daina yahaowaa nae banaayo haai
lyrics: kao. aaja kaa daina yahaowaa nae banaayo haai
hama isamaem aananadaita hao, aananadaita ho (2)
1. aataa haoon taerae paasa, maujhakao haai taujhasae aasa
maujhakao kabaoola karalae, paapaom sae shaudadha kara dae .
2. jaeewana sae jayaotai jalae, jaeewana yaha aisaa banae
jayaotai maem chala hama sakae, dauaa haai taujhae yahaee .
3. parabhau kaee mahaimaa mailae, chaahae ho maeraa apamaana
waha baढ़e maaim ghaṭaoom, rahae isaee kaa dhayona .
4. satautai parashamsaa karae, kayaom na kauchha haotaa rahae
usakao hama bhaatae rahae, chaahae jahaan bhaye rahae .

songs.title: aaja khaushaee chhau ma (2) Yeshukao lagi khaushaee chhau ma
lyrics: aaja khaushaee chhau ma (2)
Yeshukao lagi khaushaee chhau ma
uhaanlae maerao paapalaaee dhaunau bhao
yasakaaraṇa khaushaee chhau ma
1. aaja upharainachhau ma (2)
Yeshukao lagi upharainachhau ma
uhaanlae maerao paapalaaee dhaunau bhao
yasakaaraṇa upharainachhau ma (2)
2. aaja gaauchhau ma (2)
3. aaja naanchachhau ma (2)
4. aaja ramaaunchhau ma (2)
5. aaja karaaunchhau ma (2)

songs.title: aaja kharaeeṣhaṭakao janama bhayao baethalaehaemakao gaaunmaa (2)
lyrics: kao. aaja kharaeeṣhaṭakao janama bhayao baethalaehaemakao gaaunmaa (2)
1. jayaotaiṣhaeeharaoolae taaraalaaee haeraee (2)
garaeeba gharamaa gaee aड़ie (2), khaushaee bhaye bhaeṭaee chaढ़ae .
2. eeshawarakao pautara parabhau Yeshu kharaeeṣhaṭa (2)
gaaeekao gaoṭhamaa awataara laiee aae (2), jayajayakaara unakaai gaaaun .
3. naidaraalaaee tayogaee uṭha, banadhau-bhaai (2)
jaaaun haamaee sabaai Yeshukahaan (2) jayajayakaara gaaundaai jaaaun .

songs.title: aaja jaiiuṭhae Yeshu naai ha... lalaelaooyoha
lyrics: 1. aaja jaiiuṭhae Yeshu naai, ha... lalaelaooyoha,
haamarao baड़a dainamaa, jaya ha... lalaelaooyoha,
jasalae karaoosamaa daie paraaṇa, ha... lalaelaooyoha,
haamarao lagi garae taraaṇa, ha... lalaelaooyoha .
2. gaaaun dhanayawaadakao gaana, ha... lalaelaooyoha,
sawaragakao raaja kharaeeṣhaṭakao maana, ha... lalaelaooyoha,
karaoosa chaihaanakao baokae bhaara, ha... lalaelaooyoha,
unakao baaṭao chha udadhaara, ha... lalaelaooyoha .
3. sahae unalae dauhkha naai, ha... lalaelaooyoha,
malaaee maukatai dainalaaee, ha... lalaelaooyoha,
aba sawaragamaa raajaa bhaye, ha... lalaelaooyoha,
daootalae gaaunchhana‌ unakao, jaya ha... lalaelaooyoha .

songs.title: aaja bhaolai bharaai bhanadaai jaeewana yahaan asataaunchha
lyrics: kao. aaja bhaolai bharaai bhanadaai jaeewana yahaan asataaunchha
kharaeeṣhaṭalaaee maayo garanae maanachhae maृtayau paaraee udaaunchha .
1. maerao haृdayakao maoorataiharaoolaaee kharaeeṣhaṭa haṭaai bakasaiyaosa‌
kharaeeṣhaṭa maerao raajaa maalaika yahaan raaja garaibakasaiyaosa‌,
waigata dainaharaoo wayarathaai gaumaaen waratamaana chaड़aunchhau
Yeshukao premakao kahaanaee sabalaaee gaeetabaaṭa saunaaunchhau .
2. waishawamaa sadhaain ma basanae haoina baṭauwaa maatara haun
yao baaṭao phaerai ma hainḍanae chhaaina eka taeerathayotaraee haun
waijayaee kharaeeṣhaṭakao shakatailae sabaai karatawaya saulajhaaunchhau
samapaooraṇa kaaraya shaeṣha bhaepachhai ma sawadaesha phairanaechhau .

songs.title: aaja maeraa bhaeḍaaharau kataa laagayao
lyrics: aaja maeraa bhaeḍaaharau (kataa laagayao) (2)
khaojaee daeoona saathaeeharau maayo laagayao (2)
sanataanababae, anaṭhaanababae, unanasaya euṭaa khaoee
bhaokakaai chha haolaa, payosaee chha haolaa
laḍayao kaee kataai, chaoṭa laagayao haolaa (2)
premalae premaeelaaee aawaaja daiyao... mayo...

songs.title: aaja maile jaosha paaen Yeshukao waradaana paaen
lyrics: kao. aaja maile jaosha paaen Yeshukao waradaana paaen
sawaraga chhaड़ee aae, mahaimaa parakaṭa garae
1. sausata jaeewana thaiyao haृdaya jagaaidaie
bhaulairahaekaalaaee baaṭao wachanakao daie .
2. sawaragaeeya jayaotai mamaa parakaashaita bhayao
yoda gara aba dharataee naai sawaraga bhayao .
3. baolaaunchhana‌ haamaeelaaee Yeshu aaphanao chhaeumaa
chhaड़na samsaarakao maoha sataya prem kalawaraeemaa .

songs.title: aaja raatabharai sawaragadaoota aaoona‌
lyrics: aaja raatabharai sawaragadaoota aaoona‌,
pakhaeṭaa phaailaaee rakaṣhaka bhairahaoona‌ .

songs.title: aaja haamaee saanaa chhaaun bhaolai ṭhaoolaa haunae chhaaun
lyrics: 1. aaja haamaee saanaa chhaaun bhaolai ṭhaoolaa haunae chhaaun
haamaee ṭhaoolaa bhaera, maisainaraee haunae chhaaun (2)
2. aaja baaibala paढ़nauchha, kharaeeṣhaṭamaa aghai baढ़nauchha
ṭaaढ़a ṭaaढ़a gaera, wachanalaaee saunaaunauchha (2)
3. saukha dau:kha sahanauchha, aaphanao bhaaraee baokanauchha
agauwaa bhaera, kharaeeṣhaṭakao bagaala haeranauchha (2)

songs.title: aaja haamarao udadhaara garae kalawaraeemaa jhauṇaḍainae Yeshulae
lyrics: kao. aaja haamarao udadhaara garae, kalawaraeemaa jhauṇaḍainae Yeshulae
aaja haamarao parabhau bananau bhao, maृtayaudaekhai baaurainae kharaeeṣhaṭa Yeshu .
1. haimaalakao ṭaapaooharaoo gaunyajaee uṭhachhana‌
samaunadarakao chhaalaharaoo naanchadaai gaaunchhana‌
sawaragakao ḍhaokaa khaolaera aawaaja dainachhana‌ haamaeelaaee
haamarao bainataeelaaee saunanae Yeshu aaja jaeewaita chhana‌ .
2. pahaaड़ee paakhaamaa jhaulakayao ghaama
jayaotai Yeshu anadhaerao jagatamaa
sawaragakao ḍhaokaa khaolaera sahaaraa dainachhana‌ haamaeelaaee
haamarao baaṭao bananae Yeshu aaja jaeewaita chhana‌ .

songs.title: aaja haamarao parabhau Yeshu janamae baethalaehaema shaharamaa
lyrics: kao. aaja haamarao parabhau Yeshu janamae baethalaehaema shaharamaa
maukatai chha sabalaaee unaaimaa maatara gaihaera tyo ṭhaaunmaa
1. paramaeshawarakao tyo katarao dayo haamaeemaa hauna gao’
jasakao kaaraṇa pautara Yeshu (2) gaoṭhaaimaa janama lainaubhao’
tana-mana-dhana saba bhaeṭaee chaढ़aundaai (2)
unakaai charaṇamaa aaoon (2)
2. paramaeshawarakao tyo katarao dayo haamaeemaa hauna gao’
jayajayakaara gaaundaai bhaeṭaee chaढ़aundaai (2)
unakaai charaṇamaa aaoon (2)
janama laieekana aae haamaeemaa (2)
jayajayakaara unakaai gaaoon (2)

songs.title: aajakao daina (2) (unalae sairajaekaa) (2)
lyrics: (aajakao daina) (2), (unalae sairajaekaa) (2)
ramaaundaai jaaoon, khaushaee manaaoon, (ra aananada garaaun) (2)
aajakao daina unalae sairajaekaa, ramaaundaai jaaoon ra khausaee manaaoon
(aajakao daina) (2), unalae sairajaekaa

songs.title: aajakao daina khaushaee manaaaun sabaailae
lyrics: 1. aajakao daina khaushaee manaaaun sabaailae
haamarao parabhau maukataidaataa phaerai jaiiuṭhae (2)
aajakao daina bharaiyaosa‌ khaushaeelae samsaara (2)
haamarao parabhau maukataidaataa phaerai jaiiuṭhae (2)
2. karaoosamaa haamaraolaagai daie kharaeeṣhaṭalae paraaṇa
aaphanao ragatakao baaṭaolae kainae haamarao paraaṇa (2)
kharaeeṣhaṭalaaee dhanyawad chaढ़aaun manalae jayajaya gaaaun (2)
aaphanaa ragatakao baaṭaolae kainae haamarao paraaṇa (2)
3. jaananauparachha manamaa haamaee sabaailae
haamaee panai baauraee uṭha‌chhaaun anatakao dainamaa (2)
uhailae parabhau Yeshu chhana‌, sadaa rahanachhana‌ (2)
haamaee panai baauraee uṭhachhaaun, anatakao dainamaa (2)
4. haamaee paapaeelaaee unalae daie saukha,
dhanaya eeshawarakaa pautara sawaragakao raajaalaaee (2)
parabhau aaunchhana‌ eka daina tayora basa sadaa (2)
dhanaya eeshawarakaa pautara sawaragakao raajaalaaee (2)

songs.title: aajakao daina khaushaeekao daina parashamsaa garaau sabaailae
lyrics: kao. aajakao daina khaushaeekao daina parashamsaa garaau sabaailae
mailaeejhaulaee sabaailae jaya (2) kaara garaau parabhaukao
1. parabhaukao aashaisha haamaeemaa haosa‌ aatamaamaa baḍadaai jaao
parabhaukao kaृpaa haamaeemaa bhao uhaankao kaama dhaairaai haosa‌ (2)
2. ekataakao jaeewana laiera aghai baḍaau aatamaamaa (2)
parabhaulae haamaeelaaee saatha dainachhana‌ uhaankao mahaimaa garanalaaee (2)

songs.title: aajakao daina daekhai maerao jainadagaeelaaee Yeshumaa
lyrics: aajakao daina daekhai
maerao jainadagaeelaaee Yeshumaa daieehaalachhau
dauee dainae jainadagaeemaa
maerao parabhau Yeshu samahaalaee daeu malaaee
1. maeraai naimatai katai raoyou maeraai khaataira sawaraga tayogayou
haatapaaumaa kaanṭaee ṭhaokaee maerao jainadagaeelaaee bachaayou
taimaee naai maerao sahaaraa (2)
2. samsaarakao janyajaalabaaṭa ṭaaḍhaa ṭaaḍhaa laaijaau malaaee (2)
jainadagaeekao haraeka kadamamaa baisataaraai ḍaorayou parabhau malaaee (2)
taimaee naai maerao sahaaraa (2)

songs.title: aajakao daina mahaimaakao daina (2) mahaimaa chaḍhaaunchhau
lyrics: kao. aajakao daina mahaimaakao daina (2)
mahaimaa chaḍhaaunchhau parabhau tapaaeemlaaee (2)
aajakao daina mahaimaakao daina (2)
1. aakaashakaa chanadara saooraya taaraaharaoolae (2) haawaa, bataasa ra baadala baraṣhaaharaoolae (2)
mahaimaa chaḍhaaunchhana‌ parabhau tapaaeemlaaee (2) Yeshukao naaunmaa mahaimaa parabhau (2)
2. nadaee, samaudara saagara jharanaaharaoolae (2) jala thalamaa bhaekaa paraaṇaeeharaoolae (2)
mahaimaa chaḍhaaunchhana‌ parabhau tapaaeemlaaee (2) Yeshukao naaunmaa mahaimaa parabhau (2) .
3. haimaala ra pahaaḍa parawata maaidaanaharaoolae (2) hae saaraa paृthawaeekaa maanaisaharaoo hao, (2)
aaphanao saृṣhaṭaikarataakao mahaimaa gara (2) Yeshukao naaunmaa mahaimaa parabhau (2)

songs.title: aajakao waalaka bhaolaikao karaṇadhaara
lyrics: aajakao waalaka bhaolaikao karaṇadhaara
satayataamaa ḍaorayounau tapaaeem haamarao ho yao
jaimamaewaara
aaoo uṭhaaum saikaaum saikaaunalaaee
yao bhaoomai kharaeeṣhaṭamaa jaitanalaaee
haamarao paaurakha dainau chha yanaan
baala aatamaa bachaaunalaaee
parakaasha banai udaaunaechhana‌
