kharaeeṣhaṭakao jayaotai phaailaaunaechhana‌ .
aaoo raopaaum maayo garaau
bhaolaee phaoola jhaai yaee phaoolalae chhana‌ (2)
daeshalaaee saunadara wanaaunae chhana‌
kharaeeṣhaṭakao raajaya layounae chhana‌
aaoo uṭhaaum saikaaum saikaaunalaaee (2)
yao bhaoomai kharaeeṣhaṭamaa jaitanalaaee (2)

songs.title: aajakao saanjha aajakao saanjha parabhau Yeshu janamae
lyrics: kao. aajakao saanjha, aajakao saanjha parabhau Yeshu janamae
dharataee halayao, yao sausanadaesha laiee haamaee aayou
1. thaiena kaohaee samsaaramaa aaja maukatai dainae paapaeelaaee (2)
aaja janamae jaeewanadaataa maukatai daina haamaeelaaee (2)
tayasaailae garahaṇa gara uhaankao sausaanadaesha .
2. mahala haoina gaoṭhamaa janamae, kaokarao haoina ḍaunड़aimaa sautae (2)
saukha haoina, dauhkha naai sahae, khaushaee haoina kaṣhaṭa naai raojae, baalaka satakaara (2)
tayasaailae aaoo, sauna uhaankao sausanadaesha .

songs.title: aajakao haamaee kaopailaa
lyrics: aajakao haamaee kaopailaa
bhaolaikao phaoola haau
payorao saathaee Yeshu sangaai
shamaaundaai phaoolanae chhaaum
payorao saathaee Yeshu sangaai
ramaaundaai phaoolanae chhaaum
kahailae haiḍachhaaum mausakauraaudaai
khaushaee baaḍadaai Yeshusanga (2)
katai maayo garachhana sadhaai
taimaee haamaee sabaailaaee (2)
aaoo haai maeraa saathaee ho
Yeshukao nyano kaakhaaimaa (2)
aananada chha haai shaanatai chha
uhaankao payorao raajayamaa (2)

songs.title: aajanyo garanauhaosa‌ premakao ऋṇaee chhau jaana tayora chhau
lyrics: kao. aajanyo garanauhaosa‌, premakao ऋṇaee chhau, jaana tayora chhau .
1. aansau waidhawaakao pauchhanalaaee, saatha anaathakao haunalaaee daृṣhaṭai daina anadhaa sabaailaaee
2. chhauna bhaanchaekao sabaailaaee, phaukaauna banadaee sabaailaaee sausamaachaara sabalaaee saunaaunalaaee .

songs.title: aatamaa parabhaukaa premaee aatamaa parabhaukaa
lyrics: kao. aatamaa parabhaukaa- premaee aatamaa parabhaukaa
abhaye taoo aajaa- hamaarae baeecha maem
apanaee aashaeeṣha unṇaḍaela . (2)
1. parabhau kae saeenae sae maaim shaira rakhakara aaraama paaun (2)
payosaa haoon maaim taerae paratai payora dailaa maujhae aa . (2)
2. aatamaa kae waradaanaom sae taृpata kara dae maujhae (2)
jaaga uṭhaoon maaim jalanae paaoon jayaotai chamakaa maujha maem . (2)

songs.title: aatamaa bagaekao chha (4) paenaṭaikaosakao
lyrics: 1. aatamaa bagaekao chha (4)
paenaṭaikaosakao dainamaa jhaaim aatamaa bagaekao chha (2)
2. langagaaḍaa haiḍanae chha (4)
paenataikaosakao dainamaa jhaaim langagaaḍaa haiḍanae chha (2)
3. baairaalae saunanaechha (4)
paenataikaosakao dainamaa jhaaim baairaalae saunanaechha (2)
4. anadhaolae daekhanae chha (4)
paenataikaosakao dainamaa jhaaim anadhaolae daekhanae chha (2)
5. gaumgaolae baolanae chha (4)
paenataikaosakao dainamaa jhaaim gaumgaolae baolanae chha (2)
6. chamgaaee paaekao chha (4)
paenataikaosakao dainamaa jhaaim chamgaaee paaekao chha (2)

songs.title: aatamaa maṇaḍalaataa haai (3) paृthawaee para wachana paooraa karataa haai
lyrics: aatamaa maṇaḍalaataa haai (3) paृthawaee para
wachana paooraa karataa haai hamanae jao kauchha saunaa haai
aatamaa maṇaḍalaataa haai paृthawaee para ॥

songs.title: aatamaa maṇaḍaalaataa pawaitara aatamaa maṇaḍalaataa (2)
lyrics: kao. aatamaa maṇaḍaalaataa, pawaitara aatamaa maṇaḍalaataa (2)
paenaṭakausata kae daina samaana, aatamaa maṇaḍalaataa (2)
1. amdhae daekhatae haai (2) Yeshu masaeeha kae naama sae amdhae daekhatae haai . (2)
2. baharae saunatae haai (2) Yeshu masaeeha kae naama sae baharae saunatae haai . (2)
3. lamgaड़e chalatae haai (2) Yeshu masaeeha kae naama sae lamgaड़e chalatae haai . (2)
4. paapaee kaṣhamaa paatae haai (2) Yeshu masaeeha kae naama sae paapaee kaṣhamaa paatae ॥ (2)

songs.title: aatamaakao aagao baladaaichha Yeshulae haamaeelaaee chhaunauhaudaaichha
lyrics: aatamaakao aagao baladaaichha
Yeshulae haamaeelaaee chhaunauhaudaaichha
parataapaee shakataiharau haamaeemaa saradaaichha
haamarao baojhaharau halaukaa haun daaichha
Yeshukao ragatakao thaopaa chauhaudaaichha
paapakaa taee khaoṭaharau pauchhainadaaichha
bhawaiṣhayabaaṇaeeharau pauraa haundaaichha
haamaeelaaee laina Yeshu aaunau haundaaichha
Yeshu jayaotai jaeewanakao raoṭai
Yeshu tapaaee maalaika
Yeshu tapaaee jaeewanakao paanaee
taृṣhaṇaa maeṭaaee dainae
(Yeshu Yeshu) (7)
chaihaanalaaee taoḍaee maृtayaulaaee jaeetai
haamaeemaa aaunaubhao sadhaai saatha rahanaubhao

songs.title: aatamaamaa shaanatai dhairaja dharaee parakhaau haai Yeshulaaee
lyrics: kao. (aatamaamaa shaanatai dhairaja dharaee parakhaau haai Yeshulaaee
baadalamaathai aaunaechhana‌ Yeshu
taimaeelaaee lainalaaee (hao,hao) haamaeelaaee lainalaaee) (2)
1. (baaṭao sataya ra jaeewana parabhau Yeshu kharaeeṣhaṭa hauna‌
bachaau aatamaa aaja taimaeelae hao..hao.. sawaraga jaanalaaee) (2)
2. (anadhakaarakao tyo samsaaramaa napara hae, maeraa daajau-bhaai,
anaugarahakao ḍhaokaa khaulaa chha
taimaeelaaee bachaaunalaaee hao..hao.. haamaeelaaee bachaaunalaaee) (2)

songs.title: aatamaamaa shaanatai dhaeeraja dharaee parakhaaum haai Yeshulaaee
lyrics: kao. (aatamaamaa shaanatai dhaeeraja dharaee parakhaaum haai Yeshulaaee
baadalamaathai aaunaechhana‌ Yeshu
taimaeelaaee lainalaaee (hao, hao) haamaeelaaee lainalaaee) (2)
1. (baaṭao, sataya ra jaeewana parabhau Yeshu kharaeeṣhaṭa hauna‌
bachaaoo aatamaa aaja taimaeelae (hao, hao) sawaraga jaanalaaee) (2)
2. (anadhakaarakao tyo samsaaramaa napara hae maeraa daajau-bhaai
anaugarahakao ḍhaokaa khaulaa chha
taimaeelaaee bachaaunalaaee (hao, hao) haamaeelaaee bachaaunalaaee) (2)

songs.title: aatamaika daauḍa laamao chha tara dhaeerajasaatha dagauraera
lyrics: kao. aatamaika daauḍa laamao chha, tara dhaeerajasaatha dagauraera
ananata maeeraasa ra inaamalaaee, tayora haooo paraapata garanalaaee
1. baadhaa dainachha pala-palamaa naashawaana‌ yao maaṭaokao sharairalae (2)
jaagao rahaee paraarathanaa garae jayawanata taimaee naishachaya bananaechhaau . (2)
2. alamalaaunae ṭanaṭaa bhaaralaaee panasaaera dagauraenaau bhanae (2)
dauragama haunachha daauḍa daauḍanaalaaee ra daaiḍamaa asaphala bananaechhaau . (2)
3. satayataakao aatamaika paeṭaee dhaaramaikataakao jhailama pahairaee (2)
maelakao samaachaara parachaara garadaai bishwaskao ḍhaala laiee aghai baḍhaau . (2)
4. udadhaarakao daृḍha ṭaopa pahairaee wachanaraupaee tarawaara bhairaee (2)
paraarathanaa aatamaamaa naitaya garadaai ajaeya yaodadhaajhaaim waijayaee banaaum . (2)
5. kharaeeṣhaṭa Yeshu hauna‌ aatamaika naishaana aatamaika laeeka ho wachana unakao (2)
yasaaimaa daauḍaee inaama paauna samyamaee banaee daauḍamaa jaitaaum . (2)

songs.title: aatamaikaee daiyao naibhadaaina samsaarakao bataasa hauraeelae
lyrics: kao. aatamaikaee daiyao naibhadaaina samsaarakao bataasa hauraeelae,
aatamaikaee haamaee banadaainaaun parabhaukao premakao daooraeelae (2)
1. anadhakaarakao aagao baladaaichha, anadhakaarakao paanaee paradaaichha
jaagaau haai jayaotaikao sanataana banaee sahaayaka Yeshu chhandaaichhaaun .
2. jhaooṭao saakaṣha dhaeraai aaundaaichha, bishwaseekao jaeewana kadamamaa
baढ़aun haai jayaotaikao sanataana banaee sahaayaka pawaitara aatamaa chhana‌ .

songs.title: aadara kae yaogaya waha mahaimaa kae yaogaya waha
lyrics: aadara kae yaogaya waha mahaimaa kae yaogaya waha
satautai kai yaogaya waha haaim (2)
Yeshu kai lahau sae shaudadhataa kaiyo haai maujhae
aatamaakao sawatanatara kaiyo haai . (2)

songs.title: aadara kae yaogaya waha mahaimaa kae yaogaya waha
lyrics: aadara kae yaogaya waha, mahaimaa kae yaogaya waha
satautai kae yaogaya haai waha, Yeshu kae lahaun sae chhauड़ayo maujhae
aatamaa kaee aajaadaee daee, aadara kae yaogaya waha .

songs.title: aadara mahaimaa parashamsaa garanalaaee ḍaorayounauhawasa‌ parabhau
lyrics: aadara, mahaimaa, parashamsaa garanalaaee ḍaorayounauhawasa‌, parabhau, harapala malaaee
tapaaeemkao upasathaitaibhaitara sadhaain magana haunalaaee, haosananaa jaya hallelujah (4)
tapaaeemkao upasathaitaibhaitara sadhaain magana haunaalaaee .

songs.title: aadara ra mahaimaa ra (jaya tapaaeemlaaee haosa‌) (3)
lyrics: aadara ra mahaimaa ra (jaya tapaaeemlaaee haosa‌) (3)
aadara ra mahaimaa ra jaya tapaaeemlaaee haosa‌
saimhaasanamaa tapaaeemlaaee satautai, satautai sabaailae bhanauna‌ satautai
satautai, satautai saimhaasanamaa tapaaeemlaaee
halalaelaooyoha, halalaelaooyoha, hallelujah (2)
haa... haa... haa... hallelujah (2)
hallelujah (4) aamaina‌, hallelujah aamaina‌ (5)

songs.title: aadai aura amta taoo haee haai alaphaa aura omaegaa taoo haee haai
lyrics: 1. aadai aura amta taoo haee haai, alaphaa aura omaegaa taoo haee haai
daootaom kaee satautai bhaye taoo haee haai, baudadhai aura saba janyona taoo haee haai
kao. Yeshu taoo mahaana haai, Yeshu taoo achachhaa haai
Yeshu taoo jainadaa haai, Yeshu taoo dhanaya haai .
2. jaeewana bharaa paapa sae maeraa, jaga anadhaeraa aura ashaudadha saaraa
maerae paapaom sae bachaanae kao, maerae laie jaeewana daiyo haai .
3. saarae gaunaahagaaraom kae laie, apanaa khaoona bahaayo Yeshu nae
khaaee kaoड़o kaee maara bhaye, dao salaeeba para usanae apanaee jaana .
4. waayadaa kaiyo haai taoo nae, waayadaa taoo karataa haai paooraa
waayadae kae laie aatae haaim, barakataom kaee waaraisha aba uṇaḍaela .
5. nayoya karanae aanae waalaa haai, nayo kae saatha raaja karanae kao
dharamaiyaom kao laekara nayoya sae, saimhaasana para raaja karaegaa .

songs.title: aadai ra anata ra jagatakao jayaotai charaṇamaa tapaaeemkao
lyrics: 1. aadai ra anata ra jagatakao jayaotai charaṇamaa tapaaeemkao aaundachhaaun (2)
hallelujah gaaundaai, satautai saunaaundaai shaira naihauraaundachhaaun .
2. alaphaa-omaegaa ra jaeewanakao raoṭaee tapaaeemmaa jaeewana paaundachhaaun (2)
hallelujah gaaundaai, hat pasaarachhaau, aashaeerawaada paaundachhaaun .
3. ragatalae dhaoera garanaosa‌ pawaitara, paoorao pawaitarataa dainauhaosa‌ (2)
hallelujah gaaundaai, aashaa raakhadaai, tapaaeemkahaan aaundachhaaun .
4. pawaitara aatamaakao daana daiee haamaeelaaee, parataijanyo paoorao garanauhaosa‌ (2)
hallelujah gaaundaai, jayajayakaara garadaai, khaushaeelae bharaijaaaun .
5. daulahaa hauna‌ haamaraa payoraa kharaeeṣhaṭa Yeshu, chhaiṭaṭaai lainalaaee aaunaechhana‌ . (2)
hallelujah gaaundaai, khaushaee manaaunchhaaun, sawaragamaa laanaechhana‌ .
6. bharaidainaosa‌ premalae yao haamarao manalaaee ra bainataee tapaaeemlaaee garanaechhaaun (2)
hallelujah gaaundaai, haamarao mana jagaaaun yao haamaee maagadachhaaun .

songs.title: aadaimaa jauna parakaara andhayorao ra ujaara paaranaubhayao naasha
lyrics: 1. aadaimaa jauna parakaara andhayorao ra ujaara paaranaubhayao naasha, aba tayasaai, hae eeshawara
sausamaachaarakao ghaama napaugaekao saba sathaana ujayolaai haosa‌ .
2. laoka aaunaubhao’ tapaaeem saba janakao lagi layoee lagaaee parakaasha
raogaee baisaeka paaraee, anadhaolaaee parakaasha garaaee, hae kharaeeṣhaṭa aba sabaailaaee ujayolaai haosa‌ .
3. hae pawaitara aatamaa jaiyounae paraewaa waega uड़nauhaosa‌
garaee bhaanड़o ghaumaaee anaugaraha daana khanayoee, andhayorao garanau kaṣhaya ujayolaai haosa‌ .
4. hae paitaa, pautara, aatamaa, dhanaya taraieka mahaa taraaṇa paooraṇa haosa‌
saagarajhaain ho apaara, jagata‌kaa daishaai chaara sachayounalaaee samsaara ujayolaai haosa‌ .

songs.title: aadaimaa thaie paramaeshawara saba thaoka chha dainamaa sairajae
lyrics: 1. aadaimaa thaie paramaeshawara, saba thaoka chha dainamaa sairajae
saomabaara banaae, ujayolao, mamgalabaara aakaasha sairajae .
kao. (halalaelaooyoha) (3) yohawae, gaaoo hallelujah yohawae
2. baudhabaara wanasapatai, khaanaee, sairajae saagara ra bhaoomai
baihaeebaara ghaama, jaoona, taaraa, baadala, bajara, waraṣhaa, baijaulaee .
3. shaukarabaara saanaa-ṭhaoolaa janatau bagaihainड़nae saagaramaa
tayahaee daina uड़nae sabaai pakaṣhaee, chaeeladharai ra bhausaunaa .
4. shanaibaara dharataeemaathai hainड़nae wana-pashau ra gharaaiyo
sairajae maanaisa aaphanaai raoopamaa, daie adhaikaara saba thaoka .
5. chha dainamaa kaama bhao’ samaapata, saataaun daina baisaaunau bhao’
aaitabaara baisaaoo taimaee panai bhanaee saewaa gara maerao .
6. aadai-anata sarawashakataimaana‌ yohawae, raajaa sarawamahaana‌
nara-naaraee, baalaka, waृdadha gaaaun unakao satautaigaana .

songs.title: aananakao dhawanai parabhaulaaee saunaaoo uhaan satautai yaogaya chhana‌
lyrics: (aananakao aawaja parabhaulaaee saunaaoo uhaan satautai yaogaya chhana‌
aatamalae gaau taalaee bajaau parabhaukao satautai garaau) (2)
(yaogaya) (2) uhaan satautai yaogaya chhana‌
halalaelaooyoha, parabhaukao satautai gara

songs.title: aananada aananada aananada haai (2)
lyrics: 1. aananada, aananada, aananada haai (2) abadaee maohababata sae hamae prem kaiyo
apanaa baeṭaa hamaem banaa laiyo, yaha hamaaraa saaubhaagaya haai . (2)
haalalaelaooyoha sadaa gaayaemgae (2) hama parabhau Yeshu kae laie . (2)
2. aananada, aananada, aananada haai (2) aananada kae taela sae masasaa kaiyo haai (2)
pawaitara sathaana maem daakhaila hauaa, yaha hamaaraa saaubhaagaya haai . (2)
haalalaelaooyoha sadaa gaayaemgae (2) hama parabhau Yeshu kae laie . (2)
3. aananada, aananada, aananada haai (2) parabhau kaee satautai karanaa aananada haai (2)
parabhau kaee saewaa karaemgae sadaaa, yaha hamaaraa saaubhaagaya haai . (2)
haalalaelaooyoha sadaa gaayaemgae (2) hama parabhau Yeshu kae laie . (2)
4. aananada, aananada, aananada haai (2) parabhau kae aagamana kaee khaushaee haai (2)
lae jaayaemgae hamaem lalakaara kae saatha, yaha hamaaraa saaubhaagaya haai . (2)
haalalaelaooyoha sadaa gaayaemgae (2) hama parabhau Yeshu kae laie . (2)
5. aananada, aananada, aananada haai (2) saiyaona jalaala maem baasa karaemgae (2)
baapa kae daahainae baaiṭha jaayaemgae, yaha hamaaraa saaubhaagaya haai . (2)
haalalaelaooyoha sadaa gaayaemgae (2) hama parabhau Yeshu kae laie . (2)

songs.title: aananada aananada hae maerae Yeshukaee charaṇanao mae (7)
lyrics: kao. aananada (2) hae maerae Yeshukaee charaṇanao mae (7)
1. paapa maeraa kaṣhamaa kaiyo, sharaapa maeraa naikala gayo (2)
Yeshukaee lahau dawaaraa, Yeshukaee lahau dawaaraa
2. nai jaeewana Yeshu mae hae, ananata jaeekana Yeshu mae hae (2)
pawaitara aatamaa dawaaraa, pawaitara aatamaa dawaaraa

songs.title: aananada chhau ma aananada chhau Yeshukao upasathaitaimaa
lyrics: (aananada chhau ma aananada chhau Yeshukao upasathaitaimaa
khaushaee chhau ma khaushaee chhau Yeshukao upasathaitaimaa) (2)
(naachaee dainachhau naachaee dainachhau kamamara halalaaee hao... hao... hao...) (2)
aananada... upasathaitaimaa
(gaai dainachhau gaai dainachhau saora khaolaee hao... hao... hao...) (2)
(mahaimaa garachhau mahaimaa garachhau haृdaya khaolaee hao... hao... hao...) (2)
(baijaya haamarao baijaya haamarao baijaya aaja haamarao
sabaai shaaitaana khauṭaṭaa maunaee baijaya aaja haamarao
chamgaaee haamarao...

songs.title: aananada manaaaun haraṣha manaaaun
lyrics: kao. aananada manaaaun, haraṣha manaaaun,
saaraa daunaiyonlaaee sausamaachaara saunaaaun
1. uṭha daajayaoo-bhaai hao, haera taaraalaaee
Yeshujaeekao janama bhayao, uṭha, darashana garanalaaee .
2. uṭha daidaee-bahainaee, haera taaraalaaee
Yeshujaeekao janama bhayao, uṭha, darashana garanalaaee

songs.title: aananada manaayaem aao aananada manaayaem
lyrics: kao. aananada manaayaem aao aananada manaayaem
Yeshu raajaa maeraa ho gayo,
isa saृṣhaṭai kaa paalanahaara maerae haृyadakaa raajaa hauaa .
aananada haai parama aananada haai, kayo aha maeraa saaubhaagaya haai ?
isa saृṣhaṭai kaa paalanahaara, maerae haृdayakaa raajaa hauaa . (2)
1. maerae baalakapana sae usanae maujhae chauna laiyo
maaim thaa bhaṭakaa aura daoora ho gayo,
usakaee karaooṇaa nae phaira bhaye nahaeem chhaड़a
nayon jaeewana maujhae dae daiyo... aananada haai .
2. maaim banaa rahaungaa prem maem apanae parabhau kae
chaahae kaoee bhaye baadhaa paड़e, usakaee aajanyokao nahaeem bhaoolaoomgaa
jaba taka usakaa aanaa na hao.... aananada haai ॥

songs.title: aananada yahaee ho parabhaulaaee chainanau uhaankao ichachhaamaa
lyrics: 1. aananada yahaee ho - parabhaulaaee chainanau, uhaankao ichachhaamaa jaeewana jaiunau
paraiwaratana jaeewanamaa haunau, parabhau naai aananada ho .
kao. saanchao aananada, aansau jharae panai yasakao rahasaya, haृdayamaa Yeshu kharaeeṣhaṭa .
2. aananada yahaee ho - eka nayon saृṣhaṭai, Yeshu ra ma sadhaaim chhaaum najaeeka
uhaankao maukataimaa sahabhaagaee, parabhau naai aananada ho .
3. aananada yahaee ho - paapa kaṣhamaa paaunau, parabhaukao yaogaya chaalamaa jaiunau
sawaraga jaanae baaṭaomaa hainḍanau, (parabhau naai aananada hao) (3)

songs.title: aananada ra shaanatailae bharanaubhao haamaeelaaee (2)
lyrics: kao. aananada ra shaanatailae bharanaubhao haamaeelaaee (2)
sataya ra saanchao baaṭao daekhaaunau bhao haamaeelaaee (2)
1. ṭauṭaekao yao haृdayalaaee jaoḍanaubhao parabhaulae,
nairaashaadaekhai aashaamaa layounaubhao unaailae (2)
2. haamarao paapakao naimatai karashamaa paraaṇa dainau bhao Yeshulae
shaaitaanakao banadhanadaekhai haamaeelaaee chhauड़aunau bhao unaailae (2)

songs.title: aananada sae gaeeta gaao khaushaee sae hara bakata
lyrics: kao. aananada sae gaeeta gaao khaushaee sae hara bakata, mauhamabata sae bakhashaa hamaarae laiyae
kaitanaa baड़a phaja bagaaira kaoee haisaaba, raoja baraoja kaee jainadagaee maem .
1. ai maeraee aatamaa ai maerae daila, taoo kara apanae anaokhae masaeeha kaee satautai
chhalakataee haai maerae daila sae aasamaana kaee prem kaee nadaee...
haalalaelaooyoha, chhalakataee haai maerae daila sae, aasamaana kaee prem kaee nadaee .
2. rahamata sae maujhae aba taka na chhaड़a, aankha kaee pautalaee kaee taraha maeraee rakaṣhaa kaee
shaoka saba maiṭaa, aanshau bhaye paomchhae paoorae daila sae gaeeta gaao .
3. yadai waha naawa maem sae bhaye jaayae, baड़a taoophaana aakara kaitanaa ḍaraayae
hawaa aura lahara kao banada masaeeha, karakae haiphaajata sae rakhataa haai .
4. yaradana kao paara kaiyo usakaee taakata sae, yaraeehao kao gairaa daiyo usakaee satautai sae
Yeshu kae naama phataha mailaegaa, hamaeshaa hama jaitaemgae .
5. pawaitara laogaom kae dauhkha aura mausaibata, bahauta jaladaee khatama haonae waalae haai
gaatae haue hama maunatajaira rahaem Yeshu jaladaee aaegaa .

songs.title: aananadakaee aawaaja parabhaukao karao waha satautai yaogaya haai
lyrics: aananadakaee aawaaja parabhaukao karao,
waha satautai yaogaya haai .
aatamaa sae gaao taalaee bajaao,
parabhau kaee satautai karao ॥
yaogaya yaogaya waha satautai yaogaya haai
haalalaelaooyoha parabhau kaee satautai karao ॥

songs.title: aananadakao aawaaja parabhaumaa garaaum uhaan satautaikao yaogaya chha
lyrics: aananadakao aawaaja parabhaumaa garaaum uhaan satautaikao yaogaya chha
aatamaamaa gaaaum taalaee bajaaaum parabhaukao satautai garaaum
yaogaya yaogaya uhaan satautai yaogaya chha
hallelujah parabhaukao satautai garaaum - 2

songs.title: aaphaailaaee bairasaeeera aaundaaichhau ma taimaeekahaan
lyrics: aaphaailaaee bairasaeeera aaundaaichhau ma taimaeekahaan
samahaalaeedaeu jaeewana maerao angagaalaeedaeu jaeewana maerao
aaphaailaaee bairasaeeera...
1. paapaai paapakao samsaaramaa ḍaubairahaekao thaien ma (2)
anadhakaarakao bhaumaraeemaa (2) ghaumairahaekao thaien ma
jaeewanalaaee saumapaiera aaundaaichhau ma taimaeekahaan
pachhayoera jaiunalaaee aaundaaichhau ma taimaeekahaan
samahaalaeedaeu jaeewana...
2. lakaṣhaya wainaakao jaeewana maerao taimaee maai naai lakaṣhaya paaen (2)
thaakaisakaekao jaeewana maerao (2) taimaee maai naai waisharaama paaen
aaphaailaaee bairasaeeera...

songs.title: aaphanaai bhaoomaimaa naaṭaiera ma haun phayolaiekaau jaatai
lyrics: aaphanaai bhaoomaimaa naaṭaiera
ma haun phayolaiekaau jaatai
garaiwaikao wasatara chaaraaitaira ṭaalaielao jaatai
ma ta samahaalaie jaatai
saanjha waihaana bhaokaaekao waelaa
wachana khauwaaee paalaiekao jaatai
raoodaa haansadaa sadhaaim (Yeshu maerao saathaee)
ma ta samahaalaie jaatai
anadhao langagaḍao bhaekao waelaa
parabhaoolaenaai sawayama daopayoekao jaatai
kaृpaa Yeshukao bhaera (aaja ma sabaai bhanda maathaee)

songs.title: aaphanao karamalae haoina (Yeshu taimarao anaugarahalae) (2)
lyrics: aaphanao karamalae haoina (Yeshu taimarao anaugarahalae) (2)
aaphanao baudadhailae haoina (Yeshu taimarao anaugarahalae) (2)
aaphanao karamalae haoina...
1. kahaan sakathae ra paalana garana maile sabaai taee aajanyoharaulaaee
kahaan sakathae ra taimaeelaaee raijhaauna
galataee nagaraee jaeewana bharaeelaaee (2)
yasaailae Yeshu maile nasakadaa (2) taimaeelae aaphaai naai (pauraa garayou) (4)
2. kae naai thaiyao ra paapaee samsaaramaa jaiunae udaeshaya taimaee wainaa
kao naai thaiyao baaṭao daekhaaunae malaaee bachaaunae taimaee wainaa (2)
yasaailae Yeshu maile nasakadaa (2) taimaeelae aaphaai naai (pauraa garayou) (4)

songs.title: aamaina‌ (3) hallelujah aamaina‌ uhaankao parashamsaa
lyrics: aamaina‌ (3) halalaelaooyoha, aamaina‌, uhaankao parashamsaa .
parashamsaa (3) halalaelaooyoha, parashamsaa, uhaankao parashamsaa .

songs.title: aayo masaeeha daunaiyon maem taoo paapaeeyaom kao bachaanae kao
lyrics: kao. aayo masaeeha daunaiyon maem taoo paapaeeyaom kao bachaanae kao
laayae eemaana jao baeṭae para, karaegaa paapa isa daunaiyo kao .
1. daunaiyon gaunaaha maem ḍaooba rahaee thaee, saadaika gaumaraaha ho rahae thae .
chhaड़a aasamaana, banaa inasaana, mailaee najaata isa daunaiyon kao .
2. baaitalahama kae maaidaanaom maem gaड़raiyae raata sao rahae thae
saunaa pharaishataom kaee jauwaana, paaidaa hauaa kharaeeṣhaṭa naidhaana .
3. aalaimaom nae kaitaabaom sae paढ़ee paaidaaeesha kaee taphashaeela
chala daiyae waha bhaye oonṭao para, taerae hayota kaa paeechhaa kara .
4. samaudara saba laharaom para daunaiyo kaee saba jauwaanaom para
haai usakaa naama, haai usakaa kaama, saaraa jahaan laayae eemaana .

songs.title: aayo-aayo-aayo-aayo daehadhaaraee ho Yeshu aayo
lyrics: kao. aayo-aayo-aayo-aayo daehadhaaraee ho Yeshu aayo (2)
gaayo-gaayo-gaayo-gaayo daootaom nae sawaraga gaana gaayo .
1. udadhaaraka mailaegaa eka hamae kahae gayae thae yae wachana pahalae sae (2)
parabhautawa haogaee usakaee kamdhao para daehadhaaraee haee maanawa pautara kahalaayo .
2. waaibhawa patha shakatai saba wayaratha haai yahaan
ucha-naeecha jaata kayaom haai yahaan (2)
daeena haokae namara haokae chhaड़a sawaraga kao
mana raoopaee charanaee maem aaja waha aayo .
3. shaanataikaa raajakaumaara aa gayo haai
baढ़tae rahaegaee sadaa usakaee parabhautawa (2)
asaeemaita rahaegaee sadaa shaanatai usakaee
hamapara rahaegaee sadaa usakaee parabhautawa ॥

songs.title: aayae haai hama taerae charaṇaom maem laekara hama satautai
lyrics: aayae haai hama taerae charaṇaom maem, laekara hama satautai (2)
hama bachachae haaim paramapaitaa kaee baढ़naa haai hamaem bachanaom maem (2)
payorae masaeehaa aashaiṣha dae hamaem, aatamaa sae bhara dae hamaem (2) ॥
haalalaelaooyoha-haalalaelaooyoha-haalalaelaooyoha-haalalaelaooyoha (2)

songs.title: aayao karaisamasa phaerai pharakaera haansaau khaelaaun daajaubhaai hae
lyrics: kao. aayao karaisamasa phaerai pharakaera
(haansaau khaelaaun daajaubhaai hae daidaeebahainaee) (2)
maukataidaataakao janamamaa (2) gaunyajaaaun ḍaanड़akaanड़a (2)
1. maerao haraṣha taimarao aananada parabhaukao janamakao yahaee sanadaesha (2)
baaड़aun paratayaeka dainalaai, aaja maukataidaataakao janamamaa (2)
2. yahaee chaढ़aun yahaee baelaa maeeṭhao maausama haraṣhakao gaeeta (2)
gaaoon paratayaeka dailalae, aaja maukataidaataakao janamamaa (2)

songs.title: aayao ṭhaoolao parawa daiwasha yao haomarao parabhau maukataidaataa
lyrics: kao. aayao ṭhaoolao parawa daiwasha yao haomarao parabhau maukataidaataa
aananada manaaudaai haraṣha manaaudaai (2) hayopaee kharaeeṣhaṭamasa (3) sabaailaaee
1. daisamabara mahainaa chaisao tyo raatamaa ishaukao janama baetalaehaema gaaunmaa (2)
gaaee ra gaoraookao maajhamaa laḍairahaechhana paraalamaa hayopaee kharaeeṣhaṭamasa (3)
2. daaudakao shaharamaa haeraodakao paalaamaa Yeshukao janama baetalaehaema gaaunmaa (2)
maukataidaataa janamanau bhao namaunaa banaee gaoṭhaaimaa hayopaee kharaeeṣhaṭamasa (3)

songs.title: aayao rae aayao rae Yeshukao aagamana aayao rae
lyrics: (aayao rae aayao rae Yeshukao aagamana aayao rae) (2)
kao. (laau bhana taimaee) (2) tayoraee chhaau kae
laau bhana taimaee tayoraee chhaau kae
(aayao rae aayao rae Yeshukao aagamana aayao rae) (2)
1. (jaaga rahao taimaee sachaeta rahao
daushaṭakao banadanalaaee taoḍaee rahao) (2)
(sadhaaim sakataeeshaalaee hauwa taimaee
nairabala bhaye nabasa) (2)
2. (aatamaakao aagaolaaee naibana nadaeu
aatamaakao daiyaolaaee baujana nadaeu) (2)
(baudadhaee mataee jasataai hauwa taimaee
nairabaudadhaee bhaye nabasa) (2)

songs.title: aayao haai jhailaee ra mailaee kharaeeṣhaṭamasakao baelaa (2)
lyrics: kao. aayao haai jhailaee ra mailaee kharaeeṣhaṭamasakao baelaa (2)
aaidaeoo gaaidaeoo uhaanlaaee mahaimaa chaḍaau (2)
1. jaeewana chhahaai Yeshumaa maukatai chha haai Yeshumaa
haamaeelaaee jaeewana daina Yeshu aae yao dharataeemaa (2)
aauna bishwas gara taimaeelae paaunae chhaau jaeewana
2. aauna sagaai naachaau na aauna sagaai gaauna
Yeshukao janamadaina ho yao ramaauna sabaai mailaera (2)
aauna bishwas gara taimaeelae paaunae chhaau jaeewana

songs.title: aayoun aayoun aayoun haamaee parabhau naama saunaee haraṣhalae (2)
lyrics: kao. aayoun, aayoun, aayoun haamaee parabhau naama saunaee haraṣhalae (2)
1. aaoo daajayaoo-bhaai-bahainaee unakao satautai gaaunalaaee (2)
unaailae dainachhana‌ maukatai haamaeelaaee (2)
2. unaee hauna‌ haamaraa maukataidaataa, unaee hauna‌ jagakaa taaraṇahaara (2)
unaee hauna‌ haraeka khaanchaokao utatara (2)
3. ahailae chhana‌ unaee sawaragalaokamaa parama paitaakao daahainae haatamaa (2)
ekapalaṭa phaerai aaunaechhana‌ unaee (2)

songs.title: aaraadhanaa aaraadhanaa hallelujah parabhaukao aaraadhanaa (2)
lyrics: aaraadhanaa aaraadhanaa hallelujah parabhaukao aaraadhanaa (2)
changagaaee garanae parabhaukao aaraadhanaa jaeewana dainae parabhaukao aaraadhanaa
aaraadhanaa aaraadhanaa aaraadhanaa aaraadhanaa

songs.title: aaraadhanaa karaoongaa maaim paooraee mana sae
lyrics: aaraadhanaa karaoongaa maaim paooraee mana sae
jaeewana bhara maaim taeraee naihaaraoongaa maaim
sarawasawa haai arapaṇa taeraee saewaa maem
maaim haoon taeraa daasa ॥
parabhau maaim haoon taeraa daasa (3), taoo maeraa naatha,
taoo maerae haai sharaṇa, taoo maerae sanaatana,
taoo maerae paraiyatama, taoo maeraa naatha ॥

songs.title: aaraadhanaa karae aaraadhanaa upakaaraom laogaom usakaee yoda karae
lyrics: kao. aaraadhanaa, karae aaraadhanaa, upakaaraom laogaom usakaee yoda karae
hat uṭhaakae dhanyawad karae, unchae sawaraom sae usakaee satautai karae (2)
haalalaelaooyoha... (4) ...haalalaelaooyoha... (4)
1. Yeshu kae lahaun sae paapaom kao maukatai daee
Yeshu kae lahaun sae laogaom kao chamgaaee daee
samahaalataa maujhae upanaee laoka haataom sae (2)
maujhae laoee chainataa nahaeem .
2. aatamaa kae phalaom sae parabhau bharadae maujhae
prem kaee upakaaraom kaa shakatai dae dae maujhae (2)
haradama rahaungaa maaim usakae saeenae sae maaim (2)
usakaee charaṇaom maem satautai karaoongaa .

songs.title: aaraadhanaa garaaun unalaaee daṇaḍawata‌ garaaun
lyrics: aaraadhanaa garaaun, unalaaee daṇaḍawata‌ garaaun,
(satautaikao gaeeta gaaundaai, hallelujah bhanadaai halalaelaooyoha) (3) aamaina‌ .

songs.title: aaraadhanaa garachhau mahaana‌ parabhau tapaaeemjhaain chhaaina araoo
lyrics: (aaraadhanaa garachhau, mahaana‌ parabhau
tapaaeemjhaain chhaaina araoo
aaraadhanaa garachhau, shaanataikaa kaumaara
yasaai garana chaahanachhau, ma satautai garachhau
tapaaeem maerao dhaaramaikataa, aaraadhanaa garachhau mahaana‌ parabhau,
tapaaeemjhaain chhaaina araoo) (2)

songs.title: aaraadhanaa garachhau maerao jaeewanabharai (2)
lyrics: aaraadhanaa garachhau maerao jaeewanabharai (2)
hat uchaaladaai tapaaeemkao satautai gaaunchhau (2)
tapaaeemkao naaun dhanayakao bhanadachhau
haृdaya paraaṇasamaetalae ma gaaundachhau
Yeshu, aaraadhanaa garachhau (3)
maeraa eeshawara ra maerao raajaa .

songs.title: aaraadhanaa garachhaau tapaaeemtaira aankhaa uchaalada jaagaa
lyrics: kao. (aaraadhanaa garachhaaum tapaaeemtaira aankhaa uchaalada
jaagaa rahanachhaaum hara ghaḍaee paraarathanaamaa tapaaeemkao saatha rahadaai) (2)
1. (pawaitara banaaunauhaosa‌ parabhau haamaeelaaee sarawaangagaai, paृthawaeemaa sawaada dainae naunajhaaim) (2)
kaृtajanya bhaye jaeeunchhaau tapaaeemkao wachanamaa rahai sadhaaim
saewaa garachhaaum laganashaeela bhaye baadalamaa tapaaeemkao parataikaṣhaa garadaai) (2)
2. (saakaṣhaee banaaunauhaosa‌ parabhau haamaeelaaee jhalamalalaai
ḍaanḍaamaathai basaalaiekao shahara jhaaim) (2)

songs.title: aaraadhanaa garachhaau haamaee ekamaatara jaiwaita eeshawarakao
lyrics: kao. aaraadhanaa garachhaaum haamaee ekamaatara jaeewaita eeshawarakao
unaailaaee sadhaaim uchaalachhaaum haamaee satautai ra parashamsaa garadaai
(imamaanauela imamaanauela tapaaeem sabakaa paramaeshawara) (2)
1. (bharaosaa yaogaya paramaeshawaralaaee bhakataisaatha sadhaaim paujadachhaau
unakao yao mitho naamalaaee saaraa jaataimaa parachaarachhaaum) (2)
(unaee pawaitara chhana‌ shakataishaalai chhana‌ yasaailae haamaee uchaalaaum) (2)
2. (sawaragabaaṭa sadhaaim haamaeelaaee utatama kauraalae bharanauhaosa‌
tapaaeemkao abhaiṣhaeka taelalae haamarao yao shairamaa khanayounauhaosa‌) (2)
(taba bananae chhaaum yao daeshamaa tapaaeemkao jaiundao saakaṣhaee) (2)

songs.title: aaraadhanaa garachhaau haamaee haृdayakao dawara yao aaja khaolaee
lyrics: kao. aaraadhanaa garachhaau haamaee haृdayakao dawara yao aaja khaolaee
jaeewana saatha arapanachhaau haamaee Yeshukao payorao naaunkao aghai .
aaraadhanaa...
1. anatara manakao taara jhanakaai jaeewanasaajha aaja jagaai
aakaashasamamaai aawaaja uṭhaai jayajayakaara garachhaau haamaee
2. aakaashadaekhai dharataeemaa aai jaeewana gaeeta saunaaunae parambhaulaaee
maृtayaumaathai panai waijayaee haunae sawaragajaanae mahaimaita parabhaulaaee (2)

songs.title: aaraadhanaa garana haamaee sabaai bhaelaa bhaekaa chhaaun (2)
lyrics: 1. (aaraadhanaa garana haamaee sabaai bhaelaa bhaekaa chhaaun) (2)
aaraadhanaa garana haamaee sabaai bhaelaa bhaekaa chhaaun aaja,
aaraadhanaa garaaun Yeshulaaee .
2. (bairasaee aaphaai-aaphaailaaee, ekaagara haaun parabhau kharaeeṣhaṭamaa) (2)
bairasaee aaphaai-aaphaailaaee, ekaagara haaun parabhau kharaeeṣhaṭa Yeshumaa,
aaraadhanaa garaaun Yeshulaaee .
3. (unaee maerao dhaaramaikataa, rahanachha daृḍha bhaye sadaasarawadaa) (2)
unaee maerao dhaaramaikataa, rahanachha daृḍha bhaye sadaasarawadaa utamaa,
aaraadhanaa garaaun Yeshulaaee .
4. (pawaitara hat uchaalaee, garaaun unakao naaunkao baḍhaai) (2)
pawaitara hat uchaalaee, garaaun unakao naaunkao baḍhaai aaja,
aaraadhanaa garaaun Yeshulaaee .

songs.title: aaraadhanaa paramaeshawaralaaee aaraadhanaa raajaalaaee
lyrics: aaraadhanaa paramaeshawaralaaee, aaraadhanaa raajaalaaee,
raajaaharaookaa raajaa parabhauharaookaa, parabhau
haamaeelaaee bachaaunae, hallelujah (2) aaraadhanaa tapaaeemlaaee .

songs.title: aaraadhanaa mae chhauṭakaaraa (2) aaraadhanaa mae changagaaee (2)
lyrics: aaraadhanaa mae chhauṭakaaraa (2)
aaraadhanaa mae changagaaee (2)
sharaeera paraaṇa aatamaamae (2)
shaanatai aananada daetaa haai (2)
jaanasae bhai payoraa parabhau (2)
paraarathanaa karao aaraadhanaa karao (2)
wao achachhaa hae kaitanaa bhalaa hae (2)
chhauṭakaaraa paae hamaesaa
hallelujah chhauṭakaaraa paae hamaesaa
paraarathanaa karao nairanatara (2)
paraarathanaa karao waishawaa sae (2)
dharamaijana kao pararathanaa bishwaskao paraarathanaa sae (2)
khautalaee haai saarae banadhana (2)
paraarathanaa karao aaraadhanaa karao (2)
wao achachhaa hae kaitanaa bhalaa hae (2)
chhauṭakaaraa paae hamaesaa
hallelujah chhauṭakaaraa paae hamaesaa

songs.title: aaraadhanaa ho aaraadhanaa
lyrics: kao. aaraadhanaa ho aaraadhanaa
khaudaawanata Yeshu kaee aaraadhanaa (2)
1. shaanatai daataa kaee aaraadhanaa
maukatai daataa kaee aaraadhanaa (2)
2. pawaitara daila sae aaraadhanaa
premaee mana sae aaraadhanaa (2)
3. maeraee masaeeha kaee aaraadhanaa
jaeewana daataa kaee aaraadhanaa (2)
4. daootaom kae ho samga aaraadhanaa
satautai parashamsaa aaraadhanaa (2)

songs.title: aaraadhanaa haosa‌ aaraadhanaa parabhau Yeshukao aaraadhanaa (2)
lyrics: aaradhanaa haosa‌ aaradhanaa parabhau Yeshukao aaradhanaa (2)
haृdayamaraikao aaradhanaa pawaitara manadaekhai aaradhanaa (2)
aaradhanaa haosa‌...
saृṣhaṭaikarataakao aaradhanaa maukataidaataakao aaradhanaa

songs.title: aaraadhanaamaa aaraadhanaamaa gaaunchhau kharaeeṣhaṭakao satautai
lyrics: kao. aaraadhanaamaa, aaraadhanaamaa, gaaunchhau kharaeeṣhaṭakao satautai haृdayakao
tahadaekhai aaraadhanaamaa... hallelujah ! hallelujah !! gaaunchhau...
1. daृढ़ bishwas garaee darashanakao aasha raakhaee (2) jhaukaaunchhau shaira,
bhakataibharai gaaurawa, mahaimaa bhaeṭaeesarai chaढ़aunchhau parabhau,
paerai dhanayawaada, mauṭaubharai .
2. paapaharaoo maerao janamadaekhaikao kharaeeṣhaṭakao ragatalae shaudadha bhayao (2)
adharama maerao haृdayabharaikao kharaeeṣhaṭakao ragatalae ḍhaakaidaiyao .

songs.title: aaraadhanaakao gaeeta ho yao haृdaya khaolai gaanuchhau
lyrics: (aaraadhanaakao gaeeta ho yao haृdaya khaolai gaanuchhau
parashamsaakao samgaeeta ho yao haृdaya bhaeṭaee chaḍhaauchhau) (2)
jasalae maraoobhaoomaimaa manana jauṭaaunau bhao
(malaaee panai jauṭaaunae uhaan haunauhaunachha) (2)
(hao... haohao... haohaohao hao... haohao) (2)
kathaa haoina itaihaasa ho chaelaa matataee marakaoosakao
laookaa yaoohananaalae daiekaa tai gawaahaee sataya hao) (2)
jasaraee paancha raoṭaee ra dauee maachhaalae
(malaaee panai khauwaaunae Yeshu haunauhaunachha) (2)
(hao... haohao... haohaohao hao... haohao) (3)

songs.title: aawaaja uṭhaaemgae hama saaja bajaaemgae
lyrics: kao. aawaaja uṭhaaemgae, hama saaja bajaaemgae
haai Yeshu mahaana apanaa, yaha gaeeta saunaaemgae .
1. na daekha sakaa hamakao, taoo paapa kae saagara maem
aura banakae manauṣhaya aayo, aakaasha sae saagara maem
maukatai kaa taoo daataa haai, daunaiyon kao bataaemgae .... haai Yeshu .
2. samsaara kaee saunadarataa maem, yaha raoopa jao taeraa haee
ina chaanda saitaaraom maem, haai akasa jao taeraa haee
mahaimaa kaee taeraee baataem, hama saba kao bataaemgae .... haai Yeshu
3. daila taeraa khajanaa haai, eka paaka mauhababata kaa
thaaha paa na sakaa kaoee, saagara haai taoo ulaphata kaa
hama taeraee mauhababata sae, daila apanaa sajaayaemgae .... haai Yeshu ॥

songs.title: aawaaja daiee nairawataamaa malaaee baolaaunae kao ho ?
lyrics: kao. aawaaja daiee nairawataamaa malaaee baolaaunae kao ho ?
hara ghaड़ee, hara kaṣhaṇa baolaairahanae maerao payorao parabhau ho (2)
1. thaahaa tapaaee paapakao bhaaraee laiee hainड़irahanachhau ma
andhayorao pathamaa ṭhaokara khaandaa parabhaulaaee samajhanachhau ma,
daui dainakao chaolaa palabhara haolaa, yasalaaee samahaalanae kao ho ?
paukaara saunaee daui hat dainae maerao payorao parabhau ho .
2. aashaa-nairaashaakao kaalao baadala aaee malaaee ghaeradaaichha
patha-bharaanata pathaikajhaain ḍaulairahandaa yao jaeewana jaanaechha,
jaeewana maai haun bhanaera malaaee baaṭao daekhaaunae kao ho ?
ananatakao tyo ramaahaṭamaa laanae maerao payorao parabhau ho .
3. narakalaoka aaee paralaokamaa bhaoolaee bhaṭakairahaekao chhau ma
wayathaa paokhana napaaee alajhairahaekao chhau ma,
jaeewana jayaotai naibhanae ho kahailae yasalaaee samahaalanae kao ho ?
amara jaeewana saitataaimaa dainae maerao payorao parabhau ho .

songs.title: aashaa chha parabhaumaa jao paraaṇa aaphanao daie maerao saba paapakao
lyrics: 1. aashaa chha parabhaumaa jao paraaṇa aaphanao daie
maerao saba paapakao maola kalawaraeemaa tairae .
kao. maeraai lagi marae unaee,
ananata jaeewana ra jayaotai dainachhana‌ unaee
2. kamaaee maerao haoina karaodha shaanata garaauna
maerao euṭaai aashaa chha kharaeeṣhaṭakao dhaaramaikataa .
3. paitaakao saamaumaa jaiunchhana‌ maerao lagi
ra karaoosakao chaoṭa daekhaaundaai sawaeekaarachhana‌ malaaee .
4. apaara chha anaugaraha bishwas garanauchha
prem karaoosakao sawaeekaara garaee kharaeeṣhaṭa lainauchha .

songs.title: aashaakao daiyao naibhadaaina (2) jaeewana amara amara chha
lyrics: kao. (aashaakao daiyao naibhadaaina) (2)
jaeewana amara, amara chha Yeshumaa
aashaakao daiyao naibhadaaina
1. (sahaaraahaina yao jainadagaeemaa jaeewanakao maoolaya gaumaaen
samsaaramaa jaeewana saumapaera jaeewanakao lakaṣhaya haraaen) (2)
tara Yeshu sahaaraa banaera haraeka kadamamaa saatha dainaubhao .
2. (daauḍairahaem anayaola yotaraamaa karaoosakao prem bhaulaera
bhaḍakairahaem yao anadhakaaramaa jayaotai waihaina bhaera) (2)
saanchao gaoraeṭao Yeshu naai rahaechha jayaotai jaeewanakao unaaimaa rahaechha .

songs.title: aashaiṣhakao waraṣhaa maagadachhaaum hae sawaragaeeya paitaa haamaee
lyrics: kao. aashaiṣha‌kao waraṣhaa maagadachhaaum, hae sawaragaeeya paitaa haamaee aaundachhaaum . (2)
1. kamajaora haeena chhaaum chhaaina taakata, bharadaeoo haamaeemaa aaphanaai taakata (2)
payosaa haृdayalaaee laiera (2) hae sawaragaeeya paitaa hamaee aaundachhaaum .
2. dhaeraai bhaoolalae kalamkaita banayoum, baekamamaa rahaee dauhkhaita taulayoyoum (2)
sharamalae shairalaaee jhaookaaera (2) hae sawaragaeeya paitaa haamaee aaundachhaaum .
3. parabhau mahaana‌ shakataimaana‌ chhaau, saamarathaya, taejalae saushaobhaita chhaau (2)
hallelujah ra parashamsaa gaaee (2) hae sawaragaeeya paitaa haamaee aaundachhaaum .
4. aaphanao daasalaaee kahailayoi nabhaulaee bachaayou usalaaee paraaṇaai aaphanao daiee (2)
tayahaee asaeema payoralaaee chaahandaai (2) hae sawaragaeeya paitaa haamaee aaundachhaaum .

songs.title: aashaeeṣha tauma sae chaahatae haaim hae sawaragaeeya paitaa hama aatae haaim
lyrics: kao. aashaeeṣha tauma sae chaahatae haaim hae sawaragaeeya paitaa hama aatae haaim . (2)
1. na kaoee khaoobaee haai na laiyokata, bakhashao hamakao apanaee taakata
khaalaee dailaom kao laataem haai (2) hae sawaragaeeya paitaa hama aatae haai .
2. hamanae bahauta khataayaem kaee haaim, rahae naikamamae japhaayaem kaee haaim (2)
sharama sae shaira jhauka jaatae haai (2) hae sawaragaeeya paitaa hama aatae haai .
3. tauma ho shakataimaana parabhaujaee, dayo bhaye haai apaara parabhau jaee (2)
satautai hama saba gaatae haai (2) hae sawaragaeeya paitaa hama aatae haai .
4. banadaom kao taoo kabhaye na bhaoolae, dauhkha sahae daunaiyo maem taoonae (2)
usa haee payora kao chaahatae haai (2) hae sawaragaeeya paitaa hama aatae haai ॥

songs.title: aashaeeṣha mahaimaa aadara saamaratha shakatai aura adhaikaara
lyrics: aashaeeṣha mahaimaa aadara, saamaratha, shakatai aura adhaikaara
taujhakao ho maerae dhanaya parabhau . (2)
unchae saimhaasana sae naeechae aakara karaoosa para taoo maraa
maauta sae uṭhakara taoo jaiyo maujhae jaya dailaanaekao ॥

songs.title: aashaeeṣha, mahaimaa, aadara saamaratha shakatai aura adhaikaara
lyrics: aashaeeṣha, mahaimaa, aadara saamaratha shakatai aura adhaikaara
taujhakao ho maerae dhanaya parabhau (2)
oonchae saimhasaana sae naeechae aakara karaoosa para taoo maraa
maauta sae uṭhakara taoo jaiyo maujhae jaya dailaanae kao ॥

songs.title: aasamaana kae ai maukadasaom masaeeha kae ho madadaaha
lyrics: 1. aasamaana kae ai maukadasaom masaeeha kae ho madadaaha
hamaarae saatha khaudaawanada kao jaanao shaahanashaaha .
2. aura tau jao usakao umamata ho karao usa para naigaaha
apanae najaata dahainadaa kao tauma jaanao shaahanashaaha .
3. ai gaunahagaaraom yoda rakhao masaeeha kaa payora athaaha
masalaooba hakaeera gamajadaa kao tauma jaanao shaahanashaaha .
4. saba naiaamataom kao shaakaira ho ai saaraee khalaka ulalaaha
jamaeena jamaana kae maalaika kao tauma jaanaom shahanashaaha .
5. aasamaanaiyaom maem shaamaila ho khaudaa haee kaee daragaaha
ababala aura aakhaira Yeshu kao hama jaanaem shaahanashaaha .

songs.title: aahaa katai maeeṭhao wachana parabhaulae daiekao rachanaa (2)
lyrics: kao. aahaa, katai maeeṭhao wachana, parabhaulae daiekao rachanaa (2)
1. jaba ma wachana paढ़dachhau jhana‌ ṭhaoolao ichachhaa baढ़dachha
jaba ma wachana saunadachhau taba mana khaushaeelae bharadachha .
2. jaba ma paapalae bharaethaen taba anadhakaaralae chhapaethaen
parabhaulae malaaee baolaaunaubhao’ anai khaushaeekao khabara saunaaunaubhao’
3. ma, taimaee, haamaee, sabaai paapaee thaiyoun anai saanchao parabhaulaaee chainadaainathayoun
parabhau aae aaphaai sawaraga chhaड़era, haamaraolaagai ujayolao jayaotai baalaera .
4. karaoosamaa parabhau maranaubhayao, haamarao paapakao bhaara uṭhaaunaubhayao
maृtayaubaaṭa parabhau baauraee uṭhanaubhao’ ra haamaeelaaee sawaragakao ḍhaokaa khaolanaubhao’ .
5. aaoo daajayaoo-bhaai daidaee-bahainaee, parabhaukao maeeṭhao bachana paढ़na
aaphanaa paapalaaee haṭaaee saanchao parabhau Yeshumaa bishwas garana .

songs.title: aahaa katai ramaailao khaushaikao yao daina aayao
lyrics: kao. aahaa! katai ramaailao khaushaikao yao daina aayao
ramaaee ramaaee gaauna mana lagaayao
aahaa katai ramaailao samsaaraai ujayolao bhao
(khausaiyolaee chaaraaitaira bhao) (2)
1. (harasakao gaeetaa gaaudaai, naachadaai ramaaudaai
manaauna yaeshau kao janama dainalaaee) (2)
mahaimaa garaau, parashamshaa garaau
raajaaharaukaa raajaalaaee
2. (kathaa haoina yao, saataya ghaṭanaa
eeshawara aaunau bhao maanaisakao raupamaa) (2)
balai haunaubhao sharaapaita karausamaa
paapa daekhai chhauṭaauna
3. (paapakao kaṣhamaa dainae, jaeewana dainae
yaeshau maataraai hauna oodadhaarakarataa) (2)
baaṭao ra sataya, jaeewana dainae
yaeshaunaai hauna masaiha

songs.title: ai khaudaa kalawaraee sae eka lahara aba bhaeja apanaee
lyrics: 1. ai khaudaa kalawaraee sae eka lahara aba bhaeja
apanaee daulahana kao saapha kara abhaye
phataha kaee kauwawata dae, paooraee khaushaee aura taeja
waayadae kae laie ṭhaharatae sabhaye
kao. apanaee kauwawata jalaalaee aba bhaeja (2)
saba kamajaoraom kao phatahamamda aba banaa
apanaee kauwawata jalaalaee aba bhaeja .
2. hamakao Yeshu sae aura shaikaṣhaa jaeewana maem dae
hara laड़aee maem jaya paanae kaee taakata dae
khaushaee sae apanae maaraga para chalaa
apanae payora aura eemaana maem baड़a .
3. sausata aura sarada dailaem kao raooha maem bailakaoola jagaa
daunaiyo maem jao ulajha gayae haai
waaraisha barakata kaee hama para aasamaana sae barasaa
karaoosa kaee tarapha hama saba daekhatae haai ॥

songs.title: aura saamaratha (2) aura janyona (2) chaahataa haoon maerae khaudaa
lyrics: 1. aura saamaratha (2) aura janyona (2) chaahataa haoon maerae khaudaa,
aaraadhanaa taeraee maaim karaoongaa
satautai taeraee gaataa rahaoongaa, sadaa sarawadaa .
2. aura anaugaraha (2) aura saahasa (2) chaahataa haoon maerae khaudaa,
saewaa maaim taeraee daila sae karaoongaa
mausaibataom sae nahaeem ḍaraoongaa, paeechhae na haṭaoomgaa ॥

songs.title: chamgaai waraṣhaa aaudaai chha najaika aaudaaichha yao shaharamaa
lyrics: chamgaai waraṣhaa aaudaai chha najaika aaudaaichha yao shaharamaa
dhanaee garaeeba kamajaora balabaana yasalae dayo layoirahaechha
chamgaai baraṣhaa aagaojhaai yahaan jharadaaichha uccha paarana
chamgaai baraṣhaa manaiira chhau sawaragaeeya baraṣhaalae ma dhaoina

songs.title: chaṭaṭaana sae madhau sae maeeṭhaa (2) parabhau chaṭaṭaana sae madhau sae
lyrics: chaṭaṭaana sae madhau sae maeeṭhaa (2)
parabhau chaṭaṭaana sae madhau sae maeeṭhaa haai
chakha kara daekhao parabhau bhalaa haai
waha chaṭaṭaana sae madhau sae maeeṭhaa haai . (2)

songs.title: chattanako mahabhanadaa maeeṭhaa (2) parabhau chattanako
lyrics: chattanako mahabhanadaa maeeṭhaa (2), parabhau chattanako mahabhanadaa maeeṭhaa chhana‌
chaakhaihaera, parabhau bhalao chhana‌, parabhau chattanako mahabhanadaa maeeṭhaa chhana‌ .

songs.title: chaढ़aunchhau parabhau dhanyawad aaja karaoosakao tyo premakao
lyrics: kao. chaढ़aunchhau parabhau dhanyawad aaja karaoosakao tyo premakao naimatai
thaukaai ra kauṭaai sahaunaubhao’ jatai taee saba thaie maeraai naimatai (2)
1. kaanड़e maukauṭa pahairaee shairamaa, haata-paaulaaee jaड़ee karaoosamaa (2)
haunaubhao’ balai maerao naai naimatai nairadaoṣha paaṭhaokao raoopamaa (2)
2. paeeड़a tapaaeemlaaee, shaanatai malaaee, karaoosa tapaaeemkao, maukauṭa maerao (2)
maृtayau tapaaeemlaaee, jaeewana malaaee, prem malaaee kaina yasatao ? (2)
3. daekhachhau mahaimaita sawaraga maerao, tara haoina kamaaee maerao (2)
haraṣhaasharau jhaaradaai parashamsaa garachhau, yao taa ho daana tapaaeemkao (2)
4. ghaृṇaita paapalaaee garachhau ghaृṇaa, kaaraṇa yahaee ho laanae karaoosamaa (2)
sajaaunchhau saimhaasana parabhau haृdayamaa, rahanauhaosa‌ parabhau yasamaa (2)

songs.title: chalatae chalatae apanaom sae paoochha kai kaauna haoon maaim
lyrics: kao. chalatae chalatae apanaom sae paoochha kai kaauna haoon maaim
kauchha bhaye karanae sae pahalae, jaraa saomchao kayo kara rahaa haoon maaim . (2)
haa... haa... haa... hallelujah (7) aamaina .
1. kayaom ho gaumashauma, kayaom ho khaoyae, auraom kae laiyao jaisao
masaeehaee nae anaokhaa payora saikhaayo, tauma bhaye payora karanaa saikhao .
hallelujah (2) chalatae chalatae... .
2. usanae hansakara saba kauchha tayogaa, usakaa saatha na chhaड़o
usakao aagae rakhao sadaa tauma, paeechhae kabhaye bhaye na mauड़o .
hallelujah (2) chalatae chalatae... ॥

songs.title: chalaun (2) usakae paeechhae chalaun isa samaya hara samaya maaim bhaye
lyrics: chalaun (2) usakae paeechhae chalaun isa samaya
hara samaya maaim bhaye chalaungaa .
chalaun (2) usakae paeechhae chala jahaan kahaeem
wao chalae maaim bhaye chalaungaa ॥

songs.title: chalao-chalao rae, baaitalahaema gaanwa chalao rae (2)
lyrics: kao. chalao-chalao rae, baaitalahaema gaanwa chalao rae (2)
taujhae bachaanaekao, maujhae bachaanaekao, aayo masaeeha rae . (2)
1. waha daekhao naeela aakaasha maem, ṭhamḍaee ṭhamḍaee bataasa maem (2)
daenaekao jaeewana aayo, samga wao maukatai laayo, samga wao maukatai laayo rae
chalao rae chalao, chalao rae chalao, chalao chalao rae . (2)
2. chhaड़kara aasamaanakao, bachaanae isa jahaanakao (2)
paapaom sae hamakao bachaanae, bharapaoora jaeewana paanae
bharapaoora jaeewana paanae rae . (2)
chalao rae chalao, chalao rae chalao, chalao chalao rae ॥ (2)

songs.title: chaanड़ai aaunaechhana‌ Yeshu raajaa (2)
lyrics: kao. chaanड़ai aaunaechhana‌, Yeshu raajaa (2)
sawaragaeeya daootagaṇa saathamaa laiee, baadalakao sawaaraeemaa aaunaechhana‌
hallelujah (4) maerao Yeshu raajaa phaerai aaunaechhana‌
1. saanaa-saanaa maotaee sabalaaee baechaee asala maotaeelaaee kainaejasatao
bishwas garanae haraeka sabalaaee sawaragaeeya raajaya panai haunachha yasatao .
2. laukaiekao gaaड़dhanalaaee bhaeṭaee aaphanao saaraa bhaoomai baechaejasatao
kainanaelaaee tyo bahaumaoolaya bhaoomai sawaragaeeya raajaya panai haunachha yasatao .

songs.title: chaanḍaai aaunaechhana‌ Yeshu raajaa (2) sawaragaeeya daootagaṇa
lyrics: chaanḍaai aaunaechhana‌ Yeshu raajaa (2)
sawaragaeeya daootagaṇa saathamaa laiee baadalakao sawaaraeemaa aaunaechhana‌
hallelujah (4) maerao Yeshu raajaa phaeraee aaunaechhana‌
1. saanaa saanaa maotaee sabalaaee baechaee asala maotaeelaaee kainae jasatao
bishwas garanae haraeka sabalaaee sawaragaeeya raajaya panai haunachha yasatao
halalaelaooyoha...
2. laukaiekao gaaḍadhanalaaee bhaeṭaee aaphanao saaraa bhaumaee baechae jasatao
kainanaelaaee tyo bahaumaoolaya bhaoomaee sawaragaeeya raajaya panai haunachha yasatao
halalaelaooyoha...

songs.title: chaanḍaai dhaeraai chaanḍaai haamaee raajaalaaee bhaeṭanaechhaaun (3)
lyrics: chaanḍaai, dhaeraai chaanḍaai haamaee raajaalaaee bhaeṭanaechhaaun (3)
halalaelaooyoha, halalaelaooyoha, haamarao raajaalaaee bhaeṭanaechhaaun .
khaushaee haunaechhaaun, haamaee haamarao raajaalaaee bhaeṭanaechhaau
maृtayau haundaaina, haamaee haamarao raajaalaaee bhaeṭanaechhaau
rauwaai haundaaina, haamaee haamarao raajaalaaee bhaeṭanaechhaau

songs.title: chaara daina kai jainadagaee haai dao daina kai haai jawaanaee
lyrics: kao. chaara daina kai jainadagaee haai, dao daina kai haai jawaanaee
kaṭa jaayaegaee yae chaara daina kai jainadagaee,
daunaiyon sae chala jaayaemgae .
1. saarae samsaara nae paapa kaiyo haai, rababa kaee mahaimaa sae daoora haue haai
paapaee kaa sawaraga maem naiwaasa nahaeem haai,
saomcha lao aba taumahaaraa waasa kahaa haai .
2. rahanaa nahaeem daunaiyon maem hamaeshaa hamaem
jaanaa tao paड़egaa eka daina daunaiyo sae hamaem
jaanae sae pahalae yae baata saocha lao
maranae kae baada tauma kahaan jaaogae .
3. paapaom sae bachaanae kaewala eka haee aayo haai
Yeshu udadhaarakaratataa jaeewana laayo haai
wao haee parabhau eka daina nayoyaee banaegaee
saocha lao taumahaaraa kayo phala aayaegaa .
chaara daina kai jainadagaee... ॥

songs.title: chaalaeesa dainakaa bhaokaa daekhaee shaaitaana aaee parabhauchhaeu
lyrics: 1. chaalaeesa dainakaa bhaokaa daekhaee shaaitaana aaee parabhauchhaeu
bhananalaagayao, “yaee ḍhaungagaalaaee raoṭaee banaaee khaandaai jaaoo” .
dauṣhaṭa shaaitaanakao wachana saunaee utatara daie parabhaulae
“raoṭaeelae maataraai baanchanae chhaainaau, bachaainachhaau wachanalae” .
2. euṭaa alagao ṭhaaunmaa paurayoee bhanana laagayao raajaya daekhaaee,
“ekaaipalaṭa paraṇaama‌ garae dainaechhau ma taimaeelaaee”
“dauṣhaṭa shaaitaana, laekhaekao chha taainlae aaphanao eeshawaralaaee
paraṇaama garanaoo, saewaa garanaoo, garanaoo satautai unakaai” .
3. manadairamaathai chaढ़ai bhanana laagayao shaaitaanalae
“kharaeeṣhaṭa haau bhanae haamaphaala, aaee samaaunchhana‌ daootalae” .
utatara daie, “dauṣhaṭa shaaitaana, paraeekaṣhaa nagara eeshawaralaaee
lajajaita bhaye bhagaigayao ekalaai chhaaड़ee parabhaulaaee” .

songs.title: chaanhaidaaina hairaa maotaee chaḍaau haudaya bhaeṭaee
lyrics: kao. chaanhaidaaina hairaa maotaee chaḍaau haudaya bhaeṭaee
unakao nyano angalo haamarao jaeewana daekhaee .
1. samsaaramaa haamaee maanawa kaehaee kaṣhaṇa baanchachhaau
aaja haansaee bhaolaee raoodaain kauna ṭhaaunmaa jaanachhaau
arapaihaalaau yao jaeewana unakao nayonau haatamaa
anai jaanachhaau taimaee haamaee sawadaesha unakao saathamaa .
2. haamarao sharaeera maaṭaakao chha maaṭaamaa naai mailanae
kaṣhaṇabharakao samsaaramaa kaelaaee parakhaee basanae
daihaalaau haamarao jaeewana unakao payorao haatamaa
anai jaanachhaau taimaee haamaee sawadaesha unakao saathamaa .

songs.title: chaahae khaaoo taimaee chaahae paioo chaahae jae saukaai gara (2)
lyrics: chaahae khaaoo taimaee chaahae paioo chaahae jae saukaai gara (2)
parabhaukaai mahaimaa gara parabhaukaai mahaimaa gara
chaahae khaaoo taimaee chaahae paioo chaahae jae saukaai gara (2)

songs.title: chaahae taumakao dailasaem gaae yae gaeeta mailakae
lyrics: chaahae taumakao dailasaem, gaae yae gaeeta mailakae
taerae naaun Yeshu naaunkaee jaya
jailasa naaunmaem hae jainadagaee, wao naaun ho Yeshu masaeeha
jaisa naaunmaem hae banadhakaee wao naaun hae
Yeshu masaeeha ((Yeshu naaun) (6) kaee jaya) (2) ...hao
Yeshu naaunmaem mailataee hae kaṣhamaa
Yeshu naaunmaem mailataee hae saiphaa
Yeshu naaunmaem mailataee hae kaृpaa
Yeshu naaunmaem karauṇaa dauwaa
(Yeshu naaun) (4)
(Yeshu naaun) (6) kaee jayae
(Yeshu naaun) (6) kaee jayae

songs.title: chaahaera maile jaeewana parabhaulaaee aaja naai chaढ़aee daien
lyrics: kao. chaahaera maile jaeewana parabhaulaaee aaja naai chaढ़aee daien
gaaundaina gaeeta samsaarakao phaerai aaja naai maile chhaaड़idaien (2)
1. patatharakao maooratailaaee ma sataya khaojaechhau
aakaashakao taaraalaaee wayarathaai raojaechhau (2)
eeshawara bhanaera paujaen maailae, maile euṭaa bhaoola garaechhau (2)
2. maayo ra maoha ta kaehaee panai haoina raitatao chha kaewala samsaara yahaan
paapamaai basaera baitaae jaeewana kaewala nairaashaamaa (2)

songs.title: chainanauparachha sabaailae (2) chainanauparachha sabaailae Yeshu kao hauna‌
lyrics: kao. chainanauparachha sabaailae (2), chainanauparachha sabaailae Yeshu kao hauna‌
1. unaee shaanatai dainae kharaeeṣhaṭa hauna‌, jagata‌kaa hauna‌ taaraṇahaara
taimarao-maerao maukataidaataa chainanauparachha sabaailae .
2. unaee maerao payorao maitara, manamaa khaushaee daindachhana‌
maerao jaeewanakao ujayolao, chainanauparachha sabaailae .
3. unaee naiṣhakalamka awataara, pautara hauna‌ paramaeshawarakaa
phaerai pachhai aaunae raajaa, chainanauparachha sabaailae .

songs.title: chaiyobaaraee paakhaa pakhaeraomaa baanchaekaa maeraa
lyrics: kao. chaiyobaaraee paakhaa pakhaeraoomaa baanchaekaa maeraa sanataanaharaoolaaee
sausamaachaara kharaeeṣhaṭakao paurayoidainachhau baanchaera maranae maerao maanachhaeharaoolaaee (2)
1. baanchaera maranau jaeewana haoina maraera baanchanau jaeewana chha haai (2)
garaera dharama sawaraga paugainana (2) Yeshu kharaeeṣhaṭalaaee chainanauparachha haai (2)
2. karunaimaa alajhae Yeshu kharaeeṣhaṭa naai chaihaana aaja saakaṣhaee chha haai (2)
garaera karama aatamaa baanchainana Yeshu kharaeeṣhaṭamaa aaunauparachha haai (2)

songs.title: chaisao chaisao bataasa chalayao wanaaimaa
lyrics: kao. chaisao chaisao bataasa chalayao wanaaimaa
aashaiṣhakao aabhaaṣha bhayao manaaimaa
(taimarao prema) (2) kalawaraeekao taimarao prem
1. euṭaai paitaakao euṭaai naataa thaiyao
bhaedabhaawa rahaitakao samaaja haamarao (2)
chaaraai daishaamaa euṭaai lakaṣhaya chha
pawaitara aatamaakao sadhaaim saatha chha
taimarao prema...
2. haraaekaalaaee aawaaja dainae
aansau jhaaranaelaaee pauchhaidainae (2)
paradaeshaeelaaee sahaaraakao raupa
andhayoraomaa balanae daipa
taimarao prema...

songs.title: chaisao-chaisao haawaamaa nyano maayo haai baokaera
lyrics: kao. (chaisao-chaisao haawaamaa nyano maayo haai baokaera
Yeshu raajaa aaekaa chhana‌ haai udadhaara laiera) (2)
1. paradaeshaee banaera aae, sawaragalaaee chhaड़era aae, pasaraie gaoṭhaaimaa
(aakaashamaa taaraa baalaera, dharataeemaa jayaotai chharaera andhaeraee haṭaae) (2)
(parashamsaa haamarao Yeshulaaee haृdaya khaolaera) (2)
2. nayon aashaa haृdayamaa chha maukataidaataa Yeshukao payorao sanadaesha saunaera
(haृdayakao ḍhaokaa khaolaera jaeewana laeoo Yeshumaa aaja bishwas garaera) (2)
(mahaimaa haamarao Yeshulaaee haृdaya khaolaera) (2)
3. aba ta dauhkhakaa daina gae shaanatai
aananada uralaera aae haamarao yao aaganamaa
(aau haamaee mailaee parachaaraau badalaiera
unalaaee pachhayoau jayajayakaara garaera) (2)
(dhanayawaada haamarao Yeshulaaee haृdaya khaolaera) (2)

songs.title: chaihaanabhaitara thaie kharaeeṣhaṭa parabhau maeraa samaya paoorao hauna
lyrics: 1. chaihaanabhaitara thaie kharaeeṣhaṭa parabhau maeraa, samaya paoorao hauna parakhairahaethae .
kao. chaihaanadaekhai kharaeeṣhaṭa uṭhae, jayakao dhawanaisanga kharaeeṣhaṭa uṭhae
anadhakaarakao raajayalaaee haṭaaeekana jayaotaimaa raaja garana sanataharaoosanga
kharaeeṣhaṭa uṭhae, kharaeeṣhaṭa uṭhae, hallelujah kharaeeṣhaṭakao jaya
2. ḍhaungagaamaa chhaapa lagaaee, paharaa raakhae wayarathaaimaa chaihaanalaaee rakaṣhaa garae .
3. maृtayaulae sakaena raokana parabhaulaaee, baauraee uṭhae Yeshu, jayawanata bhaye .

songs.title: chaupa laaga jaana ma eeshawara haun (3)
lyrics: 1. chaupa laaga, jaana ma eeshawara haun (3)
2. ma parabhau taimaeelaaee bachaaunae (3)
3. ma parabhau taimaeelaaee naikao paaranae (3)
4. ma parabhau taimaeelaaee payora garanae (3)
5. chaupa laaga, jaana ma eeshawara haun .

songs.title: chaupa haai yaha chamda chaupa haai yae taarae janamaa haai janamaa
lyrics: kao. chaupa haai yaha chamda, chaupa haai yae taarae
janamaa haai janamaa, janamaa masaeeha .
raatakaee khaamaoshaee maem . (3)
1. kaaisaee yaha charaṇaee, kaaisaee yaha raata, saoyo haai saaraa
jamaanaa-jamaanaa, baaitalahaema maem aayo masaeeha
laekae khaushaee kaa khajaanaa .
raata kaee khaamaoshaee maem... . (3)
2. raata maem aakae, raataom maem gaakae, daootao nae sabakao
jagaayo, jagaayo, shaanataikaa daataa maukataikaa sawaamaee
hamakao bachaanae aayo .
raata kaee khaamaoshaee maem... . (3)

songs.title: chaokhao paraeetakao sanadaesha... yao saunaidaeoo...
lyrics: kao. chaokhao paraeetakao sanadaesha... yao saunaidaeoo...
haamarao baitaekaa jaeewanakaa saakaṣhaee kharaeeṣhaṭa naai hauna‌ .
1. raitataiekao jaeewanalaaee maeeṭhaa-maeeṭhaa sawaragaeeya
aananadakaa sanadaesha laee naaulao jaeewanakao gaoraeṭaomaa
ḍaorayounae chhana‌ kharaeeṣhaṭa Yeshulae .
2. maanawa jaeewanakao yauga-yaugadaekhaikaa katai-katai sharaapaharaoo
dauhkha saukhakao paeeraharaoo maeṭaaunaechhana‌ kharaeeṣhaṭa Yeshulae .

songs.title: chaoṭa thaiyao ghaau thaiyao manaai amailao haeranae aankhaa haedaan
lyrics: chaoṭa thaiyao ghaau thaiyao manaai amailao
haeranae aankhaa haedaan haeradaai haunathayao dhamailao (2)
ḍhaakaiekao rahaechhau ma ta anadhakaara kaueeraolae
paraina laagaekao rahaechhau paapaaikao pahairaolae
laau laau ho ho laau laau hao...
1. anaugarahalae ḍaorayoundaai paurayoyao malaaee Yeshukahaan
naikao bhaen shaanatai paaen chhauṭakaaraa unaaimaa (2)
ghaama ra jauna ra taaraalae kasatao dharataeelaaee ujayolao chharae jasatao
Yeshukao maayo ta rahaechha yasatao paaekao chhau maile tyo parashasatao
jaeewana naai unaaimaa jaeewana naai unaaimaa
2. Yeshu naai hauna‌ jaeewana bharaee gaairahanae maerao gaeeta
gaansaeeekao chha ananata ananatalaaee naataa samabanadha unaai saita (2)
phaoolalae saubaasanaa chharae jasatao baadalalae basanata paṭhaae jasatao
saimasaimae paanaeemaa inadaraeṇaee jasatao saunadara bhao jaeewana Yeshumaa yasatao
khaushaee naai khaushaeelae bharaiekao khaushaee naai khaushaeelae bharaiekao

songs.title: chaautaaraeekao chhaanyomaa thaitalataalae ḍaakadaaichha (2)
lyrics: chaautaaraeekao chhaanyomaa shaitalataalae ḍaakadaaichha (2)
taimarao maerao bhaaraeelaaee baisaauna tayahain jaatai chha (2)
1. paailaa saarana gaaharae bhao mana yao jhanaai gaharaunga bhao
saanghaurao baaṭao apaṭhayorao charakao ghaama haunae bhao (2)
bhaaralaaee thaamanae chaautaaraee hainḍanalaaee saghaaunae Yeshu hauna‌ (2)
manakao jawaalaa haṭaaee shaitalataa dainae unaai hauna‌ (2)
2. bhausakao aagao kaama chhaaina daauraakao naai chaahainachha (2)
paapabaaṭa haamaee sabaailaaee Yeshumaa maukatai chha
sharaeera kaewala dauee dainakao sadhaaim rahanae ta aatamaa ho (2)
tayahai aatamaalaaee bachaauna dharataeemaa Yeshu aaunaubhao (2)

songs.title: chaautaaraeemaa wara haoina paipala kharaeeṣhaṭakao chhaeumaa jaeewana
lyrics: chaautaaraeemaa wara haauina paipala kharaiṣhaṭakao chhaeumaa jaeewana shaeetala
paarai banakao tyo nayoulaee charaee (2)
garanauhaunana jaeewanamaa mana parai (2)
1. hae hae haa haa sauna daajau sauna bhaai sauna aamaa baau (2)
samsaarakao baaṭao tayogaee kharaeeṣhaṭakao charaṇamaa aau (2)
kharaeeṣhaṭalaaee hajaura laau garahaṇa gara jaanaee baujhaee narakamaa napara (2)
2. hae hae haa haa maanaisaharau ishawara khaojana tairatha yotaraa dhaaunchhana‌ (2)
saanchao ishawara kahaan paaunau dhaokaa maataraai paaunchhana‌ (2)
saanchao ishawara saumsaaramaa chhaaina Yeshu baahaeka maukataidaana kahain chhaaina (2)
3. hae hae haa haa ishawaralae samsaaralaaee yasatao prem garae (2)
samsaarakao paapa baokaee kharausaaimaa marae (2)
bishwas garaee udadhaara laeu paapaee jaeewana Yeshulaaee naai daeu (3)

songs.title: chhama chhama naachaauna la haai la haai gaaauna
lyrics: chhama chhama naachaauna la haai la haai gaaauna (2)
parabhaukao bachana yao dailamaa raakhaauna (2)
khausaeeyolaee manaaauna nayon gaeeta gaaauna (2)
udadhaara karataalaaee mahaimaa chaड़aauna (2)
(kaohai thaiena samsaaramaa shaanatai layouna
kaohai bhaena jaeewanamaa aashaa daina
paapamaya daladalaee hailaobaaṭa bachaaunae
maraekaa tai jaeenadagaeelaaee nayon
jaeewanadainae hao... hao) (2)

songs.title: chhamam chhamam naachaauhauna haraidaya khaolaee gaahauuna
lyrics: 1. (chhamam chhamam naachaauhauna haraidaya khaolaee gaahauuna) (2)
(aaja yao baḍaa dainamaa yaeshaukao janama dainamaa) (2)
(hayopapaee hayopapaee karaisaṭamasa
hayopapaee hayopapaee karaisaṭamasa sabaailaaee) (2)
2. (sawaragaeeya baaibhawa chhaḍaera aaunaubhao maanaisakao raupa laiera) (2)
(anadhakaara maathai baijaya dainaubhao jaiwanakao jayaotai banaera) (2)
(hayopapaee hayopapaee karaisaṭamasa
hayopapaee hayopapaee karaisaṭamasa sabaailaaee) (2)
3. (chhauṭakaaraa daina aaunaubhayao paapa daekhai sabaailaaee) (2)
(gaaeekao gaoṭhaaimaa janamanau bhao raajaaharaukaa raajaa) (2)
(hayopapaee hayopapaee karaisaṭamasa
hayopapaee hayopapaee karaisaṭamasa sabaailaaee) (2)

songs.title: chharaitao chhaiṭao bhaera Yeshukao kaamamaa dagaurachhau
lyrics: kao. chharaitao chhaiṭao bhaera (Yeshukao kaamamaa dagaurachhau‌) (2)
alajhaaunae kauraa phaalaera (tayora sadhaaim rahanachhau) (2)
1. laṭayounae rakamakao thauparaolae alamalayouna khaojachha
laobha ra laalachakao wasataulae tarakaaunae kaothaiṣha garachha .
2. darashaaunau bhaekao kauraamaa sadhaaim laagairahanachhau
Yeshukao waaṇaeemaa aḍaina chahanachhau .
3. jaeewana maukauṭa paainalaaee kauratai saatha dagaurachhau
dhaokaa dainae tanamanalaaee paiṭaera adala raakhachhau .
4. jaeewana maukauṭa paaunalaaee phaoorataisaatha dagaurachhau
ghanaiṣhaṭhataamaa Yeshukao jhana‌jhana‌ baḍhadaai jaanachhau .

songs.title: chhaaḍaee gayao samsaarakao maayolae (2) malaaee kahailae
lyrics: chhaaḍaee gayao samsaarakao maayolae (2)
malaaee kahailae chhaaḍaena Yeshukao maayolae (2)
chhaaḍaee gayao...
1. haijao samama kauna samsaaramaa thaien ma
aaja kauna samsaaramaa bhaen ma (2)
yaee sabaai naai parabhaukao aashaiṣha ho
yaee sabaai naai Yeshukao aashaiṣha ho
chhaaḍaee gayao saathaee ra sangagaeelae (2)
malaaee kahailae Yeshukao sangagatalae (2)
2. Yeshukao mahaimaa gaanudaai hainḍachhau ma
unaaikao yao sanadaesha saunaaudaai hainḍachhau ma (2)
yaee sabaai naai parabhaukao aashaiṣha ho
yaee sabaai naai Yeshukao aashaiṣha ho
chhaaḍaee gayao aaphanataharaulae (2)
malaaee kahailae Yeshukao aaphanatalae (2)

songs.title: chhau maujhae chhau khaudaarau maujhae chhau (2)
lyrics: chhau maujhae chhau, khaudaarau maujhae chhau (2)
maerae manakao maerae tanakao, maerae badanakao chhau (2)

songs.title: chhauṭakaaraakao gaeeta gaaaun haai parabhau Yeshukahaan jaaaun haai
lyrics: kao. chhauṭakaaraakao gaeeta gaaaun haai, parabhau Yeshukahaan jaaaun haai (2)
1. balaidaana haunae kao ho ? Yeshu, paapa kaṣhamaa garanae kao hauna‌ ? Yeshu,
raogaharaoo naikao paranae, bhaootaharaoo dhapaaidainae eyashaoo .
2. haamarao waijaya Yeshumaa chha aamaina‌, haamarao aananada Yeshu naai hauna‌, aamaina‌ .
maृtayaubaaṭa uṭhaiaaunae, bishwaseelaaee shaanatai dainae Yeshu .

songs.title: chhaaina bharaosaa yao jainadagaeekao (2) garaaun bhajana aba
lyrics: kao. chhaaina bharaosaa yao jainadagaeekao (2), garaaun bhajana aba Yeshujaeekao (2)
1. baalakakaala baitayao khaelaaimaa khaelaee, jawaanaee baitayao premaaimaa bhaulaee
waृdadhakaala baitadaaichha janyajaalamaa ḍaubaee, garaaun bhajana aba Yeshujaeekao .
2. janyajaalamaa daulaeerahanachhaau katai, chaeta garaee aba saudhaara gatai
chhaaina baelaa bhaai aba atai, garaaun bhajana aba Yeshujaeekao .
3. paapa ra samtaapa baढ़dachhana‌ jatai haunaechhana‌ naṣhaṭa jaeewana utai
pharakaaoo mana aba Yeshupaṭaṭai, garaaun bhajana aba Yeshujaeekao .

songs.title: chhaaina Yeshu baahaeka bachaaekao arau kaohaeelae
lyrics: 1. chhaaina Yeshu baahaeka bachaaekao arau kaohaeelae
maerao haृdaya jaitaekao chha unakao jaeeudao bachana saanchao baolaee (2)
kao. laaibaraee laaibaraee laaibaraee laaibaraee gaaunchha maerao manalae
Yeshukao jaeewana premakao kathaa sabalaaee saunaaunchha
yao jaeewanalae (2) aahaoi aahaoi aahaoi
2. bharaiekao chha aaja maerao mana sawaragaeeya haanatailae parairawatana garanaubhao
malaaee kharaeeṣhaṭalae aaphanao premakao shakatailae (2)
3. sabaai thaokalaaee bairasaee aaraadhaaṇaa kharaeeṣhaṭakao garanaechhau
unakao parashamsaamaa ananadalae haृdaya khaeelaee naachadaai gaaunae chhau (2)
rao-rao sabalaaee saunaauchha yao jaeewanalae (2)

songs.title: chhaaina raakhanae ṭhaaun chhaaina paaṭaeekao maalaikalae bhanayao (2)
lyrics: chhaaina, raakhanae ṭhaaun chhaaina, paaṭaeekao maalaikalae bhanayao (2)
raakhanae ṭhaaun nabhaekao parabhau Yeshu, maerao manamaa aaunauhaosa‌,
maerao manamaa saanao ḍaoonḍa banaaidainaechhau,
aaunaosa‌, maerao manamaa, aaunaosa‌, saanao ḍaoonḍamaa,
aaunaosa‌, maerao manamaa, aaunaosa‌, maerao parabhau Yeshu .

songs.title: chhaṭae bachachaom kao paasa aanae dao aashaeeṣha unahaem bhaye paanae dao
lyrics: kao. chhaṭae bachachaom kao paasa aanae dao, aashaeeṣha unahaem bhaye paanae dao
unahaem manaa mata karao maerae paasa aanae dao
sawaraga kaa raajaya haai aisaom kaa . (2)
1. nanahaa baalaka aayo Yeshu paasa, apanaa khaanaa laayo Yeshu paasa
aashaeeṣha maagaee parabhau Yeshu nae, khaayo paancha hajaara laogaom nae . (2)
2. daenaa saeekhaem apanae parabhau kao, apanaa saba kauchha dae daem usaee kao
daenaa laenae sae dhanaya haai Yeshu kaa yaha anamaola wachana haai . (2)

songs.title: e alachhae uṭha kamailaakahaan jaaoo kamailaakahaan gaera
lyrics: kao. e alachhae uṭha kamailaakahaan jaaoo kamailaakahaan gaera shaikaṣhaa paaoo
tainaeeharaookao wayawahaara saikaera ramaaundaai taimaee panai satautai gaaoon (2)
kaṭaaphaṭa phaṭaaphaṭa mailaijaulai kaama garaaun phaṭaaphaṭa (2)
1. kamailaakao daeshamaa na kaohaee agauwaa kamailaakao daeshamaa na kaohaee daasa
na kaohaee jaimamaewaaraee tayahaan na kaohaee saanao ra ṭhaoolao khaasa (phaṭaaphaṭa) (3‌)
2. euṭaa kamailaalaaee kasaailae bhaulaaudaa ma atai wayasaya chhau bhanachha
wainataee chha maerao malaaee nabhaulaau saृṣhaṭaikarataakao kaama garana daeoo
bhaulanae maerao phaurasada chhaaina phaṭaaphaṭa ṭaolanae maerao samaya chhaaina phaṭaaphaṭa
gharaghara dhaaunae awasara chhaaina phaṭaaphaṭa kauraa orasaanae maerao maaukaai chhaaina phaṭaaphaṭa
(phaṭaaphaṭa) (3)
3. oraalaomaa panai tayatataikaai phaṭaaphaṭa ukaalaomaa panai tayatataikaai phaṭaaphaṭa
dauhkhamaa panai tayatataikaai phaṭaaphaṭa saukhamaa panai tayatataikaai phaṭaaphaṭa
na ta aankhaamaa aansau na gaalaamaa hat euṭaa thaakadaa arakaolae dainachha saatha
phaṭaaphaṭa phaṭaaphaṭa mailaeejaulaee kaama garaaun phaṭaaphaṭa (phaṭaaphaṭa) (3)

songs.title: e naanaee asala saochana Yeshubaaṭa saika
lyrics: e naanaee, asala saochana Yeshubaaṭa saika
e naanaee, asala baolana Yeshubaaṭa saika
e naanaee, paraarathanaa garana Yeshubaaṭa saika
e naanaee, maeeṭhao baolana Yeshubaaṭa saika
e naanaee, namara banana Yeshubaaṭa saika
e naanaee, kaṣhamaa garana Yeshubaaṭa saika
e naanaee, saewaa garana Yeshubaaṭa saika
e naanaee, dayo garana Yeshubaaṭa saika
e naanaee, maayo garana Yeshubaaṭa saika
e naanaee, shaaitaanalaaee jaitana Yeshubaaṭa saika
e naanaee, sabaai asala gauṇaharaoo Yeshubaaṭa saika

songs.title: e naoaa chaaḍaai naai jaahaajalaaee
lyrics: e naoaa chaanḍaai naai jaahaajalaaee nairamaaṇa gara
tayahaan eka baandhaee baृṣhaṭaee jharaaunae chhana‌
parabhaukao janalae aajanyo maanai chaanḍaai naai jaahaajalaaee nairamaaṇa gara
jaahaaja banaae ṭhakaṭhakaṭhaka
baृṣhaṭaee jharayao jharajharajhara
wainadhaakao daanao gaunyajaiyao
(naoaa) (2) ḍhaokaa khaola
ḍhaokaalaaee paramaeshawara sawayammalae banada garae
naṣhaṭa bhae jasalae aajanyo bhangaga garae

songs.title: e lahaai saunaaeedaeoo haai e lahaai baujhaaidaeoo haai
lyrics: kao. e lahaai saunaaeedaeoo haai, e lahaai baujhaaidaeoo haai
kai Yeshuraajaa maukataidaataa bhanaera (2)
khausaikao sanadaesha yao saunaaeedaeoo haai (2)
1. samsaaramaa waipakatai bhaye nairaasha basanae sabaailaaee
sahaaraa waihaina ekalaai basaee phaikaraee garanae sabaailaaee (2)
Yeshumaa sahaaraa laeoo bhanaidaeu haai (2)
2. haृdayamaa paira baokaee raraoihainḍanae sabaailaaee
garaibailae sataaera bhaokaai basanae sabaailaaee
shaanataikao sanadaesha yao saunaaeedaeu haai

songs.title: euṭaa aatamaa baanchadaa yahaan sawaragamaa ramaahaṭa haunachhana‌ bhanae
lyrics: kao. euṭaa aatamaa baanchadaa yahaan sawaragamaa ramaahaṭa haunachhana‌ bhanae
euṭaa aatamaa bhaḍakandaa panai sawaragamaa sabaai naai shaokaita haunachhana‌ (2‌)
(dhaikakaara chha) (3) tyo maanaisalaaee jasadawaaraa aatamaa bhaḍakannachhana‌
(dhaikakaara chha) (3) tyo maanaisalaaee jasadawaaraa aatamaa bhaḍakannachhana‌
1. usakao ghaicharaomaa jaantaokao maalaa pahairaaidainau
kahailae nanaisakanae garaee samaudaramaa phaalaidainau
paramaeshawarakao naiyama taoड़era aaphanao naiyama chalaaunaeharaoo
satayakao maṇaḍalaee bhaitara jhaooṭakao khaetaee garanaeharaoo
yasataa maanachhae yasa jagata‌maa janamanau abhaiṣhaapa bhayao
maṇaḍalaeelaaee paapa bhayao .
2. paramaeshawarakao manakao chaaha sabaailae maukatai paauna‌
yaojanaa unakao haamaeelaaee sawaragamaa sangaai rahaoonna‌
ragatakao maoolaya chaukaaee bachaaiekaa unakaa jana
bhaḍakaiera jaanachha bhanae dauhkhaita haunachha kharaeeṣhaṭakao mana
jauna maanaisalae kaama baigaarachha sharaapa usalaaee paradachha
taḍapai raḍapai maradachha .

songs.title: euṭaa naamakao uchachaaraṇa garayao yao oṭhalae yao dharataeemaa
lyrics: kao. (euṭaa naamakao uchachaaraṇa garayao yao oṭhalae
yao dharataeemaa thaahaa bhao’ sawaraga kae hao) (2)
1. chaaraaitaira bagaee hainḍanae yao haawaa jasataai halakaa bhayao chaitata maerao,
aakaashabaaṭaai uड़ee jaanae yao charaeelae chauड़ee lagayao chaitata maerao (2)
kauna baolaee baolaera kauna bhaakaa khaolaera bataau manamaa kae bhairahaechha
ekalao udaasa yao mana haera naachayao yasa naamalae udadhaara bhayao
paapaeekao aaja Yeshu naamalae
2. parashamsaakaa dhawanaiharaoolae uchaalaaum haृdaya satautaikaa dhaunaharaoolae
gaunyajaiekao dharataeekao gaanaa aakaashamaathai uṭhaera banaosa‌ sabaasanaa (2)
yao chhaṭao jaeewanakao chhaṭao gaoraeṭaomaa jaeewaita paramaeshawarakao garaaun aaraadhanaa

songs.title: euṭaai banaaunauhaosa‌ euṭaai banaaunauhaosa‌
lyrics: euṭaai banaaunauhaosa‌, euṭaai banaaunauhaosa‌,
euṭaai banaaunauhaosa‌, haamaeelaaee (2)
euṭaai banaaunauhaosa‌, paitaakao naaunma,
paitaakao naaunmaa haamaeelaaee (2)
euṭaai banaaunauhaosa‌, Yeshukao naaunmaa
Yeshukao naaunmaa haamaeelaaee (2)
euṭaai banaaunauhaosa‌, pawaitaraaatamaamaa,
pawaitaraaatamaamaa haamaeelaaee (2)

songs.title: euṭaai banaaunauhaosa‌ haamaee bishwaseelaaee
lyrics: euṭaai banaaunauhaosa‌ haamaee bishwaseelaaee
ekataakao aatamaalae bharanauhaosa‌ haamaeelaaee, pawaitara aatamaa,
euṭaai aatamaa, euṭaai waichaara, euṭaai haृdaya saृjanauhaosa‌ haamaeemaa,
Yeshu saृjanauhaosa‌ haamaeemaa pawaitara aatamaa .

songs.title: eka eka pala baढ़kara eka-eka mainaṭaom para
lyrics: eka - eka pala baढ़kara eka-eka mainaṭaom para
eka - eka ghaṇaṭaa banara pala baita rahaa haai,
daina aura hapatae, mahainae aura saala baita rahaa haai kaala
daina bahauta baurae haue haai, awasarakao bahaumaoolaya jaanakara
Yeshu kaee ichachhaa maem haimamata sae baढ़tae rahao ॥

songs.title: eka kadama aghai dasha kadama pachhai saranae bishwasee
lyrics: eka kadama aghai, dasha kadama pachhai saranae bishwasee haoinaaun haai
ghaunḍaamaa gaee saya kadama aghai saranae bishwasee haaun haamaee .
eka thaukaee saukaee, saya thaukaee nadaee, haatamaa hat mailaaee layounae ho raajaya Yeshukaai .
bishwasee jaagaaun, Yeshukao premamaa ekataakao naaraa lagaaoon haai
phasala paakaisakayao, daain garanae baelaa bhao’, samsaarakao aanganaaimaa .

songs.title: eka ṭauṭae haue daila nae taujhakao haee paukaaraa haai
lyrics: kao. eka ṭauṭae haue daila nae, taujhakao haee paukaaraa haai
aajaa haai masaeeha maujhakao, taeraa haee sahaaraa (2)
1. jaba saatha maerae taoo haai, samsaara kaee saagara maem
tauphaanaom kaa ḍara kayo haai, hara maauja kainaaraa haai (2‌)
eka ṭauṭae haue daila nae... .
2. thaoड़a saa eesaaraa haee maerae laie kaaphaee haai
eka ḍaubanae waalaom kao tainakae kaa sahaaraa haai (2)
eka ṭauṭae haue daila nae... .
3. sachachaaee kaee raahaom sae naramao kadama baढ़akae
maujhakao taeraee raahaom maem hara jaulama gawaaraa haai (2)
eka ṭauṭae haue daila nae... .

songs.title: eka daina jagatalaaee chhaड़nauchha eka daina maraṇamaa paranauchha
lyrics: kao. eka daina jagata‌laaee chhaड़nauchha, eka daina maraṇamaa paranauchha
aaunau khaalai alaika daina basanau, eka daina sabaai thaoka chhaड़nauchha
1. dhana-samapatatai, maayo pairataee jaandaainana‌ sanga yaee
samayalaaee wayaratha waitaaunchhaau kaina ? sadaa narahanae taee .
2. naasainae jagata‌maa saukha-chaaina garachhaau sabaai yao wayaratha chha
sadaa narahanae jaeewanamaa bhaoolaen wayarathaai-wayaratha chha .
3. mahala banaaee bagaainchaa lagaaee basadachhana‌ raanaee
bagaainchaamaa sadhaain baulabaula baoladaaina, yao panai wayarathaai ho .
4. baalakapana taa khaelamaa baitayao, jawaanaee paapamaa chha
marae phaerai kae yoda chhaaina narakamaa jaanauchha .
5. jagatagauraoo saaraa laokakaa maृtayaumaa parae
maraigae sabaai raajaa-mahaaraajaa maaṭaomaa mailae .
6. paapakao kaṣhamaa parabhau Yeshukao ragatamaa paaunaechhaaun
bishwas unamaa ahailae gara maukatai paaunaechhaau .

songs.title: eka daina maranaai parachha nayoyamaa paranaai parachha maanaisa jaatai
lyrics: kao. eka daina maranaai parachha, nayoyamaa paranaai parachha, maanaisa jaatai sabaai
eka daina maranaai parachha haraeka maanaisa sabaai nayoyamaa paranaai parachha,
paratayaeka aatamaa sabaai, eka daina maranaai parachha .
1. maaṭaokao sharaeera maaṭaaimaa mailachha, aatamaa eeshawarakahaan nayoya hauna jaanachha,
nayoyalae paapaee ra dharamaeelaaee chhauṭayoun chha .
2. maukataikao sanadaesha saunadaaina jasalae, Yeshumaa bishwas garadaaina jasalae,
paapaeekao sathaana paaundachha usalae .
3. paapaeelaaee daṇaḍa aganaikao shaasanaa, paeeḍaa waedanaa, yaugayaugakao yotanaa,
daaharaa kaiṭaai chha bhayonaka narakamaa .
4. Yeshumaa bishwas garanae jao wayakatai, ṭhaharainachhana‌ dharamaee paraapata garachhana‌ maukatai,
waasa garachhana sawaragamaa yauga yaugakaa naimatai .
5. maukataidaana dainae Yeshukao naama hao, dharamaee taulayounae unamaa bishwas hao,
upanaaoo hae maitara, sarala upaaya yao .

songs.title: eka dainakao kauraa gaalaeelamaa jaba parabhau Yeshu ghaumadathae
lyrics: 1. eka dainakao kauraa gaalaeelamaa jaba parabhau Yeshu ghaumadathae
saba aamaaharaoo naanaeeharaoolaaee unakahaan layoethae .
2. unalae kaakhamaa laiee haraekalaaee premalae aashaiṣha‌kao hat raakhae
yaee saanaaharaoo makahaan aauna daeoo, parabhaulae bhanaethae .
3. khaushaee waichaara ra namara sawabhaawa eka-erakaalaaee daekhaaee dayo
hae parabhau, maerao haृdayamaa tapaaeemkao sawaraga banaosa‌ .
4. yasa raharalaagadao samsaaramaa eeshawarakao prem ra mahaimaa
jasalae bhaeṭachha tyo dhanaya haosa‌ saba ṭhaaunmaa eeshawara chhana‌ .

songs.title: eka baarakao jaunaee yao laanau ta kae chha ra maraera jaanae ho
lyrics: kao. eka baarakao jaunaee yao, laanau ta kae chha ra, maraera jaanae ho
jaeewana yahaan yao amara chhaaina naai, (maaṭaomaa mailanae hao) (2)
1. maृtayaupachhai tara jaeewana arakao chha bishwasee sabaailaaee
bishwas garaaun na (sawaragaeeya paitaalaaee) (2)
2. karaoosakao nairadayaee maृtayaulaaee sahanau parabhau naai aaunaubhao’
unaailae haamarao paapa (uṭhaai laanaubhao’) (2)
3. ja-jasalae unamaathai bishwas garanaechha naasha haunae chhaaina naai
paaunaechhana‌ tainaailae (ananata jaeewana) (2)

songs.title: eka madhaura aawaaja maaim saunataa haun karaoosa kae paasa
lyrics: kao. eka madhaura aawaaja maaim saunataa haun, karaoosa kae paasa baulaanaee jao
payora bharaee aawaaja maaim saunataa haun, anaugaraha jala barasataee jao .
1. parabhau jaeewana jalakaee maujhae, aaja mailataa jao kaewala taerae paasa
aaja phaailataa haun maaim hat rakha maujhae taoo apanae saatha (2)
eka madhaura aawaaja... .
2. parabhau jagakaa ujayolaa haai taoo, mamgalamaya saubahakaa raajaa taoo
aawaaja e jaeewana saunataa rahaa haun sharaṇa taeraee maaim karataa rahaa haun (2)
eka madhaura aawaaja... .

songs.title: eka maitara maile paaekao chhau payora garanae aghaidaekhai
lyrics: 1. eka maitara maile paaekao chhau payora garanae aghaidaekhai
prem saootaralae taanae unalae, malaaee sangagatamaa baandhaee,
ra maerao haृdaya yasatao chha kahailayoi unalaaee natayogaee
ma kharaeeṣhaṭakao haun, kharaeeṣhaṭa maeraa hauna‌ sadaasarawadaakao lagi .
2. eka maitara maile paaekao chhau, taraaṇa dainau unaee marae
jaeewana daana ra unakao saatha kharaeeṣhaṭa aaphaailaaee daiihaalae,
ma aaphanaa sabaai tauchachha maanachhau, daataakao lagi raakhaee
haृdaya saamaratha jaeewana sabaai unakaa sadhaainkaa lagi .
3. eka maitara maile paaekao chhau, unakao ho sabaai saamaratha
yotaraamaa maerao agauwaa jasalae sawaraga paurayounchhana‌,
sawaraga daeshakao daekhachhau mahaima, tyo malaaee saahasa dainachha
aba paharaa kaama ra laड़ain taba waisharaama sadhaain haunachha .
4. eka maitara maile paaekao chhau, dayolau saanchao, napara
khaooba janyonaee raajaa, agauwaa, saamarathaee, rakaṣhaa garanae,
yasatao prem garanaedaekhai kauna shakatai malaaee chhauṭayounchha ?
kae jaeewana, maृtayau sawaraga, naraka ? haoina, ma unakaai haunachhau .

songs.title: ekataakao saootaramaa (baandhanauhaosa‌ haamaeelaaee) (2)
lyrics: kao. (ekataakao saootaramaa (baandhanauhaosa‌ haamaeelaaee) (2) premakao ḍaoraeelae) (2)
(naṭauṭaosa‌ yao kharaeeṣhaṭaeeya prem haamaeemaa,
jabasamama kharaeeṣhaṭakao aagamana haunana) (2)
1. euṭaai paramaeshawarakao sanataana haaun haamaee,
euṭaai kharaeeṣhaṭakao ragatalae kainaiekaa haamaee (2)
euṭaai naaunmaa bapataisamaa laiekaa,
(baandhanauhaosa‌ haamaeelaaee premakao ḍaoraeelae) (2)
2. sawaragaeeya raajayakao sanataana haaun haamaee,
karaoosakao jhaṇaḍaa samsaaramaa phaailaaundaai (2)
uccha paaranae mahaimaita naaun Yeshukao,
(baandhanauhaosa‌ haamaeelaaee premakao ḍaoraeelae) (2)

songs.title: gama ho tao mausakauraao hara ghaड़ee gaunagaunaao
lyrics: kao. gama ho tao mausakauraao, hara ghaड़ee gaunagaunaao
aao mailakara, gaeeta masaeeha kae, samga hamaarae gaao rae gaao . (2)
1. jaaisae patathara para ghaisatae haee, hainaa ramga laataa haai (2)
gama mausaibata maem haee inasaana, usasae bala paataa haai
mata ghabaraao, sahatae jaao, Yeshu kaa tauma samga apanaao .
2. yae jaeewana eka lamabaa saphara haai, chalatae haee jaanaa haai (2)
Yeshu masaeeha gara saatha haai apanae, phaira kayo ghabaraanaa haai
jaisanae kahaa maaim, aayo haoon kai, tauma jaeewanakao paalao lae paalao ॥

songs.title: gara upaasanaa parabhaukao jaatai gara jayajaya pawaitara jaatai
lyrics: gara upaasanaa parabhaukao jaatai, gara jayajaya pawaitara jaatai
gara jayajaya pawaitara jaatai, hallelujah pawaitara paitaa
(pawaitara paitaa, pawaitara paitaa, pawaitara paitaa) (2) hallelujah .

songs.title: gara bakhaana pauraanao sawaragakao kauraakao
lyrics: 1. gara bakhaana pauraanao, sawaragakao kauraakao
Yeshukao mahaimaa jaanaoon, Yeshukao prem kae bhao’,
gara bakhaana sajailao, saanaa baalakalaaee jhaain
nairabala ra haairaana chhau, chhau nairadhao ra paapamaya .
kao. gara bakhaana pauraanao (3) Yeshukao prem kae bhao’
2. gara bakhaana baisataaraai, ma baujhana sakaoon baata
udaekakao tyo udadhaaraai, jao maeṭanae paapakao gata,
gara bakhaana daohaorayoee chaanḍaai bairasanachhau ma
baihaanakao shaeeta paraaee daiunsao rahanaechha .
3. gara bakhaana kamalao, sanga yatana sawara ra dhaeera
Yeshulae paraaṇa daiihaalae, udadhaara garaaee sathaira;
gara bakhaana saba samaya, yasataai garaee naai
malaaee gaohaara saanchachaai, saba khaanchao haundaamaai .
4. gara bakhaana pauraanao, daekhaa paradaamaa
yasa laokakao wayaratha maanakao dhaeraai ichachhaa garachhau ma
an anai jaba ma khaojaoon sawaragalaokakao sataya maana
gara bakhaana pauraanao, Yeshulae garachhana‌ taraaṇa .

songs.title: garaaun jayajayakaara haamaraa parabhaukao unaai hauna‌ haamaraa saanchao
lyrics: kao. garaaun jayajayakaara haamaraa parabhaukao,
unaai hauna‌ haamaraa saanchao gaoṭhaalao
haraṣhaita haृdaya laiee dhanyawad chaढ़aoon,
bhakataisahaita sabalae daṇaḍawata‌ garaaun
1. paapakao daṇaḍa bhayangakara naraka, kamaai yao maeraai thaiyao (2)
dharama-karamakaa chayodaralae ḍhaakaee paapa ḍhaakaiindaainathayao
thaukaai ra kauṭaai sahanaubhao’ jatai (bachaauna paraaṇa daie) (2)
2. haeradachhau kalawaraee ḍaanड़alaaee, ṭaangaie parabhau karaoosamaa (2)
haatamaa kaanṭaee, khauṭaṭaamaa kaanṭaee, shairamaa taeewara paeeड़a
sahae saba paeeड़a, dauhkha ashaanatai (thaie saba maeraai naimatai)
3. achamamaaikao rahaechha prem Yeshukao ma dauṣhaṭa ghaृṇaitaparatai (2)
jaba paapamaa ‘thaen kharaeeṣhaṭa maeraa marae saba maeraa paapalaaee baokaee
shaudadha malaaee paaradaai, bahaekao ragatalae (dharamaee malaaee taulayoe) (2)
4. pathaika narakakao kharaeeṣhaṭalae phairaaundaa sawaragakao yotaraee banae (wa)
sawaraga maerao daesha bhao’ yahaan paradaeshaee baढ़chhau parataiphala aghai
daekhadaa parabhaulaaee paeeड़a bhaulanaechhau (asaeema waisharaama paaunaechha) (2)

songs.title: gahabharai aanshaukao dhaaraa premaee parabhau Yeshu raajaakao
lyrics: kao. gahabharai aanshaukao dhaaraa premaee parabhau Yeshu raajaakao
katarao paeera Yeshu raajaalaaee kalawaraeekao tyo sharaapaita karunaimaa (2)
1. aaphanao bhananau kaohaee thaiena tayahaan na taa sangaai raoee dainae (2)
naraooo bhananae euṭaai thaiena sabaai naai raoowaaee dainae (2)
taimaee panai naraoowaaoo haai parabhaulaaee hao... hao...
2. dauhkha ra kaṣhaṭa bhaogadaai bhaokaa ra payosaa banaee (2)
garaeeba ra dau:khaee bhaye nainadaa ra gailalaa sahandaai (2)
ajhaai panai naraoowaaoo haai parabhaulaaee hao... hao...

songs.title: gahairao gahairao o atai gahairao maerao haृdayamaa (2)
lyrics: gahairao, gahairao o atai gahairao, maerao haृdayamaa (2)
Yeshulaaee prem garachhaau kai ? tairamao haृdayamaa ?
hao, ma Yeshulaaee prem garachhau maerao haृdayamaa .

songs.title: gahairao premalae, prem garayao malaaee
lyrics: kao. (gahairao premalae, prem garayao malaaee) (2)
