(aamaakao bhanda gahairao tyo prema) (2)
(dhanaya tapaaeem sarawashakataimaana tapaaeem jhaai chhaaina araoo mahaana‌) (2)
(halalaelaooyoha halalaelaooyoha) (4)
1. tapaaeemlaaee parabhau bhaulanae ma chhauinna
tapaaeemlaaee Yeshu chhaḍanae ma chhauinna
tapaaeemkao saathamaa jaiunnaechhau
tapaaeemkao hat samaaee hainḍanaechhau .
2. tapaaeem naai maerao asala gaoṭhaalao
tapaaeem naai parabhau atai premailao
sadaa-sadaa mahaimaa parabhau
aaraadhanaa parasamsaa Yeshu .

songs.title: gaau bajaaoo uhaanlaaee uchaalaau saasa haunae haraeka paraaṇaeelae
lyrics: gaau bajaaoo uhaanlaaee uchaalaau (2)
saasa haunae haraeka paraaṇaeelae (2)
parama parabhaukao parashamsaa gaharaaum (2)
taurahaee baeeṇaa saaramgaee bajaaee
khaaijaḍaee ra naachagaana saathamaa
taara baajaa baansauraee bajaaee
aau jhayolaeekao saathamaa
taalaee bajaaoo, thaumaalaaee uchaalaoo (2)
saasa haunae haraeka paraaṇaeelae (2)
parama parabhaukao parashamsaa garaaum (2)

songs.title: gaaun basataee taraaee anai pahaaड़ pakhaeraomaa raoirahaechhana‌
lyrics: kao. gaaun, basataee, taraaee anai pahaaड़-pakhaeraomaa
raoirahaechhana‌ maanaisaharaoo sadhaain andhayoraomaa
yasaailae haamaee jaaoon kharaeeṣhaṭakao sanadaesha saunaauna (2)
1. asataya phayonkaee satayataa khaojanae udadaeshaya mahaana‌
saphala jaeewana wayataita garana nairaasha namaana (2)
yao kaama haamaee samahaalachhaaum, parabhau, yao jaimamaa haamarao bhao’
sahaee baaṭao pakaraee hainड़dachhaaun, masaeeha, yao paraṇa haamarao ho (2)
2. jhaukaena shaira ratataibhara panai jhana‌ ajha uccha ‘thayao
maanaisakao jasatao maraṇa haoina kharaeeṣhaṭatawa jhalakanathayao
khaedaokaa pahaaड़ katai ho katai saamaunanae taerasainathae
taee baidhanabaadhaa haṭaaunae paraarathanaa sadaaiwa jaaraee ‘thae
maanaisa bhaye maanaisajasataai jaiuna chaahanachhaaun
satayakao sanadaesha saunaaee baढ़na chaahanachhaaun .

songs.title: gaaundaai aayou lahaai satayakao sanadaesha
lyrics: kao. kaeṭaa : gaaundaai aayou lahaai satayakao sanadaesha
kataai chhaaina araoo yao bhanda kaunaai baesha (2)
kaeṭaee : taimarao lagi lahaai maukataikao khabara
baraee laai laai garaaum jaeewanakao rahara (2)
1. kaeṭaa : dharama karama garana maanaisa eeshawaralaaee chaahainana
karama garae panai eeshawaralaaee paainana .
kaeṭaee : paapa bhanae manamaa raakhaee haunana
taimaeelae paae napaaera kasaailaaee haunana .
sabaailae : yao ta sabaai maanaisakao bharamaa maatara haolaa .
kaeṭaa : khaojaera eeshawara paae bhananau sharama maatara haunana .
kaeṭaa : eeshawara aaphaai lahaai khaojachhana‌ haai maanaisalaaee
kaṭhaai maanaisa tara baujhadaainana‌ yao kauraalaaee .
kaeṭaee : eeshawara aae lahaai maanaisalaaee bhaeṭanalaaee
baraee laai laai maanaisakao paapa maeṭanalaaee .
2. kaeṭaa : janamaaidaekhai maanaisa paapaee haunachha
paapaee maanaisadaekhai eeshawara ṭaaढ़a haunachha .
kaeṭaee : paapakao maola tairana balai haunaparachha
chaokhao balai bhae paapaai naasha hanachha .
sabaailae : maanaisakaa kauraa garaee chaokhaa haunana haai .
kaeṭaee : parabhau baahaeka chaokhao araoo kao pao haunachha rae ?
kaeṭaa : balai bhae lahaai eeshawara aaphaai naai
kaṭhaai marae unaee kaaṭhaaikao karunaimaa .
kaeṭaee : eeshawaralae lahaai bagaae ragata
baraee laai laai baujhaau bachaauna yao jagata .
3. kaeṭaa : taimarao haamarao paapakao balaee bhaye dainae
Yeshu baahaeka araoo chhaaina eeshawara naai .
kaeṭaee : wayarathaai taimaee khaojachhaau kaina araoo eeshawaralaaee
garahaṇa gara eeshawaralaaee bishwasee bhaye .
sabaailae : taimaeelaaee panai khaojairahaekaa chhana‌ unaailae
yahaee chha sadhaaim sataya kauraa araoo khaojachhaaum kae .

songs.title: gaaundaai jaaaun parabhaukao mahaimaa unaaikao janama daiwasamaa
lyrics: kao. gaaundaai jaaaun parabhaukao mahaimaa unaaikao janama daiwasamaa
haansadaai baढ़aun unakaai saewaamaa jagaaundaai naaulao bhaawanaa
unaaikao janama daiwasamaa, unaaikao janama daiwasamaa
gaaundaai jaaaun parabhaukao mahaimaa, haansadaai baढ़aun unakaai saewaamaa
1. khaushaeekao yao sausamaachaara, phaailaaaun haai daishaai chaara (2)
aaunaubhayao parabhau samsaaramaa, naimatayoaun haai unalaaee haृdayamaa .
2. sawaragaraajakao waaibhawalaaee tayogaera, aae maanaisa raoopa laiera (2)
aaunaubhayao parabhau samsaaramaa, naimatayoaun haai unalaaee haृdayamaa .
3. paapaeekao bainataee saunanalaaee, sawaragakaa ḍhaokaa khaolanalaaee (2)
aaunaubhayao parabhau samsaaramaa, naimatayoaun haai unalaaee haृdayamaa .

songs.title: gaaundaai rahanachhau jaeewana yotaraamaa kaewala Yeshukao chha satautai
lyrics: kao. gaaundaai rahanachhau jaeewana yotaraamaa kaewala Yeshukao chha satautai
dhanyawad maanaaun hae bishwaseegaṇa mailaekao chha maukatai
1. ho kasatao aananada paapa-kaṣhamaa shaanatai tainakaa ma umaedawaara
maaukaa chha malaaee saunaauna sabalaaee Yeshukao sausamaachaara,
khaolao haai daanakao payorao parabhau kasaraee bahaekao
upayaoga jasakao garana najaanaee sharaṇamaa paraekao .
2. jaeewana haai maerao samaya saeemaita kasaraee chalaaunau
saikaaunauhaosa‌ parabhau paratayaeka naimaeṣhalaaee kaamalaagadao banaaunau,
tapaaeemkao saewaa garanae awasara mailaekao chha malaaee
jhalajhala balanae jayaotai ma banaoon satayakao phala phalaaee .
3. daana maile paaen, sathaana maile paaen aatamaa ra sawaragakao
samsaaramaai basaee banaen ma yotaraee sawaragaeeya maaragakao,
waishawalae jasatao aashaa garadainan paaunalaaee maukataidaana
aashaa ho maerao jaeewanakao maukauṭa parataiphala mahaana‌ .

songs.title: gaauna sabaailae parabhaukao satautai mailaera sabaai saृṣhaṭai (2)
lyrics: kao. gaauna sabaailae parabhaukao satautai, mailaera sabaai saृṣhaṭai (2)
halalaelaooyoha, mailaera sabaai saृṣhaṭai
laau bhana sabalae jaya, halalaelaooyoha, jaiiuṭhae Yeshu kharaeeṣhaṭa
1. maृtayaukao banadhana taoड़era uhaanlae chaihaanalaaee chhaड़naubhao’ (2)
jayawanata parabhau, jao aaja haamarao taraaṇakarataa haunaubhayao, halalaelaooyoha, taraaṇakarataa haunaubhao’ .
2. maृtayaukao bhayalae raajaya garanae chhaaina, Yeshu masaeeha maitara (2)
haunauhaunachha haamarao taaraṇahaara, saunana hae maitara, hallelujah saunana haunaubhao’ .

songs.title: gaaoon kharaeeṣhaṭaeeya jhauṇaḍa sabaai mailaee parabhaukao satautai (2)
lyrics: kao. gaaoon kharaeeṣhaṭaeeya jhauṇaḍa, sabaai mailaee parabhaukao satautai (2)
1. haृdaya-waiṇaakao taara bajaaee (2) satautai-mahaimaa daeoo maukataidaataalaaee,
aphanao saृjanahaaralaaee (jayajayakaara garaaun sawaramaa sawara mailaaee) (2) .
2. eeraṣhayo ra dawaiṣhakao jaala phaaḍaee (2) ekataakao saootaramaa sabaailaaee baandhaee
premakao sanadaesha baanḍaee (kaṭhainaaeelaaee para saaraee) (2) .
3. anadhakaara yao jagakao jayaotai anai (2) maiṭhaasa dainae nauna banaee
haamaee naoona banaee, (karaoosalaaee alagayoaun saakaṣhaee banaee) (2) .

songs.title: gaaoo sawaraai uchaalaee bajaaundaai taalaee (2)
lyrics: kao. gaaoo sawaraai uchaalaee bajaaundaai taalaee (2)
haamarao paramaeshawarakao garaaum haai mahaimaa
haamarao dauwaai haataai uchaalaee (2)
1. baansauraee ra waiṇaa saarangaeekao sawaramaa jha‌yolaeekao jhanakaa bajaaundaai (2)
haamaee sabaai mailaeejaulaee uhaankao naaulaaee
ekaai saathamaa uchaalaee (2)
2. haataemaalao garadaai naachadaai ramaaudaai ghanaghana maadala ghanakaaudaai (2)
tanalae manalae parashamsaa garadaai
uhaankao naaunlaaee uchaaladaai (2)

songs.title: gaaoon sawaraai uchaalaee bajaaudaai taalaee (2)
lyrics: kao. gaaoon sawaraai uchaalaee bajaaudaai taalaee (2)
haamarao paramaeshawarakao garaaum haai mahaimaa
haamarao dauwaai haataai uchaalaee (2)
1. baansauraee ra waiṇaa saarangaeekao sawaramaa jhayolaeekao jhanakaa bajaaundaai (2)
haamaee sabaai mailaeejaulaee uhaankao naaunlaaee
ekaai saathamaa uchaalaee (2)
2. haataemaalae garadaai naachadaai ramaaudaai ghanaghana maadala ghanakaaudaai (2)
tanalae manalae parashamsaa garadaai
uhaankao naaunlaaee uchaaladaai (2)

songs.title: gaaoon hallelujah parabhaulaaee (2) (gaaoon halalaelaooyoha) (2)
lyrics: 1. (gaaoon hallelujah parabhaulaaee) (2) (gaaoon halalaelaooyoha) (2)
gaaoon hallelujah parabhaulaaee .
2. (Yeshu samsaarakaa jayaotai hauna‌) (2) (Yeshu samsaarakao) (2)
Yeshu samsaarakaa jayaotai hauna‌ .
3. (raaja garana phaerai aaunaechhana‌) (2) (raaja garana phaerai) (2)
raaja garana phaerai aaunaechhana‌ .

songs.title: gaaera hainḍanae shaoka haamarao haoina
lyrics: kao. gaaera hainḍanae shaoka haamarao haoina
paaera saachanae daana haamarao haoina
shaubha sa‌nadaesha yao Yeshu janamaekao gaoṭhaaimaa (2)
1. (ragatakao balailae bhaijaekao maaṭaomaa
eeshawarakao naigaaha parayao maanaisakao paapaaimaa) (2)
daeuraalaee bhamjayongangamaa eeshawara khaojanaeharaoohao (2)
shaubha sanadaesha yao Yeshu janamaekao gaoṭhaaimaa (2)
2. (garaeeba ra dhanaeekao janyonaee ra maurakhakao
bhaedabhaawamaa baachanae hae paiḍaita maanaisa hao) (2)
ashaanataimaa shaanatai khaojanaeharaoo ho (2)
shaubha sanadaesha yao Yeshu janamaekao gaoṭhaaimaa (2)

songs.title: gaao gaao jaya kae gaeeta gaao taalaee bajaakae
lyrics: kao. gaao gaao jaya kae gaeeta gaao, taalaee bajaakae tauma gaao
Yeshu raajaa jainadaa hauaa haalalaelaooyoha, khaushaee sae yaha sabakao saunaao (2‌)
1. kabara para thaa eka baड़a patathara, daekhao kaaisae haṭa gayo waha
raomaee raajaya kao maohara banada na rakha sakaee
kabhaye bhaye eeshawara kae pautara kao .
2. rao mata rao mata wailaama karao mata, galaeela maem jaakara kahao yaha baata
kai waha wachana anausaara kabara sae naikalaa,
jaakara saunaao sausamaachaara .
3. hananaa kaaiphaa pauranaiyaom kaee sabhaa, khatarae sae hauee paraeshaana
anadhakaara kaee saamaratha, khatama haonae para
bahauta ghabaraayo shaaitaana .
4. unchae karao saira darawaajaom, aataa haai baड़a baadashaahaa
narasaimgae saitaarae aura tabalae bajaakara
gaao tauma haalalaelaooyoha... ॥

songs.title: gaaaun gaaaun jaya gaeeta gaaaun taalaee bajaaera
lyrics: kao. gaaaun-gaaaun jaya gaeeta, gaaaun taalaee bajaaera gaaaun (2)
Yeshu raajaa baauraee uṭhae halalaelaooyoha, ramaaera saunaaoo samaachaara (2)
1. chaihaanamaa thaiyao tyo ṭhaoolao ḍhaungagaa, haṭayao haera kasaraee tyo (2)
raomaee raajayakao maohara, banadhana raakhana sakadaaina ekalaauṭae pautara eeshawarakao .
2. naraooo-naraooo, wailaapa nagara, gaalaeelamaa daeoo samaachaara (2)
kai kharaeeṣhaṭa baauraee uṭhae wachanaanausaara tauraunata saunaaoo yao parachaara .
3. hananaa kaaiphaa paooraa nayoyakao sabhaa ḍaralae bhae wayokaula (2)
anadhakaarakao shakatai naṣhaṭa haunaalae saaharao aatataiyao shaaitaana .
4. bishwaseeharaoo shairalaaee unbhao uṭhaaaun aaundaaichhana‌ mahaaraajaa (2)
narasaingagaa, saitaara ra tabalaa bajaaaun, paukaaraau hallelujah .

songs.title: gaaaun gaeeta parabhaukao mailaijaulaee chhaaun saba jao (2)
lyrics: kao. gaaaun gaeeta parabhaukao mailaijaulaee chhaaun saba jao (2)
1. parabhau haamarao gaoṭhaalaa sabalaaee ghaṭaee kae haolaa ?
haraiyao-haraiyao ghaansaaimaa sabalaaee charaaee laieehainड़laana‌ (2)
2. paurayoee nairamala nadaeemaa waisharaama dainachhana‌ manaaimaa,
aaphanaai naaunkao naimataimaa ḍaorayounchhana‌ ṭhaeeka baaṭaomaa (2)
3. maृtayau chhaayo taraaeemaa hainड़chhau jaokhaima naḍaraaee
unakao laṭaṭhaee samaaee shaanatai dainachhana‌ haamaeelaaee (2)
4. saamau jaba waairaee aayao haamaraalaagai bhaoja raakhayao
haamaraa payolaa umalaiyao shairamaa taela lagaaidaiyao (2)
5. naishachaya parabhaukao dayo jaeewanabharai haoirahalaa
jaba sawaragamaa paugaaunlaa sadaasarawadaai basaaunlaa (2)

songs.title: gaaaun masaeehakao jayagaana ra dhanaya bhana unakao naama
lyrics: kao. gaaaun masaeehakao jayagaana ra dhanaya bhana unakao naama,
paृthawaee talakao nara-naaraeekao (2) eka sahaaraa masaeeha (2)
1. maukataikao pathalaaee parachaara garadaai jaeewana masaeehalae baitaae
paapa ra sharaapa maeṭaauna masaeehalae karausamaa ragata bagaae .
2. anadhakaara jagakao andhayoraolaaee premaee masaeehalae haṭaae
prem parachaaradaai, prem baढ़aundaai eeraṣhayo ra dawaeṣha maeṭaae .
3. pathaikaharaulaaee patha darashaaundaai eeshawara naataa jaoड़ae
paapakao banadhanamaa haamaee paraethayou payorao masaeehalae chhauṭaae .
4. amaola prem jao masaeehamaa paaunchhaaun tyo chhaaड़ee kahaan jaaaun ?
maukatai ra shaanatai jao unamaa paaunchhaaun jayajayakaara unakaai gaaaun .

songs.title: gaaaun Yeshujaeekao jayagaana gaaaun Yeshujaeekao shaubhanaama
lyrics: kao. gaaaun Yeshujaeekao jayagaana, gaaaun Yeshujaeekao shaubhanaama
1. yaraooshalaema shaharakao, baethalaehaema gaawaainmaa (2)
aaja janamae baalaka, jasakao Yeshu naama (2)
shaanataikao raajaa, Yeshulaaee paraṇaama‌ (2)
2. imamaanauelalae janama laie, haamarao bhawa bhao’ ujayolao (2)
paapakao wainaasha bhayao, satayalae jaitayao (2)
satayakao raajaa, Yeshulaaee paraṇaama‌ (2)
3. masaeeha Yeshu awataara bhae, ghaृṇaa, haelaa ṭaaढ़o bhayao (2)
prem janamayao, prem baढ़yao, prem baढ़daai gao’ (2)
premailao raajaa, Yeshulaaee paraṇaama‌ (2)

songs.title: gaaaum hallelujah uhaankao jaya gaaaum sabaai saृṣhaṭai
lyrics: gaaaum hallelujah uhaankao jaya
gaaaum sabaai saृṣhaṭai uhaankao jaya (2)
parabhau mahaana chha satautaeekao yaogaya chha (2)

songs.title: gaatae haai bajaatae haai khaushaiyon hama manaatae haai
lyrics: kao. gaatae haai bajaatae haai khaushaiyon hama manaatae haai
kayaomkai paramaeshawara hamaaraa saatha haai . (2)
1. jaisanae aakaasha banaayo, paृthawaee kao bhaye banaayo
saba kauchha usanae banaayo, waha paramaeshawara hamaarae saatha haai (2)
2. jaisanae hamakao banaayo, jaisanae taumakao banaayo
jaisanae sabakao banaayo, waha paramaeshawara hamaarae saatha haai (2)
3. paapa maem kayaom maratae ho payorao, Yeshu kao tauma apanaa banaalao
sabakaa taaraṇa mailaegaa, kayaokai paramaeshawara hamaarae saatha haai (2)

songs.title: gaina gaina kae satautai karaoon maaim upakaaraom kao yoda karaoon maaim
lyrics: kao. gaina gaina kae satautai karaoon maaim, upakaaraom kao yoda karaoon maaim
chakaita karatae haai maujhae taerae kaama, aashaiṣhaom kao yoda karaoon maaim .
1. parabhau nae maujha maem kayo daekhaa thaa,
kai masaeeha nae maujhae chauna laiyo
maujha paapaee para dayo daikhaakara
maeraee dauaan kao usanae sauna laiyo . (2)
2. kaitanae balawaana daunaiyo maem thae
phaira bhaye usanae maujhae baulaayo
apanaee saewaa maem wayasata karakae
apanaee mahaimaakao maujhae daikhaayo ॥ (2)

songs.title: gauṇa ma parabhau taimarao gaaunaechhau (2) satautai parashamsaa taimarao
lyrics: kao. gauṇa ma parabhau taimarao gaaunaechhau (2), satautai, parashamsaa taimarao garanaechhau,
gauṇa ma parabhau taimarao gaaunaechhau (2)
1. paapakao saagaramaa ḍaubairahaethaem aansaukao ghauṭakao paiee hainḍairahaethaem (2)
waichalaita haृdaya laiee ghaumairahaethaem (2) tayasatao samayamaa parabhau malaaee bhaeṭayou . (2)
haatamaa samaataee aaphanao gharamaa layoyoum, haatamaa samaataee aaphanao gharamaa layoyoum .
2. haृdayakaa saba paapalaaee ragatalae dhaoidaiyou, (2) ananata raajayakao bhaagaeedaara banaayou (2)
aananada, shaanatailae bharaidaiyou malaaee (2) ananata jaeewana daiee bachaayou malaaee (2)
aaphanaai kaakhamaa parabhau malaaee raakhayou, aaphanaai kaakhamaa parabhau malaaee raakhayou .
3. jaiundao aashaa daiee sawaraga chaḍhaigayou maerao naimatai ghara tayora garana (2)
aaunaechhaau phaerai malaaee laina (2) yahaee aashaamaa baanchaekao chhau ma (2)
sabaai dauhkhabaaṭa chhauṭakaaraa dainaechhaau, sabaai dauhkhabaaṭa chhauṭakaaraa dainaechhaau .

songs.title: gaetasamanaeekao bagaaimchaamaa Yeshujaee paraarathanaa garanaubhao
lyrics: kao. gaerasamanaeekao bagaaimchaamaa Yeshujaee paraarathanaa garanaubhao’
(haamaee jasatao paapaeelaaee bachaauna) (2), paapakao kachaauraa paiunaubhao (2)
1. kaohaee thaiena tyo madhaya raatamaa Yeshulaaee saatha dainae (2)
aaphanaai chaelaalae (2) panai unalaaee (ekalao chhaaड़idaie) (2)
paraarathanaa gara paraeekaṣhaamaa naparana Yeshulae bhananaubhayao
taimarao maerao naimatai daama tairaera (2) ragatalae kainanaubhayao (2)
2. hataasa udaasa haundaai parabhau paitaalaaee paukaarae (2)
ragatakao thaopaa (2) thaopaa pasainaa (paraarathanaamaa bagaae) (2)
jaagaa rahao pawaitara aatamaamaa Yeshulae samajhaaunaubhao’
taimarao maerao naimatai balaidaana bhae (2) paapadaekhai chhauड़aunaubhao’ (2)

songs.title: gaoṭha gaaeekao pautara paitaakao paapa haamarao karaoosa arakaaikao
lyrics: 1. gaoṭha gaaeekao, pautara paitaakao
paapa haamarao, karaoosa arakaaikao
maukatai haamaeelaaee, jaeewana haamaeelaaee
aananada haamaeelaaee, shaanatai haamaeelaaee .
2. tayasa andhayorao chaisao raatamaa
daootagaṇa aae eeshawara saathamaa
Yeshu pasaraie ḍaoonड़aimaa
gaae daootagaṇa maeeṭhao sawaramaa (maeeṭhao sawaramaa) (2)
3. baethalaehaemakao ekalao gaaunmaa
maraiyamakao saanao kaokhamaa (2)
aagamana eeshawarakao
haraṣha, aananada sabaailaaee naai bhao’ (sabaailaaee naai bhao’) (2)

songs.title: gaoṭhaalaharaoo bhaeड़alaaee raatamaa kauradaai thaie
lyrics: 1. gaoṭhaalaharaoo bhaeड़alaaee raatamaa kauradaai thaie
taba sawaragadaekhai daoota oralaee mahaimaasaatha aae .
2. laau naḍaraaoo daootalae bhanae ma parachaara garanalaaee
aaekao chhau, saba maanachhaelaaee sausamaachaara dainalaaee .
3. taimarao lagi chha, janamaekaa daaooda raajaa kauladaekhai
taraaṇakarataa parabhau aajakao daina daekhana paaunchhaau taimaee .
4. eka baalaka taimaee daekhanaechhaau daaoodakao shaharamaa
laugaamaa baeharaee raakhaekao ra pasaraekao ḍaunड़maa .
5. jaba yatai kauraa bhanaethae, achaanaka aaethae
saaraa sawaragadaootagaṇa jao yao gaeeta aananadasaatha gaae .
6. gauṇaanauwaada haosa‌ eeshawarakao ra jagamaa haosa‌ shaanatai
haosa‌ khaushaee maanachhaemaa ahailae anai sadaabharai .

songs.title: gaoṭhaalao maeraa hauna‌ parabhau na ghaṭaee chha malaaee
lyrics: 1. gaoṭhaalao maeraa hauna‌ parabhau na ghaṭaee chha malaaee
haraiyao ghaansakao chauramaa charaaundachhana‌ malaaee .
2. unalae saukha-chaainakao paanaeemaa ḍaorayoundachhana‌ malaaee
ra paarachhana‌ paunarajaeewaita paraaṇa dharama maaragamaa hainड़aee .
3. jaba hainड़chhau maृtayaukao chhaayomaa na ḍara na chha phaikaraee
laaurao ra laṭhaṭhaeelae unakaa dainachhana‌ malaaee shaanatai .
4. bhaoja tayora garadachhana‌ unalae shataraukao saamaunanaemaa
taela maerao shairamaa maladachhana‌, paokhainachha kachaauraa .
5. mapachhai laagachha jaeewanabhara bhalaaee ra karauṇaa
ra paramaeshawarakao gharaaimaa ma rahanaechhau sadaa .

songs.title: ghanakaiyao ghanakaiyao ḍamaphaukao taalaai ghanakaiyao
lyrics: kao. (ghanakaiyao-ghanakaiyao ḍamaphaukao taalaai ghanakaiyao) (2)
paakhaa-pakhaerao tharakaiyao, tharakaiyao pahaaड़-madhaesa,
gaaun-baensaee, ramaailao
khaushaeekao sanadaesha saunaaundaai kharaeeṣhaṭa janama daiwasa manaaundaai
(ghara-aangana-samsaaraai ujayolao) (2),
(ghanakaiyao...) (2)
1. [(naachana maaichayongaga, naachana (haai), naachana aa-haa-aa)
samalaamaa kamamara bhaachana (aa, haa, aa)] (2)
bhawaiṣhayawaaṇaee tyo jao paoorao haunae bhao’
[imamaanauela kharaeeṣhaṭakao janama bhao’ (hao hao)] (2)
(ghanakaiyao...) (2)
2. [(saunana paarangaga, saunana (haai), saunana, (aa, haa, aa)
manamaa kauraa gaunana, gaunana (aa, haa, haa)]
satautai ra parashamsaa garaera parabhaukao
[haृdayamaa unalaaee raakhana (aa, haa, haa)] (2)
(ghanakaiyao...) (2)

songs.title: ghara ghara ghaumaera parabhaulaaee parachaara kasa taimarao kamamara
lyrics: kao. ghara-ghara ghaumaera parabhaulaaee parachaara, kasa taimarao kamamara,
laau haooo tayora, laau haooo tayora, laau haooo tayora
1. paapa ra anadhakaaralae bharaiyao samsaara (2)
dharamakao jayaotai phaailaaunalaaee laau haooo tayora (3)
2. haimamata baandhaee bishwas garaee karaoosalaaee laiee naishaana (2)
Yeshujayaoo, hauna‌ kapataana haamarao, haaranaechha shaaitaana (3)
3. kharaeeṣhaṭakao wachana saunaaunalaaee kamamara sabalae kasaaun (2)
jasataai samkaṭa parae panai pachhaaड़i nahaṭaaun (3)
4. garachhaau jatai kharaeeṣhaṭakao parachaara dauhkha-kaṣhaṭa sahaera (2)
dainachhana‌ unalae parataiphala jaeewanamaa ananata (3)

songs.title: ghara ta maerao yahaan haoeena baadala paaraee chha Yeshulaaee manaparachha
lyrics: 1. ghara ta maerao yahaan haoeena baadala paaraee chha Yeshulaaee manaparachha
mauṭaubharai Yeshukao dhaeraai naai maayo chha mana maerao uḍadaai chha
(baraee laai baraee laai baraee laai mana maerao uḍadaai chha) (2)
2. (karaoosalaaee phaedaaimaa taimaee sagan saaṭaekao maayokao saainao chha) (2)
(saainaolae pairaayao jhanaai paagala baraayao jayonaai daie taimaeelaaee) (2)
(baraee laai baraee laai baraee laai jayonaai daie taimaeelaaee) (2)
3. (jayona mauṭau saaṭaaula maayo pairataee baaṭaaulaa baḍadaai chha chaahanaa) (2)
(chaautaaraeemaa basaera agaamlaomaa kasaera taimarao dailakao dhaḍakana saunaaulaa) (2)
(baraee laai baraee laai baraee laai taimarao dailakao dhaḍakana saunaaulaa) (2)
4. ghara ta maerao yahaan haoeena baadala paaraee chha Yeshulaaee manaparachha
mauṭaubharai Yeshukao dhaeraai naai maayo chha mana maerao uḍadaai chha
baraee laai baraee laai baraee laai mana maerao uḍadaai chha
baraee laai baraee laai baraee laai Yeshulaaee manaparachha

songs.title: ghaama udaaunchha paoorawabaaṭa asataaunchha pasha‍chaimamaa
lyrics: kao. (ghaama udaaunchha paoorawabaaṭa, asataaunchha pasha‍chaimamaa
maeraa kharaeeṣhaṭa Yeshu raajaa, raaja garachhana mamaa) (2)
1. (kaohaee paujachhana ḍhaungagaalaaee, kaohaee paujachhana maooढ़alaaee) (2)
(tara ma paujadachhau jaeewaita parabhaulaaee) (2)
2. (kaohaee garachhana bhaakala, kaohaee garachhana sanaana) (2)
(tara ma garadachhau parashamsaa Yeshukaai) (2)

songs.title: ghaayala unaee maeraai lagi karaoosamaa ghaayala maeraai lagi
lyrics: 1. ghaayala unaee maeraai lagi karaoosamaa ghaayala maeraai lagi
paapalaaee haṭaaee bachaae malaaee, kaaraṇa Yeshu ghaayala maeraai lagi .
2. marae unaee maeraai laagai, karaoosamaa marae maeraai lagi
unaaikao maraṇamaa paaunchhau maukatai, kaaraṇa Yeshu marae maeraai lagi .
3. baaurae unaee maeraai laagai, kabarabaaṭa baaurae maeraai lagi
maृtayaubaaṭa sadaa paaen maukatai, kaaraṇa Yeshu baaurae maeraai lagi .
4. jaiunchhana‌ unaee maeraai laagai, sawaragamaa jaiunchhana‌ maeraai lagi
palapala garachhana‌ maerao lagi wainataee, dhanaya Yeshu jaiunchhana‌ maeraai lagi .
5. aaunchhana‌ unaee maeraai paagai, samsaaramaa aaunchhana‌ maeraai lagi
daekhanaechhau uhaanlaaee khaushaee bhaye, dhanaya Yeshu aaunchhana‌ maeraai lagi .

songs.title: ghaumḍaasamama haoina kamamarasamama haoina
lyrics: kao. ghaumḍaasamama haoina kamamarasamama haoina
chauralaumamaai ḍaubana chaahanachhau
Yeshukao premakao saagaramaa
1. jauraelaee jhaai haoina bhangagaeraee jhaai haoina
chaeela jasataai uḍana chaahanachhau
Yeshukao premakao aakaashamaa
2. chhaaina araoo kaunaai naaun yao dharataeemaa
malaaee gaanuna mana laganae malaaee raoojhana mana laganae
Yeshu naaun maataraai malaaee gaanuna mana laganae
malaaee raoojhana mana laganae

songs.title: ghaumaa ghaumaa kae maaraa
lyrics: ghaumaa ghaumaa kae maaraa (4) daaoodanae gaolaiyatakao gaopana sae maaraa (2)
eka sae nahai, dao sae nahai, taina sae nahai, chaara sae nahai (2)
paancha patathara naadai sae laekara eka patathara sae maaraa (2)
ghaumaa ghaumaa kae maaraa (4) ghaumaa ghaumaa kae maaraa (4)
bala sae nahai, baudadhai sae nahai, taira sae nahai, sakatai sae nahai (2)
paancha patathara naadai sae laekara eka patathara sae maaraa (2)

songs.title: ghaumadaai phairadaai gaaeekao gaoṭhamaa aae gaoṭhaalaaharaoo
lyrics: 1. ghaumadaai phairadaai gaaeekao gaoṭhamaa aae gaoṭhaalaaharaoo
daekhae saanao ḍaunड़maa Yeshu gaoṭhamaa pasarairahaekaa .
kao. haamarao aananadakao daina aayao, dhanaya haamarao maukatai bhao’
gaaoo samsaarakao sabaai saृṣhaṭailae, maanaisa raoopa daie kharaeeṣhaṭalae
2. taaraakao agauwaai paaee aae jayaotaiṣhaeeharaoo
daekhai daṇaḍawata‌ sabalae garaee unalaaee bhaeṭaee chaढ़ae .
3. aaoo sabaai bhaai-bahainaee gaaaun saanchao satautaigaana
bhanaoona‌ sabalae hallelujah garaaun sadhaain mahaimaagaana .

songs.title: ghaoṣhaṇa garachhau udadhaarakao ghaoṣhaṇa garachhau premakao
lyrics: 1. ghaoṣhaṇa garachhau udadhaarakao, ghaoṣhaṇa garachhau premakao
ghaoṣhaṇa garachhau changagaaikao, ghaoṣhaṇa garachhau shaanataikao .
yasa samsaaramaa .
2. parabhau Yeshukao maृtayaudawaaraa, parabhau Yeshukao baauraiuṭhaaimaa
ghaoṣhaṇa garachhau udadhaarakao, ghaoṣhaṇa garachhau premakao .
yasa samsaaramaa .

songs.title: inadaraenaeejasataa rangagabairangagaee taimaraa payoraa-payoraa sapanaaharaoo
lyrics: kao. inadaraenaeejasataa rangagabairangagaee taimaraa payoraa-payoraa sapanaaharaoo
maukataidaataa Yeshusanga parataijanyo banaosa‌ aashaiṣhakao jaeewana paaee
1. samajhaihaera jaeewana naai unakao daana ho
maoolayahaeena ta chhaaina yao daama paraekao ho (2)
baearatha nahaosa‌ jaeewanamaa saitataaimaa paaekao maukatai yao,
maausamajhaain badalaee-badalaee hainड़nae taimarao jainadagaeekaa kaamanaaharaookao
maukataidaataa Yeshusanga parataijanyo banaosa‌ aashaiṣha‌kao jaeewana paaee .
2. yasataai haunachha jaeewanamaa yaee ghaṭaeeharaoo
baadhaa banaee aaunaechhana‌ taee kamaeeharaoo,
ḍaraaee nadaeoo jaeewanamaa, bhara tyo samajhaee Yeshumaa
baadalajasataa halakaa-halakaa, taimaraa payoraa sabaai-sabaai ichachhaaharaookao
maukataidaataa Yeshusanga parataijanyo banaosa‌ aashaiṣhakao jaeewana paaee .

songs.title: isa maṇaḍalaee maem bhaaiyaom hama saba eka haai hama eka haaim
lyrics: kao. isa maṇaḍalaee maem bhaaiyaom, hama saba eka haai hama eka haaim (2)
1. na kaoee oonchaa na kaoee jaeechaa na gaoraa na kaalaa (2)
hama saba... .
2. usakaee najara maem daonaom baraabara mahala ho chhapapaड़ waalaa (2)
hama saba... .
3. usakae paasa jao aanaa chaahae paeelae prem kaa payolaa (2)
hama saba... .
4. na kaoee malayolai na kaoee bamgaalaee, na rae pakakaa naepaalaee (2)
hama saba... .

songs.title: eeshawara chhana‌ premaee bachaae malaaee eeshawara chhana‌ premaee
lyrics: 1. eeshawara chhana‌ premaee bachaae malaaee, eeshawara chhana‌ premaee maeraolaagai .
kao. yasakaaraṇa gaaundaaichhau ra satautai garadaaichhau, eeshawara chhana‌ premaee maeraolaagai .
2. ma paapakao bhaaralae ḍaubaekao thaien ra maerao lagi udadhaara thaiena .
3. taraaṇa dainae Yeshu paraayashaichata bhae, paapakao bhaara anai dau:kha uṭhaae .
4. baढ़aee haosa‌ taimarao, sanaatana premaee, jabasamama jaiunchhau satautai garachhau .

songs.title: eeshawara tapaaeem udaekakaa chhaau apaara mahaanatamakaa
lyrics: 1. eeshawara tapaaeem udaekakaa, chhaau apaara mahaanatamakaa
saimhaasana shaobhaa uhaee bakhaana agaadha taeja mahaimaa .
2. athaaha tapaaeemkao ananatakaala, hae aaphaai-aapha eeshawara
sawaragadaootalae garadachhana‌ dainaraata maana paoojaa nairanatara .
3. tapaaeemkao bhaya ma maanadachhau, hae eeshawara jaiundao
pachhautaaee kaamadaai-kaamadaai aashamaa paoojaa ma garachhau .
4. taai panai parabhau aaphaai-aapha ma panai prem garachhau
an, maerao ayaogaya manakao prem tapaaeemlae maaganaubhayao .
5. hae kharaeeṣhaṭakaa paitaa, premakao maoola paramaananada haunachha yao
sawaragalaokamaa bhaoganau naitaya waasa paaee darashana eeshawarakao .

songs.title: eeshawara thaumaa pawaitara Yeshu kharaeeṣhaṭa eeshawara pautara
lyrics: eeshawara thaumaa, pawaitara Yeshu kharaeeṣhaṭa, eeshawara pautara,
uchaalaie raajaee bhaye maranalaaee
majasatao daoṣhaeelae jaanaoon ragata bagayao,
ajha bagadaaichha, shaudadha paaradaai, naikao paaradaai .
ma uccha paarachhau Yeshu, maerao balaidaana,
uccha paarachhau maukataidaataa, maeraa parabhau
ma uccha paarachhau, paramaeshawarakaa thaumaa,
daṇaḍawata‌ garachhau tapaaeemlaaee saimhaasanaaghai .

songs.title: eeshawara paitaa haamarao saunanaosa‌ khaalai saanaa maanachhae haaun
lyrics: 1. eeshawara paitaa haamarao saunanaosa‌, khaalai saanaa maanachhae haaun
taai tapaaeemlaaee ṭhaoolao bainataee garana ahailae aaekaa chhaaun .
2. kharaeeṣhaṭakao raajaya khaooba chhaiṭaṭao aaosa‌, kharaeeṣhaṭamaa sabalae paaoona‌ jaya
ra tapaaeemlaaee sabalae chainaoona‌, sabalae maanaoona‌ dhanaya bhaye .
3. kharaeeṣhaṭakao premakao maeeṭhao kauraa saunaikana maanachhaelae .
yasa samsaaramaa satautai garauna‌ jasatao sawaragamaa daootalae .
4. aaosa‌ tyo samsaara tapaaeemkao haunae ghaड़ee hae paitaa .
kainabhanae saba tapaaeemkaa raajaya paraakarama mahaimaa .

songs.title: eeshawara mahaaraajalaaee gara paraṇaama‌ an maana unakaa gauṇa
lyrics: 1. eeshawara mahaaraajalaaee gara paraṇaama‌, an maana unakaa gauṇa, saamaratha ra prem
jao haamaraa chhana‌ ḍhaala ra rakaṣhaka sadhaain, jao basachhana‌ parataapamaa pahairana satautakaalaaee .
2. parataapa aanai taeja ta gara parakaasha, ho wasatara ujayolao, ḍaeraa aakaasha
hauna‌ ratha unakaa garajanakaa baadala hajaara, bataasakaa pakhaeṭaamaa haunachhana‌ sawaara .
3. bhaoolaoka anai tayasakaa udaekakaa dhana basaalanaubhao’ tapaaeemlae, sarawashakataimaana‌
sathaira aajanyolae garanaubhao’ darailao tayasalaaee ra ghaeranaubhao’ samaudaralae khaasaṭaalae jhaain .
4. tapaaeemkao naidhaolae raakhaee bishwas saba khaanchaoanausaarakao bhaeṭachha naikaasa
tapaaeemkao anaugaraha apaara chha, saba raeeta hae karataa, hae rakaṣhaka, hae taraataa, hae maeeta .

songs.title: eeshawara yahaan upasathaita chhaau aashaiṣha‌ ahailae dainalaaee
lyrics: 1. eeshawara yahaan upasathaita chhaau aashaiṣha‌ ahailae dainalaaee
maeghalae haera, ghaeradaai aayao, ichachhaa paoorao haosa‌ taimaraai .
kao. haamaee sawaragae bapataisamaa maagachhaaun ghanaghaora waृṣhaṭai gara
paraiya Yeshu parakhamdaai chhaaun mana jagaaoo yahaee pahara
2. anaubhawa bhao’ upasathaita chhaau, bhaai’gao pawaitara bhaoomai
tara ajhaai baढ़taa maagachhaaun, aaoo manamaa yasagharaee .
3. upasathaita chha aba bainataee chha, layoundaaichhaaun aba bishwaslaaee
aatamaa aaja jalaaoo manamaa, ahailae aaphanao hat baढ़aee .
4. payorasaita haृdaya aba daekhadachhaaun, ahailae khaola bhaṇaḍaaralaaee
euṭaa garaaoo waृṣhaṭai ṭhaoolao, aashaiṣha‌ ahailae daeoo paṭhaaee .

songs.title: eeshawara sawaragaeeya paitaalae prem garaee laokalaaee ekalae chharao
lyrics: 1. eeshawara sawaragaeeya paitaalae prem garaee laokalaaee, ekalae chharao
daiihaalae jaeewana dainalaaee bhaai hao, jaeewana dainalaaee .
2. ekalae chharao nabhanaee daie laokalaaee
bishwas garaee sabaailae laeoona maukatailaaee, bhaai ho laeoona maukatailaaee .
3. sawaragabaaṭa Yeshu aae maukatai laiera
kasalae laie maukatailaaee manaai garaera, bhaai ho manaai garaera .
4. Yeshu pautara bhaera awataara laiiaae
bishwas garanae sabaailae maukataidaana paae, bhaai ho maukataidaana paae .
5. daunaiyon samsaara chha saagara paapaaikao chha wayawahaara
paapalaaee laukaairaakhaera kasaraee tarachhaaum paara, bhaai ho kasaraee tarachhaaum paara .
6. jasalae saunachhana‌ parabhaukao ajamamarae wachanalaaee
unalaaee maukatai dainaechhana‌ ajamamaraelaaee, bhaai ho ajamamaraelaaee .
7. eeshawara paitaa saamarathaee sabaai daana dainalaaee
manalaaee jagaaee tayora haau, daana lainalaaee bhaai ho daana lainalaaee .

songs.title: eeshawarakao chhaewaaimaa jaandaaichhau ma parae panai dauhkhamaa lagainachhau
lyrics: 1. eeshawarakao chhaewaaimaa jaandaaichhau ma,
parae panai dauhkhamaa lagainachhau ma .
satautai gaaundaai jaya bhanachhau, eeshawarakao chhaewaaimaa,
eeshawarakao chhaewaaimaa jaandaaichhau ma .
2. paradaeshaee jasataai chhau, ghaama ḍaubadaai chha,
waasa-gaढ़ ma khaojadaai chhau raata paradaaichha
naidaraamaa ma haunachhau eeshawarakao chhaewaaimaa,
eeshawarakao chhaewaaimaa jaandaaichhau ma .
3. sawaragalaokakao baaṭao dainachhana‌ malaaee,
saba thaoka dainachhana‌ malaaee wahaan aashaiṣha‌ paaee
daoota bhanda sharaeṣhaṭha haunachhau, eeshawarakao chhaewaaimaa,
eeshawarakao chhaewaaimaa jaandaaichhau ma .
4. dauhkha-shaokalaaee tayogaera, shaanata bhaera,
chamakandaai rahanachhau wahaan gaera
shaoka haundaaina saathamaa eeshawarakao chhaewaaimaa,
eeshawarakao chhaewaaimaa jaandaaichhau ma .
5. aananadakao pakhaeṭaa jaba lainachhau ma,
samsaarakao shaoka chainataa bairasanachhau ma .
satautai gaaundaai jaya bhanachhau, eeshawarakao chhaewaaimaa,
eeshawarakao chhaewaaimaa jaandaaichhau ma .

songs.title: eeshawarakao pautara Yeshu maanaisa raoopa dhaaraṇa garaee
lyrics: kao. eeshawarakao pautara Yeshu maanaisa raoopa dhaaraṇa garaee
sawaragakao saukhalaaee tayogaera gaoṭhamaa janama laie
sahaera dauhkha haamaeelaaee saukha dainalaaee parabhaulae
saukha dainalaaee parabhaulae
1. tainalae sabalaaee payora garae, bairaamaeelaaee changagaa garae
dauhख़eelaaee sahaayataa daiera sawaragakao parachaara garae
anadhaalaaee aankhaa, gaoongaalaaee baolaee, gaoongaalaaee baolaee
bahairaalaaee saunaae shabada, bahairaalaaee saunaae .
2. Yeshulaaee yao thaahaa thaiyao, sabaailae paapa garaekaa chhana‌
eeshawarakao wachanalae bhanadachha paapakao phala maृtayau naai hao,
paapadaekhai maukata garaauna kharaeeṣhaṭalae, garaauna kharaeeṣhaṭalae
karunaimaa paraaṇa tayogae, bhaai hao, karunaimaa paraaṇa tayogae .
3. eeshawarakao pautara Yeshu taesarao daina baauraee uṭhae
maृtayaukao banadhanalaaee taoड़era sawaragakao parachaara garae
sawaragamaa chaढ़ee eeshawarakao chhaeumaa, eeshawarakao chhaeumaa
haamaeelaaee parakhadaaichhana‌ bhaai hao, haamaeelaaee parakhadaaichhana‌ .
4. kaukaramadaekhai pharakaee parabhaumaa bishwas garanae
paaundachhana‌ taee sabalae maukatai, paramaeshawara kaṣhamaa garachhana‌
yasakaaraṇa bhaai ho bishwas gara, bishwas gara,
parabhau Yeshu kharaeeṣhaṭamaa bahainaee, parabhau Yeshu kharaeeṣhaṭamaa .

songs.title: eeshawarakao prem chha katai mahaana‌ waraṇana garaee nasakainae
lyrics: 1. eeshawarakao prem chha katai mahaana‌, waraṇana garaee nasakainae
taaraagaṇadaekhai ajha uchacha, paataalasamama phaailaiekao
waisharaamarahaita aatamaakao lagi eeshawaralae pautara daie
paapakao kaalao daagalaaee maeṭaaee haiunjasatao saetao paarae .
kao. eeshawarakao prem katai parashasata chha, bahaumaoolaya apaara
sadhaainbharai daootagaṇa samasata gaaunchhana‌ tayasakao jayajayakaara
2. aphashaosaee daina jaba baitanaechhana‌, saamsaaraika raajaya naasha haunaechha
paraarathanaa nagaranae haraeka jana maृtayau bhanaee baolaaunaechha .
eeshawarakao prem rahanae ajha katai chha daृढ़ ra mahaana‌
anaugaraha aadama wamshalaaee bhanaee gaaunaechhana‌ daootagaṇa .
3. samaudara masaeelae bharaekao, aakaasha patara bhaekao bhae
hara raookhakao ḍaanṭha kalama banaekao ra haraeka maanaisa laekhaka bhae
laekhana eeshawarakao mahaana‌ prem samaudara saukaee jaanathayao
na ta aṭaaunthayao aakaashamaa waraṇana tyo daiwaya premakao .

songs.title: eeshawarakao mahaimaa gaauna yasa samsaaramaa
lyrics: kao. eeshawarakao mahaimaa gaauna yasa samsaaramaa
haraeka bishwaseekao paramaukha karatabaya ho (2)
1. jaeewaeeta aashaa maukatai sawatanatarakao achamama jaeewanadaanakao naimatai
aau sabaai mailai gaaun unakao naaunkao jaya,
aau sabaai gaaun unakao naaunkao jaya
2. uhaankao prem ananata balaidaana sawaragaeeya maukauṭakao naimatai
aau sabaai mailaigaaun unakao naaunkao jaya
aau sabaai gaaun unakao naaunkao jaya

songs.title: eeshawarakao maanachhae uṭha chhaड़ ayaogaya karamalaaee
lyrics: 1. eeshawarakao maanachhae uṭha, chhaड़ ayaogaya karamalaaee
haृdaya, mana aatamaa, saamaratha daeoo kharaeeṣhaṭa Yeshu raajaalaaee .
2. eeshawarakao maanachhae uṭha, raajaya aaundaaichha ḍhailao
sangagatakao daina aba chhaiṭao layooo, haṭaaoo raata paapaaikao .
3. eeshawarakao maanachhae uṭha, maṇaḍalaee parakhamdachha
tyo kaama naimaitata nasakanae ho usalaaee parasaidadha banaaoo .
4. Yeshukao karaoosa uṭhaaoo hainड़ baaṭao unaaikao
maanachhaekao pautarakaa daajayaoo-bhaaikao raupamaa uṭha maanachhae eeshawarakao .

songs.title: eesha‍warakao yao waradaana maerao yao jaeewana ekalaai basana
lyrics: kao. eesha‍warakao yao waradaana maerao yao jaeewana,
ekalaai basana saृjaekao haoina,
(aajanama saatha daindaainaau bhanae ta,
palabharakao maayo malaaee chaahaindaaina) (2)
1. (pahaaड़jatarao yao jainadagaeemaa ekalaai basaoonlaa
bhanaera chaitaaekao chhaaina) (2)
(taimaraai waisha‍waasamaa aaphaoolaaee saumapaee) (2)
(manamaa kaunaai thaoka laukaaekao chhaaina) (2)
2. (barabaada nabanaosa yao maerao jaeewana,
maeeṭhaa-maeeṭhaa kauraalae, abhailaaṣhaalae) (2)
(samarapaṇa haundaaichhau taimaeesaamau aaja) (2)
(eesha‍wara chhana saakaṣhaee taimaee yoda raakha) (2)

songs.title: eeshawarakao raaja pahailae khaojaee gara uhaankao dhaaramaikataa
lyrics: 1. eeshawarakao raaja pahailae khaojaee gara, uhaankao dhaaramaikataa,
sabaai thaoka taimaeelaaee thapainaechha, halalaelaoo hallelujah .
kao. (halalaelaooyoha) (3) halalaelaoo hallelujah
2. raoṭaeelae maatara maanaisa baanchadaaina, tara haraeka wachanalae,
jao paramaeshawarakao maukhabaaṭa naisakanachha, halalaelaoo hallelujah .
3. maaga ta taimaeelaaraya daiinaechha, khaoja ta bhaeṭaṭaaunaechhaau,
ghachaghachaaoo ḍhaokaa ughaarainaechha, halalaelaoo hallelujah

songs.title: eeshawarakao wachana paooraa garanalaaee wachana daeha bhayao
lyrics: kao. eeshawarakao wachana paooraa garanalaaee wachana daeha bhayao
baalaka Yeshu sabakaa udadhaaraka (janama gaoṭhamaa bhao’) (2)
1. baalaka eeshawarakao paraiya pautara hauna‌, naaun Yeshu unakao (2)
udadhaara garanalaaee janamaekaa unaee eeshawarakaa pautara hauna‌ .
2. eeshawarakao pautara bhaera panai maanawa raupa lainaubhao (2)
aaphaailaaee raitayoee daiekao daana baalaka Yeshu hauna‌ .

songs.title: eeshawarachaahain prem hauna‌ premachaahain amara ho eeshawara prem
lyrics: 1. eeshawarachaahain prem hauna‌, premachaahain amara hao, eeshawara prem sarawasharaeṣhaṭha hao,
bishwas, aashaa ra premamadhayae panai prem sabaaibhanadaa sharaeṣhaṭha ho .
2. paooraṇa haृdaya ra shakatai, bala, paraaṇalae parama eeshawaralaaee prem garaaun,
chhaimaekaeesanga aaphaaisanga jhaain sarawadaa naiṣhakapaṭa prem garaaun .
3. premalae sadaakaala dhaeeraja dharadachha, premalae kahailayoi eekha garadaaina,
premalae kahailayoi shaekhaee garadaaina, premachaahain kahailayoi paulaindaaina .
4. premalae kauraeetai kahailayoi garadaaina, aaphanaai bhalaai khaojadaaina,
bauraaee, ghamaṇaḍa, chhala kapaṭa garadaaina, premachaahain kahailayoi maradaaina .
5. parabhau Yeshukao pachhailalao aajanyo eka-arakaasanga prem garaaun,
eka-arakaakao premakao ऋṇa baokadaai Yeshukao aajanyo paoorao garaaun .

songs.title: eeshawaralaaee paujaoon pawaitarataa laaikana daṇaḍawata‌ garaoon parachaaraee
lyrics: 1. eeshawaralaaee paujaoon pawaitarataa laaikana daṇaḍawata‌ garaoon parachaaraee parataapa
aajanyo manaaee ra daeenataa chaढ़aeekana unaaikao naaun laindaai jao aaphaai-aapha .
2. phaikaraeekaa bhaara haalaoon eeshawarakao charaṇamaa, unalae tyo haृdayamaa baokachhana uṭhaaee
shaoka maeṭaidainachhana‌, paurayoundachhana‌ sharaṇamaa paau ḍaorayoee maaraekao jhaain .
3. eeshawarakao mahalamaa wainaaḍaraaeekana chhaaun aauna sakanae daeena-haeena
manakaa bhaye khaalai sachachaain ra dhana premakao layoeekana garahaṇa garainachhaaun yaee maatara chaढ़aee .
4. yatai naai layoaun taa Yeshukao naaunmaa eeshawaralae lainachhana‌ taee kaaraṇa unakao haraṣhakao
daina dainachhana‌ shaokakao saaṭaomaa kamaaikao saaṭao bishwas darailao .
5. eeshawaralaaee paujaoon pawaitarataa laaikana daṇaḍawata‌ garaoon parachaaraee parataapa
aajanyo manaaee ra daeenataa chaढ़aeekana unaaikao naaun laindaai jao aaphaai aapha .

songs.title: eeshawaralae aaphanao pautaralaaee samsaaramaa paṭhaae
lyrics: 1. eeshawaralae aaphanao pautaralaaee samsaaramaa paṭhaae
ra karaoosamaa maraeekana haamaeelaaee bachaae
kae dainau‌ ? kae dainau ? ma Yeshulaaee kae dainae,
tyo baड़o premakao saaṭaomaa, kae dainau unalaaee ma ?
2. ma atai saanao paaṭhaolaaee kai unalaaee manaparachha
ra maile daiekao thaoka unalae garahaṇa garachhana‌,
kae dainau ? kae dainau ? tyo baड़o premakao,
tyo baड़o premakao saaṭaomaa, kae dainau unalaaee ma ?
3. ma sadhaain baaibala paḍhadachhau, aajanyokaaraee haunalaaee
ma sadhaain paraarathanaa garadachhau, unakao ichachhaa baujhanalaaee .
kae dainau ? kae dainau ? ma Yeshulaaee kae dainau,
tyo baड़o premakao saaṭaomaa, kae dainau unalaaee ma ?

songs.title: eeshawaralae daie tyo asala ṭhaaun ma bhaitara pasachhau
lyrics: eeshawaralae daie tyo asala ṭhaaun, ma bhaitara pasachhau ra ramaaunchhau
uhaankao mahaimaa ma thaahaa gachhau, uhaankao raajaya jhalakaaunchhau
uhaanlaaee satautai dainachhaaun haamaraa paraaṇa, aatamaa ra haृdayakao sawara khaolaee
saeedhaai jaanachhaaun naishaanaataira kanaanakao bhaoomaimaa .

songs.title: eeshawaralae daiekaa ramaahaṭa yasa paapaee samsaaramaa
lyrics: 1. eeshawaralae daiekaa ramaahaṭa yasa paapaee samsaaramaa
kai aaphanao wachanaanausaara dayo paainaechha
kai paratayaeka chhaina ra paratayaeka daina parashasata dayo paainachha .
kao. hallelujah hallelujah hallelujah Yeshu
2. andhayorao bhae panai ramaaunchhau sadhaain
kainakai eeshawaralae malaaee chhaड़daainana‌ kahailayoi
yotaraamaa takalaipha bhae panai sawaragamaa pauganaechhau naishachaya .
3. ma yotaraa saidhayoepachhai sawaragalaoka aaunaechhau
tayahaan nairanatara ramaahaṭa Yeshusanga paaunaechhau
sabaai pawaitara janasanga parashamsaa satautai garachhau ma .

songs.title: eeshawaralae samsaaralaaee yasatao prem garae (2)
lyrics: eeshawaralae samsaaralaaee yasatao prem garae (2)
unalae aaphanao eka maatara pautaralaaee daie (2)
ja-jasalae unamaathai bishwas garachhana‌ (2)
naasha haundaainana‌ tara ananata jaeewana paaunchhana‌ (2)

songs.title: jakakaai ekajanaa pauḍakao maanaisa thaie pauḍakao maanaisa
lyrics: jakakaai ekajanaa pauḍakao maanaisa thaie, pauḍakao maanaisa thaie unaee .
unaee euṭaa bhadaraakaṣhakao raukhamaa chaḍhae, parabhaulaaee haerana bhanaee .
jaba maukataidaataa tyo baaṭao bhaera gae, unalae raukhamaathai haerae,
“jakakaai tala orala, ma taimarao gharamaa aauna chaahanachhau .”

songs.title: jagata‌ samsaara kaehaee panai chhaaina sauna daajayaoo-bhaai (2)
lyrics: 1. jagata‌ samsaara kaehaee panai chhaaina sauna daajayaoo-bhaai (2)
bishwas garaaun haamaee sabalae, maukatai paaunalaaee (2)
kao. kharaeeṣhaṭa Yeshu chhana‌, kharaeeṣhaṭa Yeshu chhana‌
kharaeeṣhaṭa Yeshu chhana‌, tayora maukatai dainalaaee
2. laobhaai garachhaau, laalacha garachhaau samsaarakao thaokalaaee (2)
yaee sabaai thaoka kaehaee panai haoina saathamaa jaanalaaee (2)
3. aaoo sabaai phaikaraee garaaun maukatai paaunalaaee (2)
Yeshubaahaeka araoo chhana‌ chhaaina kaehaee upaaya (2)
4. aaoo sabaai daajayaoo-bhaai hao, sauna mana lagaaee (2)
kharaeeṣhaṭa Yeshu taaraṇahaarakao naimatao chha sabalaaee (2)

songs.title: jagata‌ saृṣhaṭai paalanakarataa dhanaya eeshawara daataa
lyrics: 1. jagata‌ saृṣhaṭai paalanakarataa, dhanaya eeshawara daataa
dhanaya-dhanaya parabhau Yeshu jagata‌kaa taraataa nai dhanaya .
kao. bhaja manalaaee, aaoo jana parabhaukahaan, bhaja manalaaee, bhaja manalaaee
2. paramaeshawarakao parathama wachana pautara daioonlaa bhanaee
saanchaai parabhau awataara bhae jagata‌kao maṇai nai dhanaya .
3. taeesaai waraṣha paugaepachhai parachaara garaee hainड़thae
parabhau Yeshu mahaadaataa ajamamaraee dainae nai dhanaya .
4. ajamamaraee wachana saunaaee daeshaai-waidaesha phairae
karausakao mahaa dauhkha sahaee paraaṇa daana garaidaie nai dhanaya .
5. aaoo paapaee bishwas garaee parabhaukahaan dhaaoo
paapakao maृtayau banadhanadaekhai naisataara daana paaoo nai dhanaya .
6. parabhaujaeekao daiwaya wachana dauhkhaee paapaee aaoo
daaoodakao wamshaee Yeshu kharaeeṣhaṭakao jayajaya satautai gaaaun nai dhanaya .

songs.title: jagata‌kao taaraṇahaara haamarao kharaeeṣhaṭa raajaa (4) jagata‌kao
lyrics: kao. jagata‌kao taaraṇahaara, haamarao kharaeeṣhaṭa raajaa (4) jagata‌kao
1. haamarao naimatai sawaraga chhaड़ee aae jagata‌maa (2)
balai bhae haamarao naimatai kalawaraeekao karaoosamaa (2)
2. paapakao udadhaara garana aae kharaeeṣhaṭa Yeshu raajaa (2)
pashachaatataapaee haृdayalaaee kaṣhamaa dainachhana‌ aaja (2)
3. satayataakao wachana daie saaraa janataalaaee (2)
kharaeeṣhaṭamaa bishwas garae haamaee paara tarachhaaum bhaai (2)
4. kharaeeṣhaṭakao amaola wachana paaee paapadaekhai pharaka (2)
paapadaekhai pharakayoum bhanae paaunchhaaun aananada sawaraga (2)

songs.title: jamgalaee darakhataom kae daramaiyona eka saewa kae paeड़ samaana
lyrics: kao. jamgalaee darakhataom kae daramaiyona, eka saewa kae paeड़ samaana
najara aataa haai maujhae ai masaeeha, saarae sanataom kae baeecha maem taoo .
hamada karaoon taeraee ai parabhau, apanae jaeewana bhara
isa jamgala kae saphara maem, gaaoon shaukara paujaaraee sae maaim (2)
1. taoo haee haai naragaisa khaasa shaaraona kaa haan saoshana bhaye waadaiyaom kaa
sanataom maem taoo haai atai pawaitara, kaaisae kaamaila aura shaana sae bharaa (2)
2. itara kae saamaana haai taeraa naama, khaushabaoo phaailaataa haai jahaan maem
tamgaee, mausaibata aura badanaamaee maem banaa khaushabaoodaara taerae samaana (2)
3. ghabaraahaṭa kae laharaom sae gara, ḍaubaoon dauhkha kae saagara maem
apanae jaoraabaara haatha kao baड़a maujhae apanae saeenae sae lagaa (2)
4. abhaye aa rahaan haun taerae paasa, pauraee karanae kao taeraee marajaee
taakai dae daoon maaim kaama kao amjaama, paaoon taerae daeedaara maem inaama (2)

songs.title: janama bhayao yaraooshalaemaa Yeshu raajaa gaaeekao gaoṭhaaimaa
lyrics: kao. janama bhayao yaraooshalaemaa Yeshu raajaa gaaeekao gaoṭhaaimaa
(sawaragadaootalae layoe sanadaesha Yeshu kharaeeṣhaṭalaaee taimarao dawaaramaa) (2)
1. (nainadaraalaaee tayogai aaja yao raata dainau chha) (2)
(sausanadaesha laiee aayao haamaee hajaurakao aaganamaa) (2)
(aajakao raatamaa jayaotaikao saathamaa janama bhao gaaeekao gaoṭhamaa) (2)
2. (nailao gaganamaa hainḍana laagae chamakailao tyo taaraa) (2)
(bhanadaai aae jayaotaiṣhaeegaṇa janamanaubhayao Yeshu payoraa) (2)
(aajakao raatamaa baethalaehaema gaaunmaa janama bhao gaaeekao gaoṭhamaa) (2‌)

songs.title: janama bhayao Yeshu raajaakao baethalaehaema gaaunmaa
lyrics: kao. janama bhayao Yeshu raajaakao baethalaehaema gaaunmaa
sawaraga chhaड़ee aaunaubhayao maanachhaekao bhaeṣhamaa
1. (haamaee paapaeelaaee maukatai dainalaaee janama lainaubhayao yahaee dharataeemaa) (2)
anadhakaaramaa jayaotai banaera aaunaubhayao Yeshu (yao samsaaramaa) (2)
2. (paramaeshawara pautara bhaera panai gaaeekao gaoṭhamaa janamahaubhayao) (2)
saanchao paramaeshawara chainaaunau bhanaera sawaragabaaṭa (oralaiaaunaubhao’) (2)

songs.title: jaba aaulaana‌ jaba aaulaana‌ naija haeeraa baṭaulana
lyrics: 1. jaba aaulaana‌, jaba aaulaana‌ naija haeeraa baṭaulana
sabaai haeeraa, maoolaya haeeraa Yeshukaa naai hauna‌
jasataa taaraa baihaanakao chamakandaai rahandaai
yasataai yainaai chamakanachhana‌ kharaeeṣhaṭakao maukauṭamaa .
2. taee baṭaulachhana‌, taee baṭaulachhana‌ sawaraga raajayakaa saba haeeraa
jatai raamaraa ra chamakailaa Yeshukaa naai hauna‌
jasataa taaraa baihaanakao chamakandaai rahandaai
yasataai yainaai chamakanachhana‌ kharaeeṣhaṭakao maukauṭamaa .
3. nara-naaraee, kaeṭaa-kaeṭaee kharaeeṣhaṭasanga prem garanae
haeeraa yainaai, haeeraa payoraai Yeshukaa naai hauna‌
jasataa taaraa baihaanakao chamakandaai rahandaai
yasataai yainaai chamakanachhana‌ kharaeeṣhaṭakao maukauṭamaa .

songs.title: jaba aaraadhanaa garadaai tapaaeemkao upasathaitaimaa pasadachhau
lyrics: jaba aaraadhanaa garadaai tapaaeemkao upasathaitaimaa pasadachhau
saachachaai Yeshu tapaaeemlaaee maerao aankhaalae daerawadachhau (2)
maerao sharaeera tapaaeemkao pawaitara manadaira ho
maerao haृdaya tapaaeemkao pawaitara baedaee ho
aai parabhau sawaragaeeya aagao ma maa warasaau (2)

songs.title: jaba taka maaim jaeewaita haun parabhau taeraa haee saatha rahaegaa
lyrics: kao. jaba taka maaim jaeewaita haun parabhau taeraa haee saatha rahaegaa
taerae haee samga yaha jaeewana saphara rahaegaa . (2)
1. Yeshu maeraa jaeewana daataa, jaeewana yaha usakaa haai
jaeewana kae hara pala maem, maujhakao waha samabhaalataa haai .
2. wachana parabhaukaa paaun kae laie maerae daipasaa jalataa haai
maaraga maem maerae jao saatha jalakara, raaha daikhaataa haai .
3. wachana parabhau taeraa haृdaya maem maaimnae, aisaa chhaड़a haai
paapa karaoon nahaee jaeewana maem apanae, aisaa ṭhaanaa haai .

songs.title: jaba tapaaeemkao upasathaitaibhaitara ma aaundachhau
lyrics: jaba tapaaeemkao apasathaitaibhaitara ma aaundachhau
maerao khaojaaeekao anata haunachha
jaba tapaaeemkao angagaalaomaa malaaee lainauhaunachha
maerao taृṣhaita aatamaa taृpata haunachha parabhau
(yasaailae tapaaeemlaaee parakhairahanachhau sadhaaim
prem garanalaaee aadara garanalaaee
mahaimaa dainalaaee
uchaalata tapaaeem Yeshulaaee) (2)

songs.title: jaba taimarao shakataikao ghaosanaa garachhau ma baijaya baijaya haudachhau
lyrics: jaba taimarao shakataikao ghaosanaa garachhau
ma baijaya baijaya haudachhau
ma gaauchhau taimarao satautai mahaimaa
ma garachhau taimarao baijayakao ghaosanaa (2) ghaosanaa
jaba taimarao pabaitarataamaa ma jaiuchhau
taimaeelaaee najaika najaika paaudachhau (2)
ma gaauchhau taimarao satautai mahaimaa
ma garachhau taimarao baijayakao ghaosanaa
jaba taimarao upasataithaimaa ma aauchhau
ma abhaiṣhaeka abhaiṣhaekalae bharainachhau

songs.title: jaba narasaimgaa phaunkaa jaawae shahara maem baulaanae kao
lyrics: 1. jaba narasaimgaa phaunkaa jaawae, shahara maem baulaanae kao,
kai hara eka khaudaa sae ajara paawaegaa .
jaisa wakata saatha usakae baihaishata maem baragaujaeedaa jamaa ho
takhata kae saamanae maaim bhaye haajaira haooongaa .
kao. jaisa wakata naama paukaaraa jaawae (3)
takhata kae saamanae maaim bhaye haajaira haooongaa .
2. shaubha-i-saadaika usaee daina jaba kaee jaee uṭhae maomainaeena
aura jaa pahaunchae raasatabaaja abadaee aaraamagaaha
taaja i-jainadagaee jaba paawaem baragaujaeedaa kaaimao kae,
baeecha jamaayata maaim bhaye haajaira haooongaa .
3. paasa masaeeha kae laie khaidamata saubaha sae shaama taka karaoongaa,
tao mauhababata usakaee jaahaira ho sadaa,
taba jaisa wakata khaudaa baulaawae, hamaem ajara daenae kao,
maujhae bhaye waha taaja aasamaanaee mailaegaa .

songs.title: jaba pahailaa waiwaaha bhayao aadama ra hawawaakao
lyrics: 1. jaba pahailaa waiwaaha bhayao aadama ra hawawaakao,
eeshawara haajaira haunau bhao’ waiwaaha aashaiṣhaita‌ bhao’ .
2. aajakao yao waiwaahamaa eeshawara upasathaita chhana‌,
baehaulaa ra baehaulaee dauilaaee aashaeerawaada dainaechhana‌ .
3. hae paramaeshawara, yao baehaulaee daindaaichhaaun baehaulaalaaee,
jasaraee aghai hawawaa dainaubhao’ aadamalaaee .
4. parabhau, yaee daueekao haृdaya jaoड़ee eka banaaunauhaosa‌
dauhkha, saukhamaa parabhau Yeshu, kaailae nachhaड़nauhaosa‌ .
5. an, hae pawaitara aatamaa, utaraera aaunauhaosa‌
yaee daueemaa sadhaain maela haosa‌ premakao aashaiṣha‌ barasaosa‌ .
6. kharaabaeedaekhai baanchanalaaee sahaayataa dainauhaosa‌,
jaba daueelae samsaara chhaड़chhana‌ sawaragamaa ṭhaaun dainauhaosa‌ .

songs.title: jaba payorao yaeshau jaeewanamaa aayao badalaawaṭa hauna laagayao
lyrics: jaba payorao Yeshu jaeewanamaa aayao badalaawaṭa hauna laagayao
yao dharataee amabara baganae nadaee gaeeta gaauna laagayao (2)
jao na kahailae daekhana sakayao daekhana laagayao aba
jao na kahailae saunana sakayao saunana laagayao aba (2)
jaba payorao Yeshu jaeewanamaa aayao (2)
jao na kahailae baolana sakayao baolana laagayao aba
jao na kahailae ḍainḍana sakayao hainḍana laagayao aba (2)
jaba payorao Yeshu jaeewanamaa aayao (2)

songs.title: jaba parabhaukao aatamaa maerao haृdayamaa chha ma gaaunchhau
lyrics: 1. (jaba parabhaukao aatamaa maerao haृdayamaa chha, ma gaaunchhau daaoodajhaain) (2)
(ma gaaunchhau, ma gaaunchhau, ma gaaunchhau daaoodajhaain) (2)
2. (jaba parabhaukao aatamaa maerao haृdayamaa chha satautai garachhau daaoodajhaain) (2)
(satautai garachhau, satautai garachhau, satautai garachhau daaoodajhaain) (2)
3. (jaba parabhaukao aatamaa maerao haृdayamaa chha taalaee bajaaunchhau daaoodajhaain) (2)
(taalaee bajaaunchhau, taalaee bajaaunchhau, taalaee bajaaunchhau daaoodajhaain) (2)
4. (jaba parabhaukao aatamaa maerao haृdayamaa chha ma naachachhau daaoodajhaain) (2)
(ma naachachhau, ma naachachhau, ma naachachhau daaoodajhaain) (2)

songs.title: jaba ma tapaaeemkao saimhaasanatarapha haerachhau (4) ma aananadalae
lyrics: jaba ma tapaaeemkao saimhaasanatarapha haerachhau (4) ma aananadalae bharapaoora banachhau (2)
jaba ma maerao maukauṭa tayahaan daekhachhau, naishachaya banachhau ma tyo paaunaechhau (2)

songs.title: jaba ma daekhachhau tapaaeemkao mahaanataa tapaaeemkao shakatai
lyrics: jaba ma daekhachhau tapaaeemkao mahaanataa, tapaaeemkao shakatai, tapaaeemkao anaugaraha
maerao jaeewanamaa ma thaahaa garachhau, ma gaaunchhau, ramaaunchhau, karaaunchhau
utasaahaita haunachhau, tapaaeemkao satautai gaauna, utasaahaita haunachhau,
tapaaeemkao parashamsaa garana, utasaahaita haunachhau, tapaaeemlaaee uccha paarana (2)-laaee .
kaaraṇa tapaaeem maeraa parabhau ra raaja, maerao eka maatara aashaa anai bharaosaa,
maerao bala ra chaṭaṭaana, maerao sarawasawa tapaaeem, ma naachachhau, upharanachhau, karaaunchhau, hao...
utasaahaita haunachhau, tapaaeemkao upasathaitaimaa aauna, utasaahaita haunachhau
tapaaeem parabhaulaaee bhaeṭana, utasaahaita haunachhau tapaaeemlaaee sadaa prem garana (2)-laaee

songs.title: jaba ma parabhaukao bhaera jaiuna thaalaen maile nairaashaamaa
lyrics: kao. jaba ma parabhaukao bhaera jaiuna thaalaen,
maile nairaashaamaa shaanatai paaen .
1. jaeewanakaa dhaeraai yotaraaharaoo aaphanaai ichachhaamaa hainड़irahaem (2)
maile haara samajhan, jaeewanalaaee jaeewanalaaee .
(wayaratha thaiyao yao jaeewana maerao, parabhau taimaeemaa aratha paaen) (2)
2. jaeewanakaa baankaee yotaraaharaoo parabhaukao ichachhaamaa jaiuna paaen (2)
maile jaeeta samajhaen jaeewanalaaee, jaeewanalaaee
(lainauhaosa‌ parabhau jaeewana maerao, parabhau taimaee naai sahaaraa maerao) (2)

songs.title: jaba ma marae pachhai maerao laasamaa aaee ramaaee dainau (2)
lyrics: kao. jaba ma marae pachhai maerao laasamaa aaee ramaaee dainau (2)
(haijaokao tyo maayolaaee samajhaee parabhaukao bhanaera ukaaraee dainau) (2)
1. hajaaraaun phaoolalae ḍhaakaiekao haunachha (yao maerao laasalaaee) (2)
(tayao phaulakao waasanaamaa sautaekao haunachhau phaerai najagaaoo malaaee) (2)
2. saetao kaphanalae baeraiekao haunachha (yao maerao laasalaaee) (2)
(mauradaa sharaeeramaa sautaekao haunachhau kaphana haeraera chainanau malaaee) (2)

songs.title: jaba maaim kamajaora taoo haai saamaratha taoo haee khajaanaa
lyrics: kao. jaba maaim kamajaora taoo haai saamaratha, taoo haee khajaanaa
jaisa ḍhaunढ़taa taoo maeraa sabakauchha haai,
khaojaoon maaim ratana kae samaana parabhau kabhaye
naa chhaḍaoongaa taoo maeraa sabakauchha haai .
1. Yeshu maemanaa yaogaya haai taeraa naama
Yeshu maemanaa yaogaya haai taeraa naama (2)
laiyo maeraa paapa aura karaoosa aura laaja
phaira uṭhaa dhanaya taeraa naama taoo maeraa sabakauchha haai
jaba gairaoon maujhae uṭhaataa jaba payosaa taba
payolaa bharataa taoo maeraa sabakauchha haai ॥

songs.title: jaba maaim paukaaraoo masaeeha maujhakao jawaapha dae
lyrics: kao. jaba maaim paukaaraoo masaeeha, maujhakao jawaapha dae
taeraee aawaajakao saunataa rahaungaa . (2)
1. taeraee bhajana kao maaim gaataa rahaungaa
taeraee parashamsaa maaim karataa rahaungaa,
taunae haee maujha sae prem kaiyo haai
taeraee haee prem kaa gauṇa gaataa rahaungaa . (2)
2. daunaiyon maem aakara karaoosakao uṭhaakara
maerae laie taunae bahauta dauhkha sahaa (2)
taeraee haee karaoosa kao maaim parachaara haraoongaa
taeraee haee mahaimaa maaim jaeewana bhara karaoongaa . (2)

songs.title: jaba maaimnae saochaa maaim akaelaa haun taba parabhau Yeshu nae maujha sae kahaa
lyrics: jaba maaimnae saochaa maaim akaelaa haun
taba parabhau Yeshu nae maujha sae kahaa
samsaara kae anata taka saatha rahanae waalaa
maaim taeraa saatha haun (2)
jaba maaimnae saomchaa maaim nairabala haoon
taba parabhau Yeshu nae maujhasae kahaa
shakatai daenaewaalaa saamaratha daenaewaalaa
maaim taerae saatha haoon (2) .
jaba maaimnae saochaa kaee asamabhawa haai
taba parabhau Yeshu nae maujhasae kahaa
asamabhawakao samabhawa karanae waalaa Yeshu
maaim taeraa saatha haun (2) .

songs.title: jaba shaanataikao nadaee mabhaitara bagadachha jaba hauraee bataasa
lyrics: 1. jaba shaanataikao nadaee mabhaitara bagadachha, jaba hauraee bataasa chaladachha
haraeka samayamaa gaauna saikaaunaubhao, maukata chha maukata chha maerao paraaṇa .
kao. maukata chha, maukata chha, maerao paraaṇa maerao paraaṇa
maukataa chha, maukataa chha, maerao paraaṇa .
2. shaaitaanakao khaedao ra paraeekaṣhaamaa panai, yasa naishachayataalae samahaalaosa‌
kharaeeṣhaṭalae maerao paraaṇakao waasataa garanaubhao, ra aaphanaai ragata bahaaunaubhao .
3. maerao paapa yao kasatao achamamakao satayataa, paapa saba kaewala aadhaa haoina
ṭhaokaie unakao karaoosamaa taee baokadaina ma, satautai gaaoo parabhaukao maerao paraaṇa .
4. hataaranaosa‌ tyo daina jaba bishwas daृṣhaṭai banachha, baadala paradaa jhaaim khaolainachha
taurahaee bajanaechha ra parabhau aaunaechhana‌, taba panai maukata chha maerao paraaṇa .

songs.title: jaba sae payoraa Yeshu aayo maeraa jaeewana badala gayo
lyrics: kao. jaba sae payoraa Yeshu aayo maeraa jaeewana badala gayo
jaba sae maainae usae haai paayo, maeraa jaeewana badala gayo (2)
1. maujhae gama aura mausaibataom maem sahaaraa daekara
maerae paapaom kaa baojha laekara apanae oopara
karaoosa para khaoona apanaa bahaayo (2) ... maeraa jaeewana badala gayo .
2. maujhae kharaeedaa haai masaeeha nae khaoona daekara
maaim usakaa maeraa na kaoee saiwaaya usakae
pautara nae haai paitaa sae mailaayo (2) ... maeraa jaeewana badala gayo .
3. isa jahaan kaee ganadagaee sae maujhae chhauड़ayo
aaga daekara maujhae gaunaahaom sae haai bachaayo
taba sae daila maeraa mana maeraee kaayo (2) ... maeraee jaeewana badala gayo .
4. maeraee raahaom maem kaaṭaem jaba na rahaemgae
maeraee mamjaila maem bhaye maatama aba na haomgae
ho gayaee daoora haaim maauta kaa maayo (2) ... maeraee jaeewana badala gayo .
5. raata kaalaee baeeta gaee haai hauaa sabaeraa
saubaha kaa taaraa daekhao chamakaa Yeshu maeraa
isalaie maainae yaha gaeeta gaayo (2) ... maeraa jaeewana badala gayo .

songs.title: jabasamama jaeewana rahanachha dhanyawad ra parashamsaakao bhaeṭaee
lyrics: jabasamama jaeewana rahanachha
dhanyawad ra parashamsaakao bhaeṭaee chaḍhaaunchhau
yao manalae, yao tanalae, yao dhanalae
parabhau tapaaee kaai saewaa ma garachhau
(bhakataipaooraṇa haृdayalae aaraadhanaa
garachhau sawaragaeeya paitaakao) (2)

songs.title: jabasamama bhaeṭadaainaaum haamaee, parabhau kharaeeṣhaṭakao charaṇamaa
lyrics: kao. jabasamama bhaeṭadaainaaum haamaee, parabhau kharaeeṣhaṭakao charaṇamaa
jabasamama bhaeṭadaainaaum haamaee, parabhau Yeshu haamarao saatha haooo .
1. parabhau Yeshu haamarao saathamaa haooo, jaeewanakao baaṭao ḍaorayooo
haamaeelaaee aaphaoomaa mailaaoo, parabhau Yeshu haamarao saathamaa haooo .
2. parabhau Yeshu haamarao saathamaa haooo, dauhkha ra waipadadaekhai bachaaoo
aatamaika bhaojana haamaeelaaee daeoo, parabhau Yeshu haamarao saathamaa haooo .
3. paraebhau Yeshu haamarao saathamaa haooo, jaokhaima jaeewanakao jaba aaunchha
kharaeeṣhaṭakao premaee hat samaaunchha, parabhau Yeshu haamarao saathamaa haooo .
4. parabhau Yeshu haamarao saathamaa haooo, uccha raakha premakao jhaṇaḍaa
maृtayaukao baaṇalae tarasaaundaa parabhau Yeshu haamarao saathamaa haooo .

songs.title: jabasamama ma baanchanaechhau uhaankaai bhajana gaaunaechhau
lyrics: jabasamama ma baanchanaechhau uhaankaai bhajana gaaunaechhau
maerao jaeewana rahaunyajaela sadhaain naai ma naachanaechhau .
gaaunaechhau, gaaunaechhau, naachanaechhau, naachanaechhau
uhaankaai aananadamaa parashamsaa garanaechhau aananadamaa baanchanaechhau .

songs.title: jabasae payoraa Yeshu jaeewanamae aayo
lyrics: kao. jabasae payoraa Yeshu jaeewanamae aayo
badalaasaa laganae lagaa
yae dharataee amara baehaetae hae nadaiyo
gaita gaanae lagaa hallelujah gaeeta gaanae lagaa
1. jao na kabhai baolana sakaa, baolana lagae hae
jao na kabhai saunana sakaa, saunana lagae hae
jabasae payoraa Yeshu jaeewanamae aayo
2. jao na kabhai daekhana sakaa, daekhana lagae hae
jao na kabhai haiḍana sakaa, haiḍana lagae hae

songs.title: jaya jaya jaya jaya Yeshukao jaya (2) balaidaana jao
lyrics: 1. jaya jaya jaya jaya Yeshukao jaya (2) balaidaana jao bhaigayao
baehaisaaba, unakao payora chha, jaya jaya Yeshukao jaya (2)
2. bishwas layoaun haamaee Yeshumaa (2), balaidaana jao bhaigae
unakao ragatakao baaṭaolae saba haamarao paapa maeṭae (2)
3. haera haera kharaeeṣhaṭa Yeshulaaee (2), karunaimaa jao marae
karunaimaa aaphanao paraaṇa daiee haamaeelaaee bachaae (2)
4. eeshawaradaekhai yasatao dayo (2) samsaaralaaee garae payora
anatayamaa unalae aaphanaa pautara daii garae udadhaara (2)

songs.title: jaya jaya jaya jaya Yeshulae dainachhana‌ (2)
lyrics: 1. jaya jaya jaya jaya Yeshulae dainachhana‌ (2)
paoorao maukatai, Yeshulae malaaee saitataai dainachhana‌ (2)
2. jaya jaya jaya jaya Yeshu aaunaechhana‌ (2)
taimaeelaaee laina, malaaee laina chhaiṭaṭaai aaunaechhana‌ (2)
3. jaya jaya jaya jaya Yeshulae dainachhana‌ (2)
paoorao maukatai Yeshulae malaaee saitataai dainachhana‌ (2)

songs.title: jaya jaya parabhau Yeshu kaee (2)
lyrics: kao. jaya jaya parabhau Yeshu kaee (2)
hama kao bachaanae aayo jagata maem, usakaee satautai karao
laa... laa... haalalaelaooyoha aamaeena .
1. khaoona kaee dhaaraa bahataee saoolaee sae, jaisa maem dhaulae saba paapa
dhaolao tauma bhaye apanae dailakao, usamaem rahae na daaga .
2. garahaṇa karao tauma aaja Yeshu kaee khauna kaee bahataee dhaara,
usakao banaalao khaewanahaaraa, naaiyayo lagaa lao paara .
3. waasapa aataa maeraa parabhaujaee, lae jaayaegaa saatha
aashaa maeraee aba tao yahaee haai, chalao tauma maerae saatha
4. haradama haomgae saatha Yeshu kae, khaushaee aura shaanatai aaraama
aayaegaa waha laenae tauma kao, rahanaa tauma taaiyora .

songs.title: jaya baolao jaya baolao Yeshu masaihakao jaya baolao
lyrics: (jaya baolao) (2) Yeshu masaihakao jaya baolao) (2)
(anadhaokao aankha daiyo Yeshunae) (2)
(langagaḍaakao chalaa daiyo Yeshu nae) (2)
(jaya baolao) (2)
(jaya baolao) (2), Yeshu masaihakao jaya baolao) (2)
(kaoraeekao shaudadha kaiyo Yeshu nae) (2)
(laajarasakao jailaa daiyo Yeshu nae) (2)
(jaya baolao) (2)
(jaya baolao) (2), Yeshu masaihakao jaya baolao) (2)
(paapao sae shaudadha kaiyo Yeshu nae) (2)
(hamasabakao bachaa laiyo Yeshu nae) (2)
(jaya baolao) (2)
(jaya baolao) (2), Yeshu masaihakao jaya baolao) (2)

songs.title: jaya baolao masaeehaa kaee jaya baolao rae (2)
lyrics: jaya baolao masaeehaa kaee jaya baolao rae (2)
haan jaee baolao, tauma baolao saba baolao rae (2)
jaya baolao masaeehaa kaee jaya baolao rae (2)

songs.title: jaya ho jaya ho jaya ho jaya ho jaya-jaya-jaya-jaya ho
lyrics: kao. jaya hao, jaya hao, jaya hao, jaya ho jaya-jaya-jaya-jaya ho . (2)
1. aaja parabhau Yeshu janamaayo, waha janamaayo
prem kaee jayaotai laekara aayo (2)
jaeewana saukha kaa patha darashaayo, jaya jaya jaya jaya ho .
2. daesha-daesha kae janyonaee aae, janyonaee aae
saonaa maura laobaana wae laae, laobaana laae
dawaara khaulae haृdaya hama laae, jaya jaya jaya jaya ho .
3. daeena dauhkhaee paapaee saba aao, paapaee aao
saemta maem apanae paapa dhaulaao, paapa dhaulaao
gaeeta paitaa kae gauṇa kae gaao, jaya jaya jaya jaya ho ॥

songs.title: jaya haosa‌ tapaaeemkao Yeshu gaaurawamaya paaunaubhao’ ananata
lyrics: 1. jaya haosa‌ tapaaeemkao, Yeshu gaaurawamaya paaunaubhao’ ananata maृtayaumaa waijaya
chamakailao sawaragadaootalae ḍhaungagaa palaṭaae, jahaan tapaaeemkao laasha thaiyao, kaatarao maatara thaiyao .
kao. jaya haosa‌ tapaaeemkao, Yeshu gaaurawamaya paaunaubhao’ ananata maृtayaumaa waijaya
2. laau jaiundao Yeshu chaihaanadaekhai aaee paapa ra dauhkha maeṭaaunchhana‌ bhaeṭaee haamaeelaaee
kharaeeṣhaṭaeeya maṇaḍalaee garaosa‌ parabhaukao jaya jaya, haṭaigayao sabalaaee maृtayau kaalakao bhaya .
3. paoorao bharaosaa raakhachhaaun, taaraṇahaara hae parataapaee parabhau, dainauhaosa‌ gaohaara
jayawanatabhanadaa jayawanata haamaee saba banaaun maृtayau khaolaa taraee sawaragalaoka pasaaun .

songs.title: jaya haosa‌ parabhaukao jaya jaya jaya jaya haosa‌
lyrics: kao. jaya haosa‌ parabhaukao, jaya jaya jaya jaya haosa‌
1. paramapaitaakao charaṇakamalamaa, aaoo shaira jhaukaaee,
paraṇaama‌ garaaun, daṇaḍawata‌ garaaun, manakao garawa haṭaaee (2)
masaeehaee prem jao manamaa jagaaoon, manakao dawaeṣha haṭaaoon,
masaeehaee jayaotai manamaa chamakaaee jaeewana daipa jalaaoon (2)
2. sawaragalaokamaa satautai chaढ़aaun jayajaya kharaeeṣhaṭakao manaaaun
taaraṇahaarakao prem parachaaraaun maanaisalaaee kharaeeṣhaṭa chainaaaun (2)
jaeewana daeepa sabalae jalaaee, masaeehaee jaeewana laiee
anadhakaaralae paooraṇa yao jagamaa masaeehaee jayaotai phaijaaaun (2)
3. jaeewana pathamaa paau baढ़aaun maanaisalaaee kharaeeṣhaṭamaa layoaun
Yeshu, bishwasee jhauṇaḍa hao, aaoo haatamaa hat mailaaaun (2)
parabhaukao, haukauma paalana garanae manamaa utasaaha jagaaaun
taaraṇahaarakao yasha parachaaraaun, jagamaa uccha garaaaun (2)

songs.title: jaya haosa‌ Yeshu raajaakao maukataidaataakao udadhaarakarataakao
lyrics: kao. jaya haosa‌ Yeshu raajaakao, maukataidaataakao, udadhaarakarataakao (2)
1. uhaanlae haamaeelaaee prem garaee karaoosakao sabaai dauhkha bhaoganaubhao’
hara paapakao banadhanalaaee taoड़ee haamaeelaaee sawatanatara garanaubhao’
2. pauraanao jaeewana saba bhaoolaee nayon jaeewana kharaeeṣhaṭamaa jaiunaechhau
paitaakao hara parataijanyolaaee samajhaee kharaeeṣhaṭakao paailao ma pachhayounaechhau .

songs.title: jaya-jaya Yeshu jaya-jaya Yeshu jaya maृtayau para
lyrics: kao. jaya-jaya Yeshu, jaya-jaya Yeshu, jaya maृtayau para
jaya-jayakaara, saृjanaahaara, paalanahaara, taaraṇahaara .
1. daeenaom kaa dauhkha haranaewaalaa, haृdaya maem shaanatai bharanae waalaa
jaya-jaya ranajana, jaya dau:kha bhanajana .
jaya-jayakaara, saृjanaahaara, paalanahaara, taaraṇahaara .
2. nara tana dhaara laiyao awataara, dae naija paraaṇa kaiyao chhauṭakaaraa
jaya-jaya taraataa jaya saukha daataa .
jaya-jayakaara saृjanaahaara, paalanahaara, taaraṇahaara .
3. maृtayau kae bamdhana bhanajanahaara akaṣhaya jaeewana daewanahaara
raogaina shaokaina eka aadhaara .
jaya-jayakaara saृjanaahaara, paalanahaara, taaraṇahaara .
4. jaya-jayakaara karao saba payorao nara-naaraee eka samga paukaarao
naarae maarao jaya lalakaaraom .
jaya-jayakaara saृjanaahaara, paalanahaara, taaraṇahaara ॥

songs.title: jaya-jayakaara (2) Yeshu kaee jayakaara .
lyrics: kao. jaya-jayakaara (2) Yeshu kaee jayakaara .
1. maeraa Yeshu masaeeha jaba isa daunaiyon maem thaa,
usanae achachhae-achachhae kaama kaiyae, kabhaye mauradao kao jagaayo
kabhaye bhayeḍaoo kao khailaayo, aura raogaee kao chamgaa kaiyae .
2. bhayeड़ thaee paancha hajaara chaelae thae bailakaula laachaara,
unakao saujhaee na kaoee upaaya, eka laड़kaa wahaan aayo
raoṭaee-machhalaee saatha laayo, Yeshu nae daiyo bhayeड़ kao khailaayo .
3. chaara daina kabara banada, aataee thaee usasae dauraganadha
laogaom kaee na thaa bailakaula bishwas, jaaisaee Yeshu nae paukaaraa
laajara baahara naikala aayo, Yeshu nae kaiyo mauradae kao jailaayo ॥

songs.title: jayajaya gara khaushaeelae parabhaukao janama daina (2)
lyrics: kao. jayajaya gara ... khaushaeelae ... parabhaukao ... janama daina (2)
1. maraiyama garabhawataee thaiina‌ pawaitara aatamaalae,
tayoganae ichachhaa garae yaosaepha, daaoodakao chharaalae,
sawaragadaootalae yaosaephalaaee khabara paurayoe
anai unalae maraiyamalaaee aaphanaai garaae .
2. bhaeड़ee gaoṭhamaa gaoṭhaalaa saba gaoṭhaai chhaड़era
gaaundaai gae kharaeeṣhaṭakao jayajaya darashana garaera,
baethalaehaema bhananae saanao gaaunmaa kharaeeṣhaṭakao janama bhao’
agamawakataalae baolaekao wachana paoorao bhao’ .
3. saanao taaraa daekhaaparayao paoorawa daeshamaa
jayaotaiṣhaeeharaoo daauड़daai aae parabhaukao khaojamaa,
baalaka kharaeeṣhaṭakao darashana paaee aananadaita bhae
kanataura khaolaee sauna, dhaoopa, maoorarakaa, bhaeṭaee chaढ़ae .
4. aanauuhaosa‌ aajaai hae bhaai hao, bishwas garaera
maaganauhaosa‌ kaṣhamaa parabhaukao paaumaa paraera,
aaja parabhau aaunaubhao’ maukatai dainalaaee
phaerai parabhau aaunauhaunaechha nayoya garanalaaee .

songs.title: jayajaya gara saanaa naanaeeharaoo kharaeeṣhaṭa hauna‌ prem kharaeeṣhaṭa
lyrics: 1. jayajaya gara saanaa, naanaeeharaoo,
kharaeeṣhaṭa hauna‌ prema, kharaeeṣhaṭa hauna‌ prem (2)
2. saewaa gara, saanaa, naanaeeharaoo,
kharaeeṣhaṭa hauna‌ prema, kharaeeṣhaṭa hauna‌ prem (2)
3. dhanyawad bhana, saanaa, naanaeeharaoo,
kharaeeṣhaṭa hauna‌ prema, kharaeeṣhaṭa hauna‌ prem (2)
4. unalaaee bhaja, saanaa, naanaeeharaoo,
kharaeeṣhaṭa hauna‌ prema, kharaeeṣhaṭa hauna‌ prem (2)
5. payorao gara, saanaa, naanaeeharaoo,
kharaeeṣhaṭa hauna‌ prema, kharaeeṣhaṭa hauna‌ prem (2)
6. paraarathanaa gara, saanaa, naanaeeharaoo,
kharaeeṣhaṭa hauna‌ prema, kharaeeṣhaṭa hauna‌ prem (2)

songs.title: jayajaya jayajaya jayajayakaara parabhaukao
lyrics: kao. jayajaya, jayajaya jayajayakaara parabhaukao
mana maerao ragatalae shaudadha bhayao (2)
1. karunaikao chhaaiumaa jahaan ragata bagayao paapaailae dabaindaai ma gaen tayahaan (2)
mana maerao ragatalae shaudadha bhayao (2)
2. naishachaya daoora bhayao sabaai paapa haृdayamaa raajaya garachhana‌ Yeshu aaja (2)
karaoosakao chhaeumaa paooraṇa parataapa (2)

songs.title: jayajaya dhanaya Yeshu haamarao maukataidaataa saृṣhaṭai saba
lyrics: 1. jayajaya dhanaya Yeshu haamarao maukataidaataa,
saृṣhaṭai saba, achamamakao prem saunaaoo
bhaja-bhaja daootaharaoo sawaragamaa gaaunchhana‌,
unakao naamalaaee ijajata ra maana baढ़aoo
gaoṭhaalaajhaain Yeshu bhaeड़a samahaalachhana‌,
kaandhamaa baokaee saanaalaaee layonuchhana‌ ghara
aaoo saba saiyaona ḍaanड़amaa basanae
bishwasee satautai gara Yeshukao jayajayakaara .
2. jayajaya Yeshu hauna‌ haamaraa maukataidaataa,
paapakao lagi ragata bahaaee marae
haamarao aaड़ ra ananata jaeewanakao aashaa,
bhaja-bhaja Yeshu jao karaoosa chaḍhae
dauhkha bhaoganae premapaooraṇa maukataidaataa,
kaanड़e maukauṭalae ghaochayao unakao naidhaara
laaja, ghaina, inakaara, nainadaa khaaee
haamaraolaagai aba jayawanata sawaragakao raajakaumaara .
3. jayajaya dhanaya Yeshu haamaraa maukataidaataa,
sawaragadawaaramaa gaunyajaayamaana sawara saunaaoo
kharaeeṣhaṭa udadhaaraka hauna‌, agamawakataa,
paoojaaraee mahaaraajaa unalaaee maukauṭa lagaaoo
maृtayau haarayao, haraṣha manaaaun bishwasee,
hae chaihaana hao, khaoi ta jaeeta taerao ?
Yeshu bayauntae ra maृtayau bhayao sawaragae ḍhaokaa
Yeshu bayauntae maukataidaataa haamarao .

songs.title: jayajaya Yeshu (2) maृtayaumaathai jaya jayajayakaara
lyrics: kao. jayajaya Yeshu (2) maृtayaumaathai jaya, jayajayakaara
saृjanahaara, paalanahaara, taaraṇahaara jayajaya Yeshu (2)
1. dauhkhaeekao dauhkha haranaewaalaa haृdayamaa shaanatai dainaewaalaa
jaya saba bhana, dauhkha maeṭaiyao, jayajayakaara saृjanaahaara .
2. manauṣhaya sawaraoopa dhaaraṇa garaee naeecha garaeebalaaee dainaubhao’ chhauṭakaaraa
jayajaya taraataa, jaya saukhadaataa jayajayakaara .
3. maृtayau banadhana taoड़naewaalaa, sabaai jaeewana dainaewaalaa
raogaee ashaanataikao eka aadhaara jayajayakaara .
4. jayajayakaara garaaun sabaai payora nara-naaraee ekasanga paukaara
naaraa lagaaoo jayajayakaara, jayajayakaara .

songs.title: jawaanaeelaaee parabhaukao naimatai daiundao balaidaana chaढ़aoo
lyrics: kao. jawaanaeelaaee parabhaukao naimatai daiundao balaidaana chaढ़aoo
samsaaralaaee tayogaee aaphanao karaoosa uṭhaaee parabhaulaaee naai pachhayooo haai
1. yao sharaeera taimarao manadaira ho jahaan eeshawaralae waasa garachhana‌
yasalaaee sadhaain pawaitara raakha, parabhaulae raaja garachhana‌ .
2. aaphaailaaee parabhaukao saipaahaee banaaoo, laड़ain chha laamao, haraesa nakhaaoo,
bishwaskao utatama laड़ain laड़, parabhaulae jaya dainachhana‌ .

songs.title: jasakao gharamaa Yeshu chhana‌ katai aananada chha
lyrics: (jasakao gharamaa Yeshu chhana‌, katai aananada chha,
katai aananada chha, katai aananada chha) (2)
(Jesus in the family, happy happy home,
Happy happy home, happy happy home) (2)
(jaisa kae gharamae yaeeshaoo haai kaitanaa aananada haai,
kaitanaa aananada haai, kaitanaa aananada haai) (2)

songs.title: jasakao maanaisamaa raakhaiekao chha
lyrics: jasakao maanaisamaa raakhaiekao chha
jasakao bharaoshaa Yeshumaa raakhaiekao chha
(aau Yeshulaaee haera, aaoo Yeshumaa basa
Yeshulae taimaeelaaee shaanatai dainau haunachha) (2)
(Yeshu yaesa shamsaaramaa aaunau bhayao
taimarao-haamarao paapakao laagai) (2)
ra uhaa karaooshamaa maranau bhayao
taimarao nayo jaeewanakao lagi
taesaailae ma bhanchu (2)
(aau Yeshulaaee haera, aaoo Yeshumaa basa
Yeshulae taimaeelaaee jaeewana dainau haunachha) (2)
(laai laai laai) (2) (laaraa laalaa) (2) laai laai laai
(laai laai laai) (2) (laaraa laalaa) (2) laai laai laai
(jasalae Yeshukao baaṭao pachhayouda chha
jasalae uhaakao naaulaaee garahaṇa garadachha) (2)
yaesaailae ma bhanchu (2)
(aau Yeshulaaee haera, aaoo Yeshumaa basa
Yeshulae taimaeelaaee maukatai dainau haunachha) (2)
jasakao maanaisamaa raakhaiekao chha
jasakao bharaoshaa Yeshumaa raakhaiekao chha
aau Yeshulaaee haera, aaoo Yeshumaa basa
Yeshulae taimaeelaaee shaanatai dainau haunachha
Yeshulae taimaeelaaee jaeewana dainau haunachha
Yeshulae taimaeelaaee maukatai dainau haunachha

songs.title: jasaraee haraiṇalae khaolaakao paanaeekao taृṣhaṇaa garadachha
lyrics: jasaraee haraiṇalae khaolaakao paanaeekao taृṣhaṇaa garadachha
tayasaraee hae parabhau maerao paraaṇalae tapaaeemkao taृṣhaṇaa garachha .
tapaaeem maerao shakatai ra ḍhaala, maerao aatamaa tapaaeemlaaee saumapanachhau .
tapaaeem naai maerao haृdayakao chaahanaa ra satautai chaḍhaaunchhau .

songs.title: jasalae achaooka prem parabhaukao chaakhaekaa chhana‌
lyrics: jasalae achaooka prem parabhaukao chaakhaekaa chhana‌
sabaailae bhanaoona‌, (aamaina‌, parashamsaa haosa‌) (2)
jasalae adabhauta kaama parabhaukao daekhaekaa chhana‌
sabaailae bhanaoona‌, (aamaina‌, parashamsaa haosa‌) (2)
jasalae shaaitaanamaathai waijaya paaekaa chhana‌
sabaailae bhanaoona‌, (aamaina‌, parashamsaa haosa‌) (2)
aamaina‌ parashamsaa haosa‌ Yeshukao Yeshukao
amaina‌ mahaimaa haosa‌ Yeshukao
amaina‌ jayajayakaara haosa‌ Yeshukao .

songs.title: jasaai tapaaeemkao shakataikaa ghaoṣhaṇaa garachhaaum
lyrics: 1. (jasaai tapaaeemkao shakataikaa ghaoṣhaṇaa garachhaaum
jasaai tapaaeemkao naaunkao parashamsaa garachhaaum) (2)
ṭauṭaekao haृdaya jaoड़nauhaosa‌, banadana saba phaukaaunauhaosa‌
anadhakaara haṭaaunauhaosa‌ (haosananaa maaraanathaa) (4)
2. (jasaai tapaaeemmaa saaharaai khaushaee haunachhaaun
jasaai tapaaeemmaa haृdaya ramaaundachha) (2)
haraṣhakao taela khanayounauhaosa‌ dhaaramaikataa pahairayounauhaosa‌
amaiṣhaeka paṭhaaunauhaosa‌ (haosananaa maaraanathaa) (4)
(aaunauhaosa‌ hae Yeshu) (2)

songs.title: jasaai taimarao aaraadhanaa garachhau taimarao mahaimaita mauhaaralaaee
lyrics: jasaai taimarao aaraadhanaa garachhau taimarao mahaimaita mauhaaralaaee haerachhau (2)
taimarao upasathaitaibhaitara jaba pasachhau, taimarao premakao anaubhawa garachhau
laagaekaa chaoṭa ra ghaata haृdayakaa naikao haunachhana‌
aatamaa ra sharaeerakao raoga naikao haunachha (2)

songs.title: jasataai jayaotaiṣhaeeharaoolae jayaotai haerae taaraakao jasataai tayasa
lyrics: 1. jasataai jayaotaiṣhaeeharaoolae jayaotai haerae taaraakao, jasataai tayasa ujayolaomaai
aghai baढ़e ramaaundaai, tayasataai haamaee agauwaai paaaun tapaaeemkao sanamaukhamaa aaaun .
2. jasataai garae khaooba hataara bhaeṭana baalaka taaraṇaharaoo, jasataai haeraee sawaraganaatha
ghaunड़a ṭaekae namarataasaatha, tayasataai haamaee sarawadaa paaraaun kharaeeṣhaṭakao charaṇamaa .
3. jasataai paujae parabhaulaaee bahaumaoolaya bhaeṭaee layoee, tayasataai haraṣhasaatha haamaee
paapa-bhaooladaekhai shaudadha banaee chaढ़aaun tana-mana-dhana tapaaeem sawaragaeeya raajaa Yeshulaaee .
4. shaudadha Yeshu baaṭaomaa haamaeelaaee ḍaorayounauhaosa‌ sadaa anai baitaepachhai jayona
sawaragamaa paurayounauhaosa‌ paraaṇa, jahaan chhaaina ghaama-taaraa, saba chhana‌ ujajawala tapaaeemmaa .

songs.title: jasataai ma chhau ho tapaaeemkao jaeewanakaa maeeta payora
lyrics: 1. jasataai ma chhau, ho tapaaeemkao jaeewanakaa maeeta payora garachhana‌ jao
tapaaeemlaaee, ma arapaṇa garachhau, hae parabhau Yeshu, aaundaaichhau .
2. maerao aayaukao baihaanamaa khaushaeesaatha jayona ra parataijanyo
dainachhau nabhaye abaelaa, hae parabhau Yeshu, aaundaaichhau .
3. sadaa jayaotaimaa basana paaoon sadaa bhalaaee kaama garana paaoon
saewaamaa paoorao bala lagaaoon yasakaaraṇa Yeshu aaundaaichhau .
4. jaeewana sawatanatara ma haundaa shaudadha hauna chaahanachhau tapaaeemmaa
saojhao ra bhakata, dharamaatamaa, hae jaeewana sawaamaee, aaundaaichhau .

songs.title: jahaan nadaee bagachha tayahaan paooraṇataa paitaakao waasasathaanabaaṭa
lyrics: jahaan nadaee bagachha, tayahaan paooraṇataa,
paitaakao waasasathaanabaaṭa bagadachha,
Yeshu jaeewana hauna‌, unaee tyo nadaee,
jao aatamaadawaaraa haamaeebaaṭa bagadachhana‌ .

songs.title: jahaan panai parabhau paau maerao ḍaorayounaubhao’ saathaaimaa hat
lyrics: 1. jahaan panai parabhau paau maerao ḍaorayounaubhao’ saathaaimaa hat samaatana paaoon
baaṭao kaanड़e haosa‌ taai bharaekao jaalalae, pachhayounchhau ma, parabhau ḍaorayoyoun’ bhanae .
kao. jahaan panai maukataidaataa (ma pachhayounaechhau‌) (2) jahaan panai maukataidaataa ḍaorayoyoun’ bhanae
2. jahaan panai parabhau khaalai mausakauraaoo, rakaṣhaa, bala ra shaanatai daeoo, paapamaa naparaoon
baaṭao andhayorao haosa‌ tara naḍaraaoo, jahaan bhae panai parabhau saathaai daooo .
3. jahaan panai parabhau paraarathanaa yahaee garaoon, saangaurao baaṭao haiḍaoon kaailae nabhaṭakaoon
paapalae khainchana khaojae asawaeekaara garaoon, saojhao baaṭao parabhausaatha-saathaai hainḍaoon .

songs.title: jaaun haamaee sabaai jaaun jaaun jaaun jaaun Yeshukao
lyrics: jaaun haamaee sabaai jaaun jaaun jaaun jaaun
Yeshukao aajanyolaaee maanaaum (2)
1. samsaarabharaee jaaun sausamaachaara saunaau
sabaai maanaisalaaee Yeshukao chaelaa banaaun (2)
2. Yeshukaa sanataana haaum sauwaasanaa chharaaum
anadhakaara yao jagatamaa jayaotai banaaum (2)
3. Yeshu parataikao prem daekhaaun
saewaa garadaai uhaanlaaee khaushaee paaraaum (2)

songs.title: jaaga uṭha naidaraabaaṭa jaagaृtakao baelaa aaekao chha
lyrics: kao. jaaga uṭha, naidaraabaaṭa jaagaृtakao baelaa aaekao chha,
raata dhaeraai naai waitaisakayao,
aba daina aaunaai laagaekao chha .
1. janyonaee kaumaaraee jhaaim parakhanaeharaoo,
daulahaakao gharamaa parawaesha garachhana‌ (2)
maoorakha kaumaaraee jhaaim jaiunaeharaoo,
“khaola na khaola ḍhaokaa” bhanadaai raunachhana‌ (2)
2. jayaotaikaa hataiyoralaaee dhaaraṇa garaee,
kharaeeṣhaṭakaa asala saewaka banaaum (2)
bishwaskao utatama laड़nata laड़ee,
jaeewanakao maukauṭa paraapata garaaun (2)
3. haṭhaee ra baagaee maanaisa banaee,
samsaara maai kaina pharakai jaanachhaau (2)
daui dainakao saukhalaaee raojaee taimaee,
yaugaanauyaugasamama kaina raunachhaau ? (2)
4. parataipala aaphaailae aaphaailaaee jaanchaee,
pashachaatataapaee haamaee banaindaai jaaaun (2)
najaeeka chha aba nayoyakao ghaड़ee,
nairadaoṣha ra naiṣhakalamka banaindaai jaaaun (2)

songs.title: jaagaृtai paṭhaaunauhaosa‌ hae haamaraa sawaragaeeya paitaa
lyrics: jaagaृtai paṭhaaunauhaosa‌, hae haamaraa sawaragaeeya paitaa
tapaaeemkao naaun pawaitara haosa‌, tapaaeemkao raajaya aaosa‌ (2)
tapaaeemkao ichachhaa jasatao sawaragamaa chha, tayasataai yasa paृthawaeemaa paooraa haosa‌ .
ma baihaana sabaeraai uṭhanaechhau, satautai-parashamsaa chaढ़aunaechhau
Yeshukao naaunlaaee mahaimaita paaranaechhau,
marairahaekaa aatamaakao maukatai ra udadhaarakao lagi
anatarabainataeekao paraarathanaa chaढ़aunaechhau (2)
ma bhaalae baasadaa uṭhanaechhau, satautai-parashamsaa chaढ़aunaechhau,
Yeshukao naaunlaaee mahaimaita paaranaechhau,
laakhaaun-laakhaaun maanaisalae Yeshu parabhaulaaee garahaṇa garaee
maukatai ra udadhaara paaekao ma daekhanaechhau (2) jaagaृtai paṭhaaunauhaosa‌...

songs.title: jaagaृtai paṭhaaoo (4) maṇaḍalaeekao chaeetakaara
lyrics: (jaagaृtai paṭhaaoo) (4)
maṇaḍalaeekao chaeetakaara, jaagaृtai paṭhaaoo
daeshalaaee bachaaoo, jaagaृtai paṭhaaoo
kaृpaa paokhaaoo, jaagaृtai paṭhaaoo .

songs.title: jaagao saonae waalao wakata jaanae lagaa aaja taumakao
lyrics: kao. jaagao saonae waalao wakata jaanae lagaa,
aaja taumakao jagaanae kaoee aayo haai
jainadagaee maem kaisaee kaee saunaee na saunaee,
taumahaem wachana saunaanae kaoee aayo haai .
1. jaba dainakaa ujaalaa baढ़nae lagaa gaphalata maem paड़e kayaom saonae lagae
haradama taumahae kaoee jagaanae aae kabhaye jaaga uṭhae phaira saonae lagae .
aisaom kao nataeejaa kauchha na mailae taumahaem yoda dailaanae kaoee aayo haai .
2. daunaiyon maem taumanae paapa kaiyae apanae laiyae maauta kamaaee haai
aura mana kaee shaanatai paanae maem yaom saaraee umara ganwaaee haai
maranae kae pahalae jaraa saunalao taumahaem maauta sae bachaanae kaoee aayo haai .
3. aajaao Yeshu kae kadamaom maem chhaड़o yae daunaiyon kaee baataem
jao na maanae maiṭa jaatae haai, jao bacha jaatae jaeewana paatae haai
aisaa na samaya phaira aayae kabhaye taumahaem jaeewana dailaanae kaoee aayo haai .

songs.title: jaagao saonaewaalao (2) masaeeha aa rahaa haai baadalaom maem
lyrics: kao. jaagao saonaewaalao (2)
masaeeha aa rahaa haai baadalaom maem
kalaisaiyo laenaem aa rahaa haai (2)
1. samaya baita jaa rahaa haai
daina naikaṭa aa rahaa haai (2)
masaeeha aa rahaa haai baadalaom maem
kalaisaiyo laenae aa rahaa haai . (2)
