jaagao saonae waalaa haai
2. daootaom kae shabada saunaogae
masaeeha aaemgae saimhaasana maem
nayoya sabakao haogaa
jaeewana kaee pausataka khaolaegaa . (2)
jaagao saonaewaalaa... ॥

songs.title: jaagaaun shakataishaalaee jaatai khaḍaa haaun yao dharataeemaa
lyrics: jaagaaun shakataishaalaee jaatai khaḍaa haaun yao dharataeemaa,
laiaun tarawaara aatamaakao, bhatakaaoon yaojanaa shataraukao
(jaba uhaan baiuntanaubhao’) (2) Yeshu baiuntanaubhao’
(haraaunaubhao’) (2) shatarauharaoolaaee .

songs.title: jaagaraitai chaahanachhau jaagaraitai chaahanachhau
lyrics: (jaagaraitai chaahanachhau, jaagaraitai chaahanachhau
jaagaraitai chaahanachhau parabhau) (2)
(raogaikao changagaaee, baauraee uṭhaaee
jaagaraitai chaahanachhau parabhau) (2)

songs.title: jaandaina ma ṭaaḍhaa taimaeebaaṭa baanchairahanachhau sadaa
lyrics: jaandaina ma ṭaaḍhaa taimaeebaaṭa baanchairahanachhau sadaa taimaeesanga
jaandaina ma ṭaaḍhaa taimaeebaaṭa khaishaee rahanachhau sadaa taimaeesanga
[(sakadaina ma baanchana taimaee bainaa) (2)
(gaahairahanachhau sadaa taimaeemaa ma khaushaee rahanachhau sadaa Yeshumaa ma) (2)] (2)
jaandaina ma ṭaaḍhaa taimaeebaaṭa
baanchairahanachhau sadaa taimaeesanga
jaandaina ma ṭaaḍhaa taimaeebaaṭa khaushaee rahanachhau sadaa taimaeesanga
sakadainna ma baanchana... jaandaina...

songs.title: jaandaaichhana‌ Yeshu kalawaraeetaira taimarao-maerao paapakao bhaaraee
lyrics: kao. jaandaaichhana‌ Yeshu kalawaraeetaira taimarao-maerao paapakao bhaaraee baokaera
maayo kasatao, anaugaraha kasatao, naapaera naapanaai nasakanae
1. sahaera paeera-marakaa, chaoṭa kaoraraakao khaandaai
bhaokaai ra payosaee banaee, ukaalaee-oraalaee hainड़daai
karaoosakao bhaaraee baokaera larabaraindaai, dharapharaindaai
jaandaaichhana‌ jaiundao balai bhaera .
2. thaukaai ra nainadaa sahandaai, gailalaa ra maukakaa khaandaai
anatamaa jhauṇaḍaae karaoosamaa, bagae ragatakao dhaaraa
taimarao-maerao paapa dhaunalaaee maaphaee maagaidaie paitaalaaee .

songs.title: jaandaaichhau Yeshukahaan chhaaina dauhkha darada wahaan
lyrics: kao. jaandaaichhau Yeshukahaan chhaaina dauhkha, darada wahaan (2)
sadhaain haunachhau mahaimaa, jaandaaichhau Yeshukahaan (2)
1. yao sharaeera chhaड़ee ma uड़ee jaanachhau, ananata daeshamaa (2)
saunaaulao shaharakao saunadara daeshamaa mahaimaita bhaeṣhamaa (2)
2. haeradainan yahaan kaṣhaiṇaika jayaotai, ma aankhaa chaimalanachhau (2)
Yeshukao mahaimaita mauhaara haeradaai sadhaain naai ramaaunaechhau (2)

songs.title: jaandaaichhau Yeshukahaan hallelujah bhanadaai
lyrics: kao. jaandaaichhau Yeshukahaan, hallelujah bhanadaai
(baolaaundaaichha haamaeelaaee pawaitara wachanalae) (2)
1. hae daajayaoo-bhaai, hae daidaee-bahainaee nabhaoola tyo gharalaaee (2)
jaaaun haamaee sabaai jaya jaya gaaundaai, paapalaaee tayogaera (2)
2. ramaahaṭa garadaai, satautai gaaundaai ananata gharaaimaa (2)
jahaan sawaragadaootagaṇa jaya jaya gaaunchhana‌ Yeshukao chhaewaaimaa .
3. jahaan na tairakhaa-bhaoka aadai, jahaan na daina na raata (2)
basaaunlaa maathai satautai garadaai Yeshukao chhaewaaimaa .

songs.title: jaanadainan ma paramaeshawaralae prem kaina garanaubhao’
lyrics: 1. jaanadainan ma paramaeshawaralae prem kaina garanaubhao’,
waa kharaeeṣhaṭalae kaina bachaae ayaogaya paraaṇa maerao .
kao. tara kasamaathai bishwas raakhaen sao jaanadachhau ma ra naishachaya chhau ma
kai unalaaee jae maile saumapaen, raakhanaechhana‌ saurakaṣhaasaatha
2. jaanadainan kasaraee bachaaunae bishwas daie unalae
waa unakao wachana patayoundaa manamaa shaanatai paaen .
3. jaanadainan kasaraee aatamaalae jaga daoṣhaee ṭhaharayounchhana‌
waa wachanadawaaraa Yeshulaaee parakaṭa garaaunchhana‌ .
4. jaanadainan kae aaiparanaechha ma maranabhanadaa aghai
kai haunachha malaaee dauhkha waa saukha, taृpatai waa garaeebaee .
5. jaanadainan ma kahailae, kahaan Yeshu phaerai aaulaana‌
kai maraepachhai bhaeṭaoonlaa kai bhaeṭaoon aakaashamaa .

songs.title: jaayaemgae utatama eka daesha maem jaraoora rahaemgae parabhau kae saatha hama
lyrics: kao. jaayaemgae utatama eka daesha maem jaraoora, rahaemgae, parabhau kae saatha hama jaraoora
sawaragaeeya daesha, utatama bhaye waha haai, hamaaraa waha daesha jao adabhaoota haai .
1. paitaa kao bhaayo haai, hama eka raajaya dae
daunaiyon kaee saृṣhaṭai sae pahalae bahaayo haai . (2‌) jaayaemgae... .
2. adabhaoota waha nagara haai, eeshawara kaee rachanaa haai
daृढ़taa sae naetara ḍaalaee, sathaira kaiyo haai . (2) jaayaemgae... .
3. waitara nagara waha haai dhaaramaikataa rahataee haai
sawaragaeeya sawabhaawa sae taaiyora bhaye kaiyo haai (2) jaayaemgae... .
4. sanaatana raajaya waha haai yaugaanauyauga waha rahae
rahaemgae sadaa usamaem jainakao usanae chaunaa haai . (2) jaayaemgae... .

songs.title: jaiunchhau-jaiunchhau ma yasaraee naai jaiunchhau
lyrics: kao. jaiunchhau-jaiunchhau ma yasaraee naai jaiunchhau
parabhaumaa aaja ma yasaraee naai jaiunchhau
samgharaṣha baeecha bhaera panai parabhaumaa aaja
ma yasaraee naai jaiunchhau ... .
1. hauraee taoophaana samgharaṣha garaee maृtayau naai paapakao khaalaṭao taraee
aatamaikaee kadama ma raookanae chhauinan
payorao parabhaulaaee ma tayoganae chhauinan .
2. samapaooraṇa raata hara baihaanaeesamama saewaa parabhaukao sadhaaim-sadhaaim
maukataikao ragata ma bhaulanae chhauinan
jaeewana naaukaa paurayounchhau kainaaraa .

songs.title: jaiundao eeshawarakao aatamaa malaaee lainaosa‌
lyrics: jaiundao eeshawarakao aatamaa, malaaee lainaosa‌
jaiundao eeshawarakao aatamaa, malaaee lainaosa‌
maoḍanauhaosa‌ banaaunauhaosa‌, bharanauhaosa‌ chalaaunauhaosa‌
jaiundao eeshawarakao aatamaa, malaaee lainaosa‌

songs.title: jaiundao jaiundao chhana‌ Yeshu kharaeeṣhaṭa jaiundao
lyrics: jaiundao, jaiundao chhana‌ Yeshu kharaeeṣhaṭa jaiundao
haosa‌ agauwaai, dainachhana‌ malaaee ra sangagatai maeeṭhao
jaiundao, jaiundao utaarana paapadaekhai .
ma kasaraee naishachaya jaanadachhau ? manamaai jaiunchhana‌ unaee .

songs.title: jaiunalaaee kasaaikao maayo chaahainachha baanchanalaaee panai
lyrics: jaiunalaaee kasaaikao maayo chaahainachha
baanchanalaaee panai aashaa chaahainachha (2)
tyo maayo chaokhao Yeshumaa paainachha
tyo aashaa panai Yeshumaa paainachha (2)
1. haृdayakaa taimaraa chaoṭaharau sabaai Yeshumaa naikao haunachha (2)
nairadayaee paapaee yao daunaiyonmaa (2)
sahaaraa taimaeelaaee mailachha (2)
2. aau aba ramaaee Yeshukao sharaṇamaa nagaraee shamkaa manamaa (2)
jaiunaechhaau saukhaee bhaye baankaee jaeewanamaa (2)
haundaaina dhaokaa baichamaa (2)

songs.title: jainadagai ghaama chhaayo naai ho aaja yahaa bhaolai kahaa ho
lyrics: kao. (jainadagai ghaama chhaayo naai ho aaja yahaa bhaolai kahaa hao) (2)
(haasaera naai baachaidaeu yahaa) (2)
jae jae bhae jaiwanamaa
1. (kaina haara khaanachhaau taimaee jaeewanalaaee haeraera ,
maृtayaulaaee naai naraoja haai chhana dhaeraai saamadhaana) (2)
chaunaautai aauchha jaiwanamaa, jaitanau parachha parabhaumaa bhaera
(saumapaidaeuna jaiwana parabhaulaaee) (2)
dainauhaunachha shaanatai taimailaaee
2. (ṭaukaraiekao taoḍaiekao chhaau kai shaayada taimaee
saatha baihaina anadhakaaramaa bhaautaaraidaai chhaau kai taimaee) (2)
saatha chha haai parabhau yaeshaumaa, dainauhaunachha ananatasamama
(aaidaeuna parabhau yaeshaumaa) (2)
haudaaina haai dhaokaa baichamaa

songs.title: jainadagaee maeraee badala gayaee jaba sae masaeehakao paayo haai
lyrics: kao. jainadagaee maeraee badala gayaee, jaba sae masaeehakao paayo haai
khaila gayaee haai kalaiyon nayaee, Yeshu bahaara laayo haai (2)
1. jaeewana haai aisaa, pala yae dao pala kaa
kaisanae naa jaanaa, haogaa kayo kala kaa
ghaड़iyon saunaharaee, phaira na laauṭaegaee, maukatai aura jaeewana waha laayo haai
2. maaraga maem hamaarae, waha darashaka rahaegaa
kadama ḍagamagaayaem tao, haatha waha thaamaegaa
bhaṭakae hauom kao raaha daikhaanae, isa dharataee para waha aayo haai .
3. jaeewana kaee raoṭaee, aura amaृta jala kao
kaaisaee bharapaooraee sae daetaa waha hamakao
lahaoo bahaakara paapa hamaarae (2) payorae parabhau nae uṭhaayo haai .

songs.title: jainadagaeekao paanaa paanaamaa maile maerao Yeshulaaee sajhaae
lyrics: kao. jainadagaeekao paanaa paanaamaa maile maerao Yeshulaaee sajhaae
kahaee kataai paapa nagaraau bhanaera unakao wachana haृdayamaa raakhae
1. kaaiyoum bhaula garae maile baitaekaa taee dainamaa
ana phaerai garanae chhauina baankaee jaeewanamaa
waitaaunae chhau saaraa jaeewana unakaai saewaamaa
dauhkha saukha haansao aansaumaa gawaaee kharaeeṣhaṭakaai haunaechhau
2. chaahaidaaina aba malaaee samsaarakao thaokahara
chaahainachha kaewala malaaee kharaeeṣhaṭakao anamaola maayo
ekadaina ta saba chhaḍaee jaanau chha
Yeshumaa jao bishwas garanae chaanhai baaikaunaṭha baasa paaunaechha

songs.title: jainadagaeekao paanaamaa sajaaunchhau Yeshulaaee (2)
lyrics: jainadagaeekao paanaamaa sajaaunchhau Yeshulaaee (2)
unaee wainaa baanchana sakadaina Yeshu wainaa baanchana sakadaina (2)
1. maerao yao jaeewana aatamaa paraaṇalae unaeelaaee naai khaojachha
mauṭaukao dhaḍakanaharaumaa unaee sandhaai naai sajainachhana‌ (2)
sadaa sarawadaa unakao mahaimaa parashamsaa aaradhanaa unakao naaunkao
unaee wainaa baanchana sakadaina Yeshu wainaa baanchana sakadaina (2)
2. unalae daiekao yao prem ajamawaraee samama rahanachha
paapaee daunaiyonlaaee bachaauna unalae daiekao tyo balaidaana (2)
sadaa sarawadaa unakao mahaimaa parashamsaa aaradhanaa unakao naaunkao
unaee wainaa baanchana sakadaina Yeshu wainaa baanchana sakadaina (2)

songs.title: jaisa karaoosa para Yeshu maraa thaa waha karaoosa adabhaoota aba
lyrics: kao. jaisa karaoosa para Yeshu maraa thaa, waha karaoosa adabhaoota aba daekhaataa haoon
samsaaraee laabha kao chhaṭaa saa, aura yasha kao nainadaa jaanataa haoon .
1. mata phaoola jaa maerae maoorakha mana, isa laoka kae saukha aura samapata para
ho kharaeeṣhaṭa kae maranae sae parasanana, aura usa para saaraee aashaa dhara
2. daekha usakae shaira haatha paawaom kae ghaawa, yaha kaaisaa daukha aura kaaisaa payoraa
anauṭhaa haai yaha prem sawamaana, anaoopa yaha jaga kaa taaraṇahaara .
3. daekha laohaoo chaadara kae samaana, usa kae sharaeera kao ḍhaapa rahaa
hae mana! samsaara kao baairaee jaana, aura kharaeeṣhaṭa kae paeechhae karaoosa uṭhaa .
4. jao tainaom laoka dae sakataa maaim, isa prem kae yaogaya yaha haonaa kayaoon
hae Yeshu premaee aapa kae maaim, daeha aura paraaṇa chaढ़ataa haoon ॥

songs.title: jaisa naaunmaem naaunmaem (2) jaisa naaunmaem hae jainadagaee
lyrics: jaisa naaunmaem naaunmaem (2)
jaisa naaunmaem hae jainadagaee Yeshu hae wao naaun
jaisa naaunmaem hae maukatai, jaisa naaunmaem hae shakatai
jaisa naaunmaem hae shaanatai, daetaa wao naaun chamgaaee
jaisa naaunmaem hae jainadagaee, Yeshu hae wao naaun
jaisa naaunmaem hae, banadhakaee, Yeshu hae waa naaun
Yeshu taeraa naaun sabasae uccha hae (4)
1. jaisa naamasae shaaitaana ḍarae, usa naamakao jaya jaya karae
jaisa naamasaem yae jamaanaa jhaukae, usa naamakao salaama karaem
jaisa... jainadagaee... naama
Yeshu... uccha hae (4)
2. (bairaamaeesae garaibaeesaem, saraapaosaem hae chhauḍaataa
wao naama hae jao anadhaokao raoshanaee bhaye daetaa) (2)
jaisa... jainadagaee... naaun
Yeshu... uccha hae (4)

songs.title: jaisae khaudaabanada khaushaee dae waha sachamaucha haai khaushahaala
lyrics: 1. jaisae khaudaabanada khaushaee dae waha sachamaucha haai khaushahaala
jao karae bayohaa khaudaabanada maem sao sachamaucha maalaamaala .
2. ina daonao para khaudaabanada jao karatae haai naikaaha
hama taujhasae mananata karatae haaim, taoo una para kara naigaaha
3. wae jaoraoo khama haonae kao, aba karaem kaaula karaara
aura taujhasae barakata paanae kae, haaim daonaom umamaedawaara .
4. jahaan taoo daila kao karae shaada, waa sachachaee saadaee haai
jaisa ghara kao karae taoo aabaada waa khaooba aabadaee haai ॥

songs.title: jaeeundao chhana‌ Yeshu jaeeundao chhana‌
lyrics: jaeeundao chhana‌, Yeshu jaeeundao chhana‌,
maerao manamaa Yeshu jaeeundao chhana‌
samkaṭamaa maerao sahaaraa hauna‌,
Yeshu sadhaain jaeeundao chhana‌ .

songs.title: jaeenaa hae taujhamaem masaeeha maranaa hae taujhamaem masaeeha
lyrics: kao. (jaeenaa hae taujhamaem masaeeha, maranaa hae taujhamaem masaeeha) (2)
(samsaarakae haataom maem jaeewana, maeraa nahaee hae masaeeha) (2)
jaeenaa...
1. (daina ḍhalataa hae raaja gaujarataee hae) (2)
(maeraa daiyo hauaa jaeewana, ḍhalataa nahaee hae masaeeha) (2)
jaeenaa...
2. (maeraa saphara hae daunainyosaem daura kahaee) (2)
(khaogayo hamaem taujhamaem, kauchachha bhaye naisaanaa nahaee) (2)
jaeenaa... maranaa....

songs.title: jaeewana andhayoraomaa jaba aaunchha dauhkha jaba haraesa khaanachhaaun
lyrics: 1. jaeewana andhayoraomaa jaba aaunchha dauhkha
jaba haraesa khaanachhaaun ra haraaunchha saukha
taba aashaiṣha‌ gana, Yeshulaaee haera
ashaiṣha‌ ganadaa-ganadaai, laau ta katai dhaera .
kao. aashaiṣha‌ gana, gana ekaai-eka,
aashaiṣha‌ gana, haera chhana‌ anaeka
aashaiṣha‌ gana, chhakaka paranaechhaau,
parabhaulae taimaeelaaee katai dainaubhao’
2. phaikaraee, shaokakao bhaaraee taimaee baokachhaau,
kai aaunae dainakao lagi baanchaaun kasaraee
baaibala paढ़daakhaeraee taimaee baujhanaechhaau,
haamaraa premaee paitaabaaṭa saba paaunchhaaun .
3. dhana-samapatai haeradaa thauparaai arakaaikao,
taba samajhaaun haamarao dhana chha sawaragakao,
yasa samsaarakao dhanalae shaanatai mailadaaina,
tara Yeshu ḍaakachhana‌ jahaan paeera chhaaina .
4. daina-daina laḍaain haunachha chhandaa samsaaramaa,
shaaitaana jaitana khaojachha haamaeelaaee sadaa
Yeshu chhaeumaa basadaa shakatai dainaechhana‌,
sawaraga napaugaesamama aashaiṣha‌ ganadaai gana .

songs.title: jaeewana euṭaa phaulajasatao ho kaṣhaṇabharakao lagi maatara
lyrics: jaeewana euṭaa phaulajasatao ho kaṣhaṇabharakao lagi maatara rahanae (2)
aaeelaeejaanae saukaeejaanae (2)
1. saachaera jaeewana raakhana sakainana kaunabaelaa raokachha saasa jaanana sakainana (2)
saochaera haera taimaee kahaan jaadaaichhaau
waichaara gara taimaee kahaan pauganae chhaau .
kao. jaeewana euṭaa baadala jasatao ho ahailae yahaan bhaolaee kahaan ho (2)
laukaee jaanae haraai jaanae (2)
2. palabharakao jaeewana sajhaaeedaeoo
mitho sauwaasamaa phaailaaee daeoo (2)
jaeewana saakaara banaaeedaeoo
Yeshulaaee haृdayamaa raakhaeedaeoo .

songs.title: jaeewana euṭaa phaulajasatao ho kaṣhaṇabharakao lagi maatara
lyrics: jaeewana euṭaa phaulajasatao ho kaṣhaṇabharakao lagi maatara rahanae (2)
aaeelaeejaanae saukaeejaanae (2)
1. saachaera jaeewana raakhana sakainana kaunabaelaa raokachha saasa jaanana sakainana (2)
saochaera haera taimaee kahaan jaadaaichhaau
waichaara gara taimaee kahaan pauganae chhaau .
kao. jaeewana euṭaa baadala jasatao ho ahailae yahaan bhaolaee kahaan ho (2)
laukaee jaanae haraai jaanae (2)
2. palabharakao jaeewana sajhaaeedaeoo
mitho sauwaasamaa phaailaaee daeoo (2)
jaeewana saakaara banaaeedaeoo
Yeshulaaee haृdayamaa raakhaeedaeoo .

songs.title: jaeewana kae udaasa panakao parabhaujaee daoora karao maerae
lyrics: kao. jaeewana kae udaasa panakao parabhaujaee daoora karao maerae
nairaasha panakao jaeewana sae parabhaujaee daoora karao maerae
hao... hao... .
1. anadhakaara sae jayaotai maem laanaewaalaa,
daukhaiyaom kao dauhkha sae chhauड़anae waalae
baujhataee daeepaka maem raoshanaee jalaadao
jaeewana kae udaasa panakao... .
2. jao na saomchao wao karakae daikhaadao
maerae jainadagaee maem nayaee aashaa jagaadao
daunaiyon kae ulajhana sae maujhakao chhauड़alao
Yeshu taoo aakara maujhaekao bachaalao
jaeewana kae udaasa panakao... .

songs.title: jaeewana chha jaiundao Yeshumaa ananata jaeewana uhaanmaa
lyrics: kao. jaeewana chha jaiundao Yeshumaa ananata jaeewana uhaanmaa
taimarao maerao naimatai aaja,
(yao jaeewana ananatakao lagi hao) (2)
1. haamaee baanchachhaaum aaphanaai sawaarathakao lagi
haamaee jaiunchhaaum kaewala aaphanaai naimatai
jaeewana abhaishaapa maatara haoina,
tara eeshawarakao saunadara waradaana ho .
2. aba bhaoolaaim samsaarakao saukha ra dau:kha Yeshukao jaeewana laiee aba
jaeewana wayarathaai naphaalaaum haamaee parabhaukao ichachhaamaa saumapaidaeoo .

songs.title: jaeewana chha haamarao thaoraai dainakao waaphajhaaim jaeewanalaaee
lyrics: kao. jaaga uṭha, naidaraabaaṭa jaagaृtakao baelaa aaekao chha,
raata dhaeraai naai waitaisakayao, aba daina aaunaai laagaekao chha .
1. janyonaee kaumaaraee jhaaim parakhanaeharaoo, daulahaakao gharamaa parawaesha garachhana‌ (2)
maoorakha kaumaaraee jhaaim jaiunaeharaoo, “khaola na khaola ḍhaokaa” bhanadaai raunachhana‌ (2)
2. jayaotaikaa hataiyoralaaee dhaaraṇa garaee, kharaeeṣhaṭakaa asala saewaka banaaum (2)
bishwaskao utatama laड़nata laड़ee, jaeewanakao maukauṭa paraapata garaaun (2)
3. haṭhaee ra baagaee maanaisa banaee, samsaara maai kaina pharakai jaanachhaau (2)
daui dainakao saukhalaaee raojaee taimaee, yaugaanauyaugasamama kaina raunachhaau ? (2)
4. parataipala aaphaailae aaphaailaaee jaanchaee, pashachaatataapaee haamaee banaindaai jaaaun (2)
najaeeka chha aba nayoyakao ghaड़ee, nairadaoṣha ra naiṣhakalamka banaindaai jaaaun (2)

songs.title: jaeewana dainae Yeshulaaee nabhaula samsaarakao ḍhaanchaamaa taimaee
lyrics: 1. jaeewana dainae Yeshulaaee nabhaula, samsaarakao ḍhaanchaamaa taimaee nachala (2)
kharaeeṣhaṭakao yaodadhaa taimaee naai haaum, kharaeeṣhaṭakaai naimatai aghai baḍha (2)
2. samsaaralaaee naiyolaee haera, aaphaai baujhanaechhaau yasakao gataee (2)
taimarao maerao naimatai kaohaee chhaaina, Yeshu baahaeka mana mailadao saathaee (2)
3. hae yauwaa samsaaralaaee naraoja, pachhautaaoondaai ekadaina raunauparalaa (2)
samsaarakao maayomaa nabhaula, kharaeeṣhaṭakao maayo gaumaaunau paralaa (2)

songs.title: jaeewana bharaee parabhaukao mahaimaa (2) garana paaun sadhaaim (2)
lyrics: jaeewana bharaee parabhaukao mahaimaa (2) garana paaun sadhaaim (2)
parabhaukao mahaimaa (garana paaun sadhaaim) (3)
1. kae daiun parabhau tapailai amaulaya thaoka chhaaina
kasaraee chaukaaun parabhaukao premalaaee
yao jaeewana chaḍhaaunchhau tapailai (2)
sarawadaa mahaimaa parashamsaa haosa‌ (2)
2. aau sabaai mailaera uhaankao mahaimaa garaaum
saaraa samsaaramaa gaera uhaankao naaunlaaee chainaaaum (2)
sarawadaa mahaimaa parashamsaa haosa‌ (2)

songs.title: jaeewana yahaan gaulaabakao phaoola jhaain jharaera jaanae ho
lyrics: kao. jaeewana yahaan gaulaabakao phaoola jhaain jharaera jaanae ho
daui dainae chaolaa paanaeekao waapha jhaain uड़era jaanae ho
wainataee yao taimaeelaaee chha haai, aaja naai yao bhaaukaa chha haai (2)
samaya chhandaai aaphaoolaaee ahailae nae jaanchaee daeoo
maukataidaataa Yeshusanga saainao gaansaee daeoo (2)
1. aaja bhanadaai bhaolai jaeewana asataaunchha (2)
kharaeeṣhaṭamaa sadhaain jaiunaeharaoo, maृtayau paaraee udaaunchha (2)
maanawakao jaeewana yasataai hao, paahaunaa maataraai daui dainakao (2)
2. saukha-dauhkha janama-maraṇa sadhaainbharai chaladachha (2)
jaeewanakao haraeka maoड़haraoomaa haansao-raodana haundachha (2)
wachanamaa jao haड़irahanachha, jaeewanakao maukauṭa paaunaechha (2)

songs.title: jaeewana sae bhaye utatama taeraee karaooṇaa (2)
lyrics: jaeewana sae bhaye utatama taeraee karaooṇaa (2)
haomṭhaom sae satautai karaoongaa sarawadaa
taerae naama sae maaim haatha uṭhaaungaa
taerae naama sae maaim haatha uṭhaaungaa – parabhau (2)
haoṭhaom sae satautai karaoongaa sarawadaa
taerae naama sae maaim haatha uṭhaaungaa ॥

songs.title: jaeewana haamarao baadala jasataai ekadaina naishachaya
lyrics: kao. jaeewana haamarao baadala jasataai ekadaina naishachaya uड़ee jaalaa
saukhamaa taimaee haansa-khaela garachhaaum maृtayau aae kae pao haolaa .
eka pala saomchaee daeoo (4)
1. samsaarakao maayo maoha sabalaaee atai aananada laagachha (2)
yasakao naimatai maanaisalae eeshawaralaaee panai tayogachha (2)
2. aaphaoosanga chhaaina waaibhawa chhaaina kaohaee yahaan maitara (2)
nairaashaa ra thaakaekaakao Yeshu kharaeeṣhaṭa chhaaina‌ maitara (2)

songs.title: jaeewana-yotaraamaa maerao jahailaesamama rahaunlaa gauṇa gaana garana
lyrics: kao. jaeewana-yotaraamaa maerao jahailaesamama rahaunlaa
gauṇa gaana garana taaraṇahaarakao shakatai daeoo malaaee parabhau (2)
shakatai daeoo malaaee parabhau... .
1. jaeewanakao maerao paratayaeka kadamamaa, parabhau malaaee ḍaorayoidaeoo (2)
kharaeeṣhaṭa taimarao haarakao sahaayataa daiee, yotaraa paooraṇa garaidaeoo (2)
2. jaeewana sawachachha baitaaunalaaee, parabhau nairanatara saatha daeoo (2)
nakakalaee saukha-chaainakao dhaokaadaekhai, parabhau malaaee bachaaidaeoo (2)
3. parataikaṣhaṇa maerao karaoosa uṭhaauna, dailamaa utasaaha bharaidaeoo (2)
karaoosakao dauragama pathamaa baḍhadaa, sadaa sadaa saatha-saatha rahaidaeoo (2)
4. premalae khainchaiee charaṇamaa rahanae, laalasaa paaidaa garaidaeoo (2)
saamsaaraika waibhawa dhaoolaomaa phayonkachhau, kharaeeṣhaṭa naai waibhawa banaidaeoo (2)

songs.title: jaeewanakao kae bharaosaa daui dainakao jaeewana khaelamaa
lyrics: kao. jaeewanakao kae bharaosaa daui dainakao jaeewana khaelamaa
parabhaukao satautai gaaaun (3)
1. aashaa garadachhaau wayarathamaa yao waidhayo, baudadhai dhanamaa (2)
laiera ghamaṇaḍa manamaa laabha haunana yao jaeewanamaa (2)
2. hae kharaeeṣhaṭaeeya laoga hao, jaaga paapamaya jaeewanalaaee tayoga (2)
sawaragaeeya aashaiṣha‌ maaga, parabhaukao naimatai jaaga (2)
3. karauṇaa-saagara Yeshu, unaee hauna‌ haamarao sahaaraa (2)
parabhaukahaan haamaee jaaaun, parabhaukao satautai gaaau (2)

songs.title: jaeewanakao kaehaee bhara chhaaina palabharamaa baitaijaanachha
lyrics: kao. jaeewanakao kaehaee bhara chhaaina palabharamaa baitaijaanachha
anaishachaita yotaraa kae haunae kasao haunae thaahaa chhaaina (2)
1. haraekakao bharaosaa kaehaee chhaaina bhaolaikao sapanaa daekhanau kae ? (2)
aajalaaee saatha paauna nasakae bhaolailaaee aashaa garanau kae ? (2)
maanaisakao kaehaee bhara chhaaina kaṣhaṇa bharamaa pagalaidainachha
bhaemaa aaphanao nabhae bairaanao maeeṭhao baoladaai dhaokaa dainachha .
2. daekhaaunchhana‌ aashaa maanachhae yahaan anai maoorataijhaain banaera baanchaidainachhana‌ (2)
saisaajhaain haृdayalaaee taoḍaidaiera jaiundao laasajhaain banaaidainachhana‌
khaolaajhaain jaeewana bagairahaechha mahaasaagaramaa pauganalaaee
dhaunwaajhaain jaeewana uड़irahaechha naeela gaganamaa haraaunalaaee .

songs.title: jaeewanakao gaoraeṭaomaa parabhau Yeshu ḍaorayounauhaosa‌
lyrics: kao. jaeewanakao gaoraeṭaomaa, parabhau Yeshu ḍaorayounauhaosa‌
pawaitara aatamaalae bharaera, parabhau malaaee chalaaunauhaosa‌ (2)
1. Yeshurahaita jaeewanamaa shaanatai kahaeen paainan (2)
Yeshu aae makahaan, paapa-kaṣhamaakao naishachayataa
(paaen maile bhaitara manamaa) (2)
2. maृtayaubaaṭa aatamaa maerao, parabhau kharaeeṣhaṭalae bachaaunaubhayao (2)
aankhaabaaṭa aansau maerao, parabhau kharaeeṣhaṭalae pauchhaidainaubhayao
(kamajaora paaulaaee balaiyao banaaunaubhayao) (2)

songs.title: jaeewanakao tyo raoṭaee bhaanchaera daeoo jasaraee bhaanchanaubhao’
lyrics: 1. jaeewanakao tyo raoṭaee bhaanchaera daeoo,
jasaraee bhaanchanaubhao’ samaudarachhaeu
pawaitara pausatakamaa khaoja garadachhau,
chhau khaojaee tapaaeemkaai, hae paraaṇa parabhau
2. jaeewanakao tyo raoṭaee malaaee jauraosa‌
tapaaeemkao tyo wachana manamaa basaosa‌
ra saudharaosa‌ maerao mana, haun parasawaarathaee,
saba maerao baehaoraa tapaaeemmaathai .
3. tyo bachana khaolaidaeoo, ma daekhana paaoon,
tyo wachana khaolaidaeoo, ma baujhana paaoon
tapaaeemkao sangagatamaa sangaai hainड़daai,
mamaa tapaaeemkao raoopa parakaasha haundaai .
4. parabhau sataya awataara, aashaeerawaada daeoo,
jasaraee jaoṭaeemaa gaalaeelakao chhaeu
taba banadhana chhauṭalaa saangalao bhaanchaee,
shaanatai taba paaoonla sataya shaanatai .

songs.title: jaeewanakao daeepa jaeewana parabhaa chairaananada parakaasha daeoo
lyrics: kao. jaeewanakao daeepa, jaeewana parabhaa chairaananada parakaasha daeoo
haृdaya maerao laiera nawaeena aatamaika banaaidaeoo (2)
1. anataraatamaalae maerao wainaya yahaee garadachha (2)
kalangaka saba dhaoera masaeehaee jaeewana banaaidaeoo .
2. jaeewana arauṇakao raoshanaee layoee yao maerao haृdayokaashamaa (2)
aatamaamaa nawa umangaga daeoo, hae parabhau, bainataee saunailaeoo .
3. aashaa, bishwas ra premamaa sathaira rahanae shakatai daeoo (2)
jaeewana-yotaraa shaeṣha bhae aatamaa yao garahaṇa garailaeoo .

songs.title: jaeewanakao nadaee bagaaunauhaosa‌ parabhau maerao jaeewanamaa
lyrics: jaeewanakao nadaee bagaaunauhaosa‌, parabhau maerao jaeewanamaa
malaaee jagaृta garaaunauhaosa‌, pawaitara aatamaamaa .
badalaina chaahanachhau, parabhau tapaaeemkao raoopamaa
paitaakao lagi phala phalaaunae, jaeewana jaiuna chaahanachhau
maerao yao jaeewanabaaṭa tapaaeemlaaee alagayouna chaahanachhau .

songs.title: jaeewanakao baaṭao kaanड़alae paooraṇa samgaraama chha bhaaraee mana haunachha
lyrics: 1. jaeewanakao baaṭao kaanड़alae paooraṇa,
samgaraama chha bhaaraee mana haunachha chaooraṇa
maraujhaain shauṣhaka haunachha kahailae,
rasailao anai bharailao pahailae
samaya tyo thaiyao chainana tapaaeemlaaee,
dhanyawad premaee paramaeshawara paitaa
daekhadachhau ma tyo baadalakao khaanbao
ujajawala chamakailao ḍaorayounae malaaee .
2. anadhakaara kasatao, ḍhaakadachha malaaee,
nairaashakao naitaya haundaaichha baढ़ai
kasaraee hainड़nau, paailaa kahaan haalanau,
chaahananan parabhau, jaeewana yao phaalanau
dhanayawaada, paitaa, kaalao baadalakao
paarai daekhadachhau jayaotai jaeewanakao
saodhana mana laagachha kaina, hae parabhau,
saikaaunauhaosa‌ malaaee, dhaairaya, hae Yeshu .
3. lachhaara ra pachhaara samsaarakao atai
ghainalaagadao paapamaya chha maerao gatai
laड़ain ra jhagaड़a chha daesha-waidaeshamaa,
ghamaṇaḍa chha tainakao waidhayo ra bhaeṣhamaa
dhanaya chha Yeshu maerao ho aashaa,
baadalamaa ujajawala daekhanaechhau raajaa
sabaaikaa maalaika, shaanataikaa daataa,
shakataikaa parabhau kharaeeṣhaṭa maukataidaataa .
aaunauhaunaechha (3), chaanड़ai naai
mahaimaita baadalamaa Yeshujaee aaunauhaunaechha .

songs.title: jaeewanakao baaṭao daekhaaunae baaṭao naai unaee hauna‌
lyrics: kao. jaeewanakao baaṭao daekhaaunae baaṭao naai unaee hauna‌
(taimarao ra maerao jaeewanakao baaṭao eka Yeshu hauna‌) (2)
(jaeewanakao sataya unaee, sataya naai Yeshu hauna‌) (2)
(taimarao ra maerao jaeewanakao, sataya naai Yeshu hauna‌) (2)
1. (janamanae ra maranae karama yao, kaehaee kaṣhaṇakao haansao ra aansau yao) (2)
(maatara haoina hae saathaee hao, kharaeeṣhaṭawainaa jaeewana adhaurao bhao’) (2)
2. (aaphanaai khaushaee, aaphanaai ichachhaaharaoo, palabharakaa aaphanaai jaeetaharaoo) (2)
(yatai haoina hae saathaee hao, kharaeeṣhaṭawainaa jaeewana apaoorao bhao’) (2)

songs.title: jaeewanakao yotaraamaa ḍaorayounauhaosa‌ malaaee
lyrics: kao. jaeewanakao yotaraamaa ḍaorayounauhaosa‌ malaaee
tapaaeemkao baaṭaomaa, tapaaeemkao baaṭaomaa
1. ma adharamaee paapaee charaṇamaa aaen, yao jaeewana lainauhaosa‌ (2)
tapaaeemkao naimatai jaiunaechhau parabhau (2), shakataidaana dainauhaosa‌ (2)
2. tapaaeemkao gahairao wachanakao aratha malaaee saikaaunauhaosa‌ (2)
janyona, baudadhai, waiwaeka pawaitara aatamaa (2), daana malaaee dainauhaosa‌ (2)

songs.title: jaeewanakao raoṭaee khaandaaichhau ra maoolakao paanaee paiundaaichhau
lyrics: jaeewanakao raoṭaee khaandaaichhau ra maoolakao paanaee paiundaaichhau
ra Yeshu bhanachhana‌ jasalae paiunchha usalaaee kahailayoi tairakhaa laagadaaina .
kayo rae tairakhaa laagadaaina ? kahailayoi tairakhaa laagadaaina (2)
ra Yeshu bhanachhana‌, jasalae paiunchha usalaaee kahailayoi tairakhaa laagadaaina .

songs.title: jaeewanakao raoṭaee hauna‌ kahailae na tairakhaaunae
lyrics: kao. jaeewanakao raoṭaee hauna‌ kahailae na tairakhaaunae
paanaeekao saraota hauna‌ jaeewanakao raoṭaee hauna‌ .
1. saadhanaalae upaasanaalae bhaeṭaṭaaunae chhaainaaum haai
saanchao manalae bishwas garae Yeshu aaunnaechhana‌ taimarao manamaa
asala gaoṭhaalao hauna‌ chhaḍadaainana‌ euṭaailaaee
jaeewanakao daataa hauna‌ jaeewanakao raoṭaee hauna‌ .
2. saadhanaalae upaasanaalae bhaeṭaṭaaunae chhaainaaum haai
saanchao manalae bishwas garae, Yeshu aaunaechhana‌ taimarao manamaa
asala gaoṭhaalao hauna‌ taimaeelaaee ḍaorayounchhana‌
jaeewanakao baaṭaomaa jaeewanakao raoṭaee hauna‌ .

songs.title: jaeewanakao sawaamaee parabhaulaaee mahaimaa haosa‌ sadhaain
lyrics: 1. jaeewanakao sawaamaee parabhaulaaee mahaimaa haosa‌ sadhaain
ma jaba bhaulachhau tapaaeemlaaee, kalawaraeemaa ḍaorayooo .
kao. bhaulachhau jaba galagathaakao kaṣhaṭakao paraarathanaa tapaaeemkao
bhaulachhau jaba prem tapaaeemkao kalawaraeemaa ḍaorayooo
2. daekhaaoo malaaee chaihaana unakao daootagaṇalae ghaeraekao
jahaan yasa kaṭhaora haृdaya laiee garachhau arapaṇa unalaaee .
3. maraiyamalae chaihaanamaa daanalaiee tapaaeemlaaee khaojaethaee
haृdayakao daana laiee ma panai khaojana sakaoon anai .
4. chhau parabhau baokanalaaee tayora aaphanao tyo karaoosakao bhaara
garanaechhau jaeewana dauhkha paara shakatai daeoo taaraṇahaara .

songs.title: jaeewanakao haraeka ghaḍaeemaa Yeshu taimarao maatara samajhanaa aaunchha
lyrics: jaeewanakao haraeka ghaḍaeemaa Yeshu taimarao maatara samajhanaa aaunchha
chhana‌ jaeewanaharau yahaan baanchaekaa taimaraai samajhanaamaa
1. kahailaekaahaeem baaṭaomaa yotaraamaa haunachhau
taee baelaa panai taimaraai samajhanaa aaunchha (2)
aankhaa bharai aanshaoo laiee yotaraa garachhau ma baaṭaoharaumaa (2)
2. ekaanatamaa basadaa panai taimaraai samajhanaa aaunchha
chhaaina samsaarakao ratataibhara samajhanaa (2)
maayo taimaraai laiee mauṭaumaa jaiirahaechhau samsaaraaimaa ma (2)

songs.title: jaeewanadaataa waidhaataa aaundachhau taimarao sharaṇamaa
lyrics: kao. jaeewanadaataa waidhaataa, aaundachhau taimarao sharaṇamaa
paradachhau Yeshu sharaṇa, jaeewanadaataa waidhaataa
1. kalaoshaita paapaee yao anadhakaara bhawamaa (2) (bhaṭakairahaechhau paapaee jaeewanamaa
daoora taimaeedaekhai bhaen, paapakao pathamaa kadama baढ़aen) (2)
paraiṇaama ṭhaokara khaaen, paitaa pachhataaundaai sharaṇamaa taimarao ma aaen .
2. taimaee karauṇaamaya paitaa ma adharama (2) (daeena, dauhaaee maerao parabhau saunailaeoo
rakaṣhaa jaeewanakao garaidaeoo dhaoee parabhau taimarao ragatalae) (2)
yaogaya paatara banaailaeoo, paitaa naiwaedana, haृdayakao maerao saunaidaeoo .

songs.title: jaeewanadaekhai bhaagaee hainḍanae ho
lyrics: kao. jaeewanadaekhai bhaagaee hainḍanae ho
maृtayaulaaee amgaalanae aatamaaharaoo
eeshawarakao ekalao pautara Yeshu mahaana‌
aaunau bhayao bachaaunalaaee samsaarakao taraaṇa
1. maृtayau banadhana (2) maa baandhaiekaa
saaraa paapaee jana chhaaina kaohaee dharamaee jana
phaukaaunalaaee haamarao paapa dainalaaee ananata jaeewana
janamaie imamaanauela... haa... haa...
2. Yeshu mahaana‌ (2) jao paramaeshawarakao
anamaola daana garaaun unakao jayajayakaara
unakao premakao saaṭaomaa daina kae chha taimarao saatha
aajakao shaoonaya raata... haa... haa...

songs.title: jaeewanabhara prem kharaeeṣhaṭalaaee ma garanaechhau saunaidaeoo
lyrics: 1. jaeewanabhara prem kharaeeṣhaṭalaaee ma garanaechhau,
saunaidaeoo paraarathanaalaaee sharaṇa parachhau
jaeewanabhara bhakataisaatha adhaika prem ma garachhau,
tyo adhaika prem kharaeeṣhaṭa ma garachhau .
2. saamsaaraika maohamaa khaojaen aaraama,
bainataee chha daeoo malaaee aatamaika waisharaama
sadhaain-sadhaain bhakataisaatha, adhaika prem ma garachhau,
tyo adhaika prem kharaeeṣhaṭa ma garachhau .
3. shaaitaanalae baaramabaara garayao laachaara,
taimaee chhaau taaraṇahaara laaunchhaau bhawa paara
jayajayagaanasaatha parabhau, adhaika prem ma garachhau,
tyo ashaika prema, kharaeeṣhaṭa ma garachhau .
4. samsaara jaba tayogadachhau, kharaeeṣhaṭa malaaee laeoo,
taraieka eeshawarakao ma bhakata bananaechhau
yao maerao daृढ़ paraṇa hao, adhaika prem
ma garachhau taraieka parabhaulaaee prem ma garachhau .

songs.title: jaeewanabhara Yeshumaa bishwas garanaechhaaun
lyrics: kao. jaeewanabhara Yeshumaa bishwas garanaechhaaun ,
kharaeeṣhaṭaeeya prem chharadaai haamaee jaiunaechhaau
1. (Yeshu karausamaa chaḍhaethae haamaeelaaee bachaauna ,
dauhkha kaṣhaṭa bhaulaethae haamaeelaaee nachaauna) (2)
tayasataai prem garanaechhaau haamaee baaḍaera ,
chaoṭamaa malama laaunaechhaau , aaphanaai ṭhaanaera
2. (sabaai saathalae chhaḍaenaee kharaeeṣhaṭalae chhaḍadaainana‌ ,
arau naataa maoḍaenai unalae taoḍadaainana‌) (2)
ho haamarao aashaa tayasaailae kahailayoi maradaaina ,
unakao bachana jaeewaita chha , kahailayoi ṭaladaaina

songs.title: jaeewanabhara Yeshumaa bishwas garanaechhaaun
lyrics: kao. jaeewanabhara Yeshumaa bishwas garanaechhaaun ,
kharaeeṣhaṭaeeya prem chharadaai haamaee jaiunaechhaau
1. (Yeshu karausamaa chaḍhaethae haamaeelaaee bachaauna ,
dauhkha kaṣhaṭa bhaulaethae haamaeelaaee nachaauna) (2)
tayasataai prem garanaechhaau haamaee baaḍaera ,
chaoṭamaa malama laaunaechhaau , aaphanaai ṭhaanaera
2. (sabaai saathalae chhaḍaenaee kharaeeṣhaṭalae chhaḍadaainana‌ ,
arau naataa maoḍaenai unalae taoḍadaainana‌) (2)
ho haamarao aashaa tayasaailae kahailayoi maradaaina ,
unakao bachana jaeewaita chha , kahailayoi ṭaladaaina

songs.title: jaeewanabharai naai gaaunae ho gaeetaharaoomaa bhananae ho Yeshu naai
lyrics: kao. jaeewanabharai naai gaaunae ho gaeetaharaoomaa bhananae ho Yeshu naai hauna‌ parabhau (2)
1. saasa haunae sabaai paraaṇaeelae gara paraashamsaa paramaeshawarakao
jhauṇaḍaaunae aaphaailaaee karaoosamaa ragata bahaaee, Yeshu naai hauna‌ parabhau (2)
2. bhana-bhana parabhau Yeshulaaee maerao haृdayakaa raajaa hauna‌
sawaragaa ra paृthawaeekaa sabaai ghaunड़a ṭaeka yasao bhanadaai, Yeshu naai hauna‌ parabhau (2)

songs.title: jaeewanabharaee parabhau taimaeelaaee aadara mahaimaa satautai bhakatai
lyrics: kao. jaeewanabharaee parabhau taimaeelaaee aadara, mahaimaa, satautai, bhakatai
dhanyawad daindaai jayajayakaara garadaai, parashamsaa gaaunaechhau taimarao sadhaaim (2)
jaeewanabharaee parabhau taimaeelaaee... .
1. maeraa udadhaarakarataa parabhau ! taimarao udadhaara mahaana‌, jaeewaita sataya paramaeshawara (2)
taimarao saamaratha ra taimarao mahaimaa (2) sadaaiwa rahanaechhana‌ . (2)
2. maeraa bishwasyaogaya parabhau ! taimarao bishwasyaogayataa, yauga-yaugasamama rahanaechha (2)
taimaraa dhaaramaikataa ra satayataa (2) pahaaḍajhaaim aṭala chhana‌ . (2)
3. maerao karauṇaamaya parabhau ! taimaraa karauṇaa, bhalaaee maeraa naimatai asala chhana‌ (2)
taimaraa saamarathaee pakhaeṭaa maunai (2) ma saurakaṣhaita haunachhau . (2)
4. maeraa parashamsaakaa parabhau ! taimarao satautai parashamsaa, ananatasamama rahanaechhana‌ (2)
taimarao jayaotaikao parakaashamaa (2) hallelujah gaaunaechhau . (2)

songs.title: jaeewaita saamarathaee mahaana‌ haamaraa parabhaulaaee haृdaya khaolaee
lyrics: kao. jaeewaita, saamarathaee, mahaana‌ haamaraa parabhaulaaee
haृdaya khaolaee chaḍhaaun aadara mahaimaa sadhaaim
pawaitarataamaa, satayataamaa bhakatai ra aaraadhanaa
naitaya naitaya chaḍhaaoon uhaankaai charaṇamaa (2‌)
1. adabhauta paraakaramaee sarawashakataimaana parabhaulaaee
naitaya, chaaubaisa paraachaeenalae panai jaya jayakaara garadachhana‌
uhaankaai paraakarama ra waaibhawa pawaitarataalaaee
haृdaya khaolaee, shaira naihauraaee daṇaḍawata‌ garaaum .
2. shadadha, waiwaeka bhakatai ra bhaawa anai premalae
tharatharaaee, ḍaraaee anai jhaukaaum sharadadhaa ra bhakatailae
uhaankaai dayo karaooṇaa bhalaaeelaaee naai samajhaee
pawaitara aatamaalae chaḍhaaoon aaraadhanaa uhaanlaaee .

songs.title: jauna saasalae ma jaiunchhau upasathaitai tapaaeemkao mabhaitara
lyrics: jauna saasalae ma jaiunchhau, upasathaitai tapaaeemkao mabhaitara chha
anai ma tapaaeem wainaa haraaunchhau, anai ma tapaaeem wainaa chhaṭapaṭainachhau
anai ma tapaaeem wainaa haraaunchhau,
jauna bhaojanalae ma jaiunchhau, upasathaitai tapaaeemkao mabhaitara chha
anai ma tapaaeem wainaa haraaunchhau,
anai ma tapaaeem wainaa chhaṭapaṭainachhau anai ma tapaaeem wainaa haraaunchhau .

songs.title: jae garanaubhao’ maerao jaeewanamaa parabhau jae garana chaahanauhaundaaichha
lyrics: jae garanaubhao’ maerao jaeewanamaa, parabhau, jae garana chaahanauhaundaaichha,
ma jae chhau tapaaeemkao kaृpaalae naai hao, tapaaeem naai maerao aadhaara, Yeshu dhanayawaada,
Yeshu, dhanayawaada, dhanyawad parabhau, harapala dhanayawaada, dhanyawad Yeshu .
malaaee prem garaee maukataidaana dainaubhayao, aaphanaai paraaṇa panai balai dainaubhayao,
parabhau, dhanayawaada, Yeshu, dhanayawaada, kaृtajanyataasaatha dhanayawaada, dhanyawad .

songs.title: jao kauchha taoo chaahae rababa maujhasae kara
lyrics: 1. jao kauchha taoo chaahae rababa maujhasae kara
maaim maiṭaṭaee haun aura taoo haai kaumahaara
haathaom maem laekara maujhae taoo gaoomdha, daekha taerae saamanae haajaira maaim haun (2)
2. jao kauchha taoo chaahae rababa maujhasae kara
jaancha maerae daila kao aaja saraasara
abhaye kara maujhae barapha sae saraphada, taujha sae haai maeraee yahaee umamaeeda (2)
3. jao kauchha taoo chaahae rababa, maujhasae kara
jakhamao laachaara para phajala aba kara,
kaudarata aura taakata taeraee haee haai, chhau aura shaiphaa dae Yeshu maujhae (2)

songs.title: jao bishwas garachha bapataisamaa lainachha tyo udadhaara paaunaechha
lyrics: 1. jao bishwas garachha, bapataisamaa lainachha tyo udadhaara paaunaechha
kharaeeṣhaṭakao maृtayaumaa laiee bapataisamaa nayon saृṣhaṭai haunachha
kharaeeṣhaṭa Yeshudawaaraa paaee chhauṭakaaraa pauganaechha sawaragamaa
jahaan naiṣhapaapaee maṇaḍalaee parataapaeesanga haunachha khaड़a .
2. eka manakaa bhaye bainataee chaढ़aee aayoun, hae paramaeshawara
dayokao saathamaa pawaitara aatamaa dainauhaosa‌ mahaana‌ wara
Yeshukao maraṇa sadagauṇa samajhaera paapa kaṣhamaadaana dainaosa‌
ananata jaeewana paaaun bhanaera unanatai daainaika haosa‌ .

songs.title: jao haunachha saahasaee oo yataa aaosa‌
lyrics: 1. jao haunachha saahasaee oo yataa aaosa‌
jae-saukaai hawasa‌, gata bishwasee hawasa‌, haundaaina nairaasha,
oo rahanachha sathaira sadaa, ra garanaechha ichachhaa sawaraga-yotaraa garanau .
2. jao-jao usalaaee saunaaunchhana‌ kathaa ḍaralaagadao
aaphaailaaee bhaulaaunchhana‌ bala baढ़chha usakao, na saimhadaekhai bhaya,
na shataraudaekhai ḍara, usakao chha adhaikaara sawaraga yotaraa garanau .
3. na bhaoota, na shaaitaanalae usalaaee tarasaaunchha,
oo jaeewana anatayamaa unanata paaunchha,
saba shamkaa maeṭaiyao, ḍara chhaaina maanachhaekao,
daina-raata bala garachha oo sawaraga yotaraa garanau .

songs.title: jaogaaee raakhaekao chhau taimarao yao jaeewana jalaaee yao daiyao
lyrics: jaogaaee raakhaekao chhau taimarao yao jaeewana
jalaaee yao daiyao saanjha waihaana
laina aaunchhaau bhanaera (2)
yahaan chhau ma yahaan Yeshu taimarao parakhaaimaa (2)
1. aatamaika daiyao baaladaai naisakanachhau khaojana aatamaa anadhakaaramaa (2)
chhapachhana‌ chaaraaitaira baairaeelae naibhaaunalaaee maerao daiyao (2)
chalaaunchhau ma tarawaara wachanakao anai bhaagachhana‌ baairaee ṭaaḍao (2)
2. aaunchhana katai bhaela baaḍhaeeharau bagaauna maerao jaeewanalaaee (2)
paauḍaeedaai naisakanachhau kainaaraa kaaiyoum chaoṭaharau sahaera (2)
samajhanachhau taimaeelaaee tayataikhaera bhaulaera saaraa daukha paeera (2)

songs.title: jaoḍaeeekao samabanadha yao pausataaun samamakaai naataa ho
lyrics: kao. jaoḍaeeekao samabanadha yao, pausataaun samamakaai naataa ho (2)
paramaeshawarakao hatakaelaamaa, samahaalaeeekao jaataee haamaee ho (2)
thaoraai chahaee, hazarau bhao, daurabala chahaee balayao haunaebhao
samahaalaeeekao jaataee haamaee ho
1. raoowaaee, chaitakaara ra bailaapakao saora uchaalayou (2)
mananaa haamaeelaaee jhaaranau bhao, haamarao bhaokalaaee maeṭanau bhao (2)
anadhaakaaramaa haraayou, raankaobhaai baaṭao daekhaayou (2)
chaṭaanalaaee phauṭaaera, haamarao payasalaaee maeṭaaee dainau bhao (2)
2. barasaau barasakao, yoऋa thayao haamarao (2)
samaunadaृlaaee chairanau bhao, banada ḍaokaa khaolanau bhao (2)
naapanaai nasakaeenae, taaulana panai namailanae (2)
maanyo yao jaatailaaee garanau bhao, khaḍaeraimaa baadala jhaaranau bhao (2)

songs.title: jhajhalakao chha aaja tyo karaoosakao parabhau
lyrics: kao. jhajhalakao chha aaja tyo karaoosakao parabhau Yeshulae dauhkha sahaekao
1. sharaeerabaaṭa ragata bagayao unaie bhaalaa kaokhaamaa
nairadaoṣha thaie maeraa parabhaujaee jhauṇaḍaae unalaaee tyo sharaapaita karunaimaa
2. nainadaa ra gailalaa sahandaai thaukaaee ra kauṭaaee khaandaai
karunaimaa bagayao ragatakao dhaaraa balaidaana bhae paapaeelaaee bachaaunalaaee

songs.title: jharaee paṭhaaoo (4)
lyrics: 1. (jharaee paṭhaaoo) (4)
(haृdaya bhaijaaunae aatamaalaaee dhaunae) (2)
(pawaitara aatamaakao jharaee paṭhaaoo) (2)
2. (aagao paṭhaaoo) (4)
(haृdaya jalaaunae aatamaalaaee khaaranae) (2)
(pawaitara aatamaakao aagao paṭhaaoo)

songs.title: jharaeekao parabhau tapaaeemlaaee paukaaradachhaaun jharaeekao parabhau haamaee
lyrics: (jharaeekao parabhau, tapaaeemlaaee paukaaradachhaaun, jharaeekao parabhau, haamaee payosaee chhaaun) (2)
jharaeekao parabhau, aaunaosa‌
jaagaृta garaaunauhaosa‌, (jharaeekao parabhau) (2)
jaagaृta garaaunauhaosa‌, (jharaeekao parabhau) (2) aaoo,
taajaa banaaunauhaosa‌, (jharaeekao parabhau) (2)
taajaa banaaunauhaosa‌, (jharaeekao parabhau) (2) aaoo,
nayon jaeewana layounauhaosa‌ (jharaeekao parabhau) (2) nayon daakhamadhaya paiunauhaosa‌
(jharaeekao parabhau) (2) aaun, jharaee aaun (6), aaun, aatamaa, aaun (6)
(jharaeekao parabhau tapaaeemlaaee paukaaradachhaaun jharaeekao parabhau, haamaee payosaee chhaaun) (2)
jharaeekao parabhau aaunaosa‌ .

songs.title: jhalala jhalala jhalala aakaashaaimaa sausanadaesha chha haai yao
lyrics: kao. jhalala (3) aakaashaaimaa, sausanadaesha chha haai yao chaisao raataaimaa
imamaanauela pasarainaubhao’ baethalaehaema gaaeekao gaoṭhaaimaa
1. ḍaunड़aikao kaokarao, paraalakao ochhayona, kaomala baalaka satakaara chha unalaaee
baaṭao, sataya jaeewana Yeshu aaunaubhao’ samsaaraaimaa,
baethalaehaema gaaeekao gaoṭhaaimaa .
2. chaढ़auna jaeewana bhaeṭaeesawaraupa, payorao Yeshukao charaṇamaa
saurangagasaathamaa wasanata bahaara aashaiṣhaita‌ jharaee banai barasairahanaechha .

songs.title: jhauṇaḍaekao kailalaakao sahaaraamaa kasalae... baujhanae... ho
lyrics: kao. jhauṇaḍaekao kailalaakao sahaaraamaa kasalae... baujhanae... ho
ghaina laagadaa amga sabaai taee kasalae baujhanae... ho
taimarao laagaee ḍaanड़amaathai sharamalaaee phaalaera
ragata bagaaera, maranae premaee Yeshu hauna‌ .
1. saathaee sabaai bhaagae baairaee aaee ghaerae
ekalao adabhaoota maanachhae chaupachaapa naai basae
parataishaodhamaa haoina baraoo kaṣhamaa dainae garae unalae tyo chaitakaara (2)
2. katai gaaharao baujhanalaaee kaṣhamaa dainae yaojanaa
saृṣhaṭaikarataa sawayama‌ balaikao baedaeemaa
gahairao payora saagara jhaaim agalao maayo aakaasha jhaaim
mailanae araoo kahaan hao... (2)

songs.title: jhauma, ghauma, uphara taalaee bajaaoo (2)
lyrics: jhauma, ghauma, uphara taalaee bajaaoo (2)
Yeshumaa taimaee chhaau bhanae jhauma
Yeshumaa taimaee chhaau bhanae ghauma
Yeshumaa taimaee chhaau bhanae uphara
Yeshumaa taimaee chhaau bhanae taalaee bajaaoo

songs.title: kaṭanaee maanaisalae tayahaee anausaara garanaechha jauna parakaaralae
lyrics: kao. kaṭanaee maanaisalae tayahaee anausaara garanaechha
jauna parakaaralae usalae raopadachha (2)
dhaokaamaa napara, paramaeshawarakao ṭhaṭaṭaa haundaaina (2)
1. parabhau chaanḍaai aairahaechhana‌, parabhau chaanḍaai aairahaechhana‌ .
haraeka maanaisalaaee parataiphala dainalaaee (2), aaphanaa aaphanaa kaama anausaara (2)
jaancha taimaraa kaama kasataa chhana‌, aagaolae tayasakao dainaechha paramaaṇa (2)
sauna chaandaeejhaaim kaama pakakaa bhae, taimaeelae paaunaechhaaum inaama (2)
2. amaulaya wachanakaa baeeulaaee laiee, amaoolaya wachanakaa baeeulaaee laiee .
dauhkha paraisharamasaatha aansaukaa taraaeemaa (2), raundaai chharanaeharaoolae (2)
aananadakaa saathamaa baeeṭaa baokaera, haraṣha ulalaasakaa saatha pharakanaechhana‌ (2)
aatamaakaa phalaharaoo jaeewanamaa phakaaundaai, kharaeeṣhaṭakao saewaa garanaechhana‌ (2)
3. taoḍaa taimaeelae paaekaa chhaau, taoḍaa taimaeelae paaekaa chhaau .
eka taoḍaa paaunaejhaaim laukaaera taoḍaalaaee, sharaapaita taimaee bananaechhaau (2)
daobara kamaaee haisaaba chaukataa garae, mahaimaita raajayamaa aadara paaunaechhaaum (2)
aatamaamaa raopanaelae jaeewanakao kaṭanaee, sharaeeramaa wainaasha kamaaunchhana‌
4. haraesa nakhaaee asala kaama garae, haraesa nakhaaee asala kaama garae .
ṭhaeeka samayamaa haamaee kaṭanaee garanaechhaau (2), saewaakao phala haamaee paaunaechhaaum (2)
aaaum jaeewana parabhaumaa arapaṇa garaee, unakao kaarayamaa jaeewana baitaaaum (2)
parabhaumaa hat balaiyao banaaee, kharaeeṣhaṭakao awaaeelaaee parakhaihaau (2)

songs.title: katai achamamakao payora eeshawara saृjanaahaara
lyrics: kao. katai achamamakao payora, eeshawara saृjanaahaara
sawaragakao saukhalaaee tayogaera aae paapaee bachaauna tayora (2)
1. nara raoopa dhaaraṇa garaera unalae parachaarae sausamaachaara (2)
paapaeekao paapakao, dauhkhaeekao dauhkhakao uṭhaae unalae bhaara (2)
aashacharayakarama garaera unalae daekhaae mahaimaa apaara (2)
yaee sabakao badalaee paae unalae karunaikao gaharaaun bhaara (2)
2. anataima ghaड़eemaa gaetasamanaeemaa chaelaagaṇasanga gae (2)
nairanatara paraarathanaa garaera unalae pasainaa bagaae (2)
hauna sakae yao kachaauraa madaekhai haṭaai daeoo bhanaee (2)
taraai panai tapaaeemkao ichachhaa paooraṇa hawasa‌ bhanae (2)
3. Yeshu pakaड़aee barababaa chhauड़aiyao, kahaan thaiyao yao nayoya (2)
waaijanaee wasatara lagaae unalaaee karaoosamaa chaढ़aunalaaee
laड़daai galagathaa paugae raomaeekao maara khaaee (2)
kaṣhaṭaita paeeड़ita parabhaulae aaphanao paraaṇa daiihaalae, haaee (2)

songs.title: katai aananada chha jaiwana samgharaṣha ra dauhkha pachhai
lyrics: kao. katai aananada chha jaeewana samgharaṣha ra dauhkha pachhai
katai maeeṭhaa chhana‌ taee phala raopaai ra kaṭanaee pachhai
1. haamarao jaeewana yotaraa naai ho aaunchhana‌ anaeka dauhkha baadhaa (2)
jaeewana haamarao paanaee jasataai haunachha anaeka ṭhakakara yahaan (2)
samgharaṣhakao jaeewana jaiunau naai kharaeeṣhaṭaeeya jaeewana ho (2)
2. dauhkha paeeड़a sabalaaee bhaulao kharaeeṣhaṭakao wachana yoda garaee (2)
baढ़daai jaaaun aau Yeshumaa karaoosa baokaee saiyaonasamama (2)
anai taimaeelae waijaya paaunaechhaau kharaeeṣhaṭa Yeshumaa (2)

songs.title: katai gaaḍaa taee naataaharaoo Yeshulaaee bhaeṭanaeharaoo
lyrics: kao. katai gaaḍaa taee naataaharaoo Yeshulaaee bhaeṭanaeharaoo
hatai dhanaya tai bayakataiharaoo Yeshulaaee chainanaeharaoo
1. aṭauṭa banadhana maatara Yeshumaa aaja yahaan bhaolai kahaan (2)
katai aananadaita taee bayakataiharaoo Yeshulaaee chainanaeharaoo
katai dhanaya tai yakataiharaoo Yeshulaaee raojanaeharaoo
2. ṭauṭaekao haृdaya jaoḍaidainae daukhaekao ghaaulaaee malama garanae (2)
katai haraṣhaita taee nayanaharaoo Yeshulaaee haeranaeharaoo
katai khaushaee taee oṭhaharaoo Yeshulaaee bhajanaeharaoo

songs.title: katai maayo garachhana‌ malaaee maerao payoraa parabhaulae
lyrics: kao. katai maayo garachhana‌ malaaee maerao payoraa parabhaulae
maeraai maayokao taृṣhaṇaamaa sadhaain naai taड़paidainachhana‌
1. malaaee ananata jaeewana daina aaphanao paraaṇasamama daie
maile bhaoganauparanae dauhkha unalae naai laiidaie .
2. maerao jaeewana sahaaraa banaee ḍaorayounauhaosa‌ gaoraeṭaomaa
ma ta anadhao chhau, yahaan tapaaeem naai jayaotai maerao .
3. samsaara ṭalaigae panai, maृtayau naai aae panai
yao mailana ananatasamama yao paraeeta amara naai chha .

songs.title: katai ramaaeelao katai ghamaailao parabhaookao mahaimaa
lyrics: katai ramaaeelao katai ghamaailao
parabhaookao mahaimaa garana bhaelaa bhaekao
haradaya khaolaee parabhaoolaaee dhanyawad dainachhaaum
yohaanharaoolaaee panai sawaagata gadachhaaum
ṭaaḍaa najaikawaaṭa kaahaan kaahaan waaṭa
parabhaookao yaojanaalae bhaelaa bhaekaa chhaaum
ekaai mana ekaai tana bhaera haamaee gaaoo unakao bhajana
haamarao yao jaeewanalae nalagaesamama maृtayaoolae
parabhaookao charaṇamaa jhaukaee rahanae chhaaum
hat uchaaladaai taalai wajaaundaai
garaaum mahaimaa aananada manaaundaai

songs.title: katai ramaahaṭakao daina aayao yao jagatamaa
lyrics: kao. katai ramaahaṭakao daina aayao yao jagatamaa
haansadaai-khaeladaai gaanaa gaaundaai parabhau Yeshumaa
1. aaoo waृdadha jana, aaoo saba jawaana
sawaramaa sawara mailaaee gaaoo parabhaukao jaya gaana (2)
2. haamaee saba thaiyoun ghaora anadhakaaramaa
aae parabhau awataara laiee uhaee baethalaehaemamaa (2)
3. chhaड़ aba bhaai dauṣhaṭa shaaitaanalaaee
uṭha, jaaga, sawaagata gara nawajaata parabhaulaaee (2)

songs.title: katai shaitala laagayao Yeshu tapaaeemkao chhahaaraee (2)
lyrics: kao. katai shaitala laagayao Yeshu
tapaaeemkao chhahaaraee (2)
tayahai shaitalataamaa basana paaen
paugachha malaaee jaiwana bharaee (2) katai...
1. dauhkhalae chhapadaa jaeewana
aansaulae bharainadaa nayana (2)
katai madhaura laagayao Yeshu
tapaaeemkao aawaaja (2)
tayahai aawaaja sadhaaim, saunana paaen
banachha maerao jaeewana saakaara katai...
2. palabharakao khaushaee khaosaidaa
aaphanao panai paraaee bhaaidaimdaa (2)
katai nyano laagayao Yeshu
tapaaeemkao angalo (2)
tayahaee angalo baanchana paaen
saumapai dainachhau sadhaailaaee (2) katai...

songs.title: katai haolaa maoolaya ragata Yeshukao ? katai haolaa maoolaya
lyrics: katai haolaa maoolaya ragata Yeshukao ? katai haolaa maoolaya Yeshukao premakao ?
kae chaukaauna sakachhaaun yao maoolaya taimarao sauna ra chaandaeelae
taimarao waidhayo ra janyonalae ?
karaoosalaaee haera mauṭaumaa hat raakhaee samajhana Yeshukao premalaaee,
samajhana Yeshukao kaṣhaṭalaaee
aaoo, sabaai jaataikahaan aaoon, Yeshukao naaunlaaee uchaalaaun,
Yeshukao prem parachaaraaun .

songs.title: kalawaraee karaoosalaaee haeraidaeoo aaja
lyrics: kao. kalawaraee karaoosalaaee haeraeedaeoo aaja
jaeewana dainae Yeshulaaee haeraeedaeoo aaja
aananadakao sawaraga chhaड़ee aae Yeshu jagatamaa
bachaaunalaaee taimaee ra malaaee . (2)
1. paapakao banadhana taoड़na aae kharaeeṣhaṭa Yeshu
daina aananada shaanatai jaeewana chhaड़ee Yeshu sawaragalaaee
taimarao paapalaaee maeṭaaunalaaee jhauṇaḍaie Yeshu karunaimaa
2. paapakao baojha baokaee raakhachhaaum kahaan taimaee
manamaa sau:kha chhaaina baisaaunae ṭhaaun chhaaina aaja yao samsaaramaa
bhanachhana‌ Yeshu makahaan aaoo dainaechhau waisharaama taimaeelaaee

songs.title: kalawaraee ḍaanड़akao karunaimaa Yeshulae aaphanao paraaṇa daie
lyrics: kao. kalawaraee ḍaanड़akao karunaimaa Yeshulae aaphanao paraaṇa daie
taimarao ra maerao paapa dhauna, chaoṭa sahaee ragata bagaae (2)
1. naṭhaana unaee kaewala marae, baauraera phaerai panai uṭhae
raokana sakaena chaihaanalae, jaitana sakaena maृtayaulae (2)
2. maृtayau ra paapakao ḍara chhaaina, bishwas gara Yeshumaa
sawaragakao baaṭao Yeshu naai hao, saumapaidaeoo jaeewana unaaimaa (2)

songs.title: kalawaraee ḍaanड़akao tyo aḍabhauta daृṣhaya thaiyao bhaulaera bhaulana
lyrics: kao. kalawaraee ḍaanड़akao tyo aḍabhauta daृṣhaya thaiyao bhaulaera bhaulana sakainana
sawaragaeeya pautaralae daiekao balaidaana maanawalae baujha‌na sakaena
tyo prem tyo prem
1. kaoraakao chaoṭa khaae apamaana sahaidaie
kaanḍaakao maukauṭalaaee kaṣhamaadaana daina sakanae .
2. kailalaalae ṭhaokaethae bhaalaalae ghaochaechae
ragata bagaaethae (2) tyo prem .

songs.title: kalawaraee ḍaanड़akao tyo karaoosamaa jahaan kharaeeṣhaṭa ṭaangaie
lyrics: 1. kalawaraee ḍaanड़akao tyo karaoosamaa jahaan kharaeeṣhaṭa ṭaangaie
katarao udaekakao tyo prem unakao mamaa parakaṭa garaae,
unakao haृdaya chhaeड़iyao, haatamaa kaeelaakao daaga
paau kaanṭaeelae jao ghaochaiyao, maerao taimarao yao bhaaga .
kao. dhanaya ho paaṭhao eeshawarakao satautai parabhaukao
Yeshukao gaaundaai rahanaechhau yasha sadaa, unakao jaya haosa‌
2. baanchanae upaaya araoo nadaekhanae ma karaoosamaa gaen
kharaeeṣhaṭalae aaphanao dayokao haatalae changagaa garaae,
udaekakao badalaawa mamaa layoe kharaeeṣhaṭalae
haृdayakao dauhkha naikaalaera aaphanao shaanatai daie .
3. aaoo hae maitara kharaeeṣhaṭa parabhaumaa unalae baolaaunchhana‌
haृdaya ashaanatailae bharaekao paapalae dabaekao jaeewana,
paapa kaṣhamaa ra shaanatai kharaeeṣhaṭa dainaechhana‌ usalaaee
araoo kaohaee daataa chhaaina parabhau masaeeha saiwaaya .

songs.title: kalawaraee ḍaanḍaakao pauraanao pausataakao jhalajhalaee haeradaai ma yoda
lyrics: 1. kalawaraee ḍaanḍaakao pauraanao pausataakao jhalajhalaee haeradaai ma yoda garachhau
samsaarakao lagi naai thaumaa bhaye eeshawarakao naiṣhapaapaee Yeshu balai bhaakao
kao. chhaḍanaechhaaina ma payorao karaoosalaaee chhaḍanau parae panai araoolaaee
samsaara yao jaba chhaḍaee jaanachhau maukauṭa mahaimaakao ma laaunchhau .
2. samsaaralae tayogaekao ra ghaृṇaa garaekao katai payorao chha malaaee tyo karaoosa
kaaraṇa maukatai daina ma paapaeelaaee jasatao parabhau Yeshu kharaeeṣhaṭa balai bhaakao
3. kalawaraee ḍaanḍaakao katai saunadara tyo karaoosa
pawaitara ragatakao daagasaraee yoda garaaum uccha dauhkha
parabhaulae sahaekao garana udadhaara sabaai paapaeekao
4. jaeewanabharaee maerao bishwasee rahanachhau, karaoosakao samkaṣhaṭa ma sahanachhau
shaeṣhamaa sawaragaeeya maerao gharamaa jaba jaanachhau, kharaeeṣhaṭa parabhausanga sadhaaim basachhau

songs.title: kalawaraee ḍaanड़akao mahaa dauhkha sahanauparayao parabhaulae
lyrics: kao. kalawaraee ḍaanड़akao mahaa dauhkha sahanauparayao parabhaulae
majasatao paapaeelaaee bachaauna karausaaimaa paraaṇa daie
1. kataikao nainadaa, kataikao thauka, kataikao bhanaai sahaera (2)
tyo gaharaaun karaoosa baokaera galagathaa paurayoe .
2. saipaahaeeharaoo mailaera Yeshulaaee karaoosamaa chaढ़ae (2)
unaaikaa wasatara phaukaaee chaiṭhaṭhaa lagaae .
3. haataaimaa kaanṭaee, paawaaimaa kaanṭaee ṭhaokae daushamanaharaoolae (2)
kaokhaamaa bhaalaa haanaekao sahae parabhau Yeshulae .
4. jaba karaoosamaa chaढ़ae, Yeshukaee maataa maraiyama (2)
raundaai-raundaai aaipaugaina‌ Yeshukao chhaewaaimaa .
5. hae daajayaoo-bhaai, hae daidaee-bahainaee, pashachaatataapa garaaun haamaeelae (2)
dainaechhana‌ haamaeelaaee maukatai parabhau Yeshulae .

songs.title: kalawaraee para Yeshu mauaa (2) wahaan jaeewana kaa saotaa
lyrics: kao. kalawaraee para Yeshu mauaa (2) wahaan jaeewana kaa saotaa naikaalaa
paapaee payosa taoo apanaee baujhaa – (2)
1. usakae pamjara maem bhaalaa chhaidaa usakae haathaom maem kaeelae ṭhaukhae
usanae kayo kayo dauhkha na sahaa . (2) kalawaraee... .
2. usakae lahaoo sae lae taoo nahaa saapha haomgae taerae gaunaaha
waha saba kae laie haai mauaa . (2) kalawaraee... .
3. hae paapaeeyaom tauma bhaye paeeo, hae dharamaiyaom tauma bhaye paeeo
waha saba ka laie haai mauaa . (2) kalawaraee... ॥

songs.title: kalawaraee pahaaḍalae aaja ḍaakadachha Yeshukao ragatalae shaudadha
lyrics: kalabaraee pahaaḍalae aaja ḍaakadachha Yeshukao ragatalae shaudadha paaradachha (2)
1. paapakao baojha laiera ta maृtayau angagaalanau chha
kharaeeṣhaṭakao chaokhao prem baokaera jaeewana paaunau chha (2)
jaeewanakao paraibhaaṣhaa aaja samajhana
baanchanakao aratha dhaeraai rahaechha bhanaera (2)
2. paeerakao aanshau paiera ta daukha angagaalanau chha
kharaeeṣhaṭakao radada wayathaa marainaai maukataikao sanadaesha chha (2)
jaeewanakao paraibhaaṣhaa aaja samajhana
baanchanakao aratha dhaeraai rahaechha bhanaera (2)

songs.title: kalawaraeekao ḍaanḍaamaa sharaapaita karaoosalaaee rangagaayou
lyrics: kao. kalawaraeekao ḍaanḍaamaa sharaapaita karaoosalaaee sangagaayou
aadama daekhaikao paapalaaee taimaeelae karaoosamaa ṭangagaayou . (2)
1. anamaola ragata ra maृtayaudawaaraa, wayawasathaa taimaeelae paooraa garayou,
haamaee paapaeelaaee aaja taimaeelae, parashasata anaugarahamaa bharayou (2)
2. aashaai thaiena anayaolamaa thaiyoum, thauparaai dainaharaoo wayarathamaa jaiyoum,
bagaayou taimaeelae ragatakao dhaaraa, haamaee paapaeelaaee daina chhauṭakaaraa (2)

songs.title: kalawaraeekao pahaaड़lae aaja ḍaakadachha (2)
lyrics: kao. kalawaraeekao pahaaड़lae aaja ḍaakadachha (2)
Yeshukao ragatalae shaudadha paaradachha (2)
1. paapakao baojha laiera ta maृtayau angaalanau chha
kharaeeṣhaṭakao chaokhao prem baokaera jaeewana paaunau chha
jaeewanakao paraibhaaṣhaa aaja samajhana baanchanakao aratha dhaeraai rahaechha bhanaera .
2. pairakao aanshau paiera ta dau:kha angaalanau chha
kharaeeṣhaṭakao darada wayothaa bharainaai maukataikao sanadaesha chha
jaeewanakao paraibhaaṣhaa aaja samajhana baanchanakao aratha dhaeraai rahaechha bhanaera .

songs.title: kalawaraeekao sharaapaita karaoosamaa kharaeeṣhaṭalae jaeewana arapaidaie
lyrics: kao. (kalawaraeekao sharaapaita karaoosamaa kharaeeṣhaṭalae jaeewana arapaidaie) (2)
sabaai paapabaaṭa bachaauna (ragatakao maoolaya chaukaae) (2)
1. (haata, paau ra sharaira kharaeeṣhaṭakao chaoṭaai chaoṭa thaiyao
kaanḍae maukauṭa shairamaa laaundaa mahaimaita ragata wagayao) (2)
(karaoosamaa kharaeeṣhaṭalaaee ṭaanganaeharaoo aananadalae ramaae) (2)
(kharaeeṣhaṭalaaee maayo garanaeharaoo chhaatao paiṭaee raoe) (2)
2. (bhaoka tairakhaa anaidao sahaera raatabharaeekao
thaukaai paiṭaai kaoraraaharaoo paae dauṣhaṭaharaookao) (2)
(kaḍaa ghaama payosa laagadaa taitao paitata pailaae) (2)
(paitaasanga kaṣhamaa maagai haamarao paapa sawaai maeṭaae) (2)

songs.title: kasakaa saamaoo gaoṭhamaa ghaunड़a ṭaekachhana‌ gaoṭhaalaa ?
lyrics: 1. kasakaa saamaoo gaoṭhamaa ghaunड़a ṭaekachhana‌ gaoṭhaalaa ?
kao. parabhau ho udaekakao kauraa, parabhau ho waaibhawakaa raajaa
ghaunड़a ṭaekadaai haamaee aaaun, parabhau kharaeeṣhaṭamaa maukauṭa laaaun
2. khaushaee bhaye gharaaimaa aaphanao haatalae kaama garadaa .
3. saarao bhaokao jamgalamaa shaaitaanasanga yaudadha garadaa .
4. aaphanao maeetakao chaihaanamaa ubhaye dauhkhalae raundaa .
5. samkaṭa bhaye baaraeemaa aadhaa raata paraarathanaa garadaa .
6. paapakao karaoosamaa ṭaangaidaa, shataraulaaee aashaiṣha‌ daindaa .
7. aaphanao naija chaihaana chhaड़daa, yasa samsaarakao taraaṇa garadaa .
8. sawaragakao saimhaasanamaa basaeekana raajaya garadaa .

songs.title: kasakao khabaramaa bishwas garanae bishwas garanae parabhaukao
lyrics: kasakao khabaramaa bishwas garanae bishwas garanae parabhaukao khabaramaa
uhaankao khabaramaa changagaaee chha uhaankao khabaramaa bharaipauraṇa chha
uhaankao khabaramaa sawatanatara chha uhaankao khabaramaa waijaya chha

songs.title: kasaraee chaढ़yao, kasaraee marayao kalawaraee karunaimaa (2)
lyrics: kao. kasaraee chaढ़yao, kasaraee marayao kalawaraee karunaimaa (2)
1. paitaakao premalaaee paramaaṇa garana sawaragalaoka chhaड़naubhao’
haamaee paapaeelaaee bachaauna bhanaee jaeewana dainaubhao’ .
2. karaoosamaa chaढ़ee ragata bahaaee paapa naṣhaṭa garanaubhao’
paapa ra sharaapa naṣhaṭa garaera maukatailaaee layounaubhao’ .
3. dhanaya haosa‌ taimarao, hae maukataidaataa ra gauṇaanauwaada haosa‌
jayajayakaara taimarao, parashamsaa taimarao, ananata haoirahaosa‌ .

songs.title: kasaraee chaukaaoon yao ऋṇa tapaaeemlaaee
lyrics: kasaraee chaukaaoon yao ऋṇa tapaaeemlaaee
kasaraee bhaulaoon yao prem tapaaeemkao haृdaya phauṭaera aaunchha...
jaba samajhanachhau galagathaalaaee, yao jaeewana daiera panai haunana
aba kae garaoon ma ?, yao jaeewanamaa marachhau parataidaina
mahaimaa haosa‌, sadaa-sadaalaaee .

songs.title: kasalae banaae phaulaharaoolaaee phaulaharaoolaaee phaulaharaoolaaee ?
lyrics: 1. kasalae banaae phaulaharaoolaaee, phaulaharaoolaaee, phaulaharaoolaaee ?
kasalae banaae phaulaharaoolaaee ? eeshawara jao sawaragamaa chhana‌ .
2. kasalae banaae maachhaaharaoolaaee, maachhaaharaoolaaee, maachhaaharaoolaaee ?
kasalae banaae maachhaaharaoolaaee ? eeshawara jao sawaragamaa chhana‌ .
3. kasalae banaae charaaharaoolaaee, charaaharaoolaaee, charaaharaoolaaee ?
kasalae banaae charaaharaoolaaee ? eeshawara jao sawaragamaa chhana‌ .
4. kasalae banaae taaraaharaoolaaee, taaraaharaoolaaee, taaraaharaoolaaee ?
kasalae banaae taaraaharaoolaaee ? eeshawara jao sawaragamaa chhana‌ .
5. kasalae banaae taimaeelaaee-malaaee, taimaeelaaee-malaaee ?
kasalae banaae taimaeelaaee-malaaee ? eeshawara jao sawaragamaa chhana‌ .

songs.title: kasaai kasaaikao raeetai bhae bhaaim eka ṭhaaunmaa bhaelaa hauna
lyrics: kao. kasaai kasaaikao raeetai bhae bhaaim eka ṭhaaunmaa bhaelaa hauna haamaee nachhaaḍaau
eka-arakaalaaee utasaaha daindaai rahaaum jatai tyo daina najaika aaekao daekhachhaaum (2)
1. bishwas garaekao daina daekhai paraiya paooraa udadhaara haamarao atai najaika chha
paapakao raata dhaeraai na baitai sakaekao chha, aba daina naisakana laagaekao chha .
2. paapakao madhaya raata aaja samsaaramaa chhaaekao daekhainachha jaagaृta aatamaamaa haera
daulahaalaaee bhaeṭana haamaee tayora haooon aa-aaphanao daiyaolaaee aaphaai chhaanṭaaum .

songs.title: kasaailae chhayao malaaee (2)
lyrics: kasaailae chhayao malaaee (2)
jaba raoirahaekao thaie , Yeshulae chhayao malaaee (2)
kasaailae chhayao malaaee (2)
1. ma ta anadhakaarama ma ta dau:khaharaoomaa (2)
jaba raoirahaekao thaie , Yeshulae chhayao malaaee (2)
kasaailae baolaayao malaaee (2)
2. maerao chaoṭaai chaoṭamaa, maerao ekalao panamaa (2)
jaba paraarathanaa garairahaethae Yeshulae baolaayao malaaee (2)
kasaailae chhatao malaaee (2)

songs.title: kasaailae chhayao malaaee (4) jaba ma paraarathanaa garaeerahaethae
lyrics: kasaailae chhayao malaaee (4) jaba ma paraarathanaa garaeerahaethae kasaailae chhayao malaaee
Yeshulae chhayao malaaee (4) jaba ma paraatharanaa garaiharaethae Yeshulae chhayao malaaee
kasaailae daerawayao malaaee (4) jaba ma paraarathanaa garaeerahaethae kasaailae daerawayao malaaee
Yeshulae daerawayao malaaee (4) jaba ma paraatharanaa garaiharaethae Yeshulae daerawayao malaaee

songs.title: kasakao khabaramaa bishwas garanae ? bishwas garanae parabhaukao
lyrics: kasakao khabaramaa bishwas garanae ? bishwas garanae parabhaukao khabaramaa (3)
uhaankao khabaramaa chamgaai chhau
uhaankao khabaramaa bharaiekao chhau
uhaankao khabaramaa sawatanatara chhau
uhaankao khabaramaa waijaya chhau

songs.title: kasatao anamaola balaidaana daiyou maanawa jaatailaaee
lyrics: kao. kasatao anamaola balaidaana daiyou maanawa jaatailaaee (2)
(chaahanachhau ma parabhau taimaeelaaee naai) (2‌)
1. nayon aashaa nayon umamga nayon kairaṇa, paaen maile (2)
Yeshu taimarao hat samaaee, nayon jaeewana paae maile
(aba chhaaड़naechhaaina taimarao hat aba tayoganaechhaaina taimaraosaatha) (2)
2. maerao dauhkhamaa dauhkhaee banaee dauhkha sabaai uṭhaaunaubhao’ (2)
maerao naimatai baoṣhaee banaee daoṣhabaaṭa chhauṭaaunaubhao’
(aba chhaaड़naechhaaina taimarao hat aba tayoganaechhaaina taimaraosaatha) (2)

songs.title: kasatao anaauṭhao rahaechha parabhau taimarao tyo prem
lyrics: kasatao anaauṭhao rahaechha parabhau taimarao tyo prem
paapakao tyo dahadaekhaee naikaalanaubhao malaaee
yasaailae dhanyawad parabhau taimaeelaaee maerao yao haृdayadaekhaee (2)
1. maeraai laagaee parabhau karausamaa balai haunaubhao
maeraai laagaee chaoṭaharau sahai kauraupa bananaubhao (2)
kasatao sahanashaeelataa parabhau taimaeemaa
sahaidaiyou tai sabaai wayathaa maerao naimatai (2)
2. aau maukatai paauna karausakao chhahaaraeemaa
saitataaikao yao waradaana ho taimaee ra malaaee (2)
saaṭaee haalaaum haamarao paraita parabhausanga
jao sadaa amara haunachha taimarao maerao lagi (2)

songs.title: kasatao prem garayou parabhau ma jasatao paapaeelaaee (2)
lyrics: kasatao prem garayou parabhau ma jasatao paapaeelaaee (2)
waraṇana kasaraee garaaum kalawaraeekao tyo anamaola premakao (2)
1. shaeeramaa maukauṭa kaanḍhaakao pahairaee hatakaelaamaa kaanṭaee ṭhaokaee
shaeeramaa maukauṭa hae... kaanḍhaakao pahairaee
shaeeramaa maukauṭa kaanḍhaakao pahairaee hatakaelaamaa kaanṭaee ṭhaokaee
maranaubhao parabhau aaja kaewala taimarao ra maerao laagaee (2)
kasatao prem garayou...
2. kaokhaamaa bhaalaa sharaeeramaa chaoṭa kharausabharaee ragata bagaae
kaokhaamaa bhaalaa hae... sharaeeramaa chaoṭa
kaokhaamaa bhaalaa sharaeeramaa chaoṭa
kaokhaamaa bhaalaa sharaeeramaa chaoṭa karausabharaee ragata bagaae
kasaraee rabaisaun ma maerao parabhaukao tyo balaidaana
kasatao prem garayou...

songs.title: kasatao badalaau mamaa (3) jaba Yeshukahaan gaen
lyrics: kao. kasatao badalaau mamaa (3) jaba Yeshukahaan gaen
1. sadhaain khaanae thaoka, maile khaana chhaड़en (3), jaba Yeshukahaan gaen .
2. sadhaain paiunae thaoka, maile paiuna chhaड़en (3), jaba Yeshukahaan gaen .
3. sadhaain jaanae ṭhaaun, ma jaana chhaड़en (3), jaba Yeshukahaan gaen .

songs.title: kasatao balaiyao jaga haera pawaitara jana taimarao bishwaskao
lyrics: 1. kasatao balaiyao jaga, haera pawaitara jana taimarao bishwaskao jaga, kharaeeṣhaṭakao sharaeṣhaṭha wachana
parayopata chha unakao wachana taimaeelaaee, jao Yeshukahaan sharaṇa paaunalaaee .
2. “naḍaraa ma chhau najaeeka, nahao nairaasha, ma haun taeraa paramaeshawara, garachhau gauhaara
maerao dhaaramaikataakao daayon haatalae tan khaḍaa haunaechhasa‌ maerao saamarathayalae” .
3. “aagaokao paraeekaṣhaa bhaera jaandaa, maerao anaugaraha parashasata haunachha sadaa
jawaalaalae tanlaaee paolanaechhaaina kataai, kasaralaaee phaalaera khaarainachhasa‌ sauna jasataai” .
4. “tayao paraaṇa jao sharaṇa lainachha kharaeeṣhaṭa Yeshumaa chhaḍadaina kadaapai shataraukao haatamaa
tyo paraaṇalaaee shaaitaanalae khaojae naasha garana ma kadaapai, kadaapai tyo tayomanaechhaaina” .

songs.title: kasatao ho samabanadha yao kahaeelae nataoḍainae
lyrics: kasatao ho samabanadha yao kahailae nataoḍainae
katai maeeṭhao samajhanaa kahailae nabairasanae
Yeshu taimarao maayokao (2)
1. jayaotai banai ḍaorayoyou andhayorao maerao jaeewanamaa
paapakao saagara taarai malaaee layoyou ananata kainaaramaa
hat samaaee malaaee baolaayou aaphanaai angagaalaomaa baandhayou
katai gahairao yao naataa kahailae nachhauṭanae
katai maeeṭhao chaahanaa kahailae namaeṭainae
Yeshu taimarao maayokao (2)
2. paaeena maile taimarao jasatao saanchao maayo samsaaramaa
maerao naimatai katai ṭhaoolao tayoga taimarao aaphaailaaee chaḍhaayou karausamaa
maile paaen nayon aashaa nayon jaeewana Yeshumaa (2)

songs.title: kahaan jaandaaichhaau taimaee pharakaera aaoo parabhaumaa
lyrics: kao. kahaan jaandaaichhaau taimaee, pharakaera aaoo parabhaumaa
chhaaina aba taa samaya, baiyonlao nagaraee parabhau Yeshulaaee bishwas gara (2)
1. gairahaechhaau taimaee kahaan, thaahaa chha kae taimaeelaaee ?
paugachhaau kahaan taimaee, kauna baaṭaomaa jaandaaichhaau ?
Yeshumaa aaoo ahailae naai, parakhairahanaechhana‌ taimaeelaaee .
2. baanchaekao chha kae aatamaa, waichaara garaekaa chhaau kae ?
yasakaaraṇa aaoo chaanड़ai naai, aatamaakao phaikaraee garaee
parakhairahaechhana‌ Yeshu aatamaa bachaauna taimarao .
3. nagaraee ḍhailao aba, samaya haundaai chaanड़ai aaoo
unalae sawaraga laana chaahanachhana‌, bishwas garayou bhanae maatara
parakhairahanaechhana‌ Yeshu, abaera nagaraee aaoo .

songs.title: kahaansamama jaanae yotaraee ho maukataikao baaṭao khaojaera (2)
lyrics: kao. kahaansamama jaanae yotaraee hao, maukataikao baaṭao khaojaera (2)
daui baaṭao banaiekao chha (2)
euṭaa baaṭao pharaakailao chha, baalaamasamama pauganae
arakao baaṭao yasatao panai chha, kharaeeṣhaṭa Yeshusamama pauganae
kahaan jaanae ho kataa jaanae ho nairaṇaya gara (2)
1. maृtayaukao ḍaralae aajaeewana bharaee daasatawamaa phansaekaaharaoolaaee
ḍaanड़akaanड़a daeuraalaee bhanajayongaga wara paipalamaa alajhaekaaharaoolaaee
(aakaasha chhaichaolaera jaanae Yeshulae) (2), chhauṭakaaraa taimaeelaaee dainaechha .
2. wairahamaa jalanae maanawalaaee harapala sataaunae garadachha
dharataeelaokamaa bainataee saunanae eka udadhaarakarataa chha
(baaikauṇaṭhadhaama unakao raajaya chha) (2), Yeshumaa maatara parawaesha chha .

songs.title: kahailae mailana kahailae waichhaḍa
lyrics: kao. kahailae mailana kahailae waichhaḍa
kahailae haansaa kahailae raodana, yasataai naai chha yao karausakao jaeewana (2)
1. sharaeeramaa raodana bhaepanai sawaragaeeya paitaakao daeshamaa
raodana waichhaḍa haundaaina, aankhaabharaikao aanshau uhaanlae aaphanaai haatalae
pauchhaidainae chhana‌ samsaaramaa bhaekao dauhkhaharaoo
aananadakao kaaraṇalae wairasainae chhaaun (2)
2. nairaashaa aauchhana‌ jaeewanamaa
jaeewana naai baehaosaee haunachha, nairaasaakao kaaraṇalae
wayarathaaimaa maile hat haalaechhau, bhananae parashana ubajanachha
tara yaee saba haunau na aaphanao naimatai waikaasakao baaṭao rahaechha

songs.title: kahailayoi nachhaauड़nae kahailayoi natayoganae taimarao karaara
lyrics: kao. kahailayoi nachhaड़nae, kahailayoi natayoganae, taimarao karaara aṭauṭa chha (2)
1. naisasaara eka paradaeshaee bhaye (2), lakaṣhahaeena gaoraeṭaomaa gairahaethae (2)
jayaotairamaya parabhau, sahaaraa daiyou, sawaragaeeya pathamaa pharakaai layoyou (2)
2. ghanaa jamgalakao anadhakaaramaa (2), aashaa thaiena baanchanae maeraa (2),
madhaura aawaajalae baolaayou malaaee, sanaatana premalae angaalayou malaaee (2)
3. paeeड़a ra kalaeshalae paeeड़ita haundaa (2), nairaasha bhaye anayaolamaa thaien (2)
tara taimarao madhaura aawaajalae, sadaaiwa shaanatailae malaaee bharayou (2)
4. yasaratha taimarao parashamsaa garachhau (2), hara pala maerao saatha rahayou (2)
aankhaakao raanaeejhaain jaogaairaakhayou, isaraaelaeelaaeejhaain rakaṣhaa garayou (2)

songs.title: kaanḍae maukauṭa gailalaa ra karaoosa tapaaeemlae raojanau bhayao
lyrics: kao. kaanḍae maukauṭa gailalaa ra karaoosa tapaaeemlae raojanau bhayao
bachaauna ma paapaeelaaee, paitaakaai ichachhaa sawaeekaara garaee
daṇaḍa bhaoganaubhayao bachaauna ma paapaeelaaee (2)
1. maoolayahaeena maerao jaeewanalaaee bahaumaoolaya banaaunalaaee
majasatao aghaora aparaadhaeelaaee daṇaḍabaaṭa bachaaunalaaee
maeraa paapaharaoo sawaeekaara garaee daṇaḍa bhaoganaubhayao (dhanayawaada tapaaeemlaaee) (2)
2. samarapaṇa garachhau aba yao jaeewana tapaaeemkaai manajhaaim haunasakaosa‌
tapaaeemkao naimatai sangagharaṣha garadaai daina waa daina yao mana ramaaosa‌
anaugarahalaaee sawaeekaara garaee hainḍana chaahanachhau parabhau (saamarathaya dainausa‌ aba) (2)

songs.title: kaamakao paoorao phala kaamakao paoorao phala layounaechhaaum
lyrics: kaamakao paoorao phala kaamakao paoorao phala
layounaechhaaum ramaaundaai kaamakao paoorao phala (2)
1. baihaana samaya raopachhaau dayoraupaee baeeulaaee
daiunsao panai raopachhaaum saanjha naparaunyajaela
dhairajalae kaama garachhaaum phalakao aashaa raakhaee
layounaechhaaum ramaaundaai kaamakao paoorao phala
2. dauhkha sahaee raopachhaa, saukha bhaogaee raopachhaau
jharaeemaa jaaḍaomaa rahanachhaau aṭala
kaaṭanae baelaa haamaee paakaekao phala paauchhaaum
layounaechhaaum ramaaundaai kaamakao paoorao phala
3. parabhau kharaeeṣhaṭakao laagaee raudaai panai raopaaum
haanailaaee daekhaera nabanaaum chanyajala
daukhakao anata haunachha eenaama panai aaunchha
layounaechhaaum ramaaundaai kaamakao paoorao phala

songs.title: kaitanaa madhaura samaya haai (2) jaba maeraa Yeshu maujhakao
lyrics: kao. kaitanaa madhaura samaya haai (2) jaba maeraa Yeshu maujhakao
charaṇaom maem haai baiṭhaataa maujhakao khaalaee karakae
aatamaa sae bharataa jaataa . (2) ...
1. maujhakao haraee haraee ghaasa maem charaataa jaeewana jala bhaye pailaataa (2)
maujhakao haai bachaataa jaeewana maem saukha waha laataa . (2)
2. chaahae maaim ghaora anadhakaara sae chalaoon, paanaee sae bhaye naḍaraoon (2)
taeraee saoṭhaee aura laoṭhaee sae mana maeraa shaanatai haai paataa (2)

songs.title: kaitanaa mahaana paramaeshawara (3) usakaee saewaa karatae hae hama
lyrics: kaitanaa mahaana paramaeshawara (3)
usakaee saewaa karatae hae hama
aao taalaeeyo bajaae hama (3)
parabhau kaee satautai karae hama
aao jhaumae naachae gaae hama (3)
parabhau kaee satautai karae hama
apanae haathao kao uṭhaae hama (3)
parabhau kaee satautai karae hama .

songs.title: kaidaraona khaolaapaarai eka saanjha haamarao parabhau kharaeeṣhaṭalae
lyrics: 1. kaidaraona khaolaapaarai eka saanjha haamarao parabhau kharaeeṣhaṭalae
dauhkhaita haundaai yao bainataee garae (2)
tayasa baaraeemaa aaphanao lagi
samabhaawanaa bhae yao payolaa madaekhai tarakaaeedainauhaosa‌,
taaipanai ichachhaa tapaeemkao .
2. sabaailae kharaeeṣhaṭalaaee chhaaड़e pakaड़aindaa unaee,
saamanaa garaee naiṣhaṭhauraee maamalaa (2)
adaalatamaa unaee ekalaai,
aakhairamaa Yeshulaaee wahaan daṇaḍa-aajanyo daie sabaailae,
barababaa maukata garaaiyao .
3. parabhau karaoosamaa ṭaangaie chaora ra ḍaakaookao sanga
paapakao baojha ra dauhkha sahandaai (2),
galagathaamaa rakata bahaae
taba unalae bhanae, aba samaapata bhayao maerao kaama,
hae paitaa, lainaosa‌ maerao paraaṇa .
4. jaeewana kharaeeṣhaṭalae dainalaaee garae maृtayau saamanaa
thaahaa chha kao taimaeelaaee sao kauraa (2),
jao kalawaraeemaa taimarao lagi
parakhanachhana‌ aaja kharaeeṣhaṭa bhanadaai taimaeelaaee madhaura sawaraaimaa
aauna paaunaechhaau jaeewanamaa .

songs.title: kainabhanae eeshawaralae samsaaralaaee yasatao prem garanaubhao’
lyrics: kao. kainabhanae eeshawaralae samsaaralaaee yasatao prem garanaubhao’
euṭaai nabhanaee haamaeelaaee unakao aaphanao pautara panai daiihaalanau bhao’
unaaimaathai bishwas garanae kaohaee naṣhaṭa hauna paaundaainana‌
tara ananata jaeewana paaee parabhaukao saathamaa sadaa basanaechhana‌
1. sawaragakao maunai araoo kaunaai naaunmaa udadhaara chhaaina bhaai (2)
sataya ho jhauṇaḍaiekao eeshawara taimarao lagi .
2. yahaee sausamaachaara saunaaidaeoo saaraa samsaaramaa aaja (2)
maanaisakao raoopa laiera aaunaubhao’ Yeshu maukataidaataa .

songs.title: kaisakaee khabara para bishwas karaogae
lyrics: kao. kaisakaee khabara para bishwas karaogae
bishwas karaogae parabhau kaee khabara para (4)
1. waha khabara kahataee haai maaim chamgaa haun
waha khabara kahataee haai maaim bharaa haun
waha khabara kahataee haai maaim aajaada haun
waha khabara kahataee haai maaim jaya haee jaya ॥

songs.title: kaueeraolae ḍhaakayao taimarao jaeewanalaaee ghaama panai laagaena
lyrics: kaueeraolae ḍhaakayao taimarao jaeewanalaaee ghaama panai laagaena
wachana ta dhaeraai saunaee sakayou hao... hao... paraiwaratana bhaena
1. dhauekao laugaa chamakailao haunachha maailaa ta haundaaina (2)
sangagatai dhaeraai hainḍaisakayou hao... hao... paraiwaratana bhaena
2. bagaekao khaolaa bagaera gayao pharakanana bhanaera (2)
parabhau ta dhaeraai raunau bhayao hao... hao... pharakanachhau bhanaera
3. baihaana uṭhaee ainaa ta haerachhaau sharaeerakao laagaee ho (2)
bishwaskao kaṣhaetaramaa hainḍaenaau bhanae hao... hao... sawaragamaa paugadaainaau

songs.title: kauchha bhai tao nahai haai masaiha taerae bainaa yae ज़inadagaee
lyrics: kao. (kauchha bhai tao nahai haai masaiha, taerae bainaa yae ज़inadagaee) (2)
jao bhai haoo maai tao abhai, taerae kaृpaa sae hau masaiha
kauchha bhai tao nahai .......
1. (aadaimaai bachana thaa wao bachana taujha mae hai thaa
wao bachana tau hai thaa wao bachana daehadhaara hauwaa) (2)
jainaa chaahaataa hau taerae laie, hara ghaḍai hara pala masaiha
2. (payora aura jaiwana daiyo, anaugaraha aura aashaa daiyo
paapasae chhauṭakaaraa daiya, eetanaa oosanae payora kaiyo) (2)
jainaa chaahaataa hau taerae laie hara ghaḍai hara pala masaiha
3. (kauchha bhai tao nahai haai masaiha, taerae bainaa yae ज़inadagaee) (2)
jao bhai haoo maai tao abhai, taerae kaृpaa sae hau masaiha

songs.title: kauna baaṭao haiड़daaichhaau haiड़ekao kaina (2)
lyrics: kao. kauna baaṭao haiड़daaichhaau haiड़ekaee kaina (2)
Yeshu naai tayora chhana‌ maukataidaana daina (2)
1. jaeewana haamarao daui dainakao ghaama chhaayo maataraai ho (2)
Yeshumaa naai jaeewana chha maanaisa jaataikao
Yeshu aae samsaaramaa sawaraga chhaḍaera
(naasha nahaosa‌ kaohaee panai baanchaosa‌ bhanaera) (2)
2. nabaitaau jaeewana haamarao wayarathaai wayarathaaimaa (2)
maukatai laeoo saitataai parabhau Yeshumaa
baitaijaanachha samaya pharakaee aaudaaina
(bishwas garae aatamaa haamarao marana paaundaaina) (2)

songs.title: kaunaai eka daina paृthawaee paapasaagara haundaa kaunaai eka daina
lyrics: 1. kaunaai eka daina paृthawaee paapasaagara haundaa,
kaunaai eka daina sawaraga-dhanaee Yeshu
sawaragalaokabaaṭa aaee kanayobaaṭa janamaindaa maanawa raoopa laie,
udaaharaṇa maerao .
kao. prem garaee aae, maradaa bachaae,
gaaड़indaa paapa maerao haṭaaidaie
bayauntaee unalae malaaee nairadaoṣha ṭhaharaae,
aaunaechhana‌ Yeshu ho khaushaeekao daina
2. kaunaai eka daina unalaaee kalawaraee lagae,
kaunaai eka daina karaoosamaa ṭaangae Yeshu
gailalaa samkaṣhaṭa ra haelaa khaaera baokae saba paapa,
maukataidaataa maerao .
3. kaunaai eka daina unalaaee chaihaanamaa raakhae,
kaunaai eka daina unalaaee aaraama mailayao
sawaragadaoota aaera paharaa garae,
nairaashaamaa aashaa udadhaaraka maerao .
4. kaunaai eka daina maraṇabaaṭa jaiiuṭhae,
kaunaai eka daina chaihaanakao ḍhaungagaa palaṭayao
Yeshu bayauntae maृtayaumaathai, jayawanata sawaraga pharakae,
mahaaparabhau maerao .
5. kaunaai eka daina taurahaee shabada saunainachha,
kaunaai eka daina pharakaee aaunchhana‌ Yeshu
jayajayakaara unakao aakaashamaa gaunyajainachha,
taraataa Yeshu mahaaraajaa maerao .

songs.title: kaunaai kauraakao phaikaraee nagara haraekamaa paraarathanaa gara
lyrics: 1. kaunaai kauraakao phaikaraee nagara, haraekamaa paraarathanaa gara
bainataeedawaaraa maagaharaoo jaahaera gara, parabhaulaaee dhanaya bhana .
kao. saaraa haृdayalae bishwas gara,
aaphanaai samajhamaa bhara napara
sabaai kauraamaa parabhau samajha,
parabhaulae taimaeelaaee ḍaorayounaechhana‌ .
2. anaekaaum paraikaṣhaaharaoomaa paradaa, yasalaaee paooraa aananada samajha
yao jaanaera taimarao bishwaskao jaachalae, dhaairaya utapanana garachha .
3. “naḍaraaoo, ma taimarao saathaaimaa chhau, taimaeelaaee madadata garachhau
ma haun taimarao paramaeshawara nairaasha nahaooo, dharamaikataamaa samahaalanaechhau .”

songs.title: kauhau kauhau garanae wanamaa uड़nae kaoilaee charaee chhana‌
lyrics: kao. kauhau-kauhau garanae, wanamaa uड़nae kaoilaee charaee chhana‌
khaulaulaulau gadaai khaolaa baganae tapaaeemkaa saृṣhaṭai hauna‌
hae eeshawara, tapaaeemkaa saृṣhaṭai hauna‌
1. (jakajaka garanae batataeejhaain balanae aakaashamaa taaraa chhana‌) (2)
(jaoonakao kairaṇa katai ho narama) (2) tapaaeemkaa saृṣhaṭai hauna‌,
hae eeshawara, tapaaeemkaa saृṣhaṭai hauna‌,
maृgakaa paaṭhaa kae raamaraa garaee wanamaa upharaekaa,
pashau ra pakaṣhaee kae raamaraa garaee tapaaeemlae rachaekaa, hae eeshawara, tapaaeemlae rachaekaa .
2. (wanamaa jaanachhau, phala-phaoola haerachhau tapaaeemlaaee samajhanachhau) (2)
(tapaaeemkao rachanaa samajhaera manamaa) (2) ma chhakaka paradachhau, hae eeshawara, ma chhakaka paradachhau,
nayoulaee charaee bailaaunaa gaaee wanamaa uḍaekaa
pashau ra pakaṣhaee kae raamarao garaee tapaaeemlae rachaekaa, hae eeshawara, tapaaeemlae rachaekaa .
3. (abaraahaama, isahaaka, yokaoobakaa eeshawara, daataa jaeewanakaa) (2)
(paapaeekaa naimatai atai prem garaee) (2) pautara daie balaidaana,
hae eeshawara, tapaaeem taaraṇahaara
paapaee haृdaya chhaṭapaṭa garaee khaojachha maukatai upaaya
maukataikao baaṭao sawaragakaa waaibhawa tapaaeemlae rachaekaa, hae eeshawara, tapaaeemlae rachaekaa .

songs.title: kaृtajanya bhaye shaira jhaukaaee jaeewana chaढ़auna aaekaochhau
lyrics: kao. kaृtajanya bhaye, shaira jhaukaaee jaeewana chaढ़auna aaekaochhau,
amaoolaya bhaeṭa araoo kae chha ra ? (jaeewana maeraai arapaekao chhau) (2)
1. ṭaaढ़o jaandaa premalaaee bhaulaee, ghaayala haunachha mana parabhaukao (2)
(haunachhau najaeeka) (2) (taimarao naai sakatainan ma jaana ṭaaड़o) (2)
2. manalaaee khainchanae waaibhawa jagatakaa, wailaasa banalaana baadhaka maeraa (2)
kharaeeṣhaṭakao adabhaoota premaaikao naimatai tayogachhau yainalaaee manaaibaaṭa (2)
3. prem chha agaadha parabhau taimarao naai, bayona garanae shakatai chhaaina (2)
ananatakaala saewaa naai garaoon, yasa premabaaṭa uऋṇa ma haunanan (2)
4. jagakao naimatai jaiundainan, parabhau, na taa jaiunchhau aaphanaai naimatai (2)
sakatainan ma arapaṇa nagaraee chhaṭao jaeewana taimarao naai naimatai (2)
5. dauhkhaita chhau ma samayakao naimatai baitaethayao jao sahandaa paapamaa (2)
baankaee jaeewana kaृtajanyataamaa arapaita haosa‌ parabhaukaai saewaamaa (2)

songs.title: kae chha ra maile laanau naai tayahaan saba chhaḍaee jaanau chha
lyrics: kae chha ra maile laanau naai tayahaan saba chhaḍaee jaanau chha
sauna ra chaandaee hairaa maotaee (na tyo naai laanau chha) (2)
1. karakalaakao paanaee jasatao jaeewana paaen maile
baolaaee daindaa maathaibaaṭa jaanauparachha ahailae (2)
kaina garanau jhaaim-jhagaḍaa kae kao raisa raaga (2)
jaanau chha haai aakhairamaa (2) kaina dhakakau dhaaka (2)
2. saृṣhaṭaikarataa paramaeshawaralaaee paukaarae thaem maile
paeeḍaa wayathaa waedanaalae garasaira bhaen jahailae (2)
maerao jaeewana bagadaai thaiyao naisasaara bhangagaalaomaa (2)
taanaera kharaeeṣhaṭalae sahaaraa banaee (2) haalae angagaalaomaa (2)

songs.title: kae taimaeelaaee yasakao naama thaahaa chha ? ho malaaee
lyrics: 1. kae taimaeelaaee yasakao naama thaahaa chha ? hao, malaaee yasakao naama thaahaa chha .
yao eka saunadara gaeeṭaara hao, yao bajanasakachha raingaṭaingaṭainga‌ .
unakao aawaaja saunachhaau bhanae, Yeshulae haamaeelaaee prem garachhana‌ .
yao bajanasakachha (raingaṭaingaṭainga‌) (2)
2. kae taimaeelaaee yasakao naama thaahaa chha ? hao, malaaee yasakao naama thaahaa chha .
yao eka saunadara paiyonao hao, yao bajanasakachha saa-rae-ga-ma .
unakao aawaaja saunachhaau bhanae, Yeshulae haamaeelaaee prem garachhana‌ .
yao bajanasakachha (saa-rae-ga-ma) (2)
3. kae taimaeelaaee yasakao naama thaahaa chha ? hao, malaaee yasakao naama thaahaa chha .
yao eka saunadara ḍarama-saeṭa hao, yao bajanasakachha ḍauma‌-ḍauma‌-ḍaisa‌ .
unakao aawaaja saunachhaau bhanae, Yeshulae haamaeelaaee prem garachhana‌ .
yao bajanasakachha (ḍauma‌-ḍauma‌-ḍaisa‌) (2)
