4. kae taimaeelaaee yasakao naama thaahaa chha ? hao, malaaee yasakao naama thaahaa chha .
yao eka saunadara maadala hao, yao bajanasakachha dhaina-taangaga-taangaga .
unakao aawaaja saunachhaau bhanae, Yeshulae haamaeelaaee prem garachhana‌ .
yao bajanasakachha (dhaina-taangaga-taangaga) (2)

songs.title: kae thaaha taimaeelaaee jainadagaee kae ho chhaaina chhaaina chhaaina
lyrics: kae thaaha taimaeelaaee jainadagaee kae ho
chhaaina chhaaina chhaaina bharaosaa bhaolaee kae haunae ho (2)
1. laagachha haolaa taimaeelaaee yao jainadagaee yasaai
usaai baitaee gae haunachha (2)
nasaomcha haai sajailao chha ajamawaraee jaeewana paauna
nayoya panai saakhaiekao chha (2)
kae thaaha taimaeelaaee...
2. aaja naai ho taimarao laagaee yao maaukaa shaurau garanae jaeewanakao yotaraa (2)
paapakao kaṣhamaa paauna ananatakao aananada paauna
bishwas gara parabhau Yeshulaaee (2)
kae thaaha taimaeelaaee...

songs.title: kae ma jaaoon raitataai hat laiee yasaai bhaeṭaoon parabhaulaaee ?
lyrics: 1. kae ma jaaoon raitataai hat laiee, yasaai bhaeṭaoon parabhaulaaee ?
kae ma ekaai dainakao kaamalaaee daina nasakaoon unalaaee ?
kao. kae ma jaaun raitataai hat laiee, yasaai bhaeṭaoon parabhaulaaee
kaina Yeshukahaan nalayooon euṭaai panai saathaeelaaee ?
2. ḍaraai chhaaina maृtayaudaekhai kharaeeṣhaṭa bachaaunae chhana‌ malaaee
tara unakahaan raitataai jaandaa raunaechha maerao haृdaya .
3. tyo samaya jao paapamaa kaaṭaen, tyo pharakaina sakae taa
parabhaulaaee tyo dainae thaien hainड़daai unakao ichachhaamaa .
4. kharaeeṣhaṭaeeya jana hao, jaaga, uṭha, baelaa haundaa bala lagaaoo
aaphanao maृtayaubhanadaa aghai sakabhara dhaeraai paraaṇa bachaaoo .

songs.title: kae haolaa yao jaeewana bhanaekao aansau ho kai haansao ho yao
lyrics: kao. kae haolaa yao jaeewana bhanaekao,
aansau ho kai haansao ho yao
dharama-karamakao pauraanao raiwaaja ho kai
(sawaragakao naaulao aawaaja hao) (2)
1. shaanatai waishawamaa haraairahaechha,
aaphanao shatarau maanachhae aaphaai naai banaechha
aatangaka, anayoyakao ḍaढ़elao salakaechha
(haamarao nairalajajataa yao saḍakamaa salakaechha) (2)
Yeshukao aawaajalaaee eka palaṭa saunaihaera shanatai
waisharaama dainae wachana ekapalaṭa baujhaihaera .
2. maanachhae aaphaailae aaphanao aatamaalaaee katai
daama tairaee bachaauna sakachha ra ?
paoojaa ra bhakatai, aaphanaai parayatanalae maailao
paapa haamarao bagaauna sakachha ra ? (2)
Yeshukao kaṣhaṭa ra waedanaa ekapalaṭa baujhaihaera,
sawaragamaa kaoraekaa yaojanaa
kalawaraee ḍaanḍaalaaee haera kae haolaa yao ?

songs.title: kaelae dhaunachha maerao paapa ? kaewala Yeshukao ragatalae
lyrics: 1. kaelae dhaunachha maerao paapa ? kaewala Yeshukao ragatalae
haunachhau naikao kasaraee ? kaewala Yeshukao ragatalae
kao. amaoolaya dhaaraa yao haunachhau, haiun jasatao saetao
chhaaina kaunaai maoola yasatao, kaewala Yeshukao sagatalae .
2. kaṣhamaa paainae sakhachhau ma, kaewala Yeshukao ragatamaa
shaudadha hauna sakachhau ma, kaewala Yeshukao ragatalae .
3. paapalaaee ḍhaakana sakainachha, kaewala Yeshukao ragatalae
asala kaamalae sakadaaina, kaewala Yeshukao ragatalae .
4. maerao aashaa ra shaanatai, kaewala Yeshukao ragatamaa
maerao paooraṇa dhaaramaikataa, kaewala Yeshukao ragatamaa .

songs.title: kaehaee kauraamaa chainataita nahaoo
lyrics: kaehaee kauraamaa chainataita nahaoo,
sabaai kauraamaa dhanayawaadasaatha paraarathanaa gara .
paramaeshawakao shaanatailae taimarao haृdaya ra
taimarao waichaaralaaee Yeshumaa rakaṣhaa garanaechha .

songs.title: kaaisaa badalaa maujhae (3) jaba Yeshu kae paasa maaim gayo
lyrics: kao. kaaisaa badalaa maujhae (3) jaba Yeshu kae paasa maaim gayo .
1. ganadaee chaeejaom kao maainae daekhanaa chhaड़a
ganadaee baataom kao maainae paढ़naa chhaड़a... .
ganadaee baataom kao maainae saunanaa chhaड़a
jaba Yeshu kae paasa maaim gayo... .
2. ganadae shabadaom kao maainae baolanaa chhaड़a
ganadaee chaeejaom kao maainae khaanaa chhaड़a... .
ganadaee chaeejaom kao maainae paeenaa chhaड़a
jaba Yeshu kae paasa maaim gayo... .

songs.title: kao chha eeshawarapaṭaṭai raajaalaaee maananae kasalae gauhaara garanae
lyrics: 1. kao chha eeshawarapaṭaṭai raajaalaaee maananae,
kasalae gauhaara garanae ra paraaṇa bachaaunae
kasalae samsaara tayogaee shataraulaaee jaitanae,
kao chha eeshawarapaṭaṭai ra aghai baढ़nae
parabhaukao kaृpaalae, an anaugarahalae,
haamaee eeshawarapaṭaṭai hamaee unakaa haaun .
2. kharaeeṣhaṭa parabhaulae kainae na sauna, chaandaeelae,
tara aaphanao ragatalae maukauṭakao lagi
bharapaoora aashaiṣha‌ dainau sabaai aaunaelaaee,
haamaeelaaee khausha garaaee sawatanatara banaaee
paraaṇa aphanao daiee kainae, an anaugarahalae,
haamaee eeshawarapaṭaṭai haamaee unakaa haaun .
3. laड़ain ṭhaoolao haolaa, shatarau balawaana‌ chha,
raajaakao lasakaralaaee kasalae jaitanae chha
unakao jhaṇaḍaeemaunai waijaya naishachaya chha,
unakao wachana sataya jayawanata haunalaaee
aaaun unamaa ramaaundaai, an anaugarahalae,
haamaee eeshawarapaṭaṭai haamaee unakaa haaun .
4. chhaanaiyoun saipaahaee shataraukao daeshamaa,
ganaiyoun, bishwasee kapataanakao jhauṇaḍamaa
parabhaukao kaama garana haamaee naḍaraaaun,
haamaee bhakata, udaara sataya, waeera banaaun
parabhau chhana‌ bachaaunae, an anaugarahalae,
sadhaain eeshawarapaṭaṭai haamaee unakaa haaun .

songs.title: kao ho chhaimaekaee (2) kaisasaa Yeshukao daohaorayounchhau nai
lyrics: kao. kao ho chhaimaekaee (2),
kaisasaa Yeshukao daohaorayounchhau nai
1. baaṭaomaa jaanae baepaaraeelaaee chaoraharaoolae bhaeṭae
kauṭaipaiṭaee baehaosa‌ paaraee dhana samapatatai lauṭae
aaphanaai ragatamaa laṭapaṭaiekaa baepaaraeelaaee daekhaee
pauraohaita ra dharama-gaurau hainड़e baaṭao tarakaee .
2. saanao jaatakao saamaraeelae baepaaraeelaaee daekhae
chaoṭa-paṭaka dhaoera ghaauharaoo baandhae .
raogaeelaaee uṭhaaera pashaumaathai raakhae .
chaora-ḍaankaukao khayola namaanaee aaphanao baaṭao laagae .
3. saamaraee ra raogaee wayakatai jasaai paaṭaee paugae
paaṭaeedaarakao haatamaa tainalaaee jaimamaa laae
kaehaee kharacha daiera baepaaraeelaaee bhanae
pharakaee aaundaa tairaaunlaa ma kharacha araoo laagae .

songs.title: kaoilaee charanae paakhaamaa kharaeeṣhaṭakao gaeeta gaunajaechha
lyrics: kao. kaoilaee charanae paakhaamaa kharaeeṣhaṭakao gaeeta gaunajaechha
sayola raoonae ḍaanड़amaa haamarao paailaa paugaechha (2)
1. ghaama chhaayon kae ho (2) kharaeeṣhaṭakao naimatai baḍhanau chha
jharaee baadala kae ho (2) kharaeeṣhaṭakao naimatai laḍanau chha
aanshau haamarao chhachhalakainachha usakao raookhao utataramaa
jatai jae bhao bhaulaee dainachhaaum kharaeeṣhaṭamaa amara payoraamaa
2. bhaokaa payosaa kae ho (2) jharanaalae naai maeṭaaunchhaau
amga haamaraa thaakaee sakayao (2) paailaa aghai baढ़aunchhaau
nairaashaakao baadala aaee ḍhaakana chaahae katai katai
raata jatai baitae panai hataasha haamaee banadaainaaum

songs.title: kaokarao unakao chhaaina ḍaunड़ naai ochhayona bhao’
lyrics: 1. kaokarao unakao chhaaina, ḍaunड़ naai ochhayona bhao’,
saanao parabhau Yeshu gaoṭhamaa pasaraie
sawaragadaekhai taaraaharaoo unalaaee haeradaai gae, saanao parabhau Yeshu paraalamaa sautae .
2. gaaee-gaoraoo karaae, baalaka baioonjhaie, na unaee karaae, na kaailae raoe
hae parabhau payora garachhau, sawaragabaaṭa haeranaoo ra baihaanaaisamama masanga rahanaoo .
3. payora garanauhaosa‌ malaaee yao bainataee garachhau, ananatasamama haunauhaosa‌ najaeeka
parabhau aashaiṣha‌ sabalaaee daiee sabakao rakaṣhaa garanaosa‌ haamaeelaaee
sawaragalaokamaa basanae yaogaya paaranaosa‌ .

songs.title: kaomala haृdaya dainauhaosa‌ malaaee tapaaeemkao prem anaubhawa
lyrics: kaomala haृdaya dainauhaosa‌ malaaee, tapaaeemkao prem anaubhawa garanalaaee
chaooraṇa haृdaya dainauhaosa‌ malaaee, tapaaeemkao waasasathaana bananalaaee
tapaaeemkao upasathaitai, maerao aananadakao bharapaooraee, tapaaeemkao aananada naai maerao saamaratha
(jaya gaaunchhau) (2) tapaaeemkao .

songs.title: kaohai chhaaina kaohai chhaaina haृdayalae tapaaee jhaaim chaahaekao
lyrics: kaohai chhaaina kaohai chhaaina haृdayalae tapaaeem bhaaim chaahaekao
aba ta baanchana panai sakadainama tapaaeem wainaa (2)
pala pala malaaee Yeshu chaahainachha
hara kaṣhaṇa malaaee Yeshu chaahainachha

songs.title: kaohaee chhaaina tapaaeemjasatao paramaeshawara (2)
lyrics: kaohaee chhaaina tapaaeemjasatao paramaeshawara (2)
saagarabhanadaa gahairao chha, haimaalabhanadaa uccha chha (2)
tapaaeemkao waichaara, tapaaeemkao waichaara .

songs.title: kaauna jaaegaa kaauna jaaegaa (2) parabhau taoo maujhakao
lyrics: kao. kaauna jaaegaa? kaauna jaaegaa (2)
parabhau taoo maujhakao bhaeja maaim jaaoon wahaan
parabhau taoo maujhakao bhaeja taoo chaahae jahaan . (2‌)
1. baaigara kaoee gae wahaan, wae kaaisae laaen imaana
baaigara laiyae maeraa naama, wae kaaisae paae najaata
kaauna jaaegaa ? ... .
2. khaeta paka chaukae haai kaauna jaaegaa
charawaahae baina yae maeraee bhaeड़e, bhaṭaka rahaee anajaana .
3. kaauna masaeeha kae paeechhae apanaa karaoosa uṭhaaegaa ?
hajaaraom laogaom kao usakaa wachana saunaaegaa ?
kaauna jaaegaa ? ... ॥

songs.title: karaoosa taimarao parabhau kalakaraeekao maeraa naimatai atai naai paraiya
lyrics: kao. karaoosa taimarao parabhau kalawaraeekao, maeraa naimatai atai naai paraiya chha
kaaraṇa banae maeraa kaanड़aharaoo, taimaraa shairakaa maukauṭa !
1. maerao paeera ṭhaoolao samajhanachhau, ra maerao ghaau aalao
banaidainachha jaba kalawaraeekao, daृshaya waisataaraai dhamailao
tara haoina rahaechha parabhau yasatao, banayou taimaee awahaelaita
bhaulanaechhaaina ma tyo kathaa, taimaee bhaethayou karaoosamaa dalaita .
2. paeeḍaa nainadaa waedanaa ra kaṣhaṭa, maeraa pathakaa paraeraṇaaharaoo hauna‌
sabaai haaralae malaaee sadhaaim, jaeetakaa sanadaesha dainachhana‌
taimaraa ghaauharaoo chaumachhau parabhau, taee hauna‌ maeraa raogamaa changagaai
aashalae bharainachhau sawaasathaya paaunchhau, taimaraai taee haatakao saparasha paaee .
3. anaugaraha taimarao parashasata chha, maerao daurabalataamaa jhana‌ baḍhaee
thaakachhau jaba saanghaurao baaṭaomaa hainḍadaa, aaunchhaau parabhau saamaratha banaee
yasaratha ramaauchhau haraeka chaoṭamaa, kamajaoraeemaa ra daurabalataamaa
nairaasha haunanan ma kahailayoi kaunaai, paraisathaitai ra samasayomaa .

songs.title: karaoosakao chhaeumaa aaunchhau tayasamaa aashaa paaundachhau
lyrics: 1. karaoosakao chhaeumaa aaunchhau, tayasamaa aashaa paaundachhau
jasamaa bhayao balaidaana, jasalae haunachha maerao taraaṇa .
kao. Yeshumaa ma raakhachhau aashaa, balai bhayao karaoosamaa khaasa
karaoosakao aashaiṣha‌ malaaee daeoo maerao gaharaaun bhaaraee laeoo
2. ma taa paapaee kalaeshaita thaien, aaphanaa karamalae dauhkhaita thaien
khaojadathaen taraaṇakao upaaya, jaanadainathaen sata‌ sahaaya .
3. parabhau Yeshu maerao naatha, samaatachhau ma unakaai hat
khaalai Yeshu sata awataara Yeshudaekhai chha udadhaara .

songs.title: karaoosakao chhaeumaa raakhanauhaosa‌ jahaan maukataikao dhaaraa chha
lyrics: kao. karaoosakao chhaeumaa raakhanauhaosa‌, jahaan maukataikao dhaaraa chha
jahaan paapakao paraayashachaita chha, jahaan paeeड़akao anata chha
?. (tapaaeemkao dhanaya maananaechhau, sadaa ma dhanaya maananaechhau
tapaaeemkao chhaeumaa jaba haunaechhau kaृpaa parabhau malaaee garanauhaosa‌
karaoosakao chhaeumaa jaba haunaechhau kaृpaa parabhau malaaee garanauhaosa‌
paapa maerao kaṣhamaa daiee sawaragaeeya raajaya dainauhaosa‌
karaoosakao chhaeumaa jaba haunaechhau ... .

songs.title: karaoosakao baaṭaomaa hainḍana chaahanachhaau kae aaphaailaaee inakaara
lyrics: 1. karaoosakao baaṭaomaa hainḍana chaahanachhaau kae ? aaphaailaaee inakaara garanau parachha naai .
uhaankao paailaa pachhayounchhaau kae ? aashaiṣha‌kao jharaee parashasata paaunchhaau .
2. karaoosakao baaṭaomaa hainḍana chaahanachhaau kae ? dauhkha kaṣhaṭa awashaya aaunchha naai .
Yeshulaaee pahailao sathaana dainachhaaum kae ? raojaaiharaoo thauparaai aaunchhana‌ naai .
3. karaoosakao baaṭaomaa hainḍana chaahanachhaau kae ? samasayoharaoo thauparaai haunachhana‌ naai .
taimaee sadhaaim bharaosaa gara, parabhau sahaayaka haunauhaunachha sadhaaim .
4. karaoosakao baaṭaomaa hainḍana chaahanachhaau kae ? dauṣhaṭa taimarao wairaodhamaa uṭhanaechha .
saamanaa garana paitaalaaee paukaara, taimarao pakaṣhamaa kharaeeṣhaṭa haunauhaunachha .
5. karaoosakao baaṭaomaa hainḍana chaahanachhaau kae ? sataawaṭa ra samasayomaa parachhaaum naai .
Yeshulaaee haeradaai jaiuna chaahanachhaai kae ? uhaankao agauwaaee sadaa haunachha naai .
6. uhaankao lagi paraaṇa gaumaauna tayora chhaau ? uhaan taimarao saathamaa haunauhaunachha .
maana ijajata gaumaauna tayora chhaau kae ? sawaragamaa maukauṭa paraapata garachhaaum naai .

songs.title: karunaimaa karunaimaa malaaee paraethayao jayaotai maerao paapakao
lyrics: karunaimaa karunaimaa malaaee paraethayao jayaotai maerao paapakao bhaaraee haṭaigao’
tayahaan bishwas garaee maile paaen daृṣhaṭai ra ahailaekao jaeewana khaushaee bhao’ .

songs.title: khachaakhacha bhao’ baethalaehaema gaaun saraayamaa thaiena
lyrics: kao. khachaakhacha bhao’ baethalaehaema gaaun, saraayamaa thaiena kharaeeṣhaṭalaaee ṭhaaun
aaja panai maanaisa wayasata bhaye garadaainana‌ kharaeeṣhaṭakao waasataa
1. paraiya pautara eeshawarakao (2) thaotarao gaoṭhamaa pasaraie
sabaaibaaṭa tayogaiera (2) garaeebabhanadaa garaeeba bhae .
2. taimarao-maerao naimatai kharaeeṣhaṭalae (2) parashasata dhana saanchaekaa chhana‌
haamarao dauhkha uṭhaaera (2) ananata saukha raakhaekaa chhana‌ .
3. atai daeena kharaeeṣhaṭa maृtayausamama (2) aajanyokaaraee bananaubhayao,
bishwaseelaaee alagaaunalaaee (2) aaphaai aghai alaganaubhao .

songs.title: khabaradaara saanao aankhaa kae haerachha (2)
lyrics: 1. khabaradaara, saanao aankhaa kae haerachha (2)
kao. taimarao sawaragae baabaulae tala haerachhana‌ payoralae
khabaradaara saanao aankhaa kae haerachha
2. khabaradaara, saanao kaana kae saunachha (2)
3. khabaradaara, saanao hat kae garachha (2)
4. khabaradaara, saanao mana kae saochachha (2)
5. khabaradaara, saanao paau kahaan jaanachha (2)

songs.title: khalalao chha jaeewana naatha atai naai ghainalaagadao
lyrics: 1. khalalao chha jaeewana, naatha atai naai ghainalaagadao
tapaaeemkao yaogayakao chhaaina sawabhaawa maerao;
khaaee ṭhaokara laड़en dhaera, lajajaita yasa jaeewanamaa
tapaaeemkao naimatai, parabhau laabha chhaaina kaehaee mamaa;
saड़ekao maerao daeha maaganauhaunachha parabhau
thaakaen ma aaphaaisaita, thaakanauhaunana, hae parabhau .
2. bhaen ma baalaka kharaeeṣhaṭakao taapanai chhau hataasha,
pawaitara prem uhaankao garadachhau kaina naasha;
dauraganadha paapakao atai malaaee naisaasadachha,
jagaaunae daoṣhakao bhaalae sadhaain naai baasadachha;
chakaita ma jhana‌-jhana‌ chhau, saunachhau jaba aawaaja,
phaikaa yasatao jaeewanalaaee daana chha Yeshukao raajaya .
3. patayounau gaaharao laagachha prem kasatao gahairao,
baekamamaa phaosarao maanaisa Yeshukao kaamalaagadao;
ghaeerajaee parabhau maerao jharakananana‌ masaita,
uṭhaaunauhaunachha malaaee laड़dachhau jaba ma;
haृdayakao aashaa ṭauṭaosa‌ yo phauṭaosa‌ maerao mana,
yathaeṣhaṭa kharaeeṣhaṭakao premalae ma haunachhau saushaobhana .

songs.title: khaanchao chha jatai hae maerao maitara bhana kharaeeṣhaṭa Yeshulaaee
lyrics: 1. khaanchao chha jatai, hae maerao maitara, bhana kharaeeṣhaṭa Yeshulaaee
jauraaunauhaunachha haamarao parabhaulae bharapaoora sabaai garaaee (2)
uhaankao lagi taimarao ra maerao atai bahaumaoolaya chha paraaṇa
yasaailae sabaai tayogaee uhaanlae garanaubhao’ haamarao taraaṇa (2)
2. samarapaṇa gara taimarao jaeewanalaaee Yeshukao haataaimaa (2)
bharaosaa panai uhaanmaathai raakha jao haamarao saathaaimaa (2)
garanauhaunaechha haृdayakao ichachhaa haamarao parabhaulae paooraṇa
paoorao haosa‌ ichachhaa parabhau Yeshukao, maerao haosa‌ saba chaooraṇa .

songs.title: khaudaawata taoo saonae sae bhaye jayodaa mahaemgaa haai
lyrics: khaudaawata taoo saonae sae bhaye jayodaa mahaemgaa haai
khaudaawata taoo chaandaee sae bhaye, jayodaa kaimataee haai
khaudaawata taoo haeerae sae bhaye jayodaa khaubasaoorata haai
aura taerae saiwaa maaim chaahaoon kauchha bhaye nahaeem ॥

songs.title: khaula jaayaegaee kaitaabaem jaba bhaye haisaaba haogaa
lyrics: kao. khaula jaayaegaee kaitaabaem jaba bhaye haisaaba haogaa
inasaapha kaee taraajaoo Yeshu kae hat haogaa (2)
khaula jaayaegaee... .
1. jao bhaye taoo kara rahaa haai, Yeshu waha daekhataa haai (2)
hara pala jao taujhakao mailataa, daenaa haisaaba haogaa
inasaapha kaee taraajaoo, Yeshu kae hat haogaa .
khaula jaayaegaee... .
2. aajaa abhaye sae mauड़kara Yeshu baulaa rahaa haai (2)
waranaa yaha yoda karalae, taeraa bhaye naasha haogaa
inasaapha kaee taraajaoo, Yeshukaa hat haogao .
khaula jaayaegaee kaitaabaem... ॥

songs.title: khausha ho khaudaawanata aayo haai usakao kabaoola karao
lyrics: 1. khausha ho khaudaawanata aayo haai, usakao kabaoola karao
ai kaula jahaana, haan hara eka daila, masaeehakao jagaha dae .
2. khausha hao, masaeeha aba baadashaaha haai, saba aadamaee hara jaoobaana
samaunadara bhaye, maaidaana pahaaड़, gaeeta gaayaem khausha ilahaana .
3. dauhkha aura takalaeepha waha karataa daoora haṭaataa haai gaunaaha
taaraeekaee maem waha daetaa naoora, aura barakata baesha-bahaa .
4. raasataabaajaee aura sachachaaee sae, waha raaja phaailaataa haai
aura apanaee kaoola haukaoomata maem paihaara daikhaataa haai ॥

songs.title: khaushaee khaushaee manaaaun khaushaee-khaushaee manaaaun (2)
lyrics: khaushaee-khaushaee manaaaun, khaushaee-khaushaee manaaaun (2)
bhana-bhana, parabhau Yeshu kharaeeṣhaṭakao jaya (2)
maeraolaagai aae, maeraolaagai jaie (2)
maeraolaagai Yeshulae dauhkha uṭhaae (2)
maeraolaagai maaraiethae, maeraolaagai gaaḍaiethae (2)
maeraolaagai baauraee uṭhae, maerao hauna‌ Yeshu
ma Yeshukao haun, haamaee Yeshukaa haaun .
khaushaee-khaushaee manaaaun, khaushaee-khaushaee manaaaun (2)
bhana-bhana, parabhau Yeshu kharaeeṣhaṭakao jaya (2)

songs.title: khaushaee-khaushaee manaao (2) baolao baolao masaeehaa kaee
lyrics: kao. khaushaee-khaushaee manaao (2)
baolao baolao masaeehaa kaee jaya jaya jaya (2)
1. maerae laie aayo maerae laie jaiyo (2)
maerae laie Yeshu nae dau:kha uṭhaayo
maerae laie maaraa gayo maerae laie gaaड़a gayo,
maerae laie phaira jaee uṭhaa maerae haai masaeeha,
maaim masaeeha haun, hama masaeeha kae haai ॥

songs.title: khaushaeekao khabara chharanalaaee aaunaubhao parabhau Yeshu
lyrics: kao. (khaushaeekao khabara chharanalaaee aaunaubhao parabhau Yeshu samsaaramaa) (2)
(sauna haai saathaee bhaai Yeshukao mitho wachana) (2)
1. anadhakaara jaeewana sadhaaim naai dauhkhamaa aansaulae bharaekao
anadhakaara jaeewana sadhaaim naai paiḍaamaa kaṣhaṭalae jalaekao
sawaragakao saukhalaaee tayogaera aaunaubhao nayon jaeewana dainalaaee
sawaragakao saukhalaaee tayogaera aaunaubhao haृdayakao chaoṭa maeṭanalaaee
2. paramaparabhaukao janyonaharaoo asala chhana‌ haृdayalaaee shaanatai dainae
paramaparabhaukao aashaiṣha‌ apaara chhana‌ jaeewanalaaee khaushaee dainae
saृṣhaṭaikarataakao aajanyo oo baolachhana‌ aankhaalaaee parakaasha dainae
saृṣhaṭaikarataakao aajanyo oo baolachhana‌ paapaeelaaee maaphaee dainae .

songs.title: khaushaeekao daina jasamaa maile Yeshumaathai raakhaen bishwas
lyrics: 1. khaushaeekao daina, jasamaa maile Yeshumaathai raakhaen bishwas
sabaailaaee kaina nasaunaaoon, chha maerao manamaa saukha-wailaasa .
kao. khaushaeekao daina, khaushaeekao daina Yeshulae paapa saba maeṭaae
aananada, paraarathanaa garadaai jaaoon bhanaera malaaee saikaae
khaushaeekao daina, khaushaeekao daina Yeshulae paapa saba maeṭaae
2. mahaana‌ saaṭaphaera paooraa bhayao, ma parabhaukao, unaee maeraa
malaaee taanae sawaralae maeeṭhao ra pachhai laagaen Yeshukao .
3. chaulabaulae mana phaeraisakayao paaechhau Yeshumaa shaanatai
parabhaudaekhai jaananan ṭaaढ़o, saba asala thaoka dainachhana‌ unaee .

songs.title: khaushaeeyolaee manaaaun dhanyawad Yeshulaaee chaढ़aaun
lyrics: kao. (khaushaeeyolaee manaaaun, dhanyawad Yeshulaaee chaढ़aaun) (2)
(janamaie Yeshu baethalaehaema gaaunmaa) (2) haamaeelaaee bachaauna) (4)
1. (garaaun sawaagata kharaeeṣhaṭa Yeshulaaee yao haamarao jaeewanamaa
janamainachhana‌ unaee ahailae naai banaaunchhana‌ jaeewana nayon) (2)
(unaee maatara hauna‌ saanchao parabhau) (2) (chhaaina kaohaee araoo) (2)
2. (waishawamaa haera jhailaimailaee chha, Yeshukao janama dainamaa
ramaairahaechhana‌ maanairaharaoo bhaelaa bhaye maṇaḍalaeemaa) (2)
(haamaee panai aananada manaaaun) (2) (Yeshukao gaeeta gaaau) (2)

songs.title: khaetaalaaharaoo dhaana kaaṭana jaaun khaetakao dhaana paakaisakayao
lyrics: kao. khaetaalaaharaoo dhaana kaaṭana jaaun khaetakao dhaana paakaisakayao (2)
1. daurabalaharaoolaaee jaitaaun bhanaee unaaikao saathaee banaee daien (2)
kasaaikasaailaaee bachaaun bhanaee unaaikao naimatai yasataai banaee (2)
2. dauhkhaeeharaoolaaee hansaau bhanaee karaoosakao aananada baanड़ee daien (2)
pairamaa paraekaalaaee samajhaaoo bhanaee kharaeeṣhaṭakao sanadaesha saunaaidaien (2)

songs.title: khaoja anai paaunnaechhaaun maaga anai dainaechha
lyrics: kao. khaoja anai paaunnaechhaaun, maaga anai dainaechha
ḍhakaḍhakaayao bhanae khaolainaechha, maerao haृdayakao dawaara
parabhau taimaeelae bhanaekaa thaiyou .
1. ma bagaalabaaṭa haraaekao bhaeड़a hauna chaahanana
(aawaaja daeoo malaaee baolaaoo) (2) taimaraai euṭaai bagaalamaa .
2. ma kae haun kao haun kaina chhau yahaan jaanana sakaoon baujhana sakaoon
(jaeewana yotaraakao paratayaeka paailaamaa) (2) taimaeesangaai hainḍana sakaoon .

songs.title: khaoja ta bhaeṭaaunaechhaau maaga ta paaunaechhaau
lyrics: khaoja ta bhaeṭaaunaechhaau, maaga ta paaunaechhaau
ḍhakaḍhakayooo ta taimarao lagi khaolainaechha
yao ho kharaeeṣhaṭakao achauka wachana, sadhaain lagaaoo yasaaimaa mana .

songs.title: khaojaee haerae (3) chaaraaitaira chaaraaitaira maile
lyrics: khaojaee haerae... 3 chaaraaitaira... chaaraaitaira maile
tara paauna sakaina Yeshu jasataai maukataidaataa arau kaohaee
(saa rae saa rae saa rae saa rae ga ma ga rae sa) (2)
1. Yeshulae maatara daindachha jaeewanadaana
Yeshulae maatara daindachha kaṣhamaadaana
Yeshulae maatara daindachha maukataidaana
Yeshulae maatara dainaubhao karausamaa paraaṇa
yasaailae aau aaja taimaee
dainalaaee kharaeeṣhaṭalaaee aaphanao jaeewana

songs.title: khaolakhaola ḍhaokaa khaoladaainaau kaina nai
lyrics: kao. khaola-khaola ḍhaokaa, khaoladaainaau kaina nai
parabhau aae taimaeelaaee maukataidaana dainau nai
1. pashachaatataapa gara, shaudadha gara, aauna sabaai ḍhailao nagara (2)
parabhau kharaeeṣhaṭalae taaraidainachhana‌ bishwas gara, paapalaaee nagara .
2. baudadhaimaanaee ma chhau, janyonaee bhanachhana‌ sabaai samsaara (2)
shaanatai dainae, maukatai dainae bhanachhana‌ parabhau Yeshu taaraṇahaara .
3. maukataidaataa aaunaubhayao samsaaramaa jayaotai banaera (2)
dajayaoo-bhaai, daidaee-bahainaee aaoona sabaai bishwas garaera .
4. karausamaathai chaढ़naubhayao haamarao parabhau Yeshu baicharaa (2)
satautai garachhau, charaṇamaa parachhau aaundaaichhau ma paapaee aghaara .
5. daajayaoo-bhaai daidaee-bahainaee, basachhaau kaina naishachainata bhaera (2)
baelaa chhaaina, baitaigayao katai basachhaau paapaai garaera .

songs.title: khaolaa naalaa pahaaḍaaimaa asainaa paanai jharaimaa (2)
lyrics: khaolaa naalaa pahaaḍaaimaa asainaa paanaee jharaimaa (2)
shaanatai ra aananadakao gaoraeṭaomaa (2)
1. paanaeekao payosaa laagae jasataai sangagataeekao bhaoka laiera (2)
haurauhaurau aaeepaugayoum sangagataeemaa (2)
2. chaahae aakaasha jharai jaauna‌ chaahae dharatai phaaṭai jaauna‌ (2)
parabhaukao apaara prem rahairahaosa‌ (2)
3. phaoolakao jasatao jaeewana haamarao oilaera jharaee jaanaechha
haiun jasataai yao jaeewana wailaera jaanaechha (2)

songs.title: khaolaera haृdaya aaoo parabhaukahaan chha maukatai kaewala parabhau Yeshumaa
lyrics: kao. khaolaera haृdaya aaoo parabhaukahaan, chha maukatai kaewala parabhau Yeshumaa (2)
kahailaesamama chaoopa laagaee basanae ho ? tayora haooo nayoyamaa ubhainalaaee
tayora haooo sawaraga jaanalaaee . khaolaera haृdaya... .
1. garabhaaimaa maanaisa paapasahaita haunachhana‌, dharamaee kaohaee haundaainana‌ (2)
laobha, ḍaahaa, ghaृṇaa, kapaṭa, abhaimaana, paapakaa daaga yasataai chhana‌ (2)
2. dharama-karamakao chayodaralae ḍhaakadaa kaunaai paapa ḍhaakaindaaina (2)
paapakaa daaga maeṭaee dharamaee taulayounae auṣhadhaee kaehaee chhaaina (2)
3. laaparawaaha banaee samsaaramaa ḍaubadaa maृtayau aaee gaanjanaechha (2)
paapaaikao jayolaa narakamaa paradaa bachaaunae kao haunachha ? (2)
4. paapaaimaa maraee aatamaa naasha paaraee taimaeelae kae paaunchhaau ? (2)
chhaṭapaṭaee, rauwaai, asahaya jalana, yahaee naai paaunnaechhaau (2)
5. paapa taimaraa thaie daṇaḍa taimarao naai, bachaauna taimaeelaaee (2)
dauhkha sahae karaoosamaa, ragata bahaae taimaraa paapa dhaunalaaee (2)

songs.title: kharaeeṣhaṭa maeraa maukataidaataa haai waha premaee maitara paapaee kaa
lyrics: kao. kharaeeṣhaṭa maeraa maukataidaataa haai, waha premaee maitara paapaee kaa
sadaa satautai ho parabhau, kaee aadara mahaimaa usakaee . (2)
1. Yeshu samsaara kaee jayaotai haai, Yeshu haee sawaraga kaee raaha haai
Yeshu haee taaraṇahaara haai, paapaee kao kaewala sahaaraa haai
2. tayogae Yeshu nae sawaraga kaa saukha, uṭhaayo paapaiyaom kaa dauhkha
daiyo Yeshu nae karaoosa para paraaṇa, kaiyo haai paapaiyaom kaa taraaṇa . (2)
3. Yeshu taaraṇahaara haai, raogaiyaom, raogaiyaom kaa waaidhaya wahaee haai
abhaiṣhaeka karanae waalaa haai, waha jaladaee aanae waalaa haai . (2)
4. Yeshu samsaara maem aayaegaa, apanaom kao waha lae jaayaegaa
kayo aapa usakae saatha jaayaemgae? saocha laijaiyae abhaye maaukaa haai . (2)

songs.title: kharaeeṣhaṭa maerao jaeewanakao maalaika haau aashaa-bharaosaa taimaee naai
lyrics: kao. (kharaeeṣhaṭa maerao jaeewanakao maalaika haau aashaa-bharaosaa taimaee naai
satautai garachhau, parashamsaa taimaeelaaee,
paraaṇa-aatamaa-sharaeera chaढ़aera) (2)
1. (hae parabhau maerao haृdayamaa waasa gara ahailae naai) (2)
garachhau saewaa taimarao jaeewana daiera
hae parabhau, ma ta jahailayoi, raitatao bhaanḍao haun ma,
hae parabhau, bharaidaeoo janyonakao jayaotailae
anajaana chhau, eka paapaee haun ma, ḍhaakaidaeoo malaaee premalae .
2. (raoowaaudainan ma hae parabhau, taimaeelaaee kahailayoi naai) (2)
ghamaṇaḍa, dauṣhaṭataakao pachhai laagaera
paapaee samsaarabaaṭa kahailayoi hainड़na ma aaphaai sakadainan,
ḍaorayooo malaaee pala-palamaa,
bana‍na sakaoon taimarao udaaharaṇa baladao daeepajhaain sadhaain .

songs.title: kharaeeṣhaṭa maerao maukataidaataa hauna‌ unaee hauna‌ maitara paapaeekao
lyrics: kao. kharaeeṣhaṭa maerao maukataidaataa hauna‌, unaee hauna‌ maitara paapaeekao
sadaa satautai haosa‌ parabhaukao aadara mahaimaa unaaikao .
1. Yeshu samsaarakao jayaotai hauna‌, Yeshu sawaragakao baaṭao hauna‌
Yeshu taaraṇahaara hauna‌, paapaeekao kaewala sahaaraa hauna‌ (2)
2. tayogae Yeshulae sawaraga-saukha, uṭhaauna paapaeeharaookaa dau:kha
daie Yeshulae karaoosamaa paraaṇa garaauna paapaeeharaookao taraaṇa (2)

songs.title: kharaeeṣhaṭa Yeshu dayolau parabhau taoo haee haai saृjanaahaara
lyrics: kao. kharaeeṣhaṭa Yeshu dayolau parabhau, taoo haee haai saृjanaahaara
hama saba gaatae haalalailaooyoha taoo haee haai taaraṇahaara .
1. janama taoo nae jagata maem laiyo, kamgaala ghara maem jaeewana baitaayo
samkaṭa kaṣhaṭa taoo nae uṭhaayo, kaiyo hamaaraa udadhaara-Yeshu payorae .
2. jaeewana naaiyayo khatarae maem jaba thaee, aandhaiyaom sae jaba ḍagamagaataee thaee
aajanyo daekara aandhaee thamaa daee, baeड़a kaiyo taoonae paara-Yeshu payorae .
3. paapa kaa raogaee maaim jaeewana bhara thaa, yatana bhaye karataa para kauchha na banaa thaa
Yeshu taeraa jaba wasatara chhaoyo thaa, chamgaa hauaa yaha baeemaara-Yeshu payorae .

songs.title: kharaeeṣhaṭa Yeshu jagata‌ chhaड़daamaa daiigae baidaa bhaye
lyrics: 1. kharaeeṣhaṭa Yeshu jagata‌ chhaड़daamaa daiigae baidaa bhaye
eka shaanataidaataa agauwaa saathaai basanalaaee .
2. saba chainataa unalae thaamadachhana‌, daoora garadachhana‌ saba ḍara .
ra sawaragakaa kauraa baoladachhana‌ jaeewana amara .
3. ra haamarao bhalaaee jatai bhao’ ra haamarao sabaai jaya
ra saocha paitaakao kauraakao hauna‌ unaaikaai .
4. hae aatamaa saba anaugarahakaa, haosa‌ daृṣhaṭai dayokao
ra haamarao ayaogaya haृdayamaa waasa tapaaeemkao .
5. haosa‌ paitaa pautarakao baढ़ai, haosa‌ panai aatamaakao
haosa‌ satautai mahaimaa taeenalaaee, jao ekaai hauna‌ .

songs.title: kharaeeṣhaṭa Yeshu maukataidaataa tapaaeemjhaain kaohaee chhaaina
lyrics: kharaeeṣhaṭa Yeshu, maukataidaataa tapaaeemjhaain kaohaee chhaaina,
tapaaeemkao tyo alaaukaika premabaarae satautai gaaunchhau ma .
maerao aashaa tapaaeem, utasaaha, sharaṇa ra shakataikao gaḍha
maerao hara shawaasa-parasawaasalae tapaaeemkao satautai gaaurahaoon .
dharataee uṭha anai satautai gaaoo, shakatai aishawaraya parabhaulaaee haosa‌
pahaaḍa jhauka anai saagara garaja, unakao naaunlaaee dhanayakao bhanaee .
tapaaeemkao aashaiṣhaita‌ kaama daekhaera khaushaee bhaye aananadalae gaaunchhau ma
paainana araoomaa Yeshukao naishachayata...

songs.title: kharaeeṣhaṭa haamarao naaumaa haundaa hauraeekao (ḍara chhaaina) (3)
lyrics: kharaeeṣhaṭa haamarao naaumaa haundaa hauraeekao (ḍara chhaaina) (3)
kharaeeṣhaṭa haamarao naaumaa haundaa hauraeekao ḍara chhaaina,
jaba haamarao naau aghai baḍhadachha, aghai baḍhadaaichhaaun (3)

songs.title: kharaeeṣhaṭa hauna‌ jaeewanakaa eka maatara asala gaoṭhaalaa
lyrics: kao. kharaeeṣhaṭa hauna‌ jaeewanakaa eka maatara asala gaoṭhaalaa
sahaayaka banachhana‌ unaee sadaa dauhkha-saukhakao baelaa
1. kalaesha, samkaṭalae ghaerachha taimaeelaaee tara kharaeeṣhaṭa taimaraainajaeeka haunachhana‌
aandhaee-taoophaana haṭaaunae parabhau taimaeeyotha yotaraa garadaaichhana‌ .
2. taradaaigaradaa bhawasaagaralaaee aandhaee aaunchha, bishwas halalaaunchha
ḍaubanalaagadaa paukaara kharaeeṣhaṭalaaee, naishachaya taimaeelaaee bachaaunchhana‌ .
3. sataawaṭa baadhaa layoee shaaitaanalae halalaaunchha khaooba jaeewana jahaajalaaee
saathamaa kharaeeṣhaṭa chhana‌, naḍaraaoo taimaee, samahaalachhana‌ unalae taimaeelaaee .
4. nairaashaa aaunchhana‌ anaeka jaeewanamaa tara haraesa nakhaaoo parabhau bhanachhana‌
waijayakao inaama jaeewanakao maukauṭa parabhaulae naishachaya dainaechhana‌ .
5. Yeshu haamaraa shakataishaalaee gaढ़ saurakaṣhaita unamaa haamaee haunachhaaun,
shaaitaanakaa hamalaa waiphala haunaechhana‌, jayawanata haamaee bananaechhaaun .

songs.title: kharaeeṣhaṭakahaan aaoo saathaee Yeshukahaan aaoo saathaee
lyrics: kao. kharaeeṣhaṭakahaan aaoo, saathaee, Yeshukahaan aaoo, saathaee
jaeewanakao jala laina, aaphanao payosa maeṭailaina (2)
1. jaeewanakao jala unaai hauna‌ yauga-yauga taृpatai dainae (2)
unalaaee yadai paiyoun bhanae taimaee
kahailayoi payosaa banadaainaaun yaugaanauyaugasamama naai .
2. jaeewanakao baaṭao unaai hauna‌ sawaraga raajayamaa paurayoidainae (2)
unalaaee yadai chaunayou bhanae paitaakahaan naishachaya
pauganae chhaai yaugaanauyauga raajaya garanalaaee .
3. jaeewanakao raoṭaee unaai hauna‌ bhaokao manalaaee taृpatai dainae (2)
unalaaee taimaeelae khaayou bhanae taimaee kahailayoi
bhaokao banadaainaau yaugaanauyaugasamamalaaee
4. euṭaa maataraai ḍhaokaa unaai hauna‌ sawaragaraajayamaa parawaesha garanalaaee (2)
yahaee baaṭao pasayou bhanae naishachaya taimaee sawaraga
pauganaechhaaun asaeema saukhakao bhaagaee haunalaaee .
5. euṭaa maatara sataya Yeshu hauna‌ saaraa jagakao udadhaara garanalaaee (2)
yadai unalaaee apanaayou bhanae ananata
daṇaḍabaaṭa umakanachhaaun, unaeesanga sadaa rahanaechhaaun .

songs.title: kharaeeṣhaṭakaai lagi sabaai kharaeeṣhaṭakaai kaama garanae shakatai maerao
lyrics: 1. kharaeeṣhaṭakaai lagi sabaai, kharaeeṣhaṭakaai kaama garanae shakatai maerao
baata, waichaara, kaamaharaoo sabaai, daina, ghaṇaṭaa sabaai maerao
kharaeeṣhaṭakaai laagai, sabaai kharaeeṣhaṭakaai kaama garanae shakatai maerao
kharaeeṣhaṭakaai laagai, sabaai kharaeeṣhaṭakaai daina, ghaṇaṭaa sabaai maerao .
2. unakao kaaraya yaee haatalae garaoona‌, paau unakao pathamaa hainḍaoona‌
aankhaalae kharaeeṣhaṭalaaee daekhaoona‌, oṭhalae unakao satautai garauna‌
kharaeeṣhaṭakaai lagi sabaai, kharaeeṣhaṭakaai paau unakao pathamaa hainḍaoona‌
kharaeeṣhaṭakaai laagai, sabaai kharaeeṣhaṭakaai oṭhalae unakao satautai garaoona‌ .
3. aankhaa jaba kharaeeṣhaṭamaa laaen kharaeeṣhaṭa ṭaangaiekao daekhaen
aatamaalae kharaeeṣhaṭa maatara daekhaen, araoo thaoka maile bhaoolaen
kharaeeṣhaṭakaai lagi sabaai kharaeeṣhaṭakaai, kharaeeṣhaṭa ṭaangaiekaa daekhaen
kharaeeṣhaṭakaai lagi sabaai kharaeeṣhaṭakaai, araoo thaoka maile bhaoolaen .

songs.title: kharaeeṣhaṭakao dayolau baataanasaara chaooraṇa ra daeena mana bhaye
lyrics: 1. kharaeeṣhaṭakao dayolau baataanasaara chaooraṇa ra daeena mana bhaye
hae parabhau, ra yasatao garachhau ma samajhanachhau tapaaeemlaaee .
2. tapaaeemkao jaeeu bhaanchaekao sawaraga-bhaojana haosa‌ maerao
ma lainachhau nayon karaarakao samajhaaunae kachaaurao .
3. gaetasamanaeekao saaharao dau:kha ra samkaṭa kalaesha haeradaai
kae taee saba kauraa bairasainachhau samajhanachhau tapaaeemlaaee .
4. jaba haerachhau kalawaraeekao karaoosa, kharaeeṣhaṭa ṭaangaie tayasamaa
eeshawarakaa thaumaa balaidaana ma raakhachhau samajhanaa .
5. an saba tapaaeemkao paeeड़akao ra prem masangakao
saasa phaeraunyajaela, an sadhaainbhara ma raakhachhau samajhanaa .
6. jaba maerao maranae baelaa chha ra maerao paraaṇa uड़aee
aaphanao raajayamaa aaundaakhaeraee samajhanauhaosa‌ malaaee .

songs.title: kharaeeṣhaṭakao phaaujamaa haunau ma khaushaee chhau (2)
lyrics: kao. kharaeeṣhaṭakao phaaujamaa haunau ma khaushaee chhau (2)
Yeshu maerao naetaa, unalaaee pachhayounchhau
kharaeeṣhaṭakao...
1. pahailaekao jaeewana tayogaera parabhaumaa chaanड़ai aaoo
aaphanao kamamara satayataalae kasaera .
2. dhaaramaikataakao chhaataeekao paataa laaera
parabhaumaa khaड़a haunachhaaun naai .
3. chhaaina dhaeraai jaiunau yahaan, aaja naai tayora haaun
premakao jautataa lagaauna tayora haaun .
4. samsaara haamarao ghara haoina, sadhaain rahandaaina
sausamaachaara dainae ra ḍhaala uṭhaaunae ho .
5. udadhaarakao daina aajaai chha, parabhaumaa aaoona
bishwasmaa aghai baढ़era raeesa-karaodha naibhaaoo .

songs.title: kharaeeṣhaṭakao maayo baokaee rahaunlaa haृdayamaa sajajaaera (2)
lyrics: kao. kharaeeṣhaṭakao maayo baokaee rahaunlaa haृdayamaa sajajaaera (2)
unakao saatha kahailaai nachhaड़ee kharaeeṣhaṭamaa baanchaaulaa (2)
1. kharaeeṣhaṭalae jaeewana chaढ़aidaie galagathaakao maaṭaomaa
kharaeeṣhaṭa Yeshu maraee daie taimarao haamarao saaṭaomaa (2)
nabhaulaaun haai karaoosakao phaedaeelaaee haृdayamaa sajajaaera (2)
2. kharaeeṣhaṭakao dauhkhalaaee samajhaera layoudaa mana maerao kalapainachha
unakao premalaaee samajhaera layoundaa aankhaamaa aansau chhalakainachha (2)
nabhaulaaun haai karaoosakao phaedaeelaaee haृdayamaa sajajaaera (2)

songs.title: kharaeeṣhaṭakao maayo baokaee rahaunlaa haृdayamaa sajajaaera (2)
lyrics: kao. kharaeeṣhaṭakao maayo baokaee rahaunlaa haृdayamaa sajajaaera (2)
unakao saatha kahailaai nachhaड़ee kharaeeṣhaṭamaa baanchaaulaa (2)
1. kharaeeṣhaṭalae jaeewana chaढ़aidaie galagathaakao maaṭaomaa
kharaeeṣhaṭa Yeshu maraee daie taimarao haamarao saaṭaomaa (2)
nabhaulaaun haai karaoosakao phaedaeelaaee haृdayamaa sajajaaera (2)
2. kharaeeṣhaṭakao dauhkhalaaee samajhaera layoudaa mana maerao kalapainachha
unakao premalaaee samajhaera layoundaa aankhaamaa aansau chhalakainachha (2)
nabhaulaaun haai karaoosakao phaedaeelaaee haृdayamaa sajajaaera (2)

songs.title: kharaeeṣhaṭakao mailana yasataai rahaosa‌ (2) yaee haamaraa haृdayaharaoo
lyrics: kao. kharaeeṣhaṭakao mailana yasataai rahaosa‌ (2)
yaee haamaraa haृdayaharaoo (wachanajhaaim pawaitara haoirahaosa‌) (2)
1. haimaalabhanadaa ajha agalao, saagarabhanadaa ajha gahairao (2)
kharaeeṣhaṭakao maayo sadhaaim sadhaaim aṭala bhaai baḍhadaai jaaosa‌ (2)
2. parabhaukao maayo paooraṇa chha yahaan hainḍanauchha euṭaai aatamaika baaṭaomaa (2)
euṭaai aatamaika baaṭaomaa sahaaraa parabhaukao paairahaosa‌ (2) .

songs.title: kharaeeṣhaṭakao wachana raakha samahaalaee (2)
lyrics: kao. kharaeeṣhaṭakao wachana raakha samahaalaee,
kharaeeṣhaṭakao wachana raakha samahaalaee
mauṭaukao mauṭaukao dhaḍakanamaa gaansaera,
kharaeeṣhaṭakao wachana raakha samahaalaee (2)
1. kharaeeṣhaṭakao wachana saunaera taimaee, uhaanmaathai bishwas gara na (2)
maukataidaataa parabhau bhanaera aaja taimaee kharaeeṣhaṭamaa ramaaoo (2)
2. katainajaela rahanachhaau taimaee, samsaarakao maoja masataeemaa (2)
pashachataaunau paralaa taimaeelaaee, kharaeeṣhaṭakao daosarao aagamanamaa (2)

songs.title: kharaeeṣhaṭamaa jaiunae sabaailaaee taimaeelae sataya paaechhaau
lyrics: kao. kharaeeṣhaṭamaa jaiunae sabaailaaee taimaeelae sataya paaechhaau
aba taimaeelae paaekao jae bhae panai na tayoga (2)
1. maृtayau bhanda ḍaralaagadao, paichhaaḍaiekao laaee bhananaichha
yadai taimaee paichhaaḍaiyou bhanae, pachhautaaunau paralaa taimaeelae
2. shaaitaanalae taimaeelaaee laobhayounae chha taimaee haosaiyora basa
Yeshu kharaeeṣhaṭakao jaeewanalaaee haera shaaitaanalae kae bhanaethayao

songs.title: kharaeeṣhaṭalaaee paujanaeharaoolae bhanathae jaeewana yao daui dainakao chaolaa
lyrics: kao. kharaeeṣhaṭalaaee paujanaeharaoolae bhanathae jaeewana yao daui dainakao chaolaa hao, saathaee
jaeewana yao bagaekao khaolaa hao, saathaee
jaeewana yao daui dainakao chaolaa ho ...
kharaeeṣhaṭalaaee paujanaeharaoolae bhanathae ...
1. (sakachhaau bhanae haera aaphaailaaee, taimaee kahaan haraairahaechhaau
saamsaaraika nashaalae taimaee aaphaailaaee gaumaairahaechhaau) (2)
(karaoosalaaee haera ta ragata bagadaaichha) (2)
(ragatalae taimaeelaaee bachaauna khaojadaaichha) (2)
2. (saukhamaa taimaraa sabaai saathaee chhana, dau:kha baujhanae kahaan kao chha ra ?
prem garachhau bhanaee ṭaopalachhana, saanchao prem kasalae garachha ra ?) (2)
(Yeshulae taimaeelaaee baolaauna khaojadaaichhana) (2)
(ananata jaeewana daiee bachaauna khaojadaaichhana) (2)

songs.title: kharaeeṣhaṭalaaee prem garanae aatamaaharaoohao unakao premalaaee
lyrics: kao. kharaeeṣhaṭalaaee prem garanae aatamaaharaoohao ! unakao premalaaee baujhaidaeoo,
kaewala khaokarao maayo haoina, haृdayalae naai garaidaeoo
kharaeeṣhaṭalaaee prem garanae ... .
1. kaewala sawaarathaee maayo haoina, sataya prem chaahainachha (2)
dhana, paraiya jana, aaphaoolaaee bhanda baesaee prem dainauchha (2)
kharaeeṣhaṭalaaee prem garanae maanachhaeharaoohao ! unakao premalaaee baujhaidaeoo,
kaewala aaḍamabara maatara haoina, saanchao prem naai garaidaeoo .
2. kaewala phaosarao jaeewana haoina, bharailao jaeewana chaahainachha (2)
kharaeeṣhaṭakao sanga-sanga jaiunalaaee jayawanata jaeewana chaahainachha (2)
kharaeeṣhaṭamaa jaiuna chaahanaeharaoohao ! unakao ichachhaalaaee baujhaidaeoo
“parabhau” kaewala omṭhalae haoina, haृdayalae naai bhanaidaeoo
3. kaewala khaokarao tayoga haoina, saidadha tayoga chaahainachha (2)
karaoosa uṭhaaee hainḍanalaaee tayoga ra balaidaana chaahainachha (2)
kharaeeṣhaṭamaa bharaosaa garanaeharaoohao ! unakao saamarathayalaaee baujhaidaeoo
kaewala asathaira bishwas haoina, daृḍha bishwas naai garaidaeoo .

songs.title: kharaeeṣhaṭalae taimaeelaaee sawatanatara garaae phaerai banadhanakao
lyrics: kao. kharaeeṣhaṭalae taimaeelaaee sawatanatara garaae,
phaerai banadhanakao jauwaamaa napara (2)
1. taimaee aaja yasa samsaaramaa chhaau tara yasa samsaarakaa haoinaau (2)
samsaarasaita ekaai chaalakao nahaooo samsaarakao jauwaamaa najaotaiau .
2. sharaeerakao maayo laalasaaharaoosangaai karaoosamaa ṭaangaidaiihaala (2)
pawaitara aatamaakao agauwaaimaa hainḍa sharaeerakao laalasaa paooraa nagara .
3. yathaochaita saewaakao raoopamaa aaphanaa-aaphanaa sharaeeralaaee (2)
pawaitara paramaeshawaralaaee manaparanae jaiundao balaidaana garaee daiihaala .

songs.title: kharaeeṣhaṭaiya jawaana jawaanaee ho yotaraa taimarao baankaee naai chha
lyrics: kao. kharaeeṣhaṭaiya jawaana jawaanaee hao, yotaraa taimarao baankaee naai chha (2)
bishwasmaa paailaa chaaladaai jaaoo, saphalataa taimarao naishachaya chha (2)
1. aaunchhana‌ katai jaeewanamaa haara, tara haara bhaitaraai chha taimarao jaeeta (2)
ḍhaaḍasa taimaee baandhadaai jaaoo, jayawanata Yeshu (saathamaa chhana‌) (2)
2. aaunchhana‌ dhaeraai udaasa khainanataa, naibhaaunalaaee taimarao aashaa (2)
aatamaamaa taimaee baḍhadaai jaaoo, anaugaraha parabhaukao (parashasata chha) (2)

songs.title: o o o sawaraga haृdayamaa chha
lyrics: o.......o.......o.......sawaraga haृdayamaa chha
o.......o.......o.......sawaraga haृdayamaa chha
Yeshukao raajaya yahaanchha – sawaraga haृdayamaa chha
uhaankao upasathaitaimaa – sawaraga haृdayamaa chha
upasathaitaimaa aananada chha – sawaraga haृdayamaa chha
pawaitara jayaotailae bharadachha – sawaraga haृdayamaa chha
haamaee uhaankao manadaira haaum – sawaraga haृdayamaa chha
kharaeeṣhaṭa naai jagakao maoola ḍhaumgaa hauna‌ – sawaraga haृdayamaa chha
unalae laina aaunae chhana‌ – sawaraga haृdayamaa chha
daulaaha aatamaalae naimatayouchhana‌ – sawaraga haृdayamaa chha .

songs.title: o maeraa raajaa (2) maeraa raajaa Yeshukao jaya) (2)
lyrics: (o maeraa raajaa) (2) maeraa raajaa Yeshukao jaya) (2)
(o maerao shaanatai) (2) maerao saanatai Yeshukao jaya) (2)
(o maerao aananada) (2) maerao aananada Yeshukao jaya) (2)

songs.title: o! aakaasha aura saooraya chanadaramaa satautai karao saaraa
lyrics: kao. o! aakaasha aura saooraya chanadaramaa satautai karao saaraa bhaoomaṇaḍala (2‌)
1. Yeshu nae taujha sae prem kaiyo, taerae laie apanaa paraaṇa daiyo
naraka sae aatamaa kao bachaa laiyo, ananata jaeewana sabakao dae daiyo . (2)
2. anaugarahakaaraee paraita Yeshu, dharamaee haokara waha daukha sahaa
haraa daiyo baairaee shaaitaana kao, maृtayau para Yeshu waijayaee hauaa . (2)
3. daootaom nae saunaayo sausamaachaara, Yeshu jaee uṭhaa haai jaraoora
jaakae bataao yaha samaachaara, baajae bajaatae gaatae jaya jayakaara ॥ (2)

songs.title: oṭhabaaṭa naisakaekaa shabadaharaoo maeraa haृdayakaa bhaawanaaharaoo (2)
lyrics: kao. oṭhabaaṭa naisakaekaa shabadaharaoo maeraa haृdayakaa bhaawanaaharaoo (2)
garahaṇayaogaya haosa‌ sadaa tapaaeemkao kaृpaa-daृṣhaṭaimaa .
1. sabaaibhanadaa utatama yao, sabaaibhanadaa sharaeṣhaṭha ho (2)
tapaaeemkao prem ra dayo, sataya chhana‌ sadaasarawadaa .
2. maeraa yaee adharamabaaṭa, dhaunauhaosa‌ malaaee (2)
nagaraosa‌ mamaa adhaikaara ra badanaamaee paapalae .

songs.title: ughaaraera paradaa maerao kaoṭhaakao jaba ma baahaira haeradachhau
lyrics: 1. (ughaaraera paradaa maerao kaoṭhaakao jaba ma baahaira haeradachhau
barasaera paanaee bharakharaai rahaekao haraiyolaee paakhaa daekhadachhau) (2)
2. (dhaunauhaosa‌ dhaunauhaosa‌ Yeshu maerao mana panai tapaaeemkao pawaitara aatamaalae) (2)
(ajhaain chaokhao banaaunauhaosa‌) (2) tapaaeemkao pawaitara wachanalae .
3. (jaiera namaoonaa banana paraekao chha jaba ma saikaaunchhau araoolaaee
baolaera maatara haundaaina rahaechha balaiyao jaga nairamaaṇa garanalaaee) (2)

songs.title: uchaaeemaa dhaeraai uchaaee gaahairaaimaa dhaeraai gaahairaai
lyrics: 1. uchaaeemaa dhaeraai uchaaee gaahairaaimaa dhaeraai gaahairaai
lamabaaeemaa dhaeraai lamabaaee chaauḍaaeemaa dhaeraai chaauḍaaee (2)
prem Yeshukao yasatao chha haृdayamaa paraiwaratana garadachha
nataa yasakao kaunaai maola chha na yasakao kaunaai saimaa chha
kao. Yeshu Yeshu maerao parabhau tapaaeemlaaee ma prem garachhau
Yeshu Yeshu sabakaa parabhau tapaaeemlaaee ma prem garachhau (2)
tapaaeemlaaee ma prem garachhau
2. ḍhaumgaenaee haृdayalaaee panai maasaukao haृdaya banaaunchha
kaṭhaora tyo manalaaee panai haiun jhaaim pagaalaee dainachha (2)
prem Yeshukao yasatao chha...
3. adharamaee paapaeelaaee panai kaṣhamaa garai jaeewana dainachha
maanawa maanawa baicha panai samabanadha nyano garaaunchha (2)
prem Yeshukao yasatao chha...

songs.title: uchalchu uccha sathaanamaa kai tapaaeem mahaapaujaahaaraee
lyrics: uchalchu uccha sathaanamaa
kai tapaaeem mahaapaujaahaaraee
uchalchu tapaaeemlaaee sababhanadaa maathai
paaundaanamaa aaunchhau aaraadhanaa garadachhau (2)

songs.title: uchalchu ma sadhaaim tapaaeemkao pawaitara naaunlaaee (3)
lyrics: (uchaalachhau ma sadhaaim tapaaeemkao pawaitara naaunlaaee) (3)
kaaraṇa tapaaeem naai maerao paramaeshawara haunauhaunachha .
(dhanayawaada chaḍaaunchhau maerao saaraa haृdayalae) (3)
kaaraṇa tapaaeemlae malaaee prem garanaubhao’ .
(parashamsaa garairahanaechhau maerao anataima saasasamama naai) (3)
kaaraṇa tapaaeemlae malaaee jaeewana dainaubhao’ .

songs.title: uchalchu Yeshukao naaun paukaarachhau Yeshukaai naaun
lyrics: uchalchu Yeshukao naaun, paukaarachhau Yeshukaai naaun
yao naaunmaa shakatai chha, yao naaunmaa jaeewana chha .
lainaosa‌ parabhau yao jaeewana, dainaosa‌ malaaee paooraṇa shakatai
bharanaosa‌ mamaa khaushaee aananada, garachhau sadhaain tapaaeemkaai bhakatai

songs.title: uchaalachhaaun uccha sathaanamaa kai tapaaeem mahaa paujaaraee
lyrics: uchaalachhaaun uccha sathaanamaa kai tapaaeem mahaa paujaaraee
uchaalachhaaun tapaaeemlaaee saba bhanda maathai
paaudaanamaa aauchhaau aaraadhanaa garana Yeshu (2)

songs.title: uccha uccha sathaanaharaumaa wairaajamaana haunae parabhau
lyrics: uccha uccha sathaanaharaumaa wairaajamaana haunae parabhau
parashamsaa mahaimaa tapaaeemlaaee sarawadaa (2)
jasakao haृdaya taoḍaiekao chha jasakao mana aanchaiekao chha
Yeshumaa aananada chha Yeshumaa shaanatai chha (2)

songs.title: uchhalatae-uchhalatae maerae aatamaa maem uchhalatae
lyrics: uchhalatae-uchhalatae maerae aatamaa maem uchhalatae
maaim naachaoon maaim gaaoon Yeshu nae maujhae bachaayo
kaoee samajhae yo na samajhae maaim kaaisae chaupa rahaoon
uchhalatae (5) daina aura raata .

songs.title: ujaaḍa yao maerao jaeewanamaa khaushaeekao wahaara Yeshumaa paaen
lyrics: ujaaḍa yao maerao jaeewanamaa khaushaeekao wahaara Yeshumaa paaen
arathahaina yao maerao jaeewanamaa jaeewanakao aratha Yeshumaa paaen
1. ekalaai hainḍadaakao gaoraeṭaoharaumaa
sahaaraa baihaina paailaaharaumaa (2)
sahaaraa baihaina maerao jaeewanamaa
jaeewanakao saathaee Yeshulaaee paaen (2)
2. aanshaoolae bhaijaekao palaharaumaa
aaphanata baairaee bhaekao kaṣhaṇamaa (2)
anadhakaara yao maerao jaeewanamaa
jaeewanakao jayaotai Yeshumaa paaen (2)

songs.title: ujayolao bhaigayao parabhau dainabharai kaama garana
lyrics: 1. ujayolao bhaigayao, parabhau, dainabharai kaama garana
alachhaee chhaड़ee ramaaee uṭhaoon, baihaanakao bhaeṭa daina (2)
2. baolaee chaalamaa chaokhao bhaye, parabhau, ghaamajasataai ujayolao
sabaai daekhachhana‌ maerao baaṭao ra waichaara saba maerao (2)
3. uchaalaidainaosa‌ mana maerao, parabhau, dainabharai kaamaaimaa
dauhkha-saukha jae-jae haolaa tapaaeemkao naawaaimaa (2)
4. gata raatakao naeendakao laagai, parabhau, dhanyawad daindachhau
tapaaeemkao daanaai bhanchu manaaimaa laindachhau (2)
5. rakaṣhaa hawasa‌ dainabharai, parabhau, tapaaeem naai daekhai
saphala hawasa‌ kaamaai jatai tapaaeemkaai lagi (2)
6. sataya-sataya eeshawara tapaaeem parabhau, kaohaee chhaaina maerao
samsaara bhanae paapalae bharayao daukhaaikao thauparao (2)
7. aaja baanchaoon paapaaikhai, parabhau, gaohaaraai paaee
maukataidaataa aaphaai tapaaeem bachaaidaeoo malaaee (2)

songs.title: uṭha anai gaaun saiyaonakaa sanataana ho
lyrics: uṭha anai gaaun saiyaonakaa sanataana ho
parabhaulae chhauṭakaaraa daie
haृdayalaaee khaolaera aananada manaau (3)
raajaa parabhau hauna

songs.title: uṭha jaaga hae kharaeeṣhaṭa premaee ho sapanaa
lyrics: kao. uṭha jaaga hae kharaeeṣhaṭa premaee ho sapanaa taoड़ee waipanaamaa taimaee
parabhau kharaeeṣhaṭakao charaṇamaa aaee maela mailaapakao aatamaa paaee
1. raitatao chha samsaara yahaan kaehaee panai chhaaina yahaan
daui dainakao paahaunaa haamaee baidaaee lainau chha yahaan
yasaailae haraekalaaee Yeshukao khaanchao chha yahaan
2. pashachataapaee haृdaya laiee unakao charaṇamaa
aaoo aaja baanchanalaaee unakao sharaṇamaa
kharaeeṣhaṭa Yeshu baadalamaa chaanड़ai naai aairahaechhana‌

songs.title: uṭha jaaga hae masaeehaee yaradanapaara jaanalaaee
lyrics: kao. uṭha, jaaga hae masaeehaee, yaradanapaara jaanalaaee (2)
tayoga, tayoga maisharakao yao saukha-wailaasa, maanalaaee (2)
1. katai panai shamkaa naraakhaee Yeshukao karaaramaa (2)
aghai baढ़ee waiwasha nabhaye (2) parabhaukao bishwasmaa .
2. samaudara garajaosa, tharakaosa‌ parawata, baaढ़ee baढ़osa‌ yao yotaraamaa (2)
pharakaee nahaeraee sadaoma nagaralaaee (2) kadama baढ़aoo saiyaona pahaaड़maa .
3. najara uṭhaaee kalawaraeemaa haeraee kharaeeṣhaṭa naishaanaalaaee (2)
haṭaaidainae baadhaa ra banadhana (2) naasha garanae anadhakaaralaaee .
4. abaraahaama, isahaaka, yokaooba, yaosaephalaaee saatha dainae, hae yohawae (2)
halalaelaooyoha, hallelujah (2), satautai mahaimaa, hallelujah .

songs.title: uṭha ra chamaka paramaeshawaralaaee mahaimaa chaḍhaaoo (2)
lyrics: uṭha ra chamaka, paramaeshawaralaaee mahaimaa chaḍhaaoo (2)
paramaeshawarakaa baalakaharaoo ho .

songs.title: uṭhaihaera aakaashaaimaa nayon taaraa udaaekao
lyrics: kao. uṭhaihaera aakaashaaimaa nayon taaraa udaaekao
saunaihaera bataasaaimaa nayon sanadaesha layoekao
aananadalae paooraṇa yao, shaanatailae paooraṇa yao
Yeshu raajaa janamaekao sausanadaesha (taimaee maeraai lagi ho ho hao) (2)
1. (anadhakaarapaooraṇa jagata‌maa jayaotai layounaubhayao uhaanlae
nairaashaalaaee jaeewana daina aashaa layounaubhayao uhaanlae) (2)
paramaeshawara awataara laiee maanawa banaee aaunaubhao’
haamarao maukataidaataa parabhau jagata‌maa aaunaubhao’ .
2. (lakaṣhayahaeena jaeewanakao lakaṣhaya banaee, kharaeeṣhaṭa jagata‌maa aaunaubhao’
paraaṇahaeena jaeewana daina ḍaunड़maa parabhau pasaranaubhao’) (2)
baaṭao, sataya ra jaeewana uhaan, maanawa banaee aaunaubhao’
taimaee-malaaee bachaaunalaaee jagata‌maa aaunaubhao’ .

songs.title: uṭhao aura gaao saiyaona kae sanataanaom
lyrics: (uṭhao aura gaao saiyaona kae sanataanaom
kayaomkai parabhau nae chhauṭakaaraa daiyo) (2)
(dailaom kao khaolao aura aananada manaao) (3)
kayaomkai raajaa parabhau haai .

songs.title: uḍaaunchhana‌ hauraeelae yao mana paataharaulaaee bataashalae jhaaim
lyrics: uḍaaunchhana‌ hauraeelae yao mana paataharaulaaee bataashalae jhaaim
samahaalaee daeu parabhau aaja hao... hao... ho samahaalaee daeu parabhau aaja
1. baehaosha jaeewanakao kahailae kahain
haara layouna khaojachha yao manalae panai (2)
mauṭaukao ḍhaukaḍhaukaee haraauna khaojachha aatamaakao daiyao naibhaauna khaojachha
samajhanachha phaeraee kharaeeṣhaṭakao yao shaanatai
aananadakao kaaraṇalae haoshamaa aaunchhau
samahaalaee daeu parabhau aaja hao... hao... ho samahaalaee daeu parabhau aaja
2. kharaeeṣhaṭakao najaramaa baanchaera yahaan waijayaeekao jaeewana jaiunau chha (2)
laḍanau chha dhaeraai laḍaaeeharau taoḍanauchha anadhakaarakao banadhanaharau
satayataalae kamamara kasaera bishwaskao ḍhaalaharau uṭhaauna
samahaalaee daeu parabhau aaja hao... hao... ho samahaalaee daeu parabhau aaja

songs.title: uड़ee jaanae baadala jhaain bagaee jaanae khaolaa jhaain
lyrics: kao. uड़ee jaanae baadala jhaain, bagaee jaanae khaolaa jhaain
wayarathaai na samajhaee daeoo taimarao maerao jaeewanalaaee (2)
1. haara maatara haoina yahaan jaeeta panai chha
aanshau maatara haoina yahaan haansao panai chha
saitataaimaa laina aaoo Yeshumaa bharapaooraṇa jaeewana layooo Yeshumaa (2)
2. aaphaoo maatara haoina yahaan dhaeraai baanchanau chha
pahaaड़ maatara haoina yahaan madhaesha panai chha
maukataikao sanadaesha phaailaaunau chha aashaakao daiyao jalaaunau chha (2)

songs.title: utasawa manaaunchhau parabhaukao lagi nayon gaeeta ma unakao
lyrics: utasawa manaaunchhau parabhaukao laagai,
nayon gaeeta ma unakao gaaunchhau (2)
satautai garachhau, nayon gaeeta ma unakao gaaunchhau (2)
hallelujah (4) halalaelaooyoha, hallelujah .

songs.title: utasawa manaaaun Yeshukao utasawa manaaaun (2)
lyrics: (utasawa manaaaun, Yeshukao utasawa manaaaun) (2)
raajaya garachhana‌ sadaasarawadaa unaee baauraee uṭhaekaa chhana‌
aaaun haamaee utasawa manaaaun, paunarautathaana haamarao parabhaukao .
eeshawarapautaralae prem garaee jaeewana daie,
satautai chaḍhaaunchhaau, kasaailae nadainae aananada daie,
bhaeṭaee laiera aaundachhaau utasawakao satautaimaa, aaaun, haamaee utasawa manaaaun,
utasawa manaaundaai gaaaun, utasawa manaaundaai gaaaun raajaalaaee,
aaaun, haamaee (utasawa manaaaun) (2) (utasawa manaaundaai gaaaun) (2) raajaalaaee .

songs.title: udaae daiwaya udadhaaraka dharataeekao anadhakaaramaa
lyrics: kao. udaae daiwaya udadhaaraka dharataeekao anadhakaaramaa
jayotairamaya kharaeeṣhaṭa udaita bhae maukataikao parakaasha laiera (2)
1. ghaora anadhakaaramaa jayaotaiwaihaina bhaye hajaaraaum ṭhaokara khaaee,
baaṭao bhaulaekaa wayokaula nairaasha nairabala yotaraeelaaee,
baaṭao daekhaaee, paau ḍaoharayoee paurayouna paramaeshawarakahaan
daiwaya udadhaaraka jayaotaimaya parakaasha udaae yasa dharataeemaa .
2. chainataa ra paeerakao bhaaralae dabaekao jagatakao saunaee chaeetakaara,
paapa, dauraganadhamaa naisasaasaiekao aatamaakao garana udadhaara,
maanawataalaaee haraaisakaekao jaeewanakao garana saudhaara
udaae taaraka, parakaashamaya taaraka, bachaauna samsaara saaraa .
3. paramaparabhaulae karauṇaalae garadaa paradaeepata kharaeeṣhaṭa paṭhaae,
samsaaralae anadhaa paaraekao aankhaa khaolanalaaee kharaeeṣhaṭa aae,
anadhakaarabaaṭa jayaotaitaira naai pharakaauna kharaeeṣhaṭa udaae
shaaitaanakao banadhanabaaṭa umakaauna parataapamaya kharaeeṣhaṭa janamae .
4. mahaana‌ parabhaukao karauṇaa paaunae yaogaya ma thaiinan
ma paapakao raogaee naraka jaanaalae haunathayao sawaraga shaoonaya ?
kaina parabhaulae malaaee khaooba khaojae ? kaina mahaimaa daina ?
awaaka‌ ma haunachhau anaugaraha daekhaee, najhaukaee ma sakatainan .

songs.title: udaayao eka chamakailao taaraa anadhaeraee raatamaa (2)
lyrics: udaayao eka chamakailao taaraa anadhaeraee raatamaa (2)
jayaotaiṣhaeeharau haiḍana laagae taaraakao agauwaaeemaa
kao. nawajaata parabhaukao darashana paae gaaeekao ḍauḍaaimaa
paapaee jagatalaaee maukatai daina janamaie samsaaramaa
1. sauna‌ ra dhaupa maurarakao
bhaeṭaee chaḍhaae parabhaumaa (2)
kaृtajanya banadaai haraṣhaashau jhaaradaai (2)
darashana garae unaailaaee
kao. maukataidaataa haamarao parabhau Yeshulaaee bhaeṭaae
saaraa samsaaramaa yao khabara khabaailaaee saunaae
2. nairaasha ra hataasamaa
chhaau kai taimaee ahailae (2)
saunaee raakha khaushaeekao khabara (2)
jaeewana dainachhana‌ Yeshulae
kao. anaugarahakao jharaee baraṣhaae kaṣhamaadaana dainalaaee
chaahaanachhana‌ Yeshu angalo haalana sadhaai taimaeelaaee

songs.title: udaayao taaraa aaja naeela gaganakao maajha
lyrics: kao. udaayao taaraa aaja, naeela gaganakao maajha
yao anadhaeraee raatalaaee, ujayolao banaaidaiyao
1. gaaeekao gaoṭhamaa pasaraekao parabhau paapaee jana sabakao udadhaara garana
janamae aaja, janamae parabhau jagamaa uhaan ekalao ḍaunड़aimaa (2)
2. aananada manaaaun yao shaubha-raatamaa, sausanadaesha saunaaaun saaraa jagata‌maa,
janamae aaja janamae parabhau jagamaa, jayaotaikaa haamaraa raajaa (2)

songs.title: udaekakao tyo taaraa chamakaiyao aakaashamaa
lyrics: 1. udaekakao tyo taaraa chamakaiyao aakaashamaa
janamanaubhao’ parabhau aaja gaaeekao gaoṭhamaa, haamaraa jaeewanamaa .
kao. haosa‌-haosa‌ parabhaulaaee mahaimaa haamarao jaeewanamaa
haosa‌-haosa‌ parabhaulaaee mahaimaa ananata kaalasamama
2. udaekakao tyo balaidaana parabhaulae jao dainaubhao’
sharaapaita karaoosamaa maranaubhao’ parabhau dainau eka waradaana
haamaeelaaee maukataidaana .
3. udaekakao tyo aashaa paaunchhaau jao parabhaumaa
aaunaechhana‌ baadalamaa taurahaeekao saathamaa
laina haamaeelaaee unakaai raajayamaa .

songs.title: udaekakao prem chha Yeshukao udaekakao prem chha Yeshukao
lyrics: udaekakao prem chha Yeshukao, udaekakao prem chha Yeshukao
udaekakao prem chha Yeshukao, atai udaekakao prem .
agalao chha, ma paugana sakatainan, gahairao chha ma ḍaubana sakatainan,
chaauḍaa chha, ma naapana sakatainan, atai udaekakao prem .

songs.title: udaekakao prem chha Yeshukao udaekakao prem chha Yeshukao
lyrics: udaekakao prem chha Yeshukao, udaekakao prem chha Yeshukao
udaekakao prem chha Yeshukao, atai udaekakao prem
agalao chha paugana sakadainan, gahairao, chha, ḍaubana sakadainan
chaauड़a chha naapana sakadainan, atai udaekakao prem .

songs.title: udaekakao premailao kharaeeṣhaṭa Yeshu raajaakao
lyrics: kao. udaekakao premailao kharaeeṣhaṭa Yeshu raajaakao
dhanyawad mahaimaa satautai haosa‌ sarawadaa
1. paitaalae pautaralaaee samsaaramaa dainaubhao’
yao katai udaekakao prem eeshawara paitaakao,
Yeshu kharaeeṣhaṭa premailao premalae sawaraga chhaड़naubhao’
gaetasamanaee panai premalae jaanaubhao’ .
2. premalae karausakao maृtayau bhaoganaulaaee jaanaubhao’
maृtayaubaaṭa taesarao daina baauraee uṭhanaubhayao
Yeshu kharaeeṣhaṭa jaeewaita chhana‌, ma unamaa jaiundachhau
tana-manalae unaaikao gaaunaechhau gaeeta jayakao .
3. udaekakao premailao kharaeeṣhaṭa Yeshu raajaakao
dhanyawad mahaimaa, satautai haosa‌ sarawadaa
jaanaubhao’ sawaragalaokamaa phairanaechhana‌ baadalamaa
laiera haamaeelaaee paurayounchhana‌ tayasa ṭhaaunmaa .

songs.title: udadhaarakao daina chha aaja naai maitara samayalaaee naparakha
lyrics: kao. udadhaarakao daina chha aaja naai maitara samayalaaee naparakha
anaishachaita chaolaakao bharaosaa kae chha ahailae naai ḍhalana sakachha
1. daekhaee ḍaralaagadao dashaa paapaeekao kharaeeṣhaṭa aghai saranaubhao’ (2)
sahaee chaoṭa tyo sharaapaita karaoosakao, maukatai dawaara khaolanaubhao’ (2)
2. dainachhana‌ parabhau kharaeeṣhaṭa maukatai ra shaanatai pachhataaunae paapaeelaaee (2)
saitataaikao maukatai lainakaa naimatai aaoo aaja Yeshukahaan (2)

songs.title: unakao jhaṇaḍaa maerao lagi prem (2)
lyrics: unakao jhaṇaḍaa maerao lagi prem (2)
unalae malaaee bhaojakao gharamaa laiee aae,
unakao jhaṇaḍaa maerao lagi prema, unakao prem (2)

songs.title: unalae chaahae ma tatapara chhau
lyrics: 1. unalae chaahae ma tatapara chhau
unalae chaahae ma haajaira chhau
unalae chaahae ma khaushaee chhau
kaama ganaechhau, ma Yeshukao jaraoora .
kao. kaama garanaechhau, ma unakao daasa haunaechhau
ma unakaai saatha hainड़naechhau ma kharaeeṣhaṭakaai haun jaraoora (2)
2. shahara, pahaaड़ haosa‌ yo madhaesha haosa‌
shahara, pahaaड़ haosa‌ yo jamghaara haosa‌
shahara, pahaaड़ haosa‌ yo taraaee haosa‌
kaama garanaechhau ma Yeshukao jaraura .

songs.title: unalae maerao hat chhaड़nae chhaainana‌ (2)
lyrics: unalae maerao hat chhaड़nae chhaainana‌ (2)
hauraee aae panai, bataasa aae panai unalae maerao hat chhaड़nae chhaainana‌ .

songs.title: unai wainaa baanchana sakadaina, Yeshu wainaa baanchana sakadaina
lyrics: kao. unai wainaa baanchana sakadaina, Yeshu wainaa baanchana sakadaina
jaeenadagaeekao paanaamaa sajaauchhau Yeshulaaee (2)
unai wainaa baachana sakadaina, Yeshu wainaa baachana sakadaina
1. maerao jaeewana aatamaa paraaṇaalae unaeeharaulaaee naai khaanachha
mauṭaukao dhaḍakanaharaumaa unaee sadhaainaai sakainachhana‌
sadaa sarawadaa unakao mahaimaa, parashamsaa, aaradhanaa unakao naaunkao
2. unalae daiekao yao prema, ajamabaraee samama rahanachha
paapaee daunaiyonlaaee bachaauna unalae daiekao tyo balaidaana
sadaa sarawadaa unakao masahamaa, parashamsaa, aaradhanaa unakao naaunkao

songs.title: unaee naai hauna‌ parabhau maृtayaubaaṭa baauranae unaee parabhau
lyrics: unaee naai hauna‌ parabhau maृtayaubaaṭa baauranae, unaee parabhau
haraeka ghaunḍaa ṭaekanaechha, hara jaibaraolae bhananaechha Yeshu kharaeeṣhaṭa naai hauna‌ parabhau .
taimaee naai haa parabhau maृtayaubaaṭa baauranae, taimaee parabhau
maeraa ghaunḍaa ṭaekanaechhana‌ ra jaibaraolae bhananaechha Yeshu kharaeeṣhaṭa naai hauna‌ parabhau .

songs.title: unaee raajaaharaookaa raajaa unaee parabhauharaookaa parabhau
lyrics: unaee raajaaharaukaa raajaa
unaee parabhauharaukaa parabhau
unalae rajaya garachhana‌ haamaee sadaa
unalae chaṭaṭaana phaoranae chhana‌
maukatai daina haamaeelaaee sadaa
halalaelaooyoha... hallelujah raaja garachha

songs.title: unaee haamarao saृjanahaara unaee haamarao taraṇahaara
lyrics: kao. unaee haamarao saृjanahaara, unaee haamarao taaraṇahaara
unaee haamarao paalanahaara, saunachhana‌ unalae haamarao paukaara .
1. yahaowaakao lagi jaya jaya garaaum aananadaita unaaikao saewaa garaaum .
gaaundaai unakao saamau aaaum yahaowae eeshawaralaaee jaanaaum .
2. unakao kharakakaa haamaee bhaeड़a haaum dhanyawad garadaai ḍhaokaabhaitara pasaaum
satautai garadaai aanganamaama basaaum dhanaya bhanaaum unakao naamalaaee .
3. yahaowae mahaana parabhau bhalao chhana‌ unakaa karaooṇaa sadaa rahanachha
unakao sachachaaee pausataa-pausataamaa amara yao rahanaechha .

songs.title: unaee haunachhana‌ sadaa thaumaa saimhaasanamaa
lyrics: unaee haunachhana‌ sadaa thaumaa saimhaasanamaa
khaushaeesaatha ghaunḍaa ṭaekaee garachhau aaraadhanaa .

songs.title: upakaarakao bhaeṭaee kharaeeṣhaṭakaa naimatai (2) haraṣhaita
lyrics: kao. upakaarakao bhaeṭaee kharaeeṣhaṭakaa naimatai (2)
haraṣhaita taulayounae sauganadha anai, garahaṇayaogaya balaidaana ho .
1. sauna chaandaee sahaita saृṣhaṭai garae paृthawaeelaaee mahaimaita parabhaulae (2)
parabhau bhanachhana‌ - “sauna chaandaee hauna‌ maeraa chaahananan kaehaee sahaaraa” (2)
yasakaaraṇa parabhaulaaee kaehaee thaoka daina bhaara ra kara haoina ho saaubhaagaya . (2)
2. parabhaukaa jana daaoodalae bhanachhana‌ - “haamaeeharaoosanga kae chha ra ? (2)
jatai samapatatai baṭaulaekaa chhaaum sabaai yaee taimaraai hauna‌ (2)
taimaraai haatadawaaraa naai paaekaa haaum, taimaeelaaee naai chaḍhaaunchhaau .” (2)
3. haraṣhasahaita dainae bishwaseelaaee parabhaulae prem garadachhana‌ sadhaaim (2)
yasakaaraṇa chaitata nadaukhaaikana haraṣhasahaita daioon unalaaee (2)
jasalae thaoraai chharachha, thaoraai baṭaulachha dhaeraai chharaaum khaoobaai baṭaulaaum . (2)
4. kae maanaisalae sataya paramaeshawaralaaee chhalana yo lauṭana sakadachha ra ? (2)
tara panai parabhaukao bhaaga nadaiee naitaya lauṭadamchhaaum unalaaee (2)
yasakaaraṇa parabhaulaaee aadara garaera unakao bhaaga layooon unakao bhawanamaa . (2)
5. sataya parabhaukao parataijanyo yao chha, “samapaooraṇa dashaamsha bhaṇaḍaaramaa layooo (2)
tayasapachhai malaaee jaanchaee haera aashaiṣha dainachhau yo dainanan ? (2)
sawaragakaa jhayolaharaoo khaolaera haoobaai aashaiṣha waraṣhaaunchhau yo waraṣhaaunanan ? (2)
6. daiera panai aashaiṣha‌ napaaoon tara panai ma dainachhau naai (2)
ghaṭaee panai maerao paooraṇa nahaosa‌ dainau maile parachha naai (2)
kainakai ma chhau ऋṇaee maeraa parabhaukao nachhauṭanae garai naitaya chhau ऋṇaee . (2)
7. saba thaoka daiyou parabhau maeraa naimatai sakatainan waraṇana garana yasakao (2)
haृdaya parashamsaalae bharainachha, daina chaahanachhau kaehaee thaoka (2)
premaee kharaeeṣhaṭa parabhaulaaee ma dainaechhau haraṣhasahaita ma dainaechhau . (2)

songs.title: upasathaita kharaeeṣhaṭakao chhaayomaa baanchairahaekao chhau yahaan
lyrics: kao. upasathaita kharaeeṣhaṭakao chhaayomaa baanchairahaekao chhau yahaan
unaaikao adabhaoota maayomaa haansairahaekao chhau yahaan
unaaikao kaomala kaृpaamaa gaairahaekao chhau yahaan
1. jaeewanamaa eka daina raata parachha yahaan, masata naidaaunchhau
kalawaraeepaarai saunadara baihaana maanaisa bayaunjhanachha
manaohara bhaagamaa sawaragaeeya raajamaa jayawanatakao gaeeta gaaunchhau
Yeshukao mauhaara aaphanaai aghai daekhaera ramaaunchhau .
2. haeeraalae jaड़ee tayora garaee raakhaekao shaharamaa
maṇai jaड़ekaa shaharakaa ḍhaokaa baaṭaa chhana‌ saunaaulaa
hainड़naechhau sadaa Yeshukao saathamaa sanatagaṇa laharamaa
haata-haatamaa Yeshukao saatha basanaechhau sarawadaa .
3. samsaarakao dauhkha kaehaee panai haoina, sawaragakao saukhamaa
sataawaṭa panai kaehaee panai haoina, sawaragakao mahaimaamaa
samamaana ra maukauṭa mailanaechhana‌ malaaee tyo paooraṇa mailanamaa
baihaanakaa taaraa, kharaeeṣhaṭa maeraa payoraa, paoojanaechhau sarawadaa .

songs.title: upahaara sawaraoopa maerao jaeewanamaa chaढ़aunchhau parabhaulaaee
lyrics: kao. upahaara sawaraoopa maerao jaeewanamaa chaढ़aunchhau parabhaulaaee
paraaṇa aatamaa sharaeera saatha arapanachhau yao jaeewana (2)
1. baalakapanadaekhaikao saaraa paapa aparaadha
dhaoidainauhaosa‌ parabhau pashachaataapa garadachhau (2)
2. jaeewanakao gaoraeṭaomaa hainḍana saikaaunauhaosa‌
shaaitaanakao baadhaadaekhai bachaaunauhaosa‌ malaaee (2)

songs.title: unbhaai taa haeraoon sawaragalaoka chha (2) undhaai taa naralaoka haera
lyrics: 1. unbhaai taa haeraoon sawaragalaoka chha (2),
undhaai taa naralaoka, haera paraiya bhaai (2)
2. taimaeelae bhanachhaau sawaraga tarachhau (2),
tarachhaaum pao kasaraee, haera paraiya bhaai (2)
3. sawaraga taranau khaelaṭhaṭaṭaa chhaaina (2),
dhaaunauchha kharaeeṣhaṭakahaan, haera paraiya bhaai (2)
4. sawaraga baaṭao euṭaa chha khaalai (2),
unaee hauna‌ parabhau kharaeeṣhaṭa, haera paraiya bhaai (2)
5. kharaeeṣhaṭalaaee bhajaee taranau chha paarai (2),
mana garaee eka chaitata, haera paraiya bhaai (2)
6. paitaalae dainachhana‌ sawaragalaokamaa (2),
basanau taa naitayanaita, haera paraiya bhaai (2)

songs.title: usakae phaaṭakaom maem parawaesha karaoongaa dhanyawad kae saatha
lyrics: usakae phaaṭakaom maem parawaesha karaoongaa dhanyawad kae saatha
usakae aanganaom maem satautai karaoongaa
maaim kahaoongaa yae daina yahaowaa nae banaayo
maaim khausha haoon kai aananadaita kaiyo
aananadaita kaiyo maujhae aananadaita kaiyo
maaim khausha haun kai aananadaita kaiyo (2)

songs.title: usanae daakharasa aura taela uṇaḍaelaa maeraee aatamaakao chamgaa kaiyo
lyrics: usanae daakharasa aura taela uṇaḍaelaa, maeraee aatamaakao chamgaa kaiyo
yaraeehao kae kainaarae adhamaooaa paड़a
usanae daakharasa aura taela uṇaḍaelaa
Yeshu, Yeshu, Yeshu maaimnae usae paa laiyo (3)
maaimnae Yeshu kao paa laiyo... ॥

songs.title: uhaan yaogaya atai yaogaya maerao daina-wa-dainakao
lyrics: uhaan yaogaya atai yaogaya
maerao daina-wa-dainakao waasataa garanalaaee
uhaan yaogaya atai yaogaya
maerao sathaitai samahaalanalaaee aaja (chabhauta)
uhaan yaogaya atai yaogaya
maile chaahaekao bhanda dhaeraai garanalaaee
uhaan yaogaya atai yaogaya
uhaanlae chaahaekao jasatao hauna malaaee -2

songs.title: uhaankao pawaitara ḍaanड़amaa haamaraa paramaeshawarakao shaharamaa
lyrics: uhaankao pawaitara ḍaanड़amaa, haamaraa paramaeshawarakao shaharamaa
paramaparabhaumaa mahaana‌ ra uccha satautaikao yaogaya haunauhaunachha (2)

songs.title: uhaankao maaragamaa haamaee hainḍanaechhaaum uhaankao jayaotaimaa haamaee
lyrics: uhaankao maaragamaa haamaee hainḍanaechhaaum uhaankao jayaotaimaa haamaee rahanachhaau
uhaankao wachanalaaee paalana garachhaau .......
parabhau haamaeesanga dhaeraai najaika parabhau haamaeesanga imaanauyala (2)
uhaankao jaeewanamaa haamaee jaiunae chhaau uhaankao satayataamaa haamaee rahanachhaau
uhaankao dharamaikataamaa haamaee hainḍanae chhaau parabhau haamaeesanga....... .

songs.title: uhaankao raajayamaa sabaailaaee naimatao chha
lyrics: kao. uhaankao raajayamaa sabaailaaee naimatao chha
garaeeba dhanaee sabaailaaee paapaee dhanaee sabaailaaee (2)
hae..hae..hae..hao (3) la... (3) hae (3)
1. unaee aae samsaaramaa maeraai naimatai unaee aae samsaaramaa taimarao naimatai (2)
baujhai daeoo haai aaja parabhaulaaee sagajhaee daeoo haai aaja parabhaulaaee (2)
2. Yeshu aae samsaaramaa jaeewana daina Yeshuaae samsaaramaa shaanatai daina (2)
baujhaidaeoo haai aaja parabhaulaaee samajhaidaeu haai aaja parabhaulaaee (2)

songs.title: uhaanlaaee mahaimaa maṇaḍalaeemaa ahailae ra sadhaain (2)
lyrics: (uhaanlaaee mahaimaa maṇaḍalaeemaa ahailae ra sadhaain) (2) (uhaanlaaee) (4)
uhaanlaaee mahaimaa maṇaḍalaeemaa ahailae ra sadhaain .

songs.title: uhaanlae malaaee satayanaashakao khaaḍala ra
lyrics: uhaanlae malaaee satayanaashakao khaaḍala ra
daladalae hailaobaaṭa taanaera naikaalanaubhayao,
uhaanlae maeraa khauṭaṭaaharaoolaaee chaṭaṭaanamaathai basaalanaubhayao
uhaanlae euṭaa nayon gaeeta maerao maukhamaa haalaidainaubhao’
haamarao paramaeshawarakao satautai (4)

songs.title: uhaanlae malaaee satayonaashakao khaaḍalabaaṭa
lyrics: uhaanlae malaaee satayonaashakao khaaḍalabaaṭa
ra daladalae hailaobaaṭa taanaera naikaalalau bhayao
uhaanlae maeraa khauṭa‌ṭaaharaoolaaee chaṭa‌ṭaanamaathai basaalalau bhayao,
uhaanlae euṭaa nayon gaeeta maerao maukhamaa haalaeedainau bhao’ .
haamarao paramaeshawarakao satautai (4)
